ree friends devise a convoluted and seemingly foolproof plan to rid themselves of their respective employers... permanently. There\'s only one problem: even the best laid plans are only as foolproof as the brains behind them. -- (C) Warner Bros','It\'s nasty, uneven, and far from original, but thanks to a smartly assembled cast that makes the most of a solid premise, Horrible Bosses works.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/36/11163673_mob.jpg'),(185,'Bridget Jones\'s Diary',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bridget_jones_diary/','13426','0243155',1,NULL,'Though there was controversy over the choice of casting, Zellweger\'s Bridget Jones is a sympathetic, likable, funny character, giving this romantic comedy a lot of charm.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/26/97/269701_mob.jpg'),(186,'Becoming Jane',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/becoming_jane/','460343705','0416508',1,NULL,'Although Becoming Jane is a well-crafted period piece, it lacks fresh insight into the life and works of Jane Austen. The film focuses too much on wardrobe and not enough on Austen\'s achievements.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/89/45/22/8945229_mob.jpg'),(187,'Bad Boys II',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bad_boys_ii/','13355','0172156',1,NULL,'Two and a half hours of explosions and witless banter.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/14/67/11146748_mob.jpg'),(188,'Phone Booth',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/phone_booth/','13499','0183649',1,NULL,'Quick pacing and Farrell\'s performance help make Phone Booth a tense nail-biter.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/47/11164711_mob.jpg'),(189,'The Lost Boys',1987,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lost_boys/','13088','0093437',1,NULL,'Flawed but eminently watchable, Joel Schumacher\'s teen vampire thriller blends horror, humor, and plenty of visual style with standout performances from a cast full of young 1980s stars.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/80/11168030_mob.jpg'),(190,'Over Her Dead Body',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1190660-over_my_dead_body/','770678536','0785007',1,NULL,'With few laughs and little romantic chemistry, Over Her Dead Body lacks the ingredients of a successful romantic comedy.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/79/10887935_mob.jpg'),(191,'Kiss Kiss, Bang Bang',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kiss_kiss_bang_bang/','8846','0373469',1,NULL,'Tongue-in-cheek satire blends well with entertaining action and spot-on performances in this dark, eclectic neo-noir homage.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/59/10885939_mob.jpg'),(192,'Blue Crush',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/blue_crush/','11611',NULL,1,NULL,'The surfing sequences are exhilarating, but the plot is pretty forgettable and trite.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/94/12/10941247_mob.jpg'),(193,'Hannah Montana/Miley Cyrus: Best of Both Worlds Concert Tour',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hannah-montanamiley-cyrus-best-of-both-worlds-concert-tour/','770677196','1127884',1,NULL,'This high-energy concert film should please Cyrus\' rabid pre-teen fan base -- and may come as a pleasant surprise for parents.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/11/97/11119717_mob.jpg'),(194,'Bangkok Dangerous',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bangkok_dangerous/','770681773','0814022',1,NULL,'With murky cinematography, a meandering pace, a dull storyline, and rather wooden performances, The Pang Brothers\' Hollywood remake of Bangkok Dangerous is unsuccessful.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/84/27/10842740_mob.jpg'),(195,'The Adjustment Bureau',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/adjustment_bureau/','770810295','1385826',1,'On the brink of winning a seat in the U.S. Senate, ambitious politician David Norris (Damon) meets beautiful contemporary ballet dancer Elise Sellas (Emily Blunt)--a woman like none he\'s ever known. But just as he realizes he\'s falling for her, mysterious men conspire to keep the two apart. David learns he is 