.com/movie/10/92/18/10921856_mob.jpg'),(212,'The Secret Life of Bees',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/secret_life_of_bees/','770680796','0416212',1,NULL,'The Secret Life of Bees has moments of charm, but is largely too maudlin and sticky-sweet.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/74/11157482_mob.jpg'),(213,'Bram Stoker\'s Dracula',1992,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bram_stokers_dracula/','16616','0103874',1,NULL,'Overblown in the best sense of the word, Francis Ford Coppola\'s vision of Bram Stoker\'s Dracula rescues the character from decades of campy interpretations -- and features some terrific performances to boot.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/59/64/98/5964985_mob.jpg'),(214,'Beverly Hills Chihuahua',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10008587-beverly_hills_chihuahua/','770767902','1014775',1,NULL,'Despite hitting some sweet notes, Beverly Hills Chihuahua is little more than disposable family entertainment.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/47/11154716_mob.jpg'),(215,'A Bug\'s Life',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bugs_life/','9749','0120623',1,NULL,'Blending top notch animation with rousing adventure, witty dialogue, and memorable characters, A Bug\'s Life is another Pixar winner.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/93/89/10938947_mob.jpg'),(216,'Vicky Cristina Barcelona',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/vicky_cristina_barcelona/','770680718','0497465',1,NULL,'A beguiling tragicomedy, Vicky Cristina Barcelona charms with beautiful views of the Spanish city and a marvelously well-matched cast.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/13/43/11134349_mob.jpg'),(217,'Life Is Beautiful (La Vita e bella)',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1084398-life_is_beautiful/','10097','0118799',1,NULL,'Benigni\'s earnest charm, when not overstepping its bounds into the unnecessarily treacly, offers the possibility of hope in the face of unflinching horror.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/53/81/55/5381553_mob.jpg'),(218,