strike_back/','13081','0261392',1,NULL,'Fans can expect a good laugh as the cast from Smith\'s previous films reunite for Jay and Silent Bob\'s last bow. The loose plotting and crude language may be too much for others though.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/93/56/10935619_mob.jpg'),(222,'Legally Blonde 2 - Red, White & Blonde',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/legally_blonde_2_red_white_and_blonde/','10776','0333780',1,NULL,'This blonde joke is less funny the second time around.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/13/81/11138190_mob.jpg'),(223,'Blade II',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/blade_ii/','13362','0187738',1,NULL,'Blade 2 takes what works in the original and gives us more. Unfortunately, plot and character development appear to have been left on the cutting room floor.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/79/11167916_mob.jpg'),(224,'Barnyard',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/barnyard/','190816315','0414853',1,NULL,'Unimaginative and unfunny, this tale of barnyard mischief borders on \'udder\' creepiness and adds little to this summer\'s repertoire of animated films.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/18/57/06/1857066_mob.jpg'),(225,'The Black Dahlia',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/black_dahlia/','287865097','0387877',1,NULL,'Though this ambitious noir crime-drama captures the atmosphere of its era, it suffers from subpar performances, a convoluted story, and the inevitable comparisons to other, more successful films of its genre.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/14/62/11146256_mob.jpg'),(226,'Men in Black II',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/men_in_black_ii/','10789','0120912',1,NULL,'Lacking the freshness of the first movie, MIB 2 recycles elements from its predecessor with mixed results.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/45/11164554_mob.jpg'),(227,'Run Fatboy Run',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10008621-run_fat_boy_run/','770670572','0425413',1,NULL,'Run, Fat Boy, Run features sporadic 