Cameron Diaz). She\'s foul-mouthed, ruthless, and inappropriate. She drinks, she gets high, and she can\'t wait to marry her meal ticket and get out of her bogus day job. When she\'s dumped by her fiance, she sets her plan in motion to win over a rich, handsome substitute (Justin Timberlake) - competing for his affections with an overly energetic colleague, Amy (Lucy Punch). When Elizabeth also finds herself fighting off the advances of a sarcastic, irreverent gym teacher (Jason Segel), the consequences of her wild and outrageous schemes give her students, her coworkers, and even herself an education like no other. -- (C) Sony Pictures','In spite of a promising concept and a charmingly brazen performance from Cameron Diaz, Bad Teacher is never as funny as it should be.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/61/11156194_mob.jpg'),(235,'Behind Enemy Lines',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1111645-behind_enemy_lines/','10599','0159273',1,NULL,'The plot for Behind Enemy Lines is more jingoistic than credible, and the overload of flashy visual tricks makes the action sequences resemble a video game.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/47/11164718_mob.jpg'),(236,'Batman Forever',1995,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/batman_forever/','11174','0112462',1,NULL,'Loud, excessively busy, and often boring, Batman Forever nonetheless has the charisma of Jim Carrey and Tommy Lee Jones to offer mild relief.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/45/11164555_mob.jpg'),(237,'Charlie Bartlett',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/charlie_bartlett/','651566900','0423977',1,NULL,'With engaging performances marked by an inconsistent tone, Charlie Bartlett is a mixed bag of clever teen angst comedy and muddled storytelling.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/87/30/68/8730680_mob.jpg'),(238,'Bandslam',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bandslam/','770686249','0976222',1,NULL,'Bandslam is an intelligent teen film that avoids teen film cliches, in an entertaining package of music and coming-of-age drama.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/89/25/10892572_mob.jpg'),(239,'Bringing Down The House',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bringing_down_the_house/','11496','0305669',1,NULL,'Though the cast shines, they can\'t save this comedy, which is overly contrived and filled with outdated and offensive racial jokes.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/26/09/260995_mob.jpg'),(240,'Bloodrayne',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bloodrayne/','2864411','0383222',1,NULL,'BloodRayne is an absurd sword-and-sorcery vid-game adaptation from schlock-maestro Uwe Boll, featuring a distinguished (and slumming) cast.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/52/91/529104_mob.jpg'),(241,'Bridesmaids',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bridesmaids_2011/','771039065','1478338',1,'This spring, Universal Pictures and producer Judd Apatow (Knocked Up, The 40-Year-Old Virgin) invite you to experience Bridesmaids. Kristen Wiig leads the cast as Annie, a maid of honor whose life unravels as she leads her best friend, Lillian (Maya Rudolph), and a group of colorful bridesmaids (Rose Byrne, Melissa McCarthy, Wendi McLendon-Covey and Ellie Kemper) on a wild ride down the road to matrimony. Annie\'s life is a mess. But when she finds out her lifetime best friend is engaged, she simply must serve as Lillian\'s maid of honor. Though lovelorn and broke, Annie bluffs her way through the expensive and bizarre rituals. With one chance to get it perfect, she\'ll show Lillian and her bridesmaids just how far you\'ll go for someone you love. -- (C) Universal','A marriage of genuine characters, gross out gags, and pathos, Bridesmaids is a female-driven comedy that refuses to be boxed in as Kristen Wiig emerges as a real star.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/55/11155567_mob.jpg'),(242,'Puss in Boots',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1209933-puss_in_boots/','770810237','0448694',1,'Long before he even met Shrek, the notorious fighter, lover and outlaw Puss in Boots becomes a hero when he sets off on an adventure with the tough and street smart Kitty Softpaws and the mastermind Humpty Dumpty to save his town. This is the true story of The Cat, The Myth, The Legend... The Boots. -- (C) Dreamworks/Paramount','It isn\'t deep or groundbreaking, but what it lacks in profundity, Puss in Boots more than makes up for with an abundance of wit, visual sparkle, and effervescent charm.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/91/11169149_mob.jpg'),(243,'16 Blocks',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/16_blocks/','49248945','0450232',1,NULL,'Despite strong performances from Bruce Willis and Mos Def, 16 Blocks is a shopworn entry in the buddy-action genre.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/31/28/312808_mob.jpg'),(244,'Pitch Black',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pitch_black/','17596','0134847',1,NULL,'Despite an interesting premise (and a starmaking turn from Vin Diesel), Pitch Black is too derivative and formulaic to recommend to sci-fi or action fans.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/28/86/288600_mob.jpg'),(245,'The Possession',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_possession/','771219076','0431021',1,'Based on a true story, The Possession is the terrifying account of how one family must unite in order to survive the wrath of an unspeakable evil. Clyde (Jeffrey Dean Morgan) and Stephanie Brenek (Kyra Sedgwick) see little cause for alarm when their youngest daughter Em becomes oddly obsessed with an antique wooden box she purchased at a yard sale. But as Em\'s behavior becomes increasingly erratic, the couple fears the presence of a malevolent force in their midst, only to discover that the box was built to contain a dibbuk, a dislocated spirit that inhabits and ultimately devours its human host. -- (C) Lionsgate','It may be based on a true story, but that doesn\'t excuse the way The Possession repeatedly falls back on hoary ghost movie cliches -- or the uninentional laughs it provides.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/86/11168615_mob.jpg'),(246,'Bambi',1942,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bambi/','9375','0034492',1,NULL,'Elegantly animated and deeply touching, Bambi is an enduring, endearing, and moving Disney classic.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/06/250691_mob.jpg'),(247,'Jackie Brown',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jackie_brown/','13004','0119396',1,NULL,'Tarantino\'s third film, fashioned as a comeback vehicle for star Pam Grier, offers typical wit and charm -- and is typically overstuffed.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/93/45/10934571_mob.jpg'),(248,'Boogie Nights',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/boogie_nights/','14134','0118749',1,NULL,'Grounded in strong characters, bold themes, and subtle storytelling, Boogie Nights is a groundbreaking film both for director P.T. Anderson and star Mark Wahlberg.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/93/70/10937063_mob.jpg'),(249,'Battle: Los Angeles',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/battle-los-angeles/','770815449','1217613',1,'For years, there have been documented cases of UFO sightings around the world - Buenos Aires, Seoul, France, Germany, China. But in 2011, what were once just sightings will become a terrifying reality when Earth is attacked by unknown forces. As people everywhere watch the world\'s great cities fall, Los Angeles becomes the last stand for mankind in a battle no one expected. It\'s up to a Marine staff sergeant (Aaron Eckhart) and his new platoon to draw a line in the sand as they take on an enemy unlike any they\'ve ever encountered before. -- (C) Sony','Overlong and overly burdened with war movie cliches, Battle: Los Angeles will entertain only the most ardent action junkies.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/53/11155301_mob.jpg'),(250,'Sleeping Beauty',1959,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1019187-sleeping_beauty/','21442','0053285',1,NULL,'This Disney dreamscape contains moments of grandeur, with its lush colors, magical air, one of the most menacing villains in the Disney canon.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/56/11155613_mob.jpg'),(251,'The Blair Witch Project',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/blair_witch_project/','13062','0185937',1,NULL,'Full of creepy campfire scares, mock-doc The Blair Witch Project keeps audiences in the dark about its titular villain -- thus proving that imagination can be as scary as anything onscreen.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/91/56/10915602_mob.jpg'),(252,'Friends With Benefits',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/friends_with_benefits/','771208131','1632708',1,'Dylan (Justin Timberlake) and Jamie (Mila Kunis) think it\'s going to be easy to add the simple act of sex to their friendship, despite what Hollywood romantic comedies would have them believe. They soon discover however that getting physical really does always lead to complications. -- (C) Sony','Friends with Benefits adds nothing new to its well-worn rom-com formula, but the chemistry between Justin Timberlake and Mila Kunis is almost enough to carry the movie by itself.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/36/11163654_mob.jpg'),(253,'Blindness',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1188215-blindness/','770672765','0861689',1,NULL,'This allegorical disaster film about society\'s reaction to mass blindness is mottled and self-satisfied; provocative but not as interesting as its premise implies.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/85/34/10853428_mob.jpg'),(254,'Dr. Strangelove Or How I Learned to Stop Worrying and Love the Bomb',1964,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dr_strangelove/','12368','0057012',1,NULL,'Stanley Kubrick\'s brilliant Cold War satire remains as funny and razor-sharp today as it was in 1964.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/33/11163386_mob.jpg'),(255,'The Birds',1963,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1002448-birds/','10078','0056869',1,NULL,'Proving once again that build-up is the key to suspense, Alfred Hitchcock successfully turned birds into some of the most terrifying villains in horror history.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/83/82/10838298_mob.jpg'),(256,'Bill & Ted\'s Excellent Adventure',1989,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bill_and_teds_excellent_adventure/','10476','0096928',1,NULL,'Keanu Reeves and Alex Winter are just charming, goofy, and silly enough to make this fluffy time-travel Adventure work.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/19/10881968_mob.jpg'),(257,'What Lies Beneath',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/what_lies_beneath/','10686','0161081',1,NULL,'Robert Zemeckis is unable to salvage an uncompelling and unoriginal film.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/34/35/84/3435848_mob.jpg'),(258,'The Blues Brothers',1980,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/blues_brothers/','13659','0080455',1,NULL,'Too over the top for its own good, but ultimately rescued by the cast\'s charm, director John Landis\' grace, and several soul-stirring musical numbers.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/84/85/10848572_mob.jpg'),(259,'Big Momma\'s House',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/big_mommas_house/','11526','0208003',1,NULL,'Big Momma\'s House is funny in some parts, but it is essentially a one-joke movie.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/49/11164907_mob.jpg'),(260,'In Bruges',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/in_bruges/','770679093','0780536',1,NULL,'Featuring witty dialogue and deft performances In Bruges is an effective mix of dark comedy and crime thriller elements.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/85/68/10856882_mob.jpg'),(261,'Bicentennial Man',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bicentennial_man/','10593','0182789',1,NULL,'Bicentennial Man is ruined by a bad script and ends up being dull and mawkish.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/65/256509_mob.jpg'),(262,'Beastly',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beastly/','770809501','1152398',1,'Beastly is an edgy teen romance about learning how to see past false surfaces to discover true inner beauty. Kyle Kingson (Alex Pettyfer) has it all - looks, intelligence, wealth and opportunity - and a wicked cruel streak. Prone to mocking and humiliating \"aggressively unattractive\" classmates, he zeroes in on Goth classmate Kendra (Mary-Kate Olsen), inviting her to the school\'s extravagant environmental bash. Kendra accepts, and, true to form, Kyle blows her off in a particularly savage fashion. She retaliates by casting a spell that physically transforms him into everything he despises. Enraged by his horrible and unrecognizable appearance he confronts Kendra and learns that the only solution to the curse is to find someone that will love him as he is - a task he considers impossible. Repulsed by his appearance, Kyle\'s callous father (Peter Krause) banishes him to Brooklyn with a sympathetic housekeeper (LisaGay Hamilton) and blind tutor (Neil Patrick Harris). As Kyle ponders how to overcome the curse and get his old life back, he chances upon a drug addict in the act of killing a threatening dealer. Seizing the opportunity, Kyle promises the addict freedom and safety for his daughter Lindy (Vanessa Hudgens) if she will consent to live in Kyle\'s Brooklyn home. Thus begins Kyle\'s journey to discover true love in this hyper-modern retelling of the classic \"Beauty and the Beast\" story. Vanessa Hudgens (High School Musical) and Alex Pettyfer (Wild Child, Stormbreaker) star in Beastly for CBS Films, the film division within CBS Corporation (NYSE: CBS.A and CBS). Daniel Barnz (Phoebe In Wonderland) directed the project which completed principal photography in Montreal in August 2009. The film will be released in theaters in July 2010. Susan Cartsonis (No Reservations, What Women Want) is producing through her company, Storefront Pictures. Roz Weisberg is co-producing. In addition to his role as director, Barnz wrote the screenplay, which is based on the Alex Flinn novel of the same name. -- (C) Disney','Fundamentally misguided, poorly written, and badly acted, Beastly adds little to the legacy of its timeless source material.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/58/11155888_mob.jpg'),(263,'Batman & Robin',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1077027-batman_and_robin/','11169','0118688',1,NULL,'Joel Schumacher\'s tongue-in-cheek attitude hits an unbearable limit in Batman & Robin resulting in a frantic and mindless movie that\'s too jokey to care much for.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/50/14/39/5014391_mob.jpg'),(264,'Before the Devil Knows You\'re Dead',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/before_the_devil_knows_youre_dead/','770676448','0292963',1,NULL,'A tense and effective thriller, Before the Devil Knows You\'re Dead marks a triumphant return to form for director Sidney Lumet.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/87/05/10870510_mob.jpg'),(265,'Brother Bear',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/brother_bear/','9948','0328880',1,NULL,'Brother Bear is gentle and pleasant if unremarkable Disney fare, with so-so animation and generic plotting.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/50/26/74/5026744_mob.jpg'),(266,'Buried',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/buried/','770819772','1462758',1,'A man is caught in a desperate race against time in this claustrophobic thriller from director Rodrigo Cortes. Paul Conroy (Ryan Reynolds) is an American truck driver who has been contracted to work in Iraq, and while delivering a load of kitchen equipment as part of a humanitarian aid program, he\'s captured by insurgent guerrillas who intend to hold him hostage. Paul is struck unconscious, put into a coffin-like box, and buried, and when he comes to, all he has to help him get out is a lighter and a cell phone. Trapped underground with a limited supply of air, Paul frantically calls his family, his employer, and American military and political representatives, trying to remain calm as his chances of survival slip farther away with each passing minute. Featuring the voice talent of Robert Paterson, Stephen Tobolowsky, Samantha Mathis, and Erik Palladino, with all the action taking place within the underground box, Buried received its world premiere at the 2010 Sundance Film Festival. ~ Mark Deming, Rovi','Wringing a seemingly impossible amount of gripping drama out of its claustrophobic premise, Buried is a nerve-wracking showcase for Ryan Reynolds\' talent.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/20/11152005_mob.jpg'),(267,'Battle Royale 3D',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/battle_royale_3d/','136269391','0266308',1,NULL,'Battle Royale is a controversial and violent parable of adolescence, heightening teenage melodrama with life-or-death stakes.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/86/11168650_mob.jpg'),(268,'Conan the Barbarian',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/conan_the_barbarian_2011/','770782767','0816462',1,'A quest that begins as a personal vendetta for the fierce Cimmerian warrior soon turns into an epic battle against hulking rivals, horrific monsters, and impossible odds, as Conan (Jason Momoa) realizes he is the only hope of saving the great nations of Hyboria from an encroaching reign of supernatural evil. -- (C) Lionsgate','While its relentless, gory violence is more faithful to the Robert E. Howard books, Conan the Barbarian forsakes three-dimensional characters, dialogue, and acting in favor of unnecessary 3D effects.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/74/11157475_mob.jpg'),(269,'Meet Joe Black',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/meet_joe_black/','12724','0119643',1,NULL,'Glacially slow, uneventful.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/64/266412_mob.jpg'),(270,'Boogeyman',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/boogeyman/','10549','0357507',1,NULL,'The plot is been-there done-that generic, and none of the shock effects can do anything to build up suspense.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/97/10/26/9710267_mob.jpg'),(271,'Jonas Brothers: The 3D Concert Experience',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jonas_brothers_3d/','770801286','1229827',1,NULL,'Jonas Brothers: The 3-D Concert Experience should please the brothers\' adoring followers, but for non-converts, this concert film is largely flat and unenlightening.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/92/39/10923953_mob.jpg'),(272,'Our Idiot Brother',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/our_idiot_brother/','771224856','1637706',1,'Every family has one: the sibling who is always just a little bit behind the curve when it comes to getting his life together. For sisters Liz (Emily Mortimer), Miranda (Elizabeth Banks) and Natalie (Zooey Deschanel), that person is their perennially upbeat brother Ned (Paul Rudd), an erstwhile organic farmer whose willingness to rely on the honesty of mankind is a less-than-optimum strategy for a tidy, trouble-free existence. Ned may be utterly lacking in common sense, but he is their brother and so, after his girlfriend dumps him and boots him off the farm, his sisters once again come to his rescue. As Liz, Miranda and Natalie each take a turn at housing Ned, their brother\'s unfailing commitment to honesty creates more than a few messes in their comfortable routines. But as each of their lives begins to unravel, Ned\'s family comes to realize that maybe, in believing and trusting the people around him; Ned isn\'t such an idiot after all. -- (C) Weinstein','It\'s decidedly uneven, but like Paul Rudd\'s performance in the title role, Our Idiot Brother is too charming to resist.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/02/11160217_mob.png'),(273,'Sunset Boulevard',1950,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sunset_boulevard/','17003','0043014',1,NULL,'Arguably the greatest movie about Hollywood, Billy Wilder\'s masterpiece Sunset Boulevard is a tremendously entertaining combination of noir, black comedy, and character study.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/29/10882989_mob.jpg'),(274,'Bowling for Columbine',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bowling_for_columbine/','13038','0310793',1,NULL,'Though it may not always convince, Bowling for Columbine asks important questions and provokes thought.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/93/45/10934550_mob.jpg'),(275,'O Brother, Where Art Thou?',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/o_brother_where_art_thou/','12776','0190590',1,NULL,'Though not as good as Coen brothers\' classics such as Blood Simple, the delightfully loopy O Brother, Where Art Thou? is still a lot of fun.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/97/83/14/9783145_mob.jpg'),(276,'Big Fat Liar',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/big_fat_liar/','11367','0265298',1,NULL,'Though there\'s nothing that offensive about Big Fat Liar, it is filled with Hollywood cliches and cartoonish slapstick, making it strictly for kids.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/55/35/55/5535555_mob.jpg'),(277,'Raging Bull',1980,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/raging_bull/','15121','0081398',1,NULL,'Arguably Martin Scorsese\'s and Robert De Niro\'s finest film, Raging Bull is often painful to watch, but it\'s a searing, powerful work about an unsympathetic hero.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/93/45/10934583_mob.jpg'),(278,'Beerfest',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beerfest/','287864786','0486551',1,NULL,'Beerfest features some laugh-inducing gags, but is too long and the pacing too uneven to form a coherent, functioning comedy.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/21/92/34/2192341_mob.jpg'),(279,'Blue Valentine',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/blue_valentine/','770728350','1120985',1,'A relationship is charted from its promising beginning to its sad collapse in this independent drama from Derek Cianfrance. Dean (Ryan Gosling) meets Cindy (Michelle Williams) when they\'re in their late teens; he\'s working for a moving company, she\'s a college student visiting her elderly grandmother at a home for the elderly. Cindy is dating Bobby (Mike Vogel), her boyfriend from high school, but as she gets to know Dean better, a mutual attraction grows between them. Years later, Dean and Cindy are married and have a daughter, Frankie (Faith Wladyka), but they\'re clearly not as happy as they once were; Dean loves his daughter but feels distant from his wife, they have to look after an elderly relative (John Doman), and when Cindy bumps into Bobby while running errands, it\'s clear he still holds a grudge against her. Dean and Cindy go away for a weekend together at a hotel, but it doesn\'t take long for them to realize that the magic isn\'t coming back. Blue Valentine received its world premiere at the 2010 Sundance Film Festival. ~ Mark Deming, Rovi','This emotionally gripping examination of a marriage on the rocks isn\'t always easy to watch, but Michelle Williams and Ryan Gosling give performances of unusual depth and power.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/43/11154330_mob.jpg'),(280,'My Best Friend\'s Wedding',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/my_best_friends_wedding/','12712','0119738',1,NULL,'Thanks to a charming performance from Julia Roberts and a subversive spin on the genre, My Best Friend\'s Wedding is a refreshingly entertaining romantic comedy.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/55/35/54/5535541_mob.jpg'),(281,'Deep Blue Sea',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1090759-deep_blue_sea/','13703','0149261',1,NULL,'Aside from a few thrills, Deep Blue Sea is unoriginal and unintelligent.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/27/10/271021_mob.jpg'),(282,'Burlesque',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/burlesque/','770857928','1126591',1,'Christina Aguilera makes her dramatic feature debut as Ali, a small-town singer who takes her shot at stardom performing at a neo-burlesque nightclub in Los Angeles. Situated in a regal old theater that\'s still dazzling despite having fallen into disrepair, The Burlesque Lounge is the kind of club where legends are born. When club owner Tess (Cher) hires charismatic Ali as a cocktail waitress, the ambitious big-city newcomer goes to great lengths to make a good impression. Taken under the wing of a friendly featured dancer (Julianne Hough), Ali quickly realizes that not everyone is quite as nice when she forms a friendship with bartender/aspiring musician Jack (Cam Gigandet) and incurs the wrath of the club\'s cattiest showgirl (Kristen Bell). After making her leap to the stage with a little help from a sympathetic stage manager (Stanley Tucci) and the club\'s playfully androgynous host (Alan Cumming), Ali becomes the star attraction at The Burlesque Lounge, and the crowds start packing in. Later, a wealthy businessman (Eric Dane) makes a bid for the club while trying to charm the talented young performer straight into his arms. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Campy and cliched, Burlesque wastes its talented cast (including a better-than-expected Christina Aguilera) on a movie that wavers uncertainly between \"bad\" and \"so bad it\'s good.\"','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/58/11155850_mob.jpg'),(283,'Bigger, Stronger, Faster*',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bigger_stronger_faster_asterisk/','770682467','1151309',1,NULL,'Bigger, Stronger, Faster* is a fascinating, informative, entertaining and especially introspective account of the American \'enhancement\' culture.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/84/27/10842758_mob.jpg'),(284,'Winter\'s Bone',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10012136-winters_bone/','770856649','1399683',1,'Her family home in danger of being repossessed after her meth-cooking dad skips bail and disappears, Ozark teen Ree Dolly (Jennifer Lawrence) breaks the local code of conduct by confronting her kin about their conspiracy of silence. Should she fail to track her father down, Ree Dolly, her younger siblings, and their disabled mother will soon be rendered homeless. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Bleak, haunting, and yet still somehow hopeful, Winter\'s Bone is writer-director Debra Granik\'s best work yet -- and it boasts an incredible, starmaking performance from Jennifer Lawrence.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/63/11166307_mob.jpg'),(285,'Here Comes the Boom',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/here_comes_the_boom/','771234470','1648179',1,'In the comedy Here Comes the Boom, former collegiate wrestler Scott Voss (Kevin James) is a 42-year-old apathetic biology teacher in a failing high school. When cutbacks threaten to cancel the music program and lay off its teacher (Henry Winkler,) Scott begins to raise money by moonlighting as a mixed martial arts fighter. Everyone thinks Scott is crazy - most of all the school nurse, Bella (Salma Hayek) - but in his quest, Scott gains something he never expected as he becomes a sensation that rallies the entire school. -- (C) Official Site','Here Comes the Boom benefits from Kevin James\'s genial presence but the film doesn\'t deliver enough laughs to live up to its title -- or enough satisfying plot to make up the difference.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/85/11168526_mob.jpg'),(286,'The Beach',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beach/','13286','0163978',1,NULL,'Critics say The Beach is unfocused and muddled, a shallow adaptation of the novel it is based on. Points go to the gorgeous cinematography, though.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/47/11164758_mob.jpg'),(287,'The Secret World of Arrietty',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_secret_world_of_arrietty/','771221507','1568921',1,'Arrietty (Bridgit Mendler), a tiny, but tenacious 14-year-old, lives with her parents (Will Arnett and Amy Poehler) in the recesses of a suburban garden home, unbeknownst to the homeowner and her housekeeper (Carol Burnett). Like all little people, Arrietty (AIR-ee-ett-ee) remains hidden from view, except during occasional covert ventures beyond the floorboards to \"borrow\" scrap supplies like sugar cubes from her human hosts. But when 12-year-old Shawn (David Henrie), a human boy who comes to stay in the home, discovers his mysterious housemate one evening, a secret friendship blossoms. If discovered, their relationship could drive Arrietty\'s family from the home and straight into danger. -- (C) Disney','Visually lush, refreshingly free of family-friendly clatter, and anchored with soulful depth, The Secret World of Arrietty lives up to Studio Ghibli\'s reputation.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/10/11161029_mob.jpg'),(288,'The Bone Collector',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bone_collector/','13446','0145681',1,NULL,'A talented cast is wasted on a bland attempt at a suspenseful, serial killer flick.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/88/11168815_mob.jpg'),(289,'Goal! The Dream Begins (Goal!: The Impossible Dream)',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1158528-goal/','155654940','0380389',1,NULL,'Impressive sports action sequences are the highlight, as the run-of the-mill story invokes every known sports movie cliche.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/92/30/10923010_mob.jpg'),(290,'Breakfast on Pluto',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1153341-breakfast_on_pluto/','9270','0411195',1,NULL,'Well-acted if monotonous drama about a transvestite prostitute in London during the 1970s.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/05/250523_mob.jpg'),(291,'Ben-Hur',1959,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/benhur/','9402','0052618',1,NULL,'Uneven, but in terms of epic scope and grand spectacle, Ben-Hur still ranks among Hollywood\'s finest examples of pure entertainment.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/81/11168159_mob.jpg'),(292,'Runaway Bride',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/runaway_bride/','11674','0163187',1,NULL,'Cliche story with lack of chemistry between Richard Gere and Julia Roberts.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/84/58/10845851_mob.jpg'),(293,'Justin Bieber: Never Say Never',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/justin_bieber_never_say_never/','771217412','1702443',1,'Justin Bieber: Never Say Never is the inspiring true story and rare inside look at the rise of Justin from street performer in the small town of Stratford, Ontario to internet phenomenon to global super star culminating with a dream sold out show at the famed Madison Square Garden in 3-D. -- (C) Paramount','As a tour documentary, it\'s rather uninspired -- but as a 3D glimpse of a building pop culture phenomenon, Never Say Never is undeniably entertaining.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/54/11155447_mob.jpg'),(294,'The Best Exotic Marigold Hotel',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_best_exotic_marigold_hotel_2012/','771252912','1412386',1,'The Best Exotic Marigold Hotel follows a group of British retirees who decide to \"outsource\" their retirement to less expensive and seemingly exotic India. Enticed by advertisements for the newly restored Marigold Hotel and bolstered with visions of a life of leisure, they arrive to find the palace a shell of its former self. Though the new environment is less luxurious than imagined, they are forever transformed by their shared experiences, discovering that life and love can begin again when you let go of the past. -- (C) Fox Searchlight','The Best Exotic Marigold Hotel isn\'t groundbreaking storytelling, but it\'s a sweet story about the senior set featuring a top-notch cast of veteran actors.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/30/11163058_mob.jpg'),(295,'Grandma\'s Boy',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/grandmas_boy/','2864413','0456554',1,NULL,'A gross-out comedy that\'s more gross than comedic, Grandma\'s Boy is lazy and unrewarding.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/31/21/312192_mob.jpg'),(296,'Ramona and Beezus',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ramona_and_beezus/','770805265','0493949',1,'The adventures of young Ramona Quimby (newcomer Joey King) and her big sister Beezus (Selena Gomez) come to life in this all new film based on the best-selling books (over 30 million...and counting) by Beverly Cleary. Ramona\'s vivid imagination, boundless energy, and accident-prone antics keep everyone she meets on their toes. But her irrepressible sense of fun, adventure and mischief come in handy when she puts her mind to helping save her family\'s home. John Corbett (My Big Fat Greek Wedding) and Bridget Moynahan (I, Robot) also star as Ramona and Beezus\' parents, Robert and Dorothy Quimby, while Ginnifer Goodwin (He\'s Just Not That Into You) portrays the girls\' Aunt Bea, opposite Josh Duhamel (Transformers) as Bea\'s former flame, Hobart. Sandra Oh (Grey\'s Anatomy) plays Ramona\'s third grade teacher, Mrs. Meacham. Elizabeth Allen (Aquamarine) directs from a screenplay by Laurie Craig and Nick Pustay. Denise Di Novi and Alison Greenspan produce for Fox 2000 Pictures and Walden Media. The cinematographer is John Bailey, ASC; Brent Thomas is the production designer; and Jane Moran is the editor. Co-producer is Brad Van Arragon. Music is by Mark Mothersbaugh, and the music supervisor is Julia Michels. -- (C) 20th Century Fox','If Ramona and Beezus fails to capture the essence of its classic source material, it\'s sunny, sweet, and wholesome.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/14/90/11149032_mob.jpg'),(297,'Don\'t Be Afraid Of The Dark',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dont_be_afraid_of_the_dark_2011/','770875156','1270761',1,'While architect Alex Hurst (Guy Pearce) and his new girlfriend Kim (Katie Holmes) restore their Gothic mansion\'s period interiors, Alex\'s young daughter Sally (Bailee Madison) can investigate the macabre history and dark corners of the estate. Spurring Sally\'s investigation are the voices-rasping whispers who call out to her from the basement, who promise her understanding and friendship, who are so very hungry and would like to be set free. When Sally gives in to her curiosity, she opens a gateway into a hellish underworld from which an army of beady-eyed, sharp-clawed monsters emerge, small in size but endless in number. Confronted with the horror that now threatens to taker her life and destroy her family, Sally desperately tries to warn the whole house, but there\'s just one problem: no one believes her. -- (C) Miramax','While it\'s pleasantly atmospheric and initially quite scary, Don\'t Be Afraid of the Dark ultimately fails to deliver the skin-crawling chills of the original.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/36/11163652_mob.jpg'),(298,'The Ant Bully',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ant_bully/','205091258','0429589',1,NULL,'Sometimes inventive and witty, this animated adventure into an ant-sized world is a pleasant diversion.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/18/56/91/1856919_mob.jpg'),(299,'Big',1988,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/big/','10396','0094737',1,NULL,'Refreshingly sweet and undeniably funny, Big is a showcase for Tom Hanks, who dives into his role and infuses it with charm and surprising poignancy.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/44/11164479_mob.jpg'),(300,'Batman: The Movie',1966,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/batman_the_movie/','10340','0060153',1,NULL,'Batman: The Movie elevates camp to an art form -- and has a blast doing it, every gloriously tongue-in-cheek inch of the way.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/49/11164986_mob.jpg'),(301,'Deuce Bigalow: Male Gigolo',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/deuce_bigalow_male_gigolo/','13590','0205000',1,NULL,'According to critics, Deuce Bigalow is just too dumb and filled with old, tired gags.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/27/05/270504_mob.jpg'),(302,'Something Borrowed',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/something_borrowed_2011/','771041146',NULL,1,'Rachel (Ginnifer Goodwin) is a talented attorney at a top New York law firm, a generous and loyal friend, and, unhappily, still single-as her engaged best friend Darcy (Kate Hudson) is constantly reminding her. But after celebrating her 30th birthday, perpetual good girl Rachel unexpectedly ends up in the arms of the guy she\'s had a crush on since law school, Dex (Colin Egglesfield)...who just happens to be Darcy\'s fiance. As one thing leads to another in the frantic weeks leading up to Darcy\'s wedding, Rachel finds herself in an impossible situation, caught between her treasured friendship with Darcy and the love of her life. Meanwhile, Ethan (John Krasinski), Rachel\'s constant confidante and sometimes conscience, is busy evading the affection of Darcy\'s hopelessly love-struck friend Claire (Ashley Williams) while harboring a secret crush of his own; and the charming and irrepressible Marcus (Steve Howey) has designs on Rachel that don\'t necessarily exclude any other woman who catches his eye. -- (C) Warner Bros','In spite of solid performances from Kate Hudson and John Krasinski, Something Borrowed is an unpleasant misfire that lives down to its title.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/57/11155743_mob.jpg'),(303,'Dave Chappelle\'s Block Party',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/block_party/','49248977','0425598',1,NULL,'Dave Chappelle\'s Block Party is a raucous return to the spotlight for the comic. Buoyed by Chappelle\'s witty, infectious humor and outstanding performances from some of the more socially conscious artists in hip-hop like Mos Def, Kayne West, the Roots, and (will wonders never cease?) the reunited Fugees, this documentary/concert film is a joyous experience. With an appealing mix like that, who doesn\'t want to attend this Party?','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/87/02/10870283_mob.jpg'),(304,'Bully',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bully_2012/','771239477','1682181',1,'Directed by Sundance and Emmy-award winning filmmaker, Lee Hirsch, Bully is a beautifully cinematic, character-driven documentary. At its heart are those with huge stakes in this issue whose stories each represent a different facet of America\'s bullying crisis. Bully follows five kids and families over the course of a school year. Stories include two families who have lost children to suicide and a mother awaiting the fate of her 14-year-old daughter who has been incarcerated after bringing a gun on her school bus. With an intimate glimpse into homes, classrooms, cafeterias and principals\' offices, the film offers insight into the often cruel world of the lives of bullied children. -- (C) Weinstein','Hard-hitting and gracefully filmed, Bully powerfully delivers an essential message to an audience that may not be able to see it.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/37/11163744_mob.jpg'),(305,'Akeelah and the Bee',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/akeelah_and_the_bee/','152552156','0437800',1,NULL,'Although predictable in every way, a winning performance from its young star Keke Palmer and the rest of the cast makes it difficult not to cheer for the little heroine of Akeelah and the Bee. Sort of like Rocky for the middle school nerd set, Akeelah is a warm, family-friendly underdog story, featuring terrific supporting performances from Laurence Fishburne and Angela Bassett.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/84/08/10840854_mob.jpg'),(306,'Yogi Bear',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/yogi-bear/','770858010','1302067',1,'Everyone\'s favorite pic-a-nic basket-stealing bear comes to the big screen in \"Yogi Bear,\" a new adventure, filmed in 3D, that combines live action with computer animation. Dan Aykroyd stars as the voice of Yogi, Jellystone Park\'s notorious troublemaker, and Justin Timberlake as the voice of Boo Boo, Yogi\'s faithful pal and co-conspirator in his never-ending schemes to separate park visitors from their lunches. Yogi has always relied on his quick wit and fast feet to stay one step ahead of irate campers while dodging his long-suffering nemesis, Ranger Smith. But he and Boo Boo are about to face a situation worse than anything Yogi has ever gotten them into... Jellystone Park is being sold! To cover his mismanagement of city funds and fuel his election campaign, Mayor Brown plans to sell the park to loggers. Families will no longer be able to experience the natural beauty of the outdoors Jellystone has always provided--and, even worse, Yogi, Boo Boo, and all their friends will be tossed out of the only home they\'ve ever known. Faced with his biggest challenge ever, Yogi must prove he really is \"smarter than the average bear,\" as he and Boo Boo join forces with Ranger Smith to find a way to save the park from closing forever. -- (C) Warner Bros','Yogi Bear\'s 3D effects and all-star voice cast are cold comfort for its aggressively mediocre screenplay.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/87/11168776_mob.jpg'),(307,'Bubble Boy',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bubble_boy/','10927','0258470',1,NULL,'Bubble Boy bounces along with lame, offensive jokes that are more tasteless than funny.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/91/54/10915485_mob.jpg'),(308,'Brick',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/brick/','126518601','0393109',1,NULL,'This entertaining homage to noirs past has been slickly and compellingly updated to a contemporary high school setting.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/89/84/10898420_mob.jpg'),(309,'Men in Black',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/men_in_black/','12656','0119654',1,NULL,'Thanks to a smart script, spectacular set pieces, and charismatic performances from its leads, Men in Black is an entirely satisfying summer blockbuster hit.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/45/11164553_mob.jpg'),(310,'The White Ribbon (Das weisse Band)',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/white_ribbon/','770808692','1149362',1,NULL,'The White Ribbon effectively utilizes tension and a bleak atmosphere to deliver a thought-provoking examination of nascent fascism.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/90/27/10902706_mob.jpg'),(311,'Coco Before Chanel',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/coco_before_chanel/','770805147','1035736',1,NULL,'Though it doesn\'t quite capture the complexity of its subject\'s life, Coco Avant Chanel remains a fascinating, appropriately lovely tribute.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/89/21/10892188_mob.jpg'),(312,'Bad Lieutenant: Port of Call New Orleans',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bad_lieutenant_port_of_call_new_orleans/','770783617','1095217',1,NULL,'Befitting its unorthodox origins, this Bad Lieutenant benefits from Werner Herzog\'s typically fearless direction and a delightfully unhinged Nicolas Cage in the title role.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/95/28/10952876_mob.jpg'),(313,'Father of the Bride',1991,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1037864-father_of_the_bride/','10963','0101862',1,NULL,'While it doesn\'t quite hit the heights of the original, this remake of the 1950 classic is pleasantly enjoyable, thanks in large part to winning performances from Steve Martin and Martin Short.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/83/258323_mob.jpg'),(314,'The Jungle Book',1967,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1031385-jungle_book/','9381','0061852',1,NULL,'With expressive animation, fun characters, and catchy songs, The Jungle Book endures as a crowd-pleasing Disney classic.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/07/250701_mob.jpg'),(315,'Bewitched',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bewitched/','1783','0374536',1,NULL,'Bewitched is haunted by scattered laughs and a lack of direction.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/84/02/10840286_mob.jpg'),(316,'Babies',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10012014-babies/','770856801','1020938',1,'Filmmaker Thomas Balmes offers an adorable glimpse at the first phase of life in this film following four newborn babies through their first year of life. Ponijao, Bayar, Mari, and Hattie were born in Namibia, Mongolia, Japan, and California, respectively. By capturing their earliest stage of development on camera, Balmes reveals just how much we all have in common, despite being born to different parents and raised in different cultures. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Babies is a joyous celebration of humankind that\'s loaded with adorable images, but it lacks insight and depth.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/93/37/10933766_mob.jpg'),(317,'Bedazzled',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1101051-bedazzled/','11264','0230030',1,NULL,'Though it has its funny moments, this remake is essentially a one-joke movie with too many flat spots.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/49/11164987_mob.jpg'),(318,'Anacondas - The Hunt for the Blood Orchid',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/anacondas_the_hunt_for_the_blood_orchid/','11072','0366174',1,NULL,'A cheesy monster B-movie.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/88/258899_mob.jpg'),(319,'Bad Santa',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bad_santa/','16986','0307987',1,NULL,'A gloriously rude and gleefully offensive black comedy, Bad Santa isn\'t for everyone, but grinches will find it uproariously funny.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/85/09/10850919_mob.jpg'),(320,'Beavis and Butt-Head Do America',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beavis_and_butthead_do_america/','10358','0115641',1,NULL,'Beavis and Butt-Head Do America is unabashedly offensive, unapologetically stupid, and unexpectedly funny.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/53/255323_mob.jpg'),(321,'Looney Tunes: Back in Action',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/looney_tunes_back_in_action/','11525','0318155',1,NULL,'The plot is a nonsensical, hyperactive jumble and the gags are relatively uninspired compared to the classic Looney Tunes cartoons.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/86/11168699_mob.jpg'),(322,'Bobby',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1162559-bobby/','343970062','0308055',1,NULL,'Despite best intentions from director Emilio Estevez and his ensemble cast, they succumb to a script filled with pointless subplots and awkward moments working too hard to parallel contemporary times.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/86/10878665_mob.jpg'),(323,'God Bless America',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/god_bless_america_2011/','771253753','1912398',1,'Frank (Joel Murray) has had enough of the downward spiral of American culture. Divorced, recently fired, and possibly terminally ill, Frank truly has nothing left to live for. But instead of taking his own life, he buys a gun and decides to take out his frustration on the cruelest, stupidest, most intolerant people he can imagine -- starting with some particularly odious reality television stars. Frank finds an unusual accomplice in a high-school student named Roxy (Tara Lynne Barr), who shares his sense of rage and disenfranchisement. Together they embark on a nationwide assault on our country\'s most irritating celebrities. -- (C) Magnet Releasing','A darkly comic polemic on modern culture, God Bless America is uneven and somewhat this but the ideas behind this revenge fulfillment journey has primal appeal.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/31/11163100_mob.jpg'),(324,'Deuce Bigalow: European Gigolo',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/deuce_bigelow_european_gigolo/','3615','0367652',1,NULL,'A witless follow-up to the surprise 1999 hit, Deuce Bigalow: European Gigolo is raunchy, politically incorrect, and not particularly funny.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/24/99/249923_mob.jpg'),(325,'Dreamer: Inspired by a True Story',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dreamer/','8840','0418647',1,NULL,'Though formulaic, this horse story\'s saving grace is its strong performances.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/03/250392_mob.jpg'),(326,'Broken Flowers',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/broken_flowers/','2771','0412019',1,NULL,'Bill Murray\'s subtle and understated style complements director Jim Jarmusch\'s minimalist storytelling in this quirky, but deadpan comedy.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/24/99/249911_mob.jpg'),(327,'Terra (Battle For Terra)',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10009859-terra/','770677880','0858486',1,NULL,'Despite its earnest aspirations to be a thought-provoking sci-fi alternative, Battle for Terra lacks both a cohesive story and polished visuals, and fails to resonate.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/86/76/10867653_mob.jpg'),(328,'Nanny McPhee Returns',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nanny_mcphee_returns/','771041878','1415283',1,'A struggling mother receives some much-needed assistance tending to the family farm and raising a group of spirited children while her military husband is fighting overseas in this sequel to the whimsical 2005 fantasy comedy Nanny McPhee. Mrs. Isabel Green (Maggie Gyllenhaal) lives in a scenic valley with her two sons and one daughter. They each understand the importance of working together as a family, and things are going remarkably smoothly for the rural quartet until a pair of spoiled cousins arrives for an extended stay, effectively turning the quaint little farm into a virtual zoo. As the situation quickly gets out of hand, Nanny McPhee (Emma Thompson) suddenly appears on Isabel\'s doorstep claiming that she can bring a much-needed sense of order to the out-of-control household. In time the mysterious helper does just that, using powerful magic to teach her young charges the importance of getting along, and gradually winning their trust in the process. But when the piglets escape from their sty, the contentious kids must work together to recover the family farm\'s most valued assets, or risk losing everything their father worked so hard to build before he went off to fight in the war. Rhys Ifans and Maggie Smith co-star. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Emma Thompson\'s second labor of love with the Nanny McPhee character actually improves on the first, delivering charming family fare with an excellent cast.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/15/11151534_mob.jpg'),(329,'Basic Instinct 2',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/basic_instinct_2/','133759604','0430912',1,NULL,'Unable to match the suspense and titilation of its predecessor, Basic Instinct 2 boasts a plot so ludicrous and predictable it borders on \"so-bad-it\'s-good.\"','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/83/10898386_mob.jpg'),(330,'Time Bandits',1981,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/time_bandits/','11922','0081633',1,NULL,'Time Bandits is a remarkable time-travel fantasy from Terry Gilliam, who utilizes fantastic set design and homemade special effects to create a vivid, original universe.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/30/263020_mob.jpg'),(331,'Blue Velvet',1986,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/blue_velvet/','16022','0090756',1,NULL,'If audiences walk away from this subversive, surreal shocker not fully understanding the story, they might also walk away with a deeper perception of the potential of film storytelling.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/28/20/282022_mob.jpg'),(332,'Backdraft',1991,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/backdraft/','13033','0101393',1,NULL,'It\'s not particularly deep, but Backdraft is a strong action movie with exceptional special effects.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/56/82/34/5682347_mob.jpg'),(333,'Love and Basketball',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/love_and_basketball/','10414','0199725',1,NULL,'Confident directing and acting deliver an insightful look at young athletes.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/92/57/10925795_mob.jpg'),(334,'The Super Mario Bros.',1993,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the-super-mario-bros/','10586','0098762',1,NULL,'Despite flashy sets and special effects, Super Mario Bros. is too light on story and substance to be anything more than a novelty.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/94/59/10945936_mob.jpg'),(335,'Barbarella',1968,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/barbarella/','10569','0062711',1,NULL,'Unevenly paced and thoroughly cheesy, Barbarella is nonetheless full of humor, entertaining visuals, and Fonda\'s sex appeal.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/64/256403_mob.jpg'),(336,'Bulletproof Monk',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bulletproof_monk/','11258','0245803',1,NULL,'Venerable action star Chow Yun-Fat is the only saving grace in this silly action flick that more often than not resembles a commercial in style.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/61/10886106_mob.jpg'),(337,'Big Miracle',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/big_miracle/','771208070','1430615',1,'Inspired by the true story that captured the hearts of people across the world, the rescue adventure Big Miracle tells the amazing tale of a small town news reporter (John Krasinski) and an animal-loving volunteer (Drew Barrymore) who are joined by rival world superpowers to save a family of majestic gray whales trapped by rapidly forming ice in the Arctic Circle. -- (C) Universal','Big Miracle uses real-life events as the basis for a surprisingly satisfying family drama.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/13/11161342_mob.jpg'),(338,'Rosemary\'s Baby',1968,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/rosemarys_baby/','13060',NULL,1,NULL,'A frightening tale of Satanism and pregnancy that is even more disturbing than it sounds thanks to convincing and committed performances by Mia Farrow and Ruth Gordon.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/55/11165516_mob.jpg'),(339,'Breaking and Entering',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/breaking_and_entering/','381413316','0443456',1,NULL,'This class warfare drama feels contrived and superficial: characters don\'t act logically as the movie manipulates them towards deconstructing various social issues.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/35/11/98/3511988_mob.jpg'),(340,'Agent Cody Banks',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/agent_cody_banks/','11505','0313911',1,NULL,'Should satisfy young teens, but offers nothing new for those who are familiar with the formula.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/26/10/261011_mob.jpg'),(341,'Brazil',1985,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1003033-brazil/','13466','0088846',1,NULL,'Brazil, Terry Gilliam\'s visionary Orwellian fantasy, is an audacious dark comedy, filled with strange, imaginative visuals.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/99/269902_mob.jpg'),(342,'Not Easily Broken',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/not_easily_broken/','770798019','0795438',1,NULL,'Though well-intentioned, Not Easily Broken is bogged down by melodramatic plotting and stereotypical characters.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/84/10888473_mob.jpg'),(343,'First Blood (Rambo: First Blood)',1982,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/first_blood/','16521','0083944',1,NULL,'A much darker, more sensitive film than the sequels it spawned, First Blood is a thrilling survival adventure, and the role of haunted Vietnam vet John Rambo takes full advantage of Sylvester Stallone\'s acting skills.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/13/69/11136980_mob.jpg'),(344,'The Brothers Solomon',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/brothers_solomon/','770669969','0784972',1,NULL,'Squandering its impressive cast with poorly-directed gags, The Brothers Solomon is a one-joke film stretched well beyond its limits.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/79/10887965_mob.jpg'),(345,'Bride and Prejudice',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bride_and_prejudice/','10062','0361411',1,NULL,'A colorful and energetic adaptation of Austen\'s classic.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/38/253894_mob.jpg'),(346,'Battle in Heaven (Batalla en el cielo)',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/battle_in_heaven/','19049983','0387055',1,NULL,'Though it tries to be provocative, Battle in Heaven is lethargic and mind-numbing.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/91/62/10916250_mob.jpg'),(347,'Harry Brown',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/harry_brown/','770808794','1289406',1,NULL,'Its lurid violence may put off some viewers, but Harry Brown is a vigilante thriller that carries an emotional as well as a physical punch, thanks to a gripping performance from Michael Caine in the title role.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/63/11166310_mob.jpg'),(348,'The Beaver',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_beaver_2010/','771188157','1321860',1,'Jodie Foster directs and co-stars with Mel Gibson in The Beaver - an emotional story about a man on a journey to re-discover his family and re-start his life. Plagued by his own demons, Walter Black was once a successful toy executive and family man who now suffers from depression. No matter what he tries, Walter can\'t seem to get himself back on track...until a beaver hand puppet enters his life. -- (C) Summit','Jodie Foster\'s visual instincts and Mel Gibson\'s all-in performance sell this earnest, straightforward movie.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/44/11154481_mob.jpg'),(349,'Monster\'s Ball',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/monsters_ball/','13368','0285742',1,NULL,'Somber and thought provoking, Monster\'s Ball has great performances all around.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/26/94/269411_mob.jpg'),(350,'The Way Back',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the-way-back/','770805055','1023114',1,'Directed by six-time Academy Award (R) nominee Peter Weir, THE WAY BACK is an epic story of survival, solidarity and indomitable human will. Shot in Bulgaria, Morocco and India, the film stars Jim Sturgess (Across the Universe, The Other Boleyn Girl), Ed Harris (Appaloosa) and Colin Farrell (In Bruges) as prisoners of a Soviet Union labor camp, who, along with four others, flee their Siberian Gulag and begin a treacherous journey across thousands of miles of hostile terrain. Academy Award (R) nominee Saoirse Ronan (Atonement, The Lovely Bones) and Mark Strong (Body of Lies, RocknRolla) co-star. Written by Weir and Keith Clarke, the film is Peter\'s first since 2003\'s Master and Commander: The Far Side of the World. It is inspired by the acclaimed book The Long Walk: The True Story of a Trek to Freedom, as well as first-person accounts and anecdotes as told to, and researched by Weir and executive producer Clarke. Produced by Joni Levin, Peter Weir, Duncan Henderson (Master and Commander: The Far Side of the World) and Nigel Sinclair (Terminator 3: Salvation), THE WAY BACK is an Exclusive Media Group, National Geographic Entertainment and ImageNation Abu Dhabi presentation and an Exclusive Films production. Keith Clarke, John Ptak, Guy East, Simon Oakes, Tobin Armbrust, Jake Eberts, Edward Borgerding, Mohamed Khalaf, Adam Leipzig, Scott Rudin and Jonathan Schwartz are Executive Producers. The film\'s Co-Producer is Roee Sharon Peled and Co-Executive Producer is Alex Brunner. Weir has assembled an accomplished group of filmmakers with whom he has previously collaborated, including Academy Award (R) winning Director of Photography Russell Boyd (Master and Commander, The Year of Living Dangerously, Gallipoli), Film Editor Lee Smith (Master and Commander, as well as The Dark Knight, for which he received an Academy Award (R) nomination), Production Designer John Stoddart (Fearless, The Mosquito Coast) and Costume Designer Wendy Stites, Oscar (R) nominated for Master and Commander and with credits on nine Weir films. -- (C) New Market Films','It isn\'t as emotionally involving as it should be, but this Peter Weir epic offers sweeping ambition and strong performances to go with its grand visual spectacle.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/42/11154273_mob.jpg'),(351,'Diary of a Mad Black Woman',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/diary_of_a_mad_black_woman/','10158','0422093',1,NULL,'Tyler Perry\'s successful play can\'t make the move to the screen; this mix of slapstick, melodrama and spirituality lacks a consistent tone.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/08/10880856_mob.jpg'),(352,'Butch Cassidy and the Sundance Kid',1969,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1003318-butch_cassidy_and_the_sundance_kid/','10096','0064115',1,NULL,'With its iconic pairing of Paul Newman and Robert Redford, jaunty screenplay and Burt Bacharach score, Butch Cassidy and the Sundance Kid has gone down as among the defining moments in late-\'60s American cinema.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/49/11164965_mob.jpg'),(353,'Bratz: The Movie',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bratz_the_movie/','753995734','0804452',1,NULL,'Full of mixed messages and dubious role-models, Bratz is too shallow even for its intended audience.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/89/45/26/8945261_mob.jpg'),(354,'Boys Don\'t Cry',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/boys_dont_cry/','13339','0171804',1,NULL,'Hilary Swank\'s acclaimed performance pays fitting tribute to the tragic life of Brandon Teena.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/49/11164993_mob.jpg'),(355,'The Bodyguard',1992,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1042108-bodyguard/','98813492','0103855',1,NULL,'The Bodyguard is a cheesy, melodramatic potboiler with occasional moments of electricity from Whitney Houston.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/79/11167935_mob.jpg'),(356,'Nowhere Boy',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nowhere_boy/','770817089','1266029',1,'The true story of John Lennon\'s troubled childhood and difficult relationship with his family is brought to the screen in this period drama. Young John (Alex Ambrose) is a bright but sharp-tongued boy living in the coastal town of Liverpool during the 1950s with his aunt Mimi (Kristin Scott Thomas) and uncle George (David Threlfall). John\'s father walked out on the family when he was four years old, and the boy was given to Mimi to raise, even though his mother, Julia (Anne-Marie Duff), was still alive. While Mimi\'s straight-laced nature runs counter to John\'s more reckless personality, they clearly love one another and the household is thrown into chaos when George dies suddenly. At the funeral, teenage John (now played by Aaron Johnson) sees Julia, and learns to his surprise that she lives only a few blocks away from Mimi. John pays her a visit, and Julia gratefully welcomes him back into her life. Julia\'s personality is a much closer fit to John than Mimi, and she encourages his love for writing and music, teaching him to play the banjo. However, John\'s renewed relationship with Julia brings up a number of unanswered questions, and causes new tensions between Mimi and John. And as rock & roll becomes the hot new sound of the day, John falls in love with the bold new music and makes a friend who is interested in forming a band, Paul (Thomas Brodie Sangster). The first feature film from artist-turned-director Sam Taylor-Wood, Nowhere Boy was the closing night attraction at the 2009 BFI London Film Festival. ~ Mark Deming, Rovi','Don\'t expect any musical insights, but this look at John Lennon\'s early life benefits from its restrained, low-key approach and some fine acting from Aaron Johnson.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/53/11155328_mob.jpg'),(357,'Conviction',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/conviction_2010/','771201459','1244754',1,'CONVICTION is the inspirational true story of a sister\'s unwavering devotion to her brother. When Betty Anne Waters\' (two-time Academy Award winner Hilary Swank) older brother Kenny (Sam Rockwell) is arrested for murder and sentenced to life in 1983, Betty Anne, a Massachusetts wife and mother of two, dedicates her life to overturning the murder conviction. Convinced that her brother is innocent, Betty Anne puts herself through high school, college and, finally, law school in an 18 year quest to free Kenny. With the help of best friend Abra Rice (Academy Award nominee Minnie Driver), Betty Anne pores through suspicious evidence mounted by small town cop Nancy Taylor (Academy Award nominee Melissa Leo), meticulously retracing the steps that led to Kenny\'s arrest. Belief in her brother - and her quest for the truth - pushes Betty Anne and her team to uncover the facts and utilize DNA evidence with the hope of exonerating Kenny. -- (C) Fox Searchlight','Less compelling -- and more manipulative -- than it should be, Conviction benefits from its compelling true story and a pair of solid performances from Swank and Rockwell.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/13/77/11137760_mob.jpg'),(358,'Le Pacte des loups (Brotherhood of the Wolf)',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/brotherhood_of_the_wolf/','13211','0237534',1,NULL,'Brotherhood of the Wolf mixes its genres with little logic, but the end result is wildly entertaining.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/12/59/11125953_mob.jpg'),(359,'Ong-Bak (Ong Bak: Muay Thai Warrior)',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ongbak/','12874','0368909',1,NULL,'While Ong-Bak: The Thai Warrior may be no great shakes as a movie, critics are hailing the emergence of a new star in Tony Jaa, whose athletic performance is drawing comparisons with Bruce Lee, Jackie Chan, and Jet Li.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/69/266994_mob.jpg'),(360,'The Notorious Bettie Page',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/notorious_betty_page/','147302894','0404802',1,NULL,'This biopic only skims the surface of Bettie Page\'s life, leaving her as a cipher, and additionally fails to place her iconic status in historical context.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/93/59/10935954_mob.jpg'),(361,'Gentlemen Prefer Blondes',1953,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/gentlemen_prefer_blondes/','18528','0045810',1,NULL,'Anchored by Marilyn Monroe and Jane Russell\'s sparkling magnetism, Gentlemen Prefer Blondes is a delightfully entertaining 1950s musical.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/48/11164896_mob.jpg'),(362,'The Wind That Shakes the Barley',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wind_that_shakes_the_barley/','243241044','0460989',1,NULL,'Bleak and uncompromising, but director Ken Loach brightens his film with gorgeous cinematography and tight pacing, and features a fine performance from Cillian Murphy.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/84/04/10840436_mob.jpg'),(363,'Better Off Dead',1985,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1002213-better_off_dead/','10107','0088794',1,NULL,'Better Off Dead is an anarchic mix of black humor and surreal comedy, anchored by John Cusack\'s winsome, charming performance.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/84/19/10841913_mob.jpg'),(364,'Red Cliff (Chi Bi)',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/red_cliff/','770673136','0425637',1,NULL,'Featuring some impressively grand battlefield action, John Woo returns to Asia and returns to form in the process for this lavish and slick historical epic.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/92/60/10926027_mob.jpg'),(365,'Blast from the Past',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/blast_from_the_past/','10388','0124298',1,NULL,'Cute idea, but not consistently funny.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/55/255505_mob.jpg'),(366,'Efter brylluppet (After the Wedding)',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/after_the_wedding/','394295012','0457655',1,NULL,'The cast brings After the Wedding\'s melodramatic script to life, creating a movie that is emotionally raw and satisfying.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/55/32/40/5532400_mob.jpg'),(367,'Exorcist - The Beginning',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/exorcist_the_beginning/','13326','0204313',1,NULL,'A mediocre, gory horror film, nowhere near the quality of the 1973 original.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/90/81/10908123_mob.jpg'),(368,'December Boys',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/december_boys/','561430319','0465436',1,NULL,'December Boys\' location and settings are invitingly gorgeous, but the coming-of-age drama that takes place on them is uneventful and far too sentimental.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/95/16/76/9516766_mob.jpg'),(369,'Bernie',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bernie_2011/','771205924','1704573',1,'In the tiny, rural town of Carthage, TX, assistant funeral director Bernie Tiede was one of the town\'s most beloved residents. He taught Sunday school, sang in the church choir and was always willing to lend a helping hand. Everyone loved and appreciated Bernie, so it came as no surprise when he befriended Marjorie Nugent, an affluent widow who was as well known for her sour attitude as her fortune. Bernie frequently traveled with Marjorie and even managed her banking affairs. Marjorie quickly became fully dependent on Bernie and his generosity and Bernie struggled to meet her increasing demands. Bernie continued to handle her affairs, and the townspeople went months without seeing Marjorie. The people of Carthage were shocked when it was reported that Marjorie Nugent had been dead for some time, and Bernie Tiede was being charged with the murder. -- (C) Official Site','Richard Linklater\'s Bernie is a gently told and unexpectedly amusing true-crime comedy that benefits from an impressive performance by Jack Black.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/39/11163932_mob.jpg'),(370,'North by Northwest',1959,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/north-by-northwest/','18639','0053125',1,NULL,'Gripping, suspenseful, and visually iconic, this late-period Hitchcock classic laid the groundwork for countless action thrillers to follow.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/80/11168082_mob.jpg'),(371,'Riding in Cars with Boys',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/riding_in_cars_with_boys/','11198','0200027',1,NULL,'Riding in Cars With Boys suffers from mixing grit and pathos with cuteness and comedy. Ironically, many critics found Zahn\'s character more compelling and three-dimensional than Barrymore\'s.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/92/19/10921973_mob.jpg'),(372,'Before Sunset',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/before_sunset/','12908','0381681',1,NULL,'Filled with engaging dialogue, Before Sunset is a witty, poignant romance, with natural chemistry between Hawke and Delpy.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/59/94/32/5994322_mob.jpg'),(373,'Kinky Boots',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kinky_boots/','147302873','0434124',1,NULL,'Kinky Boots relies heavily on the Full Monty formula of Britcoms, while playing it too safe in a desperate attempt not to offend. Ejiofor\'s performance is its redeeming virtue.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/31/40/314003_mob.jpg'),(374,'District B13 (Banlieue 13)',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/district_b13/','170571851','0414852',1,NULL,'A nonstop thrill ride, District B13\'s dizzying action sequences more than make up for any expository flaws.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/90/90/10909056_mob.jpg'),(375,'Conan the Barbarian',1982,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/conan_the_barbarian/','16016','0082198',1,NULL,'Though Conan may take itself too seriously for some, this adventure film about a former slave seeking vengeance is full of quotable Schwarzenegger lines and gritty action.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/88/11168862_mob.jpg'),(376,'Beasts of the Southern Wild',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beasts_of_the_southern_wild/','771267232','2125435',1,'In a forgotten but defiant bayou community cut off from the rest of the world by a sprawling levee, a six-year-old girl exists on the brink of orphanhood. Buoyed by her childish optimism and extraordinary imagination, she believes that the natural world is in balance with the universe until a fierce storm changes her reality. Desperate to repair the structure of her world in order to save her ailing father and sinking home, this tiny hero must learn to survive unstoppable catastrophes of epic proportions. -- (C) Fox Searchlight','Beasts of the Southern Wild is a fantastical, emotionally powerful journey and a strong case of filmmaking that values imagination over money.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/45/11164596_mob.jpg'),(377,'Three Men and a Baby (3 Men and a Baby)',1987,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/three_men_and_a_baby/','10716','0094137',1,NULL,'The American remake of the popular French comedy mostly works a charm under the combined talents of the three leads, who play nicely against type -- although forced plot elements and sentimentality at times dampen the fun.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/71/257115_mob.jpg'),(378,'Anonyma - Eine Frau in Berlin (A Woman in Berlin)',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1213891-woman_in_berlin/','770797149','1035730',1,NULL,'With a powerful lead performance by star Nina Hoss, A Woman in Berlin sheds a light on the moral complications of war.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/87/58/10875835_mob.jpg'),(379,'Crazy/ Beautiful',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crazy-beautiful/','10896','0250224',1,NULL,'The story is not new, but the film gets credit for trying to move away from the genre\'s cliches. Kirsten Dunst and newcomer Jay Hernandez give believable performances.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/80/258012_mob.jpg'),(380,'Big Mommas: Like Father, Like Son',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/big_mommas_like_father_like_son_2011/','771228966','1464174',1,'Martin Lawrence reprises the role of FBI agent Malcolm Turner -- aka, undercover grandma Big Momma -- in this installment in the Big Momma\'s House franchise, Big Mommas: Like Father, Like Son. Malcolm\'s latest assignment teams him up with his teenage stepson, Trent (Brandon T. Jackson), who unwittingly makes himself a target when he witnesses a murder. In order to keep Trent out of harm\'s way and solve the case behind the killing that Trent saw, the two have no choice but to go undercover at an all-girls performing arts school, with Malcolm posing as the titular rotund old lady, Big Momma, and Trent dressing up as a heavy female student named Charmaine. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Unnecessary, unfunny, and generally unwelcome, Big Mommas: Like Father, Like Son offers more of the same for fans of Martin Lawrence\'s perplexingly popular series.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/53/11155303_mob.jpg'),(381,'Dead Alive (Braindead)',1992,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dead_alive/','17021','0103873',1,NULL,'The delightfully gonzo tale of a lovestruck teen and his zombified mother, Dead Alive is extremely gory and exceedingly good fun, thanks to Peter Jackson\'s affection for the tastelessly sublime.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/28/59/285900_mob.jpg'),(382,'Agent Cody Banks 2 - Destination London',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/agent_cody_banks_2_destination_london/','11224','0358349',1,NULL,'Young kids may find this London adventure fun, but older kids may find it too simplistic.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/87/57/10875718_mob.jpg'),(383,'Sling Blade',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sling_blade/','13636','0117666',1,NULL,'You will see what\'s coming, but the masterful performances, especially Thornton\'s, will leave you riveted.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/93/85/10938549_mob.jpg'),(384,'Black Sheep',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/black_sheep/','647845018','0779982',1,NULL,'With an outrageous premise played completely straight, Black Sheep is a violent, grotesque, and very funny movie that takes B-movie lunacy to a delirious extreme.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/58/07/67/5807672_mob.jpg'),(385,'Blue Streak',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/blue_streak/','11223','0181316',1,NULL,'Martin Lawrence lends his comedic touch, but the movie isn\'t much more than standard action-comedy fare.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/86/76/10867638_mob.jpg'),(386,'Mad Max Beyond Thunderdome',1985,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mad_max_beyond_thunderdome/','10815','0089530',1,NULL,'Beyond Thunderdome deepens the Mad Max character without sacrificing the amazing vehicle choreography and stunts that made the originals memorable.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/83/10888321_mob.jpg'),(387,'Beowulf & Grendel',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beowulf_and_grendel/','144477599','0402057',1,NULL,'Despite the impressive Icelandic scenery, Beowulf And Grendel fails to find its footing in the transition from epic tale to the big screen.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/31/37/313724_mob.jpg'),(388,'Bad News Bears',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bad_news_bears/','1970',NULL,1,NULL,'This too-faithful remake aims low for laughs, turning off the easily offendable; despite another lovably irascible contribution by Thornton, it lacks the ensemble strength and originality of the 1976 version.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168924_mob.jpg'),(389,'Black Book (Zwartboek)',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10007417-black_book/','337767239','0389557',1,NULL,'A furious mix of sex, violence, and moral relativism, Black Book is shamelessly entertaining melodrama.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/92/04/10920443_mob.jpg'),(390,'Big Trouble in Little China',1986,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/big_trouble_in_little_china/','11742','0090728',1,NULL,'Brimming with energy and packed with humor, Big Trouble in Little China distills kung fu B-movies as affectionately as it subverts them.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/47/11164784_mob.jpg'),(391,'Bullitt',1968,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bullitt/','10058','0062765',1,NULL,'Steve McQueen is cool as ice in this thrilling police procedural that also happens to contain the arguably greatest car chase ever.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/80/11168022_mob.jpg'),(392,'Varsity Blues',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/varsity_blues/','13150','0139699',1,NULL,'This is a predictable football movie that lacks intensity.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/83/268322_mob.jpg'),(393,'Little Black Book',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/little_black_book/','11157','0361841',1,NULL,'An obnoxious, awkward mix of romantic comedy and reality show satire.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/92/04/10920448_mob.jpg'),(394,'Barbershop 2 - Back in Business',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/barbershop_2_back_in_business/','10839','0337579',1,NULL,'The humor is less sharp and more warm-hearted this time around, and the characters are enjoyable to revisit.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/86/73/10867301_mob.jpg'),(395,'Waltz with Bashir',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/waltz_with_bashir/','770770030','1185616',1,NULL,'A wholly innovative, original, and vital history lesson, with pioneering animation, Waltz With Bashir delivers its message about the Middle East in a mesmerizing fashion.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/87/22/10872286_mob.jpg'),(396,'Bitch Slap',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10010153-bitch_slap/','770783512','1212974',1,'A sex-bomb, a psycho-slut, and a stripper find their attempt to extort a powerful underworld kingpin spiraling out of control in this outrageous homage to the exploitation films of yesteryear. They thought it was a foolproof plan, but these three bad girls are about to see just how bad things can get when the truth comes out, allegiances start to shift, and other desperate criminals attempt to muscle in on the take. Later, the stakes are raised when it\'s revealed that the entire plan was a setup. With the fate of the world resting in their not-so-delicate hands, these three violent beauties are about to discover that everything they thought they knew about the job is wrong, and that their may be an extraterrestrial invader lurking in their midst. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/49/11164990_mob.jpg'),(397,'Boy A',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/boy-a/','770677844','1078188',1,NULL,'Small in scale but large in impact, Boy A\'s career making performances (particularly that by star Andrew Garfield) and carefully crafted characters defy judgment and aggressively provoke debate.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/85/07/10850786_mob.jpg'),(398,'Tyler Perry\'s Madea\'s Big Happy Family',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tyler_perrys_madeas_big_happy_family/','771200179','1787759',1,'Adapted from the multi-talented playwright/filmmaker\'s hit stage play of the same name, Tyler Perry\'s Madea\'s Big Happy Family finds the cantankerous family matriarch using her unique brand of tough love to help her family weather some particularly rough waters. Madea\'s niece Shirley has received a frightening medical diagnosis, and she\'s having a hard time figuring out how to break the news to the rest of the family. Unfortunately she\'s not the only one in the midst of a crisis, either: Kimberly is suffering from anger issues that are threatening to destroy her marriage; Tammy\'s marital problems are being compounded by her disobedient children; and Byron is struggling to stay out of the drug trade after spending two years behind bars. Later, as a skeleton in the family closet pops into the picture, Madea and Aunt Bam show that love and laugher can help to overcome even the biggest obstacles. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/57/11155734_mob.jpg'),(399,'A Bronx Tale',1993,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bronx_tale/','12976','0106489',1,NULL,'A Bronx Tale sets itself apart from other coming-of-age dramas thanks to a solid script, a terrific cast, and director Robert De Niro\'s sensitive work behind the camera.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/62/10886213_mob.jpg'),(400,'The Bridge on the River Kwai',1957,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bridge_on_the_river_kwai/','11175','0050212',1,NULL,'This complex war epic asks hard questions, resists easy answers, and boasts career-defining work from star Alec Guinness and director David Lean.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/92/73/10927333_mob.jpg'),(401,'Bubba Ho-Tep',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bubba_hotep/','13048','0281686',1,NULL,'The best movie to star both the King and JFK.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/55/37/46/5537469_mob.jpg'),(402,'Good Bye, Lenin',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/good_bye_lenin/','13051','0301357',1,NULL,'Funny and poignant social critique of German reunification.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/26/78/267825_mob.jpg'),(403,'Batman: Mask Of The Phantasm',1993,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/batman_mask_of_the_phantasm/','10719','0106364',1,NULL,'Stylish and admirably respectful of the source material, Batman: Mask of the Phantasm succeeds where many of the live-action Batman adaptations have failed.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/29/11152982_mob.jpg'),(404,'To Rome with Love',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/to_rome_with_love/','771240265','1859650',1,'To Rome with Love is a kaleidoscopic comedy movie set in one of the world\'s most enchanting cities. The film brings us into contact with a well-known American architect reliving his youth; an average middle-class Roman who suddenly finds himself Rome\'s biggest celebrity; a young provincial couple drawn into separate romantic encounters; and an American opera director endeavoring to put a singing mortician on stage. -- (C) Sony Pictures Classics','To Rome With Love sees Woody Allen cobbling together an Italian postcard of farce, fantasy, and comedy with only middling success.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/51/11165143_mob.jpg'),(405,'October Baby',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/october_baby_2011/','771258769','1720182',1,'As the curtain rises, Hannah hesitantly steps onto the stage for her theatrical debut in college. Yet before her first lines, she collapses. Countless medical tests all point to one underlying factor: Hannah\'s difficult birth. This revelation is nothing compared to discovering that she was actually adopted . . . after a failed abortion attempt. Bewildered, angered and confused, Hannah embarks on a journey with Jason, her oldest friend. In the midst of her incredible journey to discover her hidden past and find hope for her unknown future, Hannah sees that life can be so much more than what you have planned. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/40/11164083_mob.jpg'),(406,'Beauty Shop',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1139289-beauty_shop/','17968','0388500',1,NULL,'Despite a strong performance by Queen Latifah, Beauty Shop is in need of some style pointers.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/31/29/312911_mob.jpg'),(407,'Kauboi Bibappu: Tengoku no Tobira (Cowboy Bebop the Movie: Knockin\' on Heaven\'s Door)',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cowboy_bebop_the_movie/','13218','0275277',1,NULL,'This may be strictly for anime junkies, but they\'ll find much to like about Cowboy Bebop\'s casual violence and cool dialogue.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/12/73/11127322_mob.jpg'),(408,'Battle in Seattle',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/battle_in_seattle/','770676275','0850253',1,NULL,'Well intentioned and passionate, this docu-drama about the 1999 WTO protests draws stronger political assertions than it does strong characters.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/88/11168858_mob.jpg'),(409,'Risky Business',1983,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1017641-risky_business/','13296','0086200',1,NULL,'Featuring one of Tom Cruise\'s best early performances, Risky Business is a sharp, funny examination of teen angst that doesn\'t stop short of exploring dark themes.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/80/11168031_mob.jpg'),(410,'Barton Fink',1991,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/barton_fink/','13030','0101410',1,NULL,'Twisty and unsettling, the Coen brothers\' satirical tale of a 1940s playwright struggling with writer\'s block is packed with their trademark sense of humor and terrific performances from its cast.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/49/11164985_mob.jpg'),(411,'Attack the Block',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/attack_the_block/','771203801','1478964',1,'From the producers of Shaun of the Dead and Hot Fuzz, Attack the Block follows a gang of tough inner-city kids who try to defend their turf against an invasion of savage alien creatures, turning a South London apartment complex into an extraterrestrial warzone. -- (C) Sony Pictures','Effortlessly mixing scares, laughs, and social commentary, Attack the Block is a thrilling, brisky-paced sci-fi yarn with a distinctly British flavor.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/70/11157065_mob.jpg'),(412,'My Blueberry Nights',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/my_blueberry_nights/','647674465','0765120',1,NULL,'Though well filmed, My Blueberry Nights is a mixed bag of dedicated performers working with thin material.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/84/94/10849415_mob.jpg'),(413,'Ong Bak 2',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10011457-ong_bak_2_2009/','770782720','0785035',1,NULL,'It suffers from comparisons to its predecessor -- not to mention Tony Jaa\'s less-than-nimble direction -- but Ong Bak 2 has all the extravagant violence and playful style that fans of the original will expect.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/91/03/10910324_mob.jpg'),(414,'Won\'t Back Down',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wont_back_down_2012/','771252918','1870529',1,'Maggie Gyllenhaal and Viola Davis play two determined mothers, one a teacher, who will stop at nothing to transform their children\'s failing inner city school. Facing a powerful and entrenched bureaucracy, they risk everything to make a difference in the education and future of their children. This powerful story of parenthood, friendship and courage mirrors events that are making headlines daily. -- (C) 20th Century Fox','Despite the best efforts of its talented leads, Won\'t Back Down fails to lend sufficient dramatic heft or sophistication to the hot-button issue of education reform.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/80/11168037_mob.jpg'),(415,'Broken Embraces',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/broken_embraces/','770770202','0913425',1,NULL,'Pedro Almodovar\'s fourth film with Penelope Cruz isn\'t his finest work, but he brings his signature visual brilliance to this noirish tale, and the cast turns in some first-class performances.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/94/29/10942909_mob.jpg'),(416,'Zatoichi (The Blind Swordsman: Zatoichi)',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/zatoichi_2003/','113352729','0363226',1,NULL,'Colorful, rich with action and wonderfully choreographed, Takeshi Kitano takes on the classic samurai character with his own brand of cinematic flair.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/60/97/609777_mob.jpg'),(417,'The Big Year',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_big_year/','771225768','1053810',1,'Steve Martin, Jack Black and Owen Wilson are at a crossroads -- one is experiencing a mid-life crisis, another a late-life crisis, and the third, a far from ordinary no-life crisis. From David Frankel, the director of The Devil Wears Prada and Marley & Me, comes a sophisticated comedy about three friendly rivals who, tired of being ruled by obligations and responsibilities, dedicate a year of their lives to following their dreams. Their big year takes them on a cross-country journey of wild and life-changing adventures. -- (C) 20th Century Fox','Though made with care and affection for its characters, The Big Year plods along, rarely reaching any comedic heights.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/03/11160380_mob.jpg'),(418,'The Boys Are Back',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1208165-boys_are_back/','770807582','0926380',1,NULL,'Great performances by Clive Owen and The Boys save this melodrama from entering into the sappy territory it might have in less competent hands.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/89/61/10896175_mob.jpg'),(419,'Beginners',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beginners/','771208735','1532503',1,'Beginners imaginatively explores the hilarity, confusion, and surprises of love through the evolving consciousness of Oliver (Ewan McGregor). Oliver meets the irreverent and unpredictable Anna (Melanie Laurent) only months after his father Hal (Christopher Plummer) has passed away. This new love floods Oliver with memories of his father who - following 44 years of marriage - came out of the closet at age 75 to live a full, energized, and wonderfully tumultuous gay life. The upheavals of Hal\'s new honesty, by turns funny and moving, brought father and son closer than they\'d ever been able to be. Now Oliver endeavors to love Anna with all the bravery, humor, and hope that his father taught him. -- (c) IFC','Wearing its twee heart on its sleeve, Beginners explores the depths of modern, multi-generational romance with wit and depth.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/73/11157346_mob.jpg'),(420,'The Bride of Frankenstein',1935,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bride_of_frankenstein/','20645','0026138',1,NULL,'An eccentric, campy, technically impressive, and frightening picture, James Whale\'s Bride of Frankenstein has aged remarkably well.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/30/28/302822_mob.jpg'),(421,'Brooklyn Rules',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/brooklyn_rules/','287865067','0283503',1,NULL,'Brooklyn Rules\' premise is old hat now, but strong performances from Alec Baldwin and the supporting cast are reasons enough to watch.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/61/97/79/6197796_mob.jpg'),(422,'Brick Lane',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/brick_lane/','770677124','0940585',1,NULL,'Frustratingly slow-moving, but ultimately saved by Chatterjee\'s solid acting and Gavron\'s gentle patience.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/90/33/10903312_mob.jpg'),(423,'Brideshead Revisited',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/brideshead_revisited/','770682219','0412536',1,NULL,'Suspenseful and beautifully mounted, Brideshead Revisited does an able job condensing Evelyn Waugh\'s novel.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/12/50/11125009_mob.jpg'),(424,'The History Boys',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/history_boys/','349219108','0464049',1,NULL,'While not quite having the impact of its original stage version, The History Boys nevertheless is a witty and involving school drama.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/31/75/25/3175255_mob.jpg'),(425,'Born To Be Wild',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/born_to_be_wild_2011/','771220733','1680059',1,'Born to be Wild 3D is an inspired story of love, dedication and the remarkable bond between humans and animals. This film documents orphaned orangutans and elephants and the extraordinary people who rescue and raise them-saving endangered species one life at a time. Captured in IMAX 3D, Born to be Wild is a heartwarming adventure transporting moviegoers into the lush rainforests of Borneo with world-renowned primatologist Dr. Birute Galdikas, and across the rugged Kenyan savannah with celebrated elephant authority Dame Daphne Sheldrick, as they and their teams rescue, rehabilitate and return these incredible animals back to the wild.-- (C) Warner Bros','The human story of Born To Be Wild is captivating and the accompanying nature footage is utterly cute and charming.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/43/11164339_mob.jpg'),(426,'Der Baader Meinhof Komplex (The Baader Meinhof Complex)',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/baader_meinhof_complex/','770783522','0765432',1,NULL,'Intricately researched and impressively authentic slice of modern German History, with a terrific cast, assured direction, and a cracking script.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/17/10891797_mob.jpg'),(427,'Murder by Numbers',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1113638-murder_by_numbers/','15357',NULL,1,NULL,'A predictable police procedural that works better as a character study rather than a thriller.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/27/90/279020_mob.jpg'),(428,'Broken English',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/broken_english/','528343842','0772157',1,NULL,'Though Broken English eventually settles into basic rom-com territory, it\'s pleasant and good-natured, and Parker Posey is spellbinding throughout the movie.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/86/10888655_mob.jpg'),(429,'Izgnanie (The Banishment)',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_banishment/','770678101','0488905',1,NULL,'Beautifully shot, but ultimately disappointing, lumbering sophomore effort from Russian potential great Andrey Zvyagintsev.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/28/45/10284532_mob.jpg'),(430,'Wonder Boys',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wonder_boys/','13257','0185014',1,NULL,'Michael Douglas and Tobey Maguire do wonders in this clever dark comedy.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/88/268894_mob.jpg'),(431,'Biutiful',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/biutiful/','770807659','1164999',1,'Biutiful is a love story between a father and his children. This is the journey of Uxbal, a conflicted man who struggles to reconcile fatherhood, love, spirituality, crime, guilt and mortality amidst the dangerous underworld of modern Barcelona. His livelihood is earned out of bounds, his sacrifices for his children know no bounds. Like life itself, this is a circular tale that ends where it begins. As fate encircles him and thresholds are crossed, a dim, redemptive road brightens, illuminating the inheritances bestowed from father to child, and the paternal guiding hand that navigates life\'s corridors, whether bright, bad - or biutiful. -- (C) Roadside Attractions','Javier Bardem\'s searing performance helps to elevate Biutiful, as does Alejandro Gonzalez Inarritu\'s craftsmanship, but the film often lapses into contrivance and grimness.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/36/11153671_mob.jpg'),(432,'The Triplets of Belleville',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_triplets_of_belleville/','10128',NULL,1,NULL,'Richly detailed and loaded with surreal touches, The Triplets of Belleville is an odd, delightful charmer.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/13/26/11132682_mob.jpg'),(433,'Bowfinger',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bowfinger/','11228','0131325',1,NULL,'A witty commentary on modern film-making, with enough jokes to keep it entertaining throughout.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/55/09/68/5509686_mob.jpg'),(434,'Baby Boy',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/baby_boy/','13883','0255819',1,NULL,'Preachy and repetitive in parts, Baby Boy still manages to exude authenticity, thanks to its competent cast.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/27/19/271920_mob.jpg'),(435,'Burke and Hare',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/burke_and_hare/','771019339','1320239',1,'From John Landis, the director of Animal House and The Blues Brothers, Burke & Hare is adark comedy/thriller staring Simon Pegg, Andy Serkis, Tom Wilkinson, Tim Curry and Isla Fisher as the unfortunate denizens of 19th century Edinburgh, a setting rife with murder, theft, prostitution, corpse snatching, experimental medicine, and of course Shakespeare. -- (C) IFC Films',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/90/11159075_mob.jpg'),(436,'Black Knight',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/black_knight/','12556','0265087',1,NULL,'Black Knight feels like a lazily constructed movie, filled with lame gags and constant mugging from Lawrence.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/48/11164899_mob.jpg'),(437,'The Air I Breathe',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_air_i_breahe/','493801965','0485851',1,NULL,'The Air I Breathe is a jumbled indie production that accomplishes little save for the squandering of a talented cast.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/84/03/10840357_mob.jpg'),(438,'Black Death',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/black_death-2010/','770859743','1181791',1,'The year is 1348. Europe has fallen under the shadow of the Black Death. As the plague decimates all in its path, fear and superstition are rife. In this apocalyptic environment, the church is losing its grip on the people. There are rumors of a village, hidden in marshland that the plague cannot reach. There is even talk of a necromancer who leads the village and is able to bring the dead back to life. Ulric (Sean Bean), a fearsome knight, is charged by the church to investigate these rumors. He enlists the guidance of a novice monk, Osmund (Eddie Redmayne) to lead him and his band of mercenary soldiers to the marshland, but Osmund has other motives for leaving his monastery. Their journey to the village and events that unfold take them into the heart of darkness and to horrors that will put Osmund\'s faith in himself and his love for God to the ultimate test. -- (C) Magnolia Releasing','Black Death delivers the fire and brimstone violence its subject matter warrants, while posing some interesting questions of faith and religion.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/45/11154592_mob.jpg'),(439,'Bandits',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bandits/','11099','0219965',1,NULL,'The story may not warrant its lengthy running time, but the cast of Bandits makes it an enjoyable ride.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/90/259014_mob.jpg'),(440,'The Birdcage',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/birdcage/','12915','0115685',1,NULL,'Mike Nichols wrangles agreeably amusing performances from Robin Williams and Nathan Lane in this fun, if not quite essential, remake of the French comedy La Cage aux Folles.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/26/71/267195_mob.jpg'),(441,'The Legend of Bagger Vance',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/legend_of_bagger_vance/','12753','0146984',1,NULL,'Despite the talent involved in The Legend of Bagger Vance, performances are hindered by an inadequate screenplay full of flat characters and bad dialogue. Also, not much happens, and some critics are offended by how the film glosses over issues of racism.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/64/266492_mob.jpg'),(442,'Simon Birch',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/simon_birch/','10305','0124879',1,NULL,'Overly mushy; tries too hard to pull at the heart-strings.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/50/255097_mob.jpg'),(443,'Invasion of the Body Snatchers',1978,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1010679-invasion_of_the_body_snatchers/','10738','0077745',1,NULL,'Employing gritty camerawork and evocative sound effects, Invasion of the Body Snatchers is a powerful remake that expands upon themes and ideas only lightly explored in the original.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/95/44/10954477_mob.jpg'),(444,'Bringing Up Baby',1938,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bringing_up_baby/','18219','0029947',1,NULL,'With Katharine Hepburn and Cary Grant at their effervescent best, Bringing Up Baby is a seamlessly assembled comedy with enduring appeal.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/00/11160044_mob.jpg'),(445,'Bucky Larson: Born to Be a Star',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bucky_larson_born_to_be_a_star/','771211554','1411664',1,'Bucky Larson: Born to Be a Star is a new comedy starring Nick Swardson, Christina Ricci, Don Johnson, and Stephen Dorff. Bucky (Swardson) is a small town grocery bagger, going nowhere in life - until he discovers that his conservative parents were once adult film stars! Armed with the belief that he has found his destiny, Bucky packs up and heads out to LA, hoping to follow in his parents\' footsteps. -- (C) Sony Pictures','A severely misguided and inept comedy incapable of even telling its single joke properly.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/84/11158443_mob.jpg'),(446,'Before Night Falls',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/before_night_falls/','13819','0247196',1,NULL,'An impressionistic, fragmented look at Reinaldo Arenas, Before Night Falls\' imagery manages to evoke a sense of the writer\'s artistry, and Bardem\'s strong performance holds the film together. Finally, a biopic done well.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/27/16/271614_mob.jpg'),(447,'The Life Before Her Eyes',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/life_before_her_eyes/','770682867','0815178',1,NULL,'Despite earnest performances, Life Before Her Eyes is a confusing, painfully overwrought melodrama.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/91/33/10913323_mob.jpg'),(448,'Barney\'s Version',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/barneys-version/','770856685','1423894',1,'This seriocomic adaptation of Mordecai Richler\'s award-winning 1997 novel stars Paul Giamatti as Barney Panofsky, who meets the great love of his life, Miriam (Rosamund Pike), at the most inopportune time imaginable: his marriage to his second wife (Minnie Driver), a wealthy Jewish princess and compulsive shopper. Narrated by Barney as a confessional, the film covers 30 years of his unusual journey -- from his first marriage to the chronically unfaithful free spirit Clara (Rachelle Lefevre) and their life in Italy together, through his third marriage to Miriam, with whom he has two children. Standing in the wings is Barney\'s father, Izzy (Dustin Hoffman), who continues to stick by him as his loyal right-hand man. Through it all, Barney experiences numerous highs and lows, but manages to consistently surprise everyone with unforeseen acts of altruism and kindness that turn him into the quintessential modern hero. ~ Nathan Southern, Rovi','With a magnificent performance by Paul Giamatti, Barney\'s Version offers much comedy and insight to the complexities of modern romance.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/44/11154466_mob.jpg'),(449,'Bel Ami',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bel_ami_2011/','771203135','1440732',1,'Bel Ami is the story of Georges Duroy, who travels through 1890s Paris, from cockroach ridden garrets to opulent salons, using his wits and powers of seduction to rise from poverty to wealth, from a prostitute\'s embrace to passionate trysts with wealthy beauties, in a world where politics and media jostle for influence, where sex is power and celebrity an obsession. -- (C) Magnolia','Bel Ami contains some soapy pleasures but it overall rushes through the narrative and suffers from a vague central performance by Robert Pattinson.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/42/11164254_mob.jpg'),(450,'Bella (Beauty)',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bella/','770673757','0482463',1,NULL,'Critics labeled Bella as a simplistic and mostly pedestrian, but positive word of mouth gave this tiny indie surprising theatrical legs.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/26/04/10260457_mob.jpg'),(451,'Bachelorette',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bachelorette/','771266282','1920849',1,'On the night before an old friend\'s wedding, three frisky bridesmaids go searching for a little fun but find much more than they bargained for. With lovely Becky (Rebel Wilson) set to marry her handsome sweetheart, Dale (Hayes MacArthur), the remaining members of her high school clique reunite for one last bachelorette bacchanal in the Big Apple. Regan (Kirsten Dunst) is an overachieving, ueber-Maid of Honor who\'s secretly smarting over the fact that she\'s not the first to marry, while Gena (Lizzy Caplan) is a whip-smart sarcastic who\'s actually a closet romantic, and Katie (Isla Fisher) is a ditzy beauty who loves the good life. But when Becky insists on keeping the bachelorette party tame, the women proceed with an after-hours celebration of their own. -- (C) Official Site','It has its moments, but Bachelorette ultimately plays it too safe with its trio of unlikable leads, betraying them with a predictably sentimental final act that undermines the bracingly honest humor preceding it.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/61/11166114_mob.jpg'),(452,'Beyond Borders',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beyond_borders/','14223','0294357',1,NULL,'Beyond Borders is good-intentioned, but the use of human suffering as a backdrop for a romance comes across as sanctimonious and exploitative.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/27/36/273605_mob.jpg'),(453,'Boiler Room',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1095081-boiler_room/','13037','0181984',1,NULL,'Its ending is disappointingly tidy, but Boiler Room boasts just enough sharp writing and brisk pacing to make getting there worthwhile.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/05/10870529_mob.jpg'),(454,'Born Into Brothels: Calcutta\'s Red Light Kids',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/born_into_brothels/','12896','0388789',1,NULL,'A powerful and uplifting documentary.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/93/23/10932362_mob.jpg'