2579',1,NULL,'Sentimental, slow, schmaltzy, and very satisfying, The Bridges of Madison County finds Clint Eastwood adapting a bestseller with heft, wit, and grace.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/45/11164516_mob.jpg'),(480,'Bad Taste',1987,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bad_taste/','17781','0092610',1,NULL,'Peter Jackson\'s early low-budget shocker boasts a disgusting premise - aliens harvesting humans for fast food - that gives the budding auteur plenty of room for gross-out visuals and absurd cleverness.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/14/76/11147638_mob.jpg'),(481,'Roll Bounce',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/roll_bounce/','7977',NULL,1,NULL,'Roll Bounce dazzles us with a classic late 1970\'s feel, but this coming of age film could have been more than just a spin around the roller rink.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/02/250201_mob.jpg'),(482,'My Boss\'s Daughter',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/my_bosss_daughter/','14918','0270980',1,NULL,'Offensive, incoherent, and ineptly acted and directed.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/92/22/10922280_mob.jpg'),(483,'Beauty and The Beast (La Belle et la bete)',1946,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1001902-beauty_and_the_beast/','21733',NULL,1,NULL,'With its magical optical effects and enchanting performances, Jean Cocteau\'s Beauty and the Beast remains the most surreal -- and soulful -- of the fairy tale\'s film adaptations.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/07/11160766_mob.jpg'),(484,'London Boulevard',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/london-boulevard/','770805054','1213648',1,'The directorial debut of William Monahan, the screenwriter of The Departed, London Boulevard follows an ex-con trying to make a fresh start in a relationship with a reclusive actress. A sexy, stylish gangster thriller bristling with wit and brutal intrigue, London Boulevard stars Colin Farrell and Keira Knightley as star-crossed lovers who run afoul of one of London\'s most vicious crime bosses. -- (C) IFC','In spite of its spotless pedigree and a strong sense of visual style, London Boulevard stumbles over its frenetic pace and crowded, cliched plot.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/10/11161027_mob.jpg'),(485,'Down to the Bone',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/down-to-the-bone/','9368','0363579',1,NULL,'A vivid portrayal of the effects of drug abuse that avoids cinematic cliches, Down to the Bone is a winning effort by first-time director Debra Granik and features a breakout performance by Vera Farmiga.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/06/250613_mob.jpg'),(486,'Seven Brides for Seven Brothers',1954,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/seven_brides_for_seven_brothers/','9937','0047472',1,NULL,'Buoyed by crowd-pleasing tunes and charming performances, Seven Brides for Seven Brothers makes a successful transition from Broadway to screen that\'s sure to please the whole family.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/80/10878085_mob.jpg'),(487,'Jumping the Broom',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jumping_the_broom/','771202934','1640484',1,'A collision of worlds when two African-American families from divergent socioeconomic backgrounds get together one weekend in Martha\'s Vineyard for a wedding. -- (C) Sony','Its heart is in the right place -- and so is its appealing cast -- but Jumping the Broom is ultimately too cliched and thinly written to recommend.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/65/11156590_mob.jpg'),(488,'The Best Years of Our Lives',1946,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/best_years_of_our_lives/','22292','0036868',1,NULL,'An engrossing look at the triumphs and travails of war veterans, The Best Years of Our Lives is concerned specifically with the aftermath of World War II, but its messages speak to the overall American experience.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/60/11156041_mob.jpg'),(489,'Badlands',1973,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1001577-badlands/','11145','0069762',1,NULL,'Terrence Malick\'s debut is a masterful slice of American cinema, rife with the visual poetry and measured performances that would characterize his work.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/07/11160769_mob.jpg'),(490,'Black Dynamite',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/black_dynamite/','770800373','1190536',1,NULL,'A loving and meticulous send-up of 1970s blaxsploitation movies, Black Dynamite is funny enough for the frat house and clever enough for film buffs.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/86/39/10863940_mob.jpg'),(491,'The Bad News Bears',1976,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1001567-bad_news_bears/','10308','0074174',1,NULL,'The Bad News Bears is rude, profane, and cynical, but shot through with honest, unforced humor, and held together by a deft, understated performance from Walter Matthau.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/87/82/10878251_mob.jpg'),(492,'Birth',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/birth/','75441611','0337876',1,NULL,'A well-mounted production is undermined by a muddled, absurd storyline of questionable taste.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/62/20/622045_mob.jpg'),(493,'The Art of Getting By',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_art_of_getting_by/','771225880','1645080',1,'The Art of Getting By stars Freddie Highmore (Finding Neverland, Charlie and the Chocolate Factory) as George, a lonely and fatalistic teen who\'s made it all the way to his senior year without ever having done a real day of work, who is befriended by Sally (Emma Roberts - Scream 4), a beautiful and complicated girl who recognizes in him a kindred spirit. -- (C) Fox Searchlight','A sitcom-level twee mess that bakes in the typical manic pixie dream girl and boring, withdrawn boy hero.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/74/11157427_mob.jpg'),(494,'Bonneville',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bonneville/','477786396','0487195',1,NULL,'The amazing cast of Bonneville is paired up with a basic, predictable script and lackluster direction.','http: