a parade of gross-out gags and sex jokes, while insulting and ogling women.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/60/10886079_mob.jpg'),(540,'Ba wang bie ji (Farewell My Concubine)',1993,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/farewell_to_my_concubine/','13016','0106332',1,NULL,'Chen Kaing\'s epic is grand in scope and presentation, and, bolstered by solid performances, the result is a film both horrifying and enthralling.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/59/10895913_mob.jpg'),(541,'The Wendell Baker Story',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the-wendell-baker-story/','358052215','0373445',1,NULL,'The Wendell Baker Story is a lackadaisical comedy of quirky characters and situations, but ultimately the lazy narrative bores instead of charms.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/12/10891277_mob.jpg'),(542,'Ballistic: Ecks vs. Sever',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ballistic_ecks_vs_sever/','14526','0308208',1,NULL,'A startlingly inept film, Ballistic: Ecks vs. Sever offers overblown, wall-to-wall action without a hint of wit, coherence, style, or originality.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/27/50/275024_mob.jpg'),(543,'Behind the Mask: The Rise of Leslie Vernon',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/behind_the_mask_the_rise_of_leslie_vernon/','377006855','0437857',1,NULL,'A smart mockumentary that presents a gory, funny, and obviously affectionate skewering of the slasher genre.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/33/48/96/3348960_mob.jpg'),(544,'Rumble in the Bronx',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/rumble_in_the_bronx/','14249','0113326',1,NULL,'An entertaining Jackie Chan stunt-fest in which the impressive action sequences overcome the low production value and by-the-numbers plot.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/62/10886212_mob.jpg'),(545,'Tomorrow, When the War Began',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tomorrow_when_the_war_began/','771040915','1456941',1,'Tomorrow When the War Began is a pulse-pounding action thriller that follows the journey of eight high school friends in an Australian coastal town whose lives are suddenly and violently upended by an invasion that no one saw coming. Caitlin Stasey stars as 17 year old Ellie Linton, a precocious teen who leads her best friends including Corrie (Rachel Hurd-Wood) and Kevin (Lincoln Lewis) to an isolated, deep in the woods camp site named \'Hell.\' Upon returning, they come to grips with the fact that their country has been overrun by a mysterious, invading army. When the hostile armed forces become alerted to the presence of the teenagers, Ellie and her friends, along with a new recruit (apathetic stoner Chris Lang, played by Andrew Ryan) - must band together to escape, outwit and strike back against the mysterious enemy that has seized control of the their town and imprisoned their friends and loved ones. -- (C) Freestyle','While the script isn\'t amazing and the story\'s race issues linger, this adaptation of John Marsden\'s book is an exciting, action-heavy adventure that should please fans of the series.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/35/11163595_mob.jpg'),(546,'Bottle Shock',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bottle_shock/','770678176','0914797',1,NULL,'Bottle Shock fails to properly utilize the inspiring true tale at its core, settling instead for an ordinary, plodding account.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/48/11164860_mob.jpg'),(547,'Boys and Girls',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/boys_and_girls/','10926','0204175',1,NULL,'Boys and Girls feels like a cheap rip-off of When Harry Met Sally. The predictable and stale story fails to engage.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/81/258191_mob.jpg'),(548,'Three Colors: White (Trzy kolory: Bialy) (Trois Couleurs: Blanc)',1994,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/white/','770804687','0111507',1,NULL,'Taking a lighter tone than the other films of the Three Colors trilogy, White is a witty, bittersweet comedy with heavier themes on its mind than one might at first realize.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/87/62/10876274_mob.jpg'),(549,'Bless the Child',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bless_the_child/','14457','0163983',1,NULL,'Bless the Child doesn\'t scare, but may provoke unintended laughter from audiences. It\'s basically a B-movie.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/27/47/274709_mob.jpg'),(550,'Being Elmo: A Puppeteer\'s Journey',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/being_elmo_a_puppeteers_journey/','771224157','1787660',1,'Beloved by children of all ages around the world, Elmo is an international icon. Few people know his creator, Kevin Clash, who dreamed of working with his idol, master puppeteer Jim Henson. Displaying his creativity and talent at a young age, Kevin ultimately found a home on Sesame Street. Narrated by Whoopi Goldberg, this documentary includes rare archival footage, interviews with Frank Oz, Rosie O\'Donnell, Cheryl Henson, Joan Ganz Cooney and others and offers a behind-the-scenes look at Sesame Street and the Jim Henson Workshop. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/06/11160655_mob.jpg'),(551,'The Bang Bang Club',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bang_bang_club/','770810669','1173687',1,'The Bang Bang Club is the true story of four young combat photographers bonded by friendship and their sense of purpose to tell the truth. They risk their lives and use their cameras to tell the world of the violence associated with the first free elections in post-Apartheid South Africa. Ryan Phillippe, Malin Akerman and Taylor Kitsch star in a film that explores the thrills, danger, and moral questions associated with exposing the truth. -- (C) tribeca',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/65/11156535_mob.jpg'),(552,'The Barbarian Invasions (Les Invasions barbares)',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/barbarian_invasions/','13669','0338135',1,NULL,'A moving and heart-felt film from director Denys Arcand.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/29/10882926_mob.jpg'),(553,'Tristram Shandy: A Cock and Bull Story',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tristram_shandy_a_cock_and_bull_story/','2847503','0423409',1,NULL,'Though Laurence Sterne\'s novel was considered more or less impossible to successfully adapt to film, director Michael Winterbottom has done it in Tristram Shandy: A Cock and Bull Story, by making movie about the making of the movie. Stars Steve Coogan and Rob Brydon add madcap, knowing performances to the mix, and the result is a fun, postmodern romp, before there was any modern romp to post.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/85/61/10856178_mob.jpg'),(554,'The Bay',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_bay_2012/','771240596','1713476',1,'Two million fish washed ashore. One thousand blackbirds dropped from the sky. On July 4, 2009 a deadly menace swept through the quaint seaside town of Claridge, Maryland, but the harrowing story of what happened that Independence Day has never been told - until now. The authorities believed they had buried the truth about the tragedy that claimed over 700 human lives. Now, three years later, a reporter has emerged with footage revealing the cover-up and an unimaginable killer: a mysterious parasitic outbreak. Told from the perspective of those who were there and saw what happened, The Bay unfolds over 24 hours though people\'s iPhones, Androids, 911 calls, web cams, and whatever else could be used to document the nightmare in Claridge. -- (C) Official Site','Barry Levinson\'s eco-horror flick cleverly utilizes familiar found-footage methods in service of a gruesome yet atmospheric chiller.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/66/11166679_mob.jpg'),(555,'Breakdown',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1077077-breakdown/','13916','0044445',1,NULL,'A brainy and suspenseful -- if somewhat uneven -- thriller.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/27/21/272107_mob.jpg'),(556,'Birthday Girl',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/birthday_girl/','14392','0188453',1,NULL,'Kidman shows her range in this quirky movie, but the shift in tone from romantic comedy to thriller may leave viewers unsatisfied.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/91/57/10915754_mob.jpg'),(557,'Tales from the Crypt Presents: Bordello of Blood',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tales_from_the_crypt_presents_bordello_of_blood/','14326','0117826',1,NULL,'Bordello of Blood is not as scary or funny as it thinks it is (or should\'ve been), and all of Dennis Miller\'s lines sound like castoffs from his stand-up material.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/79/10887978_mob.jpg'),(558,'Undercover Brother',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/undercover_brother/','11287','0279493',1,NULL,'Fast-paced and filled with racial gags, Undercover Brother serves up plenty of laughs and sharp satire.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/99/259924_mob.jpg'),(559,'Bright Star',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bright_star/','770768852','0810784',1,NULL,'Jane Campion\'s direction is as refined as her screenplay, and she gets the most out of her cast -- especially Abbie Cornish -- in this understated period drama.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/93/10889317_mob.jpg'),(560,'The Dangerous Lives of Altar Boys',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dangerous_lives_of_altar_boys/','14082',NULL,1,NULL,'The inter-cutting of animation by Spawn\'s creator, Todd McFarlane, doesn\'t always work, but the performances by the young actors capture the pains of growing up well.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/27/29/272914_mob.jpg'),(561,'Kumonosu Jo (Throne of Blood) (Macbeth)',1957,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/throne_of_blood/','17149','0050613',1,NULL,'A career high point for Akira Kurosawa -- and one of the best film adaptations of a Shakespeare play.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/28/65/286510_mob.jpg'),(562,'Black Mask',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/black_mask/','16644','0115693',1,NULL,'Stylish setting and masterfully choreographed fight scenes, but the story is low on credibility and high on excessive violence and gore.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/28/46/284617_mob.jpg'),(563,'Bad Ass',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bad_ass_2012/','771265739','1928330',1,'Decorated Vietnam hero Frank Vega returns home only to get shunned by society leaving him without a job or his high school sweetheart. It\'s not until forty years later when an incident on a commuter bus (where he protects an elderly black man from a pair of skin heads) makes him a local hero where he\'s suddenly celebrated once again. But his good fortune suddenly turns for the worse when his best friend Klondike is murdered and the police aren\'t doing anything about it. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/43/11164352_mob.jpg'),(564,'There Be Dragons',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/there_be_dragons/','770871572','1316616',1,'Tells the story of London-based investigative journalist Robert Torres (Dougray Scott), who visits Spain to research a book about Josemaria Escriva (Cox), the controversial founder of Opus Dei. But Robert hits a wall, both professionally and personally, when his most promising source-his own father, Manolo Torres (Bentley), turns out to be his least cooperative one. Robert begins to unearth his father\'s toxic secrets when he learns that Manolo was not only born in the same Spanish town as Josemaria, but that they were childhood friends and attended the same seminary. The two men take radically different paths in life, with Josemaria dedicating his life to his faith while Manolo is swept into the brutal and tumultuous Spanish Civil War. Manolo descends into a dangerous and jealous obsession when the beautiful Hungarian revolutionary Ildiko (Olga Kurylenko) doesn\'t return his affections and instead gives herself to the courageous military leader, Oriol (Rodrigo Santoro). As Robert continues to unearth the secrets of Josemaria\'s life and Manolo\'s mysterious anger, their overlapping journeys are revealed with the truths and sorrows of their past choices, which compels Manolo to confront his own secret with one last opportunity of forgiveness. -- (C) Samuel Goldwyn',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/53/11155324_mob.jpg'),(565,'The Fabulous Baker Boys',1989,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fabulous_baker_boys/','14192','0097322',1,NULL,'Its story is nothing special, but The Fabulous Baker Boys glows beneath luminous performances from its perfectly cast stars.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/27/34/273428_mob.jpg'),(566,'Tinker Bell and the Great Fairy Rescue',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tinker_bell_and_the_great_fairy_rescue/','771031477','1216515',1,'Disney fairy Tinker Bell is most well known as the friend and ally of Peter Pan, but in this CG adventure, we meet the pixie long before she knew Wendy or the Lost Boys. While summering in England, Tinker Bell meets her very first human, a little girl who believes in fairies, and who very much needs a friend. Tink may be small, but she soon learns that her big heart can help someone many times her size. ~ Cammila Albertson, Rovi',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/75/11157508_mob.jpg'),(567,'Dai-Nipponjin (Big Man Japan)',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dai_nipponjin/','770677563','0997147',1,NULL,'Hitoshi Matsumoto\'s indescribably odd mockumentary is undeniably inspired.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/91/43/10914329_mob.jpg'),(568,'Below',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/below/','14022','0276816',1,NULL,'Below is a creepy, claustrophobic exercise in style.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/84/02/10840224_mob.jpg'),(569,'Jimmy Neutron - Boy Genius',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jimmy_neutron_boy_genius/','9585','0268397',1,NULL,'What Jimmy Neutron lacks in computer animation, it makes up for in charm and cleverness.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/13/42/11134217_mob.jpg'),(570,'Invasion of the Body Snatchers',1956,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1010678-invasion_of_the_body_snatchers/','18032','0049366',1,NULL,'One of the best political allegories of the 1950s, Invasion of the Body Snatchers is an efficient, chilling blend of sci-fi and horror.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/95/44/10954478_mob.jpg'),(571,'The Red Baron (Der rote Baron)',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10010789-red_baron/','770729028','0365675',1,NULL,'It doesn\'t lack ambition, and it boasts undeniably thrilling source material, but The Red Baron is brought down by its overly sentimental script and a number of historical inaccuracies.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/84/88/10848815_mob.jpg'),(572,'Uncle Boonmee Who Can Recall His Past Lives',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/uncle_boonmee/','771042125','1588895',1,'Suffering from acute kidney failure, Uncle Boonmee has chosen to spend his final days surrounded by his loved ones in the countryside. Surprisingly, the ghost of his deceased wife appears to care for him, and his long lost son returns home in a non-human form. Contemplating the reasons for his illness, Boonmee treks through the jungle with his family to a mysterious hilltop cave - the birthplace of his first life... -- (C) Strand','Languorous and deeply enigmatic, Palme d\'Or winner Uncle Boonmee represents an original take on the ghosts that haunt us.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/55/11155577_mob.jpg'),(573,'Cecil B. Demented',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cecil_b_demented/','14425','0173716',1,NULL,'The idea behind John Waters\' latest has much potential, but the movie ends up being too sloppy and underdeveloped in terms of script and direction. Also, by today\'s standards, it fails to shock.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/86/70/10867015_mob.jpg'),(574,'The Adventures of Rocky & Bullwinkle',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/adventures_of_rocky_and_bullwinkle/','11991','0131704',1,NULL,'Though the film stays true to the nature of the original cartoon, the script is disappointing and not funny.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/34/263400_mob.jpg'),(575,'The Brady Bunch Movie',1995,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/brady_bunch_movie/','12187','0112572',1,NULL,'Though lightweight and silly, The Brady Bunch Movie still charms as homage to the 70s sitcom.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/70/30/10703022_mob.jpg'),(576,'Judy Moody and the NOT Bummer Summer',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/judy_moody_and_the_not_bummer_summer/','771229930','1547230',1,'The film chronicles Judy Moody\'s (Jordana Beatty) adventures in which she sets out to have the most thrilling summer of her life with the help of her little brother Stink (Parris Mosteller) and fun-loving Aunt Opal (Heather Graham). The script, penned by Kathy Waugh (Peep and the Big Wide World) and Megan McDonald, is based on the characters in McDonald\'s popular children\'s book series, illustrated by Peter H. Reynolds and published by Candlewick Press. -- (C) Relativity','Entertaining for some very young viewers, but for those with normal attention spans, Judy Moody is loud hyperactive overload.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/65/11156587_mob.jpg'),(577,'Bronson',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bronson/','770783965','1172570',1,NULL,'Undeniably gripping, Bronson forces the viewer to make some hard decisions about where the line between art and exploitation lies.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/91/37/10913734_mob.jpg'),(578,'Beautiful Girls',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beautiful_girls/','13143','0115639',1,NULL,'A warm, thoughtful dramedy about male insecurity, Beautiful Girls is buoyed by an excellent cast - particularly Natalie Portman in a stunning early role.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/84/53/10845361_mob.jpg'),(579,'This Must Be The Place',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/this_must_be_the_place/','771240597','1440345',1,'Cheyenne (Sean Penn) is a former rock star. At 50, he still dresses \'Goth\' and lives in Dublin off his royalties. The death of his father, with whom he wasn\'t on speaking terms, brings him back to New York. He discovers his father had an obsession: to seek revenge for a humiliation he had suffered. Cheyenne decides to pick up where his father left off, and starts a journey, at his own pace, across America. -- (C) Weinstein',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/71/11167183_mob.jpg'),(580,'La Battaglia di Algeri (The Battle of Algiers)',1966,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/battle_of_algiers/','133039722','0058946',1,NULL,'A powerful, documentary-like examination of the response to an occupying force, The Battle of Algiers hasn\'t aged a bit since its release in 1966.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/94/26/10942603_mob.jpg'),(581,'The Band\'s Visit (Bikur Ha-Tizmoret)',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bands_visit/','770672006','1032856',1,NULL,'The Band\'s Visit is both a clever, subtle slice-of-life comedy, and poignant cross-cultural exploration.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/17/94/10179459_mob.jpg'),(582,'What the Bleep Do We Know!?',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/what_the__do_we_know/','18059','0399877',1,NULL,'Educational, but as entertainment, it\'ll have viewers asking, \'What the bleep?\'','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/91/67/10916748_mob.jpg'),(583,'Aurora Borealis',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/aurora_borealis/','287865261','0387037',1,NULL,'Deeply reminiscent of other, better films, Aurora Borealis nonetheless succeeds on the strength of winning performances from Sutherland and Jackson.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/89/81/10898163_mob.jpg'),(584,'A Better Tomorrow',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/better_tomorrow/','16403','0092263',1,'John Woo established himself as one of Hong Kong\'s premiere action directors with this ultra-hip, ultra-violent action classic. The film centers around the complex relationship between two brothers: Sung Tse-kit (Leslie Cheung) is a recent graduate of the police academy while Tse-ho (Ti Lung) runs a massive counterfeiting ring along with his gangland associate, Mark Lee (Chow Yun-fat). Tension between the two brothers comes to a head when their father is murdered after a crime deal goes sour and Tse-ho lands in jail after being double-crossed. In perhaps the most influential scene in Hong Kong cinema in the 1980s, Mark avenges his friend by staging a dinner table assassination. As Mark tries to shoot his way out of the restaurant, pulling a series of hidden pistols from potted plants and alcoves, he gets horribly injured. With both founding members of the counterfeiting syndicate incapacitated, the operation falls into the hands of Shing (Waise Lee Chi-hung), Tse-ho\'s former underling who has little of his boss\' elan or experience. When Tse-ho gets out of jail, he reunites with his now-crippled comrade, Mark, to take out Shing and to protect Tse-kit whose life is in danger for investigating their former subordinate. ~ Jonathan Crow, Rovi',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/13/22/11132266_mob.jpg'),(585,'All About the Benjamins',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/all_about_the_benjamins/','13892','0278295',1,NULL,'A sloppy, poorly directed action-comedy, All About the Benjamins is too derivative and gratuitously violent.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/60/26/38/6026384_mob.jpg'),(586,'Bulworth',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bulworth/','13700','0118798',1,NULL,'Star and director Beatty\'s ambitious take on race and politics in 20th-century America isn\'t perfect, but manages to provide more than its share of thought-provoking laughs.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/47/11164732_mob.jpg'),(587,'Buffalo Soldiers',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/buffalo-soldiers/','14323','0252299',1,NULL,'Overall, this caustic comedy hits more of its targets than it misses.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/92/50/10925046_mob.jpg'),(588,'The Babymakers',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_babymakers_2012/','771271055','0835418',1,'After trying everything to get his wife Audrey (Olivia Munn) pregnant, Tommy Macklin (Paul Schneider) realizes to his horror that he may be \"shooting blanks.\" Terrified that his marriage may fall apart, Tommy recruits his friends (and an Indian ex-mobster) to rob a sperm bank where he made a deposit years ago. As with any half-baked scheme, everything can and does go wrong, testing the limits of Tommy and Audrey\'s relationship. The Babymakers is a hilarious twist on the heist film genre, a laugh-out loud comedy showing how far one couple will go in hopes of creating a new life. -- (C) Official Site','The Babymakers mistakes raunch for humor and, despite a few sporadic laughs, wastes its otherwise capable cast on gross-out gags and misfired one-liners.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/52/11165277_mob.jpg'),(589,'Brothers of the Head',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/brothers_of_the_head/','190816443','0432260',1,NULL,'As bizarre as it is, this mockumentary about a pair of conjoined rockers is surprisingly poignant and filled with authentic period details.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/89/42/10894211_mob.jpg'),(590,'The Babysitters',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/babysitters/','770677842','0796302',1,NULL,'Though built on an audacious and controversial premise, Babysitters teeters between exploitation and grossness due to uneven execution.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/84/14/10841411_mob.jpg'),(591,'The Bachelor',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1093976-bachelor/','12070','0120596',1,NULL,'Predictable and unfunny, it\'s a poor homage to Buster Keaton.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/99/11159992_mob.jpg'),(592,'Side by Side',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/side_by_side_2012/','771267748','2014338',1,'Join Keanu Reeves on a tour of the past and the future of filmmaking in Side by Side. Since the invention of cinema, the standard format for recording moving images has been film. Over the past two decades, a new form of digital filmmaking has emerged, creating a groundbreaking evolution in the medium. Reeves explores the development of cinema and the impact of digital filmmaking via in-depth interviews with Hollywood masters, such as James Cameron, David Fincher, David Lynch, Martin Scorsese, Steven Soderbergh, and many more. -- (C) Tribeca',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/60/11166072_mob.jpg'),(593,'Once Upon a Time in Anatolia',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/once_upon_a_time_in_anatolia/','771240268','1827487',1,'In the dead of night, a group of men - including a police commissioner, a prosecutor, a doctor and a murder suspect - drive through the tenebrous Anatolian countryside, the serpentine roads and rolling hills lit only by the headlights of their cars. They are searching for a corpse, the victim of a brutal murder. The suspect, who claims he was drunk, can\'t remember where he buried the body. As the night draws on, details about the murder emerge and the investigators\' own secrets and hypocrisies come to light. In the Anatolian steppes, nothing is what it seems; and when the body is found, the real questions begin. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/13/11161335_mob.jpg'),(594,'Barb Wire',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/barb_wire/','16679','0012920',1,NULL,'Barb Wire could\'ve been fun camp, but Pamela Anderson can\'t deliver her lines with any dramatic or comedic impact.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/87/18/10871816_mob.jpg'),(595,'Lucky Break',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lucky_break/','12617','0246134',1,NULL,'Lucky Break fails to do anything new with The Full Monty formula.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/91/98/10919819_mob.jpg'),(596,'Twin Dragons (Shuang long hui) (Brother vs. Brother)',1992,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/twin-dragons/','11575','0105399',1,NULL,'Despite some entertaining action, this movie has serious plot holes and bad direction.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/26/13/261391_mob.jpg'),(597,'Big Trouble',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1109942-big_trouble/','10787','0246464',1,NULL,'With its large cast and frantic comic pacing, Big Trouble labors for slapstick-style hilarity, but it never really gains steam.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/92/12/10921251_mob.jpg'),(598,'Central Station (Central do Brasil)',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/central-do-brasil-central-station/','14037','0140888',1,NULL,'Director Salles transcends road-movie cliches and crafts a film that is as moving as it is universal.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/87/55/10875583_mob.jpg'),(599,'Bounce',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bounce/','11769','0186894',1,NULL,'Critics say Bounce is more of a thud. Plot turns feel cliched and contrived, and the romance between Paltrow and Affleck fails to engage.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/84/58/10845867_mob.jpg'),(600,'City by the Sea',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/city_by_the_sea/','15027','0269095',1,NULL,'Even though the movie is well acted, it sinks under an abundance of melodrama and cliches.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/27/75/277501_mob.jpg'),(601,'Bubble',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1153488-bubble/','2864898',NULL,1,NULL,'This rigorously stripped down, seemingly mundane little film still manages to be engrossing and creepy.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/91/54/10915483_mob.jpg'),(602,'Battleship Potemkin',1925,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/battleship_potemkin/','17497','0015648',1,NULL,'A technical masterpiece, Battleship Potemkin is Soviet cinema at its finest, and its montage editing techniques remain influential to this day.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/28/11162829_mob.jpg'),(603,'Space Chimps 2: Zartog Strikes Back',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/space_chimps_2_zartog_strikes_back/','771036813','1537481',1,'Determined to become a certified space chimp by any means, ambitious tech specialist Comet takes a trip to Planet Malgor and becomes locked in a struggle against evil alien tyrant Zartog in this colorful animated space adventure. Upon arriving on Malgor, Comet makes fast friends with a kind-hearted alien named Kilowatt. When the dreaded Zartog assumes command of Mission Control, it\'s up to Comet, Kilowatt, Ham, Luna, and Titan to overthrow the extraterrestrial tyrant. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/49/11164950_mob.jpg'),(604,'Crna macka, beli macor (Black Cat, White Cat)',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/black_cat_white_cat/','770682305','0118843',1,NULL,'Rambling and eccentric, Emir Kusturica\'s comedy captures the life and energy of the Gypsy family at the heart of the tale.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/83/83/10838389_mob.jpg'),(605,'The Jungle Book 2',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jungle_book_2/','9571','0283426',1,NULL,'This inferior rehash of The Jungle Book should have gone straight to video.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/14/32/11143298_mob.jpg'),(606,'Perfect Blue',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/perfect-blue/','17170','0156887',1,NULL,'Perfect Blue is overstylized, but its core mystery is always compelling, as are the visual theatrics.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/28/66/286610_mob.jpg'),(607,'The Best Man',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1093551-best_man/','13449','0168501',1,NULL,'With a strong cast and a host of well-defined characters, The Best Man is an intelligent, funny romantic comedy that marks an impressive debut for writer/director Malcolm D. Lee.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/98/269806_mob.jpg'),(608,'The Business of Being Born',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/business_of_being_born/','770674876','0995061',1,NULL,'Epstein\'s argument in favor of home birthing is certainly biased -- but its biases are so transparent, and so impassioned, that they work in the film\'s favor.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/54/10885419_mob.jpg'),(609,'Branded',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/branded_2012/','771307091','1368440',1,'Branded is a dark and mind-bending journey into a surreal, dystopian society where corporate brands have unleashed a monstrous global conspiracy to get inside our minds and keep the population disillusioned, dependent and passive. One man\'s Misha (Ed Stoppard) passion to unlock the truth behind the conspiracy will lead to an epic battle with the hidden forces that really control our world. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/55/11165586_mob.jpg'),(610,'Blue Like Jazz',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/blue_like_jazz/','771269304','1758575',1,'Don, a pious nineteen-year-old sophomore at a Texas junior college, impulsively decides to escape his evangelical upbringing for life in the Pacific Northwest at one ofthe most progressive campuses in America, Reed College in Portland. Upon arrival, Reed\'s surroundings and eccentric student body proves to be far different than he could possibly imagine from the environment from which he came, forcing him to embark on a journey of self-discovery to understand who he is and what he truly believes. -- (C) Roadside Attractions',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/42/11164242_mob.jpg'),(611,'Bee Season',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bee_season/','9179','0387059',1,NULL,'Bee Season is an intelligent, but frustratingly distant and diffuse drama about family dysfunction.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/87/02/10870235_mob.jpg'),(612,'Bones',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bones/','15373','0166110',1,NULL,'Slow to start, the sleek looking Bones is more silly than scary.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/91/92/10919242_mob.jpg'),(613,'Brighton Rock',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/brighton_rock-2010/','770872016','1233192',1,'Screenwriter Rowan Joffe\'s debut feature Brighton Rock embraces the classic elements of film noir and the British gangster film to tell the story of Pinkie, a desperate youth who is hell bent on clawing his way up through the ranks of organized crime. When a young and very innocent waitress, Rose, stumbles on evidence linking him to a revenge killing, he sets out to seduce her to secure her silence. The film stars up-and-coming British actors Sam Riley and Andrea Riseborough as the young couple. Veterans Helen Mirren and John Hurt co-star as two friends who set out to save Rose from Pinkie\'s deviant designs. Brighton Rock is based on the iconic 1939 Graham Greene novel of innocence and evil but the action has been updated to 1964 Britain, the year the Mods and the Rockers were rioting across the South Coast. The 60s were also the era of the great British gangster, the kind of working class hero, the frightened and ambitious Pinkie longs to be. -- (C) Offical Site',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/91/11159124_mob.jpg'),(614,'Dark Blue',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dark_blue/','14831','0279331',1,NULL,'Kurt Russell gives a good performance. Too bad there\'s nothing here that you haven\'t seen before.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/27/65/276516_mob.jpg'),(615,'The Hidden Blade',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hidden_blade/','190814133','0442286',1,NULL,'A slow and steady samurai flick a la John Ford that brings emotions and psychology to an epic-scale adventure.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/37/88/1037881_mob.jpg'),(616,'The Brown Bunny',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/brown_bunny/','17010','0330099',1,NULL,'More dull than hypnotic, The Brown Bunny is a pretentious and self-indulgent bore.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/57/10885774_mob.jpg'),(617,'Waking Sleeping Beauty',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/waking_sleeping_beauty/','770816316','1159961',1,NULL,'It doesn\'t probe as deep -- or tell as many hard truths -- as it could have, but Don Hahn\'s look at Disney\'s rebirth offers a fascinating and surprisingly candorous glimpse into the studio\'s past.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/88/11168824_mob.jpg'),(618,'Le Battement d\'Ailes du Papillon (Happenstance) (The Beating of the Butterfly\'s Wings)',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/happenstance/','14149','0243135',1,NULL,'Though the plot of Happenstance is basically a gimmick, the film is a fun, light-hearted trifle.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/91/17/10911751_mob.jpg'),(619,'De Battre mon Coeur s\'est Arrete (The Beat That My Heart Skipped)',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beat_that_my_heart_skipped/','266555627','0411270',1,NULL,'Stylish and visceral, this able remake is infused with realism, grit, and a taut performance by star Romain Duris.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/18/93/97/1893979_mob.jpg'),(620,'Mutiny on the Bounty',1935,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1014481-mutiny_on_the_bounty/','18544','0026752',1,NULL,'The historical inaccuracies in this high-seas adventure are more then offset by its timeless themes, larger-than-life performances from Clark Gable and Charles Laughton, and Frank Lloyd\'s superb direction.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/81/11168110_mob.jpg'),(621,'In A Better World',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/in_a_better_world/','771206479','1340107',1,'Anton is a doctor who commutes between his home in an idyllic town in Denmark, and his work at an African refugee camp. In these two very different worlds, he and his family are faced with conflicts that lead them to difficult choices between revenge and forgiveness. Anton and his wife Marianne, who have two young sons, are separated and struggling with the possibility of divorce. Their older, ten-year-old son Elias is being bullied at school, until he is defended by Christian, a new boy who has just moved from London with his father, Claus. Christian&#8223;s mother recently lost her battle with cancer, and Christian is greatly troubled by her death. Elias and Christian quickly form a strong bond, but when Christian involves Elias in a dangerous act of revenge with potentially tragic consequences, their friendship is tested and lives are put in danger. Ultimately, it is their parents who are left to help them come to terms with the complexity of human emotions, pain and empathy. -- (C) Sony Pictures Classics','In a Better World is a sumptuous melodrama that tackles some rather difficult existential and human themes.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/62/11156213_mob.jpg'),(622,'Warriors of the Rainbow: Seediq Bale',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/warriors_of_the_rainbow_seediq_bale/','771254851','2007993',1,'Wei Te-sheng\'s epic film Warriors of the Rainbow: Seediq Bale reclaims an extraordinary episode from 20thcentury history which is little-known, even in Taiwan. Between 1895 and 1945, the island was a Japanese colony inhabited not only by the majority (Han Chinese Immigrants) but also by the remnants of the aboriginal tribes who first settled the mountainous land. In 1930 Mouna Rudo, the leader of the Seediq tribe settled on and around Mount Chilai, forged a coalition with other Seediq tribal leaders and plotted a rebellion against their Japanese colonial masters. The initial uprising took the Japanese by surprise and was almost entirely successful. But the Japanese soon sent in their army to crush the rebellion, using aircraft and poison gas. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/41/11164106_mob.jpg'),(623,'In the Land of Blood and Honey',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/in_the_land_of_blood_and_honey/','771243728','1714209',1,'Set against the backdrop of the Bosnian War that tore the Balkan region apart in the 1990s, In the Land of Blood and Honey tells the story of Danijel and Ajla, two people from different sides of a brutal ethnic conflict. Danijel, a soldier fighting for the Serbs, and Ajla, a Bosnian held captive in the camp he oversees, knew each other before the war, and could have found love with each other. But as the armed conflict takes hold of their lives, their relationship grows darker, their motives and connection to one another ambiguous, their allegiances uncertain. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/24/11162485_mob.jpg'),(624,'The Boy Who Cried Werewolf',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_boy_who_cried_werewolf/','771217707','1451423',1,'Meet the Sands family -- David and his two children Hunter and Jordan (played by Victoria Justice!). After falling on hard economic times, the Sands find out their long lost relative, Dragomir Ducovic, has willed them his mansion in Wolfsberg, Romania! Naturally, they hop on a plane to check out their new home, Wolfsberg Manor, an ancient gothic castle lorded over by the mysterious Madame Varcolac (played by Brooke Shields). Now the Sands are living large! But nothing is ever as easy as it looks. Especially with a band of bloodsuckers on the loose! Before the Sands clan gets their hands on this mansion, they\'ll have to undergo some... transformations. Things will get... hairy?',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/38/11153887_mob.jpg'),(625,'Point Blank',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/point_blank/','771217764','1545759',1,'Produced by Cyril Colbeau-Justin and Jean-Baptiste Dupont, Point Blank also stars Roschdy Zem, Gerard Lanvin and Elena Anaya. Gilles Lellouche plays Samuel, a nurse working at a hospital when his pregnant wife (Anaya) is kidnapped before his very eyes. Knocked unconscious, he comes to and discovers that a dangerous criminal named Sartet (Zem) is responsible, and if he\'s ever to see his wife again, he must do Sartet\'s bidding. Samuel quickly finds himself pitted against rival gangsters and trigger-happy police in a deadly race to save the lives of his wife and unborn child. -- (C) Magnolia',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/84/11158427_mob.jpg'),(626,'The Education of Charlie Banks',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/education_of_charlie_banks/','770678368','0783515',1,NULL,'Unevenness and earnestness mire this otherwise sweet, surprising coming of age drama.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/78/10887885_mob.jpg'),(627,'Autoreiji: Biyondo (Outrage Beyond)',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/autoreiji_biyondo_2011/','771210457','1462667',1,'In a ruthless battle for power, several yakuza clans vie for the favor of their head family in the Japanese underworld. The rival bosses seek to rise through the ranks by scheming and making allegiances sworn over sake. Long-time yakuza Otomo has seen his kind go from elaborate body tattoos and severed fingertips to becoming important players on the stock market. Theirs is a never-ending struggle to end up on top, or at least survive, in a corrupt world where there are no heroes but constant betrayal and vengeance. -- (C) Magnet Releasing',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/86/11158608_mob.jpg'),(628,'The Bishop\'s Wife',1947,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bishops_wife/','18107','0039190',1,NULL,'The Bishop\'s Wife succeeds thanks to the strength of winning performances from a stellar cast, which includes Cary Grant and Loretta Young.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/29/06/290699_mob.jpg'),(629,'Bellflower',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bellflower/','771225219','1242599',1,'Bellflower follows two friends as they venture out into the world to begin their adult lives. Literally all their free time is spent building flame-throwers and weapons of mass destruction in hopes that a global apocalypse will occur and clear the runway for their imaginary gang \"Mother Medusa\". While waiting for the world to end, their call to excitement comes unexpectedly when one of them meets a charismatic young woman and falls hard in love. Quickly integrated into a new group of friends, they set off on a journey of betrayal, love, hate, infidelity and extreme violence more devastating and fiery than any of their apocalyptic fantasies. -- (C) Official Site','This fevered, stylish vision of the end of the world stitches multiple genres together and marks writer/director/star Evan Glodell as a true talent to watch.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/89/11158949_mob.jpg'),(630,'My Best Friend (Mon meilleur ami)',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1175074-my_best_friend/','711005560','0778784',1,NULL,'Although the plot may sound contrived, the performances of Daniel Auteuil and Dany Boon manage to turn My Best Friend into an earnest and witty romp.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/00/10890062_mob.jpg'),(631,'Father of the Bride',1950,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1007154-father_of_the_bride/','18626','0042451',1,NULL,'With a terrific script, great performances from Spencer Tracy and Elizabeth Taylor, and assured direction from Vincent Minnelli, Father of the Bride endures as a sparkling comedy of its era.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/29/32/293217_mob.jpg'),(632,'Being Julia',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/being_julia/','13316','0340012',1,NULL,'Annette Bening delivers a captivating performance in Being Julia, a sophisticated comedy that follows a 1930s stage diva who experiences an identity crisis at age 40.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/84/02/10840218_mob.jpg'),(633,'I\'ll Be Home for Christmas',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1088110-ill_be_home_for_christmas/','12221','0155753',1,NULL,'Neither parent nor child will find any merriment in this mess.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/26/44/264429_mob.jpg'),(634,'Slow Burn',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/slow_burn/','465555209','0376196',1,NULL,'With wooden acting and hammy, overheated dialogue, Slow Burn isn\'t so much a noir as it is a mediocre parody of one.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/92/35/11/9235118_mob.jpg'),(635,'Brand Upon the Brain!',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/brand_upon_the_brain/','359852718','0443455',1,NULL,'A bizarre yet compelling spectacle, Brand Upon the Brain! is a unique cinematic experience.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/22/10882274_mob.jpg'),(636,'Miss Bala',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/miss_bala_2011/','771242437','1911600',1,'Miss Bala tells the story of Laura, a young woman whose aspirations of becoming a beauty queen turn against her, delivering her into the hands of a gang that\'s terrorizing northern Mexico. Although Laura succeeds in winning the beauty queen crown, her experiences as an unwilling participant in Mexico\'s violent war leave her shaken and transformed. -- (C) Fox International Productions','Miss Bala\'s subject is loaded enough, but the frantic and muscular filmmaking puts this movie in a whole new league.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/79/11157929_mob.jpg'),(637,'Girl Walks Into a Bar',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/girl_walks_into_a_bar/','771203654','1682246',1,'GIRL WALKS INTO A BAR connects a group of apparent strangers over one night across ten bars throughout Los Angeles. Zachary Quinto stars as a dentist who teams up with a feisty would-be assassin (Carla Gugino) to put the final touches on the plan to kill his wife. Once he makes a play for the assassin\'s payment, he unknowingly sets off a chain of events that fuels a crosstown journey through the many lounges, bars, strip clubs and the occasional nudist ping pong clubs scattered across Los Angeles. By turns funny and heartbreaking, this sharp-witted comedy features ten interconnected vignettes that build to a revealing finish. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/59/11155990_mob.jpg'),(638,'Trailer Park Boys: The Movie',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trailer-park-boys-the-big-dirty/','329470883','0425601',1,NULL,'Trailer Park Boys suffers from its small-screen origins, and its tasteless humor is not for everyone, but it will satisfy fans of the genre.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/27/10/36/2710360_mob.jpg'),(639,'Der Blaue Engel (The Blue Angel)',1930,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1002681-blue_angel/','19549','0020697',1,NULL,'Marlene Dietrich steals more than one show in this backstage tragedy about a lowly professor besotted with a cruel and enigmatic singer.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/29/77/297703_mob.jpg'),(640,'Mrs. Brown',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mrs_brown/','10621','0119280',1,NULL,'Thanks to some top notch acting, the chemistry between its stars, and a witty, thoughtful script, Mrs. Brown delivers a nuanced and entertaining, if not entirely factual, account of a seldom explored historical relationship.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/66/256624_mob.jpg'),(641,'Beautiful',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1100122-beautiful/','12257','0210567',1,NULL,'Sally Field\'s directing debut suffers from an inconsistent tone, implausible script, and a protagonist that critics say is one of the most loathsome to come around in a long time.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/46/264612_mob.jpg'),(642,'Blow Out',1981,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/blow_out/','14605','0082085',1,NULL,'With a story inspired by Antonioni\'s Blow Up and a style informed by the high-gloss suspense of Hitchcock, DePalma\'s Blow Out is raw, politically informed, and littered with film references.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/36/11153628_mob.jpg'),(643,'Beyond The Black Rainbow',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beyond_the_black_rainbow_2012/','771269777','1534085',1,'Set in the strange and oppressive emotional landscape of the year 1983, Beyond the Black Rainbow is a Reagan-era fever dream inspired by hazy childhood memories of midnight movies and Saturday morning cartoons. From the producer of \"Machotaildrop,\" Rainbow is the outlandish feature film debut of writer and director Panos Cosmatos. Featuring a hypnotic analog synthesizer score by Jeremy Schmidt of \"Sinoia Caves\" and \"Black Mountain,\" Rainbow is a film experience for the senses. -- (C) Magnet',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/40/11164054_mob.jpg'),(644,'I Hope They Serve Beer in Hell',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/i_hope_they_serve_beer_in_hell/','770810236','1220628',1,NULL,'I Hope They Serve Beer in Hell fails in its attempts at raunchy humor, and Tucker Max comes across so unlikable and outrageous that the film\'s inevitable story arc feels forced.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/49/11164918_mob.jpg'),(645,'Batman: Under the Red Hood',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/batman_under_the_red_hood/','771041745','1569923',1,'A diabolical villain who seems to know Batman\'s every move sets out to clean up the streets of Gotham for good and destroy the caped crime-fighter in the process. Every night, Batman protects the citizens of Gotham from the shadows. But lately another vigilante has been prowling the streets, and his merciless methods are more frightening than reassuring. Now, as the Red Hood commences to exterminating the scum of the city with extreme prejudice, the Joker resurfaces to taunt his old nemesis by digging up some skeletons that were best left buried. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/71/11157127_mob.jpg'),(646,'Eye of the Beholder',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1094646-eye_of_the_beholder/','14230','0120662',1,NULL,'Improbable and muddled.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/27/36/273619_mob.jpg'),(647,'Sita Sings the Blues',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sita_sings_the_blues/','563563091','1172203',1,NULL,'A tour de force for filmmaker Nina Paley, Sita Sings the Blues gives the Ramayana its animated due with a visually vibrant, dazzlingly imaginative triumph.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/86/48/10864817_mob.jpg'),(648,'The Ballad of Jack and Rose',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ballad_of_jack_and_rose/','14215','0357110',1,NULL,'Heavy on the symbolism and overly contrived.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/71/11157147_mob.jpg'),(649,'Theater of Blood (Theatre of Blood) (Much Ado About Murder)',1973,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/theatre_of_blood/','14313','0070791',1,NULL,'Deliciously campy and wonderfully funny, Theater of Blood features Vincent Price at his melodramatic best.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/74/10887490_mob.jpg'),(650,'Being Flynn',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/being_flynn/','771234601','0455323',1,'Writer-director Paul Weitz turns his hand to this moving portrait of fathers and sons. Based on a true story, Being Flynn follows Nick Flynn (Paul Dano) who is shocked to have his eccentric and long-absent father, Jonathan (Robert De Niro) reach out to him unexpectedly. Still feeling the loss of his mother (played in flashbacks by Julianne Moore) in the midst of starting a new relationship with Denise (Olivia Thirlby), the last person Nick wants to see is his father. But you can\'t outrun fate and slowly Nick comes to realize he has been given the chance to make a real future not only for himself, but for his struggling father too. -- (C) Focus',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/23/11162389_mob.jpg'),(651,'Buck',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/buck/','771224186','1753549',1,'\"Your horse is a mirror to your soul, and sometimes you may not like what you see. Sometimes, you will.\" So says Buck Brannaman, a true American cowboy and sage on horseback who travels the country for nine grueling months a year helping horses with people problems. BUCK, a richly textured and visually stunning film, follows Brannaman from his abusive childhood to his phenomenally successful approach to horses. A real life \"horse-whisperer\", he eschews the violence of his upbringing and teaches people to communicate with horses through leadership and sensitivity, not punishment. Buck possesses near magical abilities as he dramatically transforms horses - and people - with his understanding, compassion and respect. In this film, the animal-human relationship becomes a metaphor for facing the daily challenges of life. A truly American story about an unsung hero, Buck is about an ordinary man who has made an extraordinary life despite tremendous odds. -- (C) IFC Films',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/73/11157362_mob.jpg'),(652,'The Syrian Bride',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1153719-syrian_bride/','9271','0423310',1,NULL,'A humane and empathic work, The Syrian Bride depicts the personal impact of politics upon individuals.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/21/23/10212368_mob.jpg'),(653,'Beats Rhymes & Life: The Travels of a Tribe Called Quest',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beats_rhymes_and_life_the_travels_of_a_tribe_called_quest/','771267578',NULL,1,'A documentary film directed by Michael Rapaport about one of the most influential and groundbreaking musical groups in hip-hop history. Having released five gold and platinum selling albums within eight years, A Tribe Called Quest has been one of the most commercially successful and artistically significant musical groups in recent history, and regarded as iconic pioneers of hip hop. The band\'s sudden break-up in 1998 shocked the industry and saddened the scores of fans, whose appetite for the group\'s innovative musical stylings never seems to diminish. A hard-core fan himself, Rapaport sets out on tour with A Tribe Called Quest in 2008, when they reunited to perform sold-out concerts across the country, almost ten years after the release of their last album, The Love Movement. -- (C) Sony Classics','This documentary focuses less on the music and more on the personality clashes and in-group tensions to great, compelling effect.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/79/11157920_mob.jpg'),(654,'The Last Circus',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/balada_triste_de_trompeta/','771208507','1572491',1,'1937, Spain is in the midst of the brutal Spanish Civil War. A \"Happy\" circus clown is interrupted mid-performance and forcibly recruited by a militia. Still in his costume, he is handed a machete and led into battle against National soldiers, where he single handedly massacres an entire platoon. Fast forward to 1973, the tail end of the Franco regime. Javier, the son of the clown, dreams of following in his father\'s career footsteps, but has seen too much tragedy in his life - he\'s simply not funny and is only equipped to play the role of the Sad Clown. He finds work in a circus where he befriends an outlandish cast of characters, but as the Sad Clown he must take the abuse of the brutish Happy Clown Sergio, who humiliates Javier daily in the name of entertainment. -- (C) Official Site','The Last Circus is an uneven but winningly insane blend of hard violence, sex, black humor, and social satire.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/89/11158909_mob.jpg'),(655,'Let the Bullets Fly',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/let_the_bullets_fly/','771221037','1533117',1,'Since its release this year, Let the Bullets Fly has been lauded across the globe for its stunning mix of dark comedy and eye-popping violence. In China, this action-comedy starring Chow Yun-Fat has become the highest-grossing domestic film of all time. Set in 1920s Sichuan, the film tells the tale of the bandit \"Pocky\" Zhang Mazi, who poses as a local governor in a dusty town- but finds himself at odds with the local mobster, who is not eager to share his turf with another drifter. A complex and deadly series of mind-games ensues between the two crooks, which are as violent as they are hilarious. The rare foreign-language comedy that translates without a hitch, Let the Bullets Fly will have you falling out of your seat with laughter. -- (C) Variance',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/37/11163764_mob.jpg'),(656,'Ben X',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10009212-ben_x/','770679665','0953318',1,NULL,'Thoughtful and provocative Dutch film concerned with autism, online gaming and bullying, though loses steam in the final act.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/86/82/10868203_mob.jpg'),(657,'Left Behind - The Movie',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/left_behind/','10120','0190524',1,NULL,'Poor production values, slow pacing, and an implausible story makes Left Behind a movie only for the faithful.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/85/47/10854761_mob.jpg'),(658,'Beloved',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1057370-beloved/','13434','0120603',1,NULL,'A powerful, emotional and successful film adaptation of the original novel.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/97/269718_mob.jpg'),(659,'The Bridge',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1169498-bridge/','381413349','0799954',1,NULL,'Tactlessly morbid or remarkably sensitive? Deeply disturbing or viscerally fascinating? Critics are divided on Eric Steele\'s unique documentary on the Golden Gate Bridge, wonder of the modern world and notorious suicide destination.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/69/10876961_mob.jpg'),(660,'The Big Red One',1980,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/big_red_one/','15139','0080437',1,NULL,'The reconstruction of Samuel Fuller\'s epic account of his days in North Africa in World War II elevates the film into the pantheon of great war movies.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/93/85/10938557_mob.jpg'),(661,'Jack Goes Boating',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jack_goes_boating/','770814193','1278379',1,'Adapted from Bob Glaudini\'s play of the same name, Philip Seymour Hoffman\'s directorial debut, Jack Goes Boating, tells the simple tale of Jack (Hoffman), a shy, fortyish limo driver with a fondness for pot and reggae music -- he likes it because it sounds happy -- who meets Connie (Amy Ryan) for a blind date set up by Connie\'s co-worker Lucy (Daphne Rubin-Vega), who is married to Jack\'s best friend and fellow limo driver, Clyde (John Ortiz). As the young couple tentatively come together, breaking through layers and layers of awkwardness and low self-esteem, Clyde and Lucy\'s marriage begins to dissolve because of Clyde\'s inability to get over an incident from their past. All the while, Clyde gives Jack swimming lessons so that he can take Connie on her dream date -- a boating trip on the lake. ~ Perry Seibert, Rovi','It\'s made the journey from stage to screen somewhat worse for wear, but Jack Goes Boating remains a sensitive, well-acted character study.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/12/32/11123202_mob.jpg'),(662,'Bloody Sunday',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bloody_sunday/','13820','0280491',1,NULL,'Bloody Sunday powerfully recreates the events of that day with startling immediacy.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/90/21/10902182_mob.jpg'),(663,'The Bothersome Man (Den Brysomme mannen)',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bothersome_man/','568063487','0808185',1,NULL,'Bothersome Man is a surreal, comedic meditation, thoughtfully and skillfully made.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/96/45/24/9645242_mob.jpg'),(664,'Ball of Fire',1941,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ball_of_fire/','563550923','0033373',1,NULL,'A splendidly funny twist on the story of Snow White, Ball of Fire boasts a pair of perfect leads in Gary Cooper and Barbara Stanwyck.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/86/72/10867215_mob.jpg'),(665,'Devil in a Blue Dress',1995,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/devil_in_a_blue_dress/','13753','0112857',1,NULL,'Humor, interesting characters, and attention to details make the stylish Devil in a Blue Dress an above average noir.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/27/13/271303_mob.jpg'),(666,'Le Voyage du Ballon Rouge (The Flight of the Red Balloon)',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/flight_of_the_red_balloon/','770676377','0826711',1,NULL,'Hou Hsiao-hsien\'s remake of the 1956 classic is unhurried, contemplative, and visually rapturous.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/92/48/10924828_mob.jpg'),(667,'Breakin\' All the Rules',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/breakin_all_the_rules/','11052','0349169',1,NULL,'This formulaic screwball comedy is weighed down by a contrived, overly complicated plot.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/88/258804_mob.jpg'),(668,'A fost sau n-a fost?, (12:08 East of Bucharest)',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1208_east_of_bucharest/','377006508','0809407',1,NULL,'With a witty script full of satirical overtones and dry humor, 12:08 East of Bucharest is a thoroughly enjoyable Romanian comedy.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/41/08/83/4108836_mob.jpg'),(669,'American: The Bill Hicks Story',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/american-the-bill-hicks-story/','770820131','1179947',1,'15 years after his death, Bill Hicks is now more popular than ever, and is widely seen as one of the best comedian of the modern era. However, in America, where he challenged institutions and accepted ways of thinking, he suffered censorship and was never truly recognized by a wide audience. In the country which enshrines freedom of speech in its constitution his story is truly about what it means to be an American. -- (c) Variance','A treasure trove of archival material and interviews, American: The Bill Hicks Story is an exuberant celebration about a unique, sorely missed voice in comedy.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/62/11156244_mob.jpg'),(670,'Va, Vis et Deviens (Live and Become) (Go, See, and Become)',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/va-vis-et-deviens-live-and-become-go-see-and-become/','98651696','0388505',1,NULL,'Mihaileanu\'s story of an Ethiopian orphan\'s struggles overcomes an inflated length and script problems to explore universal issues of racial and religious identity.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/99/50/49/9950498_mob.jpg'),(671,'Beijing Bicycle',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beijing_bicycle/','11844','0276501',1,NULL,'Though rather repetitive in its plot, Beijing Bicycle provides an interesting look at the economic and social changes that have occurred in China.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/26/262692_mob.jpg'),(672,'Killing Bono',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/killing_bono_2010/','771210696','1535101',1,'Killing Bono is a rock\' n\' roll comedy about two Irish brothers struggling to forge their path through the 1980\'s music scene, whilst the meteoric rise to fame of their old school pals U2 only serves to cast them deeper into the shadows. -- (C) Arc',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/04/11160456_mob.jpg'),(673,'The Bounty',1984,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1002947-bounty/','10807','0086993',1,NULL,'Thanks in large part to its cast, and Anthony Hopkins in particular, The Bounty\'s retelling of the mutiny on the HMS Bounty is an intelligent, engaging adventure saga.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/45/10884508_mob.jpg'),(674,'L\'uccello dalle piume di cristallo (The Bird With the Crystal Plumage)',1969,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bird_with_the_crystal_plumage/','11371','0065143',1,NULL,'Combining a deadly thriller plot with the stylized violence that would become his trademark, The Bird with the Crystal Plumage marked an impressive horror debut for Dario Argento.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/26/03/260391_mob.jpg'),(675,'Battlefield America',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/battlefield_america/','771268201','1995260',1,'A steady look at the underbelly of the youth battle dance culture in Long Beach, California. Sean Lewis, a young, charismatic, successful businessman finds himself in the mix with a bunch of disheveled misfits Bad Boys, who have virtually no dance talent. Realizing his dilemma, Sean brings aboard a professional dance instructor to ease his responsibilities to these kids. Meanwhile, he finds himself falling for Sara, who runs the community center where the kids hangout and practice their moves. With Sean motivating them, The Bad Boys find the confidence to rise to the challenge and defeat their nemesis The Bang Squad, at the annual dance battle competition Battlefield America! -- (C) Cinedigm',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/43/11164385_mob.jpg'),(676,'A Boy and His Dog',1975,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/boy_and_his_dog/','13477','0072730',1,NULL,'An offbeat, eccentric black comedy, A Boy and His Dog features strong dialogue and an oddball vision of the future.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/99/269922_mob.jpg'),(677,'Bra Boys',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bra_boys/','671042362','0951318',1,NULL,'While it looks like shameless publicity for the semi-notorious Aussie surfing gang, the film packs a raw energy into this look at a culture of athleticism and male loyalty.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/61/75/19/6175198_mob.jpg'),(678,'Manda Bala (Send a Bullet)',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/manda_bala/','528367361','0912590',1,NULL,'The exciting and fast-paced documentary Manda Bala shows many sides of Brazil -- from the humorous and upbeat to the violent and disturbing.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/92/34/10923402_mob.jpg'),(679,'Bart Got a Room',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bart_got_a_room/','770792960','0472050',1,NULL,'Just enough sweetness and good performances lighten up the high school-set tensions, creating a family-appropriate teen comedy.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/83/10888364_mob.jpg'),(680,'Ong Bak 3',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ong_bak_3/','771203158','1653690',1,'Martial arts legend Tony Jaa writes, directs, produces and stars in ONG BAK 3, the third and final installment in one of the most beloved action series of all time. Picking up at the cliffhanger ending where Ong Bak 2 leaves off, Jaa ramps up the epic supernatural elements of the previous film, while still maintaining the trademark bone-crunching action that the series is known for. This time he must face his ultimate enemy: a fierce supernatural warrior named \"Demon Crow,\" played by fellow martial arts sensation Dan Chupong (Dynamite Warrior). Eagerly anticipated by martial arts aficionados for some time, the matchup of Jaa and Chupong is explosive. -- (C) Magnolia',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/39/11153999_mob.jpg'),(681,'20-seiki shonen: Honkaku kagaku boken eiga (20th Century Boys 1: Beginning of the End)',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/20th_century_boys_1_beginning_of_the_end/','770783644','1155705',1,NULL,'An overlong Japanese sci-fi epic with flashy visuals but a disjointed and frustrating approach to narrative.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/12/92/11129239_mob.jpg'),(682,'Blackthorn',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/blackthorn/','771234366','1629705',1,'It\'s been said (but unsubstantiated) that Butch Cassidy and the Sundance Kid were killed in a standoff with the Bolivian military in 1908. In Blackthorn, Cassidy (Shepard) survived, and is quietly living out his years under the name James Blackthorn in a secluded Bolivian village. Tired of his long exile from the US and hoping to see his family again before he dies, Cassidy sets out on the long journey home. But when an unexpected encounter with an ambitious young criminal (Eduardo Noriega) derails his plans, he is thrust into one last adventure, the likes of which he hasn\'t experienced since his glory days with the Sundance Kid. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/02/11160216_mob.jpg'),(683,'Blue Lagoon: The Awakening',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/blue_lagoon_the_awakening/','771316108',NULL,1,'Two high school students become stranded on a desert island and must rely on each other for survival.',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/81/11168160_mob.jpg'),(684,'Italiensk for Begyndere (Italian for Beginners)',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/italian_for_beginners/','770694395','0243862',1,NULL,'Unlike many romantic comedies, the charming Italian for Beginners feels natural and genuinely heart-warming.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/93/10889388_mob.jpg'),(685,'Piglet\'s Big Movie',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/piglets_big_movie/','9563','0323642',1,NULL,'Wholesome and charming entertainment for young children.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/14/06/11140647_mob.jpg'),(686,'Bad Kids Go to Hell',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bad_kids_go_to_hell/','771311824','1865573',1,'Six private school high school kids find themselves stuck in detention on a frightfully dark and stormy Saturday afternoon. During their 8 hour incarceration, each of the six kids falls victim to a horrible \"accident\" until only one of them remains. And as each of these spoiled rich kids bites the dust, the story takes on a series of humorous and frantic twists and turns. Is one of the kids secretly evening the school\'s social playing field? Or have the ghosts of prestigious Crestview Academy finally come to punish the school\'s worst (and seemingly untouchable) brats? One thing is for sure...Daddy\'s money can\'t save them now. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/72/11167299_mob.jpg'),(687,'Bats',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bats/','12256','0200469',1,NULL,'Neither scary nor creepy.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/84/58/10845890_mob.jpg'),(688,'The Oogieloves in The Big Balloon Adventure',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_oogieloves_in_the_big_balloon_adventure/','771268453','1520498',1,'It\'s Schluufy\'s birthday, and the Oogieloves (Goobie, Zoozie and Toofie), along with their friends J. Edgar, Windy Window and Ruffy, are organizing a party. (Shh! It\'s a secret.) Everything is going along just perfectly until J. Edgar trips and loses the last five magical balloons in all of Lovelyloveville--OH NO! The Oogiloves set out to find the magical balloons in time to save their friend\'s party. Along the way, they meet some very interesting characters indeed, including Dotty Rounder (Cloris Leachman), Bobby Wobbly (Carey Elwes), Milky Marvin (Chazz Palminteri), Rosalie Rosebud (Toni Braxton) and Lola and Lero Sombero (Christopher Lloyd and Jaime Pressly). Can these new friends help them recover the magical balloons and get back to the cottage in time to celebrate Schluufy\'s surprise birthday?','Although it may serve as a passing diversion for very young viewers, The Oogieloves fails to offer much more than several brightly colored examples of the worst stereotypes of modern children\'s entertainment.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/45/11164544_mob.jpg'),(689,'Blitz',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/blitz_2011/','771219711','1297919',1,'A fast-paced thriller set in contemporary London, \"Blitz\" reflects the challenges faced by a group of police officers working in a modern, multi-cultural society. A raw, gritty tale of moral ambiguity, outsiders and the sacrifices the police make to keep crime off British streets.',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/02/11160207_mob.jpg'),(690,'Perrier\'s Bounty',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/perriers_bounty/','770800141','1003034',1,NULL,'It has interesting characters and a strong cast, but Perrier\'s Bounty ultimately fails to do anything original with them.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/12/52/11125293_mob.jpg'),(691,'White Hunter Black Heart',1990,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/white_hunter_black_heart/','12019','0100928',1,NULL,'White Hunter Black Heart is powerful, intelligent, and subtly moving, a fascinating meditation on masculinity and the insecurities of artists.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/95/11159566_mob.jpg'),(692,'The Magic of Belle Isle',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_magic_of_belle_isle/','771303140','1839654',1,'Reuniting with director Rob Reiner from the hit film, The Bucket List, Freeman plays Monte Wildhorn, a famous Western novelist whose struggle with alcoholism has sapped his passion for writing. He takes a lakeside cabin for the summer in picturesque Belle Isle, and befriends the family next door-an attractive single mom (Madsen) and her young daughters-who help him find inspiration again. -- (C) Magnolia',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/43/11164387_mob.jpg'),(693,'To Be or Not to Be',1942,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1021557-to_be_or_not_to_be/','770670964','0035446',1,NULL,'A complex and timely satire with as much darkness as slapstick, Ernst Lubitsch\'s To Be or Not To Be delicately balances humor and ethics.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/91/04/09/9104098_mob.jpg'),(694,'Bright Young Things',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bright_young_things/','14505','0325123',1,NULL,'Colored with witty performances and a camp sense of satire, Stephen Fry\'s version of Evelyn Waugh\'s novel may only be fitfully successful but it does mark a promising debut for the British comic.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/86/10888614_mob.jpg'),(695,'The Princess Blade',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/princess_blade/','14563','0310149',1,NULL,'The action is fast and tightly choreographed, but The Princess Blade never draws its disparate elements into a compelling movie.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/44/10894430_mob.jpg'),(696,'Breaking Away',1979,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/breaking_away/','10225','0078902',1,NULL,'At once a touching, funny coming-of-age story and a compelling sports film, Breaking Away is a delightful treat.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/91/67/10916770_mob.jpg'),(697,'Leap Year',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ano_bisiesto/','771040664','1537401',1,'Laura is 25 years old. She\'s a journalist, she\'s single and lives in a small apartment in Mexico City. After a series of short-lived affairs, Laura meets Arturo. After the first time they make love, she is left deeply unsettled. They embark on an intense and passionate sexual relationship, in which pleasure, pain and love merge. As days go by which Laura conscientiously crosses out in a calendar, her secret past resurfaces, pushing Arturo to the limit. -- (C) Strand',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/82/11158262_mob.jpg'),(698,'The Best of Youth (La meglio gioventu)',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/best_of_youth/','277029659','0346336',1,NULL,'Earns its 6 hours running time by telling an engrossing story with compelling characters.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/14/78/11147822_mob.jpg'),(699,'Sin City',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sin_city/','29','0401792',1,NULL,'Visually groundbreaking and terrifically violent, Sin City brings the dark world of Frank Miller\'s graphic novel to vivid life.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/24/97/249791_mob.jpg'),(700,'Wedding Crashers',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wedding_crashers/','1967','0396269',1,NULL,'Wedding Crashers is both raunchy and sweet, and features top-notch comic performances from Vince Vaughn and Owen Wilson.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/24/98/249823_mob.jpg'),(701,'The Chronicles of Narnia: The Lion, The Witch and The Wardrobe',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chronicles_of_narnia_lion_witch_wardrobe/','24214','0363771',1,NULL,'With first-rate special effects and compelling storytelling, this adaptation stays faithful to its source material and will please moviegoers of all ages.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/91/87/10918786_mob.jpg'),(702,'A Cinderella Story',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cinderella_story/','10321','0356470',1,NULL,'An uninspired, generic updating of the classic fairy tale.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/79/11167920_mob.jpg'),(703,'Charlie and the Chocolate Factory',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/charlie_and_the_chocolate_factory/','1965','0367594',1,NULL,'Closer to the source material than 1971\'s Willy Wonka & the Chocolate Factory, Charlie and the Chocolate Factory is for people who like their Chocolate visually appealing and dark.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/24/98/249821_mob.jpg'),(704,'White Chicks',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/white_chicks/','17071','0381707',1,NULL,'Scattershot comedy that\'s silly and obvious.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/55/05/41/5505412_mob.jpg'),(705,'Pirates of the Caribbean: At Worlds End',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pirates_of_the_caribbean_3/','358174817','0449088',1,NULL,'POTC: AWE provides the thrilling action scenes, but mixes in too many characters with too many incomprehensible plot threads.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/95/55/10955508_mob.jpg'),(706,'Indiana Jones and the Kingdom of the Crystal Skull',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/indiana_jones_and_the_kingdom_of_the_crystal_skull/','769964099','0367882',1,NULL,'Though the plot elements are certainly familiar, Indiana Jones and the Kingdom of the Crystal Skull still delivers the thrills and Harrison Ford\'s return in the title role is more than welcome.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/86/88/10868884_mob.jpg'),(707,'Star Wars: Episode II - Attack of the Clones 3D',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/star_wars_episode_ii_attack_of_the_clones_3d/','10009','0121765',1,NULL,'Containing more of what made the Star Wars series fun, Attack of the Clones is an improvement over The Phantom Menace.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/94/47/10944721_mob.jpg'),(708,'I Now Pronounce You Chuck and Larry',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/i_now_pronounce_you_chuck_and_larry/','460334389','0762107',1,NULL,'Whether by way of inept comedy or tasteless stereotypes, I Now Pronounce You Chuck And Larry falters on both levels.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/91/19/52/9119522_mob.jpg'),(709,'Sin City: A Dame to Kill For',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sin_city_a_dame_to_kill_for/','686049251','0458481',1,'Dwight plans to have his vengeance against the woman who betrayed him, Ava Lord, while Nancy is trying to cope with Hartigan\'s death.',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/53/11165320_mob.jpg'),(710,'Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man\'s Chest',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pirates_of_the_caribbean_dead_mans_chest/','190815398','0383574',1,NULL,'Gone is Depp\'s unpredictability and much of the humor and originality of the first movie.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/78/63/786362_mob.jpg'),(711,'Texas Chainsaw 3D',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/texas_chainsaw_3d/','771247162','1928299',1,'A chainsaw-yielding killer known as Leatherface terrorizes a group of young teens.','As an ugly and cynical attempt to rebrand Leatherface as horror anti-hero, Texas Chainsaw 3D is a bold move for the franchise.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/74/11167480_mob.jpg'),(712,'G.I. Joe: Rise of Cobra',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/gi_joe/','770677827','1046173',1,NULL,'While fans of the Hasbro toy franchise may revel in a bit of nostalgia, G.I. Joe: The Rise of Cobra is largely a cartoonish, over-the-top action fest propelled by silly writing, inconsistent visual effects, and merely passable performances.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/12/33/11123308_mob.jpg'),(713,'The Hunger Games: Catching Fire',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_hunger_games_catching_fire/','771250004','1951264',1,'THE HUNGER GAMES: CATCHING FIRE begins as Katniss Everdeen has returned home safe after winning the 74th Annual Hunger Games along with fellow tribute Peeta Mellark. Winning means that they must turn around and leave their family and close friends, embarking on a \"Victor\'s Tour\" of the districts. Along the way Katniss senses that a rebellion is simmering, but the Capitol is still very much in control as President Snow prepares the 75th Annual Hunger Games (The Quarter Quell) - a competition that could change Panem forever. (c) Lionsgate',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/86/11168606_mob.jpg'),(714,'G.I. Joe: Retaliation',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/gi_joe_retaliation/','771241227','1583421',1,'In this sequel, the G.I. Joes are not only fighting their mortal enemy Cobra; they are forced to contend with threats from within the government that jeopardize their very existence. -- (C) Paramount',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/79/11167989_mob.jpg'),(715,'The Chronicles of Narnia: Prince Caspian',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chronicles_of_narnia_prince_caspian/','680139028','0499448',1,NULL,'The Chronicles of Narnia: Prince Caspian is an entertaining family adventure worthy of the standard set by its predecessor.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/12/92/11129292_mob.jpg'),(716,'RoboCop',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1200731-robocop/','770803774','1234721',1,'Robocop gets rebooted in this big-screen MGM production from director Jose Padilha. The picture will once again surround a slain police officer (played by The Killing\'s Joel Kinnaman) who gets resurrected as a crime-fighting cyborg until memories of his previous life begin to make him doubt his corrupt corporate overlords. Gary Oldman co-stars as the doctor who suffers a crisis-of-conscience after bringing life back to the man in the form of a mechanical body and reprogrammed brain, while Samuel L. Jackson plays a larger-than-life media mogul. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/86/76/10867607_mob.jpg'),(717,'Carrie',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/carrie/','771305077','1939659',1,'A reimagining of the classic horror tale about Carrie White (Chloe Grace Moretz), a shy girl outcast by her peers and sheltered by her deeply religious mother (Julianne Moore), who unleashes telekinetic terror on her small town after being pushed too far at her senior prom. Based on the best-selling novel by Stephen King, Carrie is directed by Kimberly Peirce with a screenplay by Roberto Aguirre-Sacasa. (c) Sony',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/72/11167282_mob.jpg'),(718,'Disney\'s A Christmas Carol',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10008502-christmas_carol/','770679843','1067106',1,NULL,'Robert Zemeckis\' 3-D animated take on the Dickens classic tries hard, but its dazzling special effects distract from an array of fine performances from Jim Carrey and Gary Oldman.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/90/90/10909071_mob.jpg'),(719,'The Croods',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the-croods/','770818015','0481499',1,'Set in the prehistoric era, a man\'s position as Leader of the Hunt is threatened by the arrival of a prehistoric genius who comes up with revolutionary new inventions ... like fire.',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/71/11167120_mob.jpg'),(720,'Captain America: The Winter Soldier',2014,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/captain_america_the_winter_soldier_2014/','771312513','1843866',1,'Steve Rogers continues his journey as the super-powered American soldier who\'s grasping to find his place in a modern world after being frozen in ice since WWII with this Marvel Studios sequel. Chris Evans returns to star, with Community director/producers Joe and Anthony Russo helming. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(721,'Anchorman 2: The Legend Continues',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/anchorman_2_the_legend_continues/','771303861','1229340',1,'The continuing, escalating misadventures of a humble San Diego news anchor.',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/52/11165268_mob.jpg'),(722,'The Haunting in Connecticut 2: Ghosts of Georgia',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_haunting_in_connecticut_2_ghosts_of_georgia/','771323314','1457765',1,'Building on the terror of A Haunting in Connecticut, this horrifying tale traces a young family\'s nightmarish descent into a centuries-old Southern hell. When Andy Wyrick (Chad Michael Murray, House of Wax) moves his wife Lisa (Abigail Spencer, TV\'s \"Mad Men\") and daughter Heidi to an historic home in Georgia, they quickly discover they are not the house\'s only inhabitants. Joined by Lisa\'s free-spirited sister, Joyce (Katee Sackhoff, TV\'s \"Battlestar Galactica\"), the family soon comes face-to-face with a bone-chilling mystery born of a deranged desire...a haunting secret rising from underground and threatening to bring down anyone in its path.',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/81/11168194_mob.jpg'),(723,'Temptation: Confessions of a Marriage Counselor',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/temptation_confessions_of_a_marriage_counselor/','771265737','2070862',1,'SYNOPSIS: A bold exploration of the intrigue and perils of infidelity, Tyler Perry\'s Temptation: Confessions of a Marriage Counselor is a compelling love story that dives straight into the heart of obsessive passion. \"It\'s about a woman who starts to get restless in her relationship and her choice to be with another man has a huge effect on the rest of her life,\" explains screenwriter/producer/director Tyler Perry. \"She goes on a journey - in her career and in her marriage - and she ends up in a very different place than she expected.\" In a departure from his previous dramas, this explosive film finds Perry exploring the nature of desire - and just how powerful and dangerous a taste of the forbidden can be. \"This is definitely one of the most provocative movies - sexually and otherwise - that I\'ve made,\" says the director. \"There are a lot of people who struggle in their relationships. They make bad choices about their marriages. They get divorced. And so many of them don\'t step out of their situation and really think about the consequences of what they\'re doing. This movie asks, \'Are you sure you want to do this?\' It sends up a flag.\" (c) Lionsgate',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/85/11168592_mob.jpg'),(724,'A Glimpse Inside the Mind of Charles Swan III',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_glimpse_inside_the_mind_of_charles_swan_iii/','771316890','2044729',1,'Set in a stylized Los Angeles, \'A GLIMPSE INSIDE THE MIND OF CHARLES SWAN III\' is a playful comedy of lost love, friendship, revenge fantasies, and Brandy Alexanders. Charles (Charlie Sheen) is a successful graphic designer whose fame, money and charm have provided him with a seemingly perfect life. When his true love, a perplexing beauty named Ivana, suddenly breaks off their relationship, Charles\' life falls apart and he swirls into a downward spiral of doubt, confusion and reflection. With the support of his loyal intimates- Kirby (Jason Schwartzman), Saul (Bill Murray), and his sister, Izzy (Patricia Arquette) -- he begins the hard road of self-evaluation to come to terms with a life without Ivana. The film begs the question: Is it possible to love and hate someone at the same time? (c) A24',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/87/11168725_mob.jpg'),(725,'The Conjuring',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_conjuring/','771312656','1457767',1,'Before there was Amityville, there was Harrisville. \"The Conjuring\" tells the true story of Ed and Lorraine Warren (Patrick Wilson, Vera Farmiga), world renowned paranormal investigators, who were called to help a family terrorized by a dark presence in a secluded farmhouse. Forced to confront a powerful demonic entity, the Warrens find themselves caught in the most horrifying case of their lives.(c) WB',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(726,'Casino Royale',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/casino_royale/','358179513','0381061',1,NULL,'Casino Royale disposes of the silliness and gadgetry that plagued recent James Bond outings, and Daniel Craig delivers what fans and critics have been waiting for: a caustic, haunted, intense reinvention of 007.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/12/81/11128111_mob.jpg'),(727,'The Company You Keep',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_company_you_keep/','771249150','1381404',1,'A wanted man and former member of the revolutionary militant group the Weather Underground goes on the run after a journalist (Shia LaBeouf) outs him in this political thriller based on Neil Gordon\'s novel. Robert Redford stars and directs this Voltage Pictures/Wildwood Enterprises production. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/75/11167522_mob.jpg'),(728,'Sound City',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sound_city/','771323012','2306745',1,'Deep in the San Fernando Valley, amidst rows of dilapidated warehouses, was rock n\' roll\'s best kept secret: Sound City. America\'s greatest unsung recording studio housed a one-of-a-kind console, and as its legend grew, seminal bands and artists such as Fleetwood Mac, Neil Young, Rick Springfield, Tom Petty, Metallica and Nirvana all came out to put magic to tape. Directed by Dave Grohl (Nirvana, Foo Fighters) and featuring interviews and performances from the iconic musicians who recorded some of rock\'s greatest albums at the studio, Sound City doesn\'t just tell the story of this real-life rock \'n\' roll shrine, it celebrates the human element of music as Grohl gathers some of rock\'s biggest artists to collaborate on a new album. Using Sound City\'s legendary analog console, together these artists continue to create musical miracles in a digital world. (c) Variance',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/85/11168569_mob.jpg'),(729,'In Another Country',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/in_another_country/','771307312','1989712',1,'Legendary French actress Isabelle Huppert (The Piano Teacher, 8 Women, La ceremonie, and the current Amour) stars in the first English-language film from South Korean master Hong Sang-soo (Hahaha, The Day He Arrives, Virgin Stripped Bare by Her Bachelors, Woman on the Beach). The Village Voice calls the film \"the love child Antonioni and Hou Hsiao-hsien never had.\" In a triptych of overlapping stories, three different French women (a filmmaker, an adulterer and a divorce - Huppert, Huppert and... Huppert) visit a small Korean resort town and encounter a flirtatious director, a lovestruck lifeguard and far too much soju. Hong\'s latest tale(s) of love, lust and misunderstanding, IN ANOTHER COUNTRY is an effortless, laugh-out-loud comedy that plays like a lost French New Wave classic. Official Selection: Cannes International Film Festival (c) Kino',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/80/11168018_mob.jpg'),(730,'Clandestine Childhood',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/infancia_clandestina/','771307284','1726888',1,'Argentina, 1979. After years of exile, Juan (12) and his family come back to Argentina under fake identities. Juan\'s parents and his uncle Beto are members of the Montoneros Organization, which is fighting against the Military Junta that rules the country. Because of their political activities they are being tracked down relentlessly, and the threat of capture and even death is constant. However, Juan\'s daily life is also full of warmth and humor, and he quickly and easily integrates into his new environment. His friends at school and the girl he has a gigantic crush on, Maria, know him as Ernesto, a name he must not forget, since his family\'s survival is at stake. Juan accepts this and follows all of his parents\' rules until one day he is told that they need to move again immediately, and leave his friends and Maria behind without an explanation. This is a story about militancy, undercover life, and love. The story of a clandestine childhood. (c) Film Movement',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/85/11168589_mob.jpg'),(731,'Upstream Color',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/upstream_color/','771322544','2084989',1,'A man and woman are drawn together, entangled in the life cycle of an ageless organism. (c) Official Facebook',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/78/11167896_mob.jpg'),(732,'The Call',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_call_2013/','771324197',NULL,1,'When veteran 911 operator, Jordan, takes a life-altering call from a teenage girl who has just been abducted, she realizes that she must confront a killer from her past in order to save the girl\'s life.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(733,'Supporting Characters',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/supporting_characters/','771315058','1874789',1,'Best friends Nick (Alex Karpovsky, \"Girls\") and Darryl (co-writer Tarik Lowe) are a New York film editing duo hired to salvage a botched comedy from a manic director (Kevin Corrigan, PINEAPPLE EXPRESS) gone AWOL. But what starts as a simple job quickly sends their relationships-with their significant others and each other-reeling. Amidst trouble with his fiancee (Sophia Takal, V/H/S), Nick finds himself falling for the film\'s flirtatious ingenue (Arielle Kebbel, \"90210\"); Darryl, meanwhile, struggles to focus on his editing work in between fights with his tempestuous girlfriend (Melonie Diaz, Be Kind Rewind). With real humor and heart, Supporting Characters offers a sharp, knowing take on life and love in the big city. (c) Tribeca Film',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/82/11168233_mob.jpg'),(734,'Tyler Perry\'s A Madea\'s Christmas',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tyler_perrys_a_madeas_christmas/','771320506','2609758',1,'Madea gets coaxed into helping a friend pay her daughter a surprise visit in the country for Christmas, but the biggest surprise is what they\'ll find when they arrive. As the small, rural town prepares for its annual Christmas Carnival, new secrets are revealed and old relationships are tested while Madea dishes her own brand of Christmas Spirit to all. (c) Lionsgate',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(735,'Captain Phillips',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/captain_phillips/','771264988','1535109',1,'The true story of Richard Phillips, the cargo ship captain who surrender himself over to Somali pirates so that his crew could be let free is adapted by screenwriter Billy Ray in this Paul Greengrass-directed docudrama starring Tom Hanks. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(736,'Cloudy 2: Revenge of the Leftovers',2014,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cloudy_2_revenge_of_the_leftovers/','771271679','1985966',1,'Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs 2 picks up where Sony Pictures Animation\'s hit comedy left off. Inventor Flint Lockwood\'s genius is finally being recognized as he\'s invited by his idol Chester V to join The Live Corp Company, where the best and brightest inventors in the world create technologies for the betterment of mankind. Chester\'s right-hand-gal - and one of his greatest inventions - is Barb (a highly evolved orangutan with a human brain, who is also devious, manipulative and likes to wear lipstick). It\'s always been Flint\'s dream to be recognized as a great inventor, but everything changes when he discovers that his most infamous machine (which turns water into food) is still operating and is now creating food-animal hybrids - \"foodimals!\" With the fate of humanity in his hands, Chester sends Flint and his friends on a dangerously delicious mission, battling hungry tacodiles, shrimpanzees, apple pie-thons, double bacon cheespiders and other food creatures to save the world again!',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(737,'Caesar Must Die',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/caesar_must_die_2012/','771284344','2177511',1,'Winner of the Golden Bear at the Berlinale, Paolo and Vittorio Taviani\'s Caesar Must Die deftly melds narrative and documentary in a transcendently powerful drama-within-a-drama. The film was made in Rome\'s Rebibbia Prison, where the inmates are preparing to stage Shakespeare\'s Julius Caesar. After a competitive casting process, the roles are eventually allocated, and the prisoners begin exploring the text, finding in its tale of fraternity, power and betrayal parallels to their own lives and stories. Hardened criminals, many with links to organised crime, these actors find great motivation in performing the play. As we witness the rehearsals, beautifully photographed in various nooks and crannies within the prison, we see the inmates also work through their own conflicts, both internal and between each other. -- (C) Adopt',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/53/11165325_mob.jpg'),(738,'Crawlspace',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crawlspace/','771316700','1890375',1,'Deep in the heart of the unforgiving Australian desert lies Pine Gap, a top-secret government facility operated by the United States military. When the base comes under attack from unknown forces, an elite team is sent in to extract the military scientists. They encounter a beautiful young woman with no memory of how she came to be in the base, and find it overrun by disturbed patients from the base\'s medical sector. But as the squad delves deeper it becomes clear that there is something far more sinister - and far more dangerous - going on at Pine Gap. A taut thriller that recalls the best classic sci-fi action films, Crawlspace is the feature debut of Justin Dix - an award winning special effects supervisor who has worked with George Lucas and Roger Donaldson. (c) IFC Films',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/82/11168278_mob.jpg'),(739,'As Luck Would Have It',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/as_luck_would_have_it_2013/','771266725','1808240',1,'Roberto (famed Spanish comic Jose Mota) once had a promising careers in advertising. But now out of work during the economic downturn, he struggles to keep his family afloat and their dire situation a secret from his adoring wife Luisa (Salma Hayek). After yet another dead end interview, it seems like reality will come crashing down on Roberto - until a freak car accident places him at the center of a wild media storm. Realizing his opportunity, Roberto hires a brazen agent to help him leverage his new found fame into fortune, but Luisa begins to worry about what lengths Roberto will go to for his family\'s security. The new film from beloved cult director Alex de la Iglesia goes into fresh territory for the daring director, a dark comedy/social satire that also works as a deeply felt drama about the devotion of a husband and father. A wild riff on manhood in the modern media world, As Luck Would Have It is a skewed take on the strange world we live in.(c) IFC Films',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/86/11168662_mob.jpg'),(740,'InAPPropriate Comedy',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/inappropriate_comedy/','771321662','1754811',1,'INAPPROPRIATE COMEDY is a no-holds barred sketch movie starring Academy Award-winner Adrien Brody as \"Flirty Harry,\" a tough, no nonsense cop with a soft middle and a flair for fashion; Rob Schneider in a dual role as both a sleazy, horny psychologist and a curmudgeonly porn critic alongside his enthusiastic counterpart Michelle Rodriguez; Lindsay Lohan living out her fantasy of taking an ultimate revenge on the salivating paparazzi who haunt her, and Ari Shaffir as \"The Amazing Racist,\" whose hilariously offensive hidden-camera encounters with members of different ethnic and minority groups push everyone\'s buttons. (c) Freestyle',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/83/11168369_mob.jpg'),(741,'Violeta Went to Heaven',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/violeta_went_to_heaven/','771257817','2014392',1,'From the marquee that she built in Santiago, Chile, Violeta Parra is visited by people who shaped her life. She\'s alive, but perhaps she\'s dead. We\'ll gradually find out her secrets, fears, frustrations and joys. Not only presenting her multiple works, but also her memories, her loves and her hopes. Her achievements are suspended in a passionate journey with the characters who made her dream, laugh and cry.(c) Official Site',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/87/11168785_mob.jpg'),(742,'Kai Po Che!',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kai_po_che/','771306559','2213054',1,'Synopsis: Best friends Ishaan, Omi and Govind - young, ambitious and restless - are trying to make a mark in the India of the early 2000\'s. These are exciting times - a new millennium has just dawned, India\'s a nuclear power and ostensibly shining - a perfect place for the 3 Ahmedabad boys to start a business that could be their ticket to fame and riches. In a country where cricket is religion, they hit upon a brilliant plan - to start a training academy that could produce India\'s next sporting superstars! What follows is without doubt the greatest adventure of their lives, as they attempt to navigate the big hurdles in the path of fulfilling their dreams. (c) UTV',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/46/11164686_mob.jpg'),(743,'Clip',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/clip/','771303327','1900908',1,'Clip is a dynamic, disturbing portrait of contemporary youth. Jasna, played fearlessly by Isidora Simijonovic, is a pretty girl in her mid-teens. With a terminally ill father and dispirited mother at home, she is disillusioned by her unglamorous life in a remote Serbian town. Opposing everyone, including herself, she goes experimenting with sex, drugs and partying. (c) Artsploitation',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(744,'ABCD: Anybody Can Dance',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/abcd_anybody_can_dance/','771321449','2321163',1,'For Vishnu (Prabhudheva), widely regarded as India\'s best dancer, dance is more than a passion - it\'s the reason he lives! So when he finds himself thrown out from the swish dance academy he himself set up, by his manipulative business partner, it feels like the oxygen has been sucked out from the air he breathes. Heart-broken, Vishnu decides to give up dance and leave Mumbai forever. However the night before his departure he witnesses a most amazing sight - a group of dancers preparing for the upcoming Ganpati Dance Battle - an annual festival that pits Mumbai\'s best dance groups against each other. Watching the raw talent of these amazing dancers helps Vishnu arrive at a decision - he will take this disparate group under his wing, help them overcome their personal rivalries and past demons and turn them into India\'s best dance squad!. From India\'s biggest film studio, UTV Motion Pictures, and renowned choreographer & director, Remo D\'souza comes India\'s first dance film in 3D-a spectacular entertainer that proves yet again that if you dare to dream, impossible is nothing! (c) UTV',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(745,'Carmen: Royal Opera House/London',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/carmen-royal-opera-houselondon/','770798607',NULL,1,'With Anna Caterina Antonacci and Jonas Kaufmann bringing rare erotic intensity to the drama of Carmen and Don Jose, this new Royal Opera production is a darkly passionate reading of one of the world\'s favourite operas.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(746,'La Scala Opera Series: Don Carlo',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/la-scala-opera-series-don-carlo/','770855613',NULL,1,'\"Don Carlo\" is possibly the most intense, deep, nuanced, rich, and masterful work of the \"mature\" Giuseppe Verdi, an extensive and monumental showcase of everything Verdi. It is also the Verdi opera that exists in the most number of versions. The version of this \"Grand Opera\" that will officially inaugurate the 2008-09 La Scala Opera Season is the 1884 Four Acts version that Verdi reduced and changed into Italian from the original 1867 Five Acts version in French. The story is based on conflicts in the life of Carlos, Prince of Asturias, after his betrothed Elisabeth of Valois was married instead to his father Philip II of Spain as part of the peace treaty ending the Italian War of 1551-1559 between the Houses of Habsburg and Valois.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(747,'Chapters',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chapters_2013/','771323888','2567370',1,'The film is narrated in text book format with every new link to the story is presented as a new chapter. The first chapter talks about four friends who are unemployed and in need of quick money. To make some money for Krishna Kumar\'s sister\'s wedding, they venture out for a risky adventure that will make them rich. It all works out well until the end when their plan goes all awry. In the second chapter, we see another group of six youngsters heading for a journey to a hill station, to register a marriage - that of Shyam and Priya. When the group return to their car after stopping for a brief while, they find a dead body in it. The group disperses in panic. The third chapter is about a long bus journey. Sethu, a middle-aged man, is on his way to the hospital, where his young son awaits a surgery and chemotherapy. Because he is carrying a huge sum of money for his young son\'s cancer treatment, Sethu is nervous and suspicious of his fellow passengers. Meanwhile, he strikes up a conversation with an old lady sitting next to him who reveals that she has a son who is in jail. In the fourth and final chapter, we see an anxious lady, Annie waiting by her son\'s bedside in the hospital awaiting her husband\'s arrival. She is astonished when he arrives with the money, but refrains from taxing him with further questions. She does manage to convince him however that the money that he has brought in should better be left where it truly belongs. The final scenes explain how the different chapters are interlinked. Though some of the characters never meet, there is a link that connects them all...',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(748,'The Condemned',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_condemned_2013/','771325239','1980959',1,'Determined to restore her dying father\'s reputation, Ana travels to the remote town of Rosales. Decades ago, he settled there and opened his first free clinic for cancer research. He launched an illustrious medical career - and fell in love. (c) Official FB',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(749,'Teatro Real De Madrid: Cavalleria Rusticana & Pagliacci',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/teatro_real_de_madrid_cavalleria_rusticana_and_pagliacci/','771038970',NULL,1,'You may be confused about the title of this opera. That\'s because it\'s TWO operas. There\'s a long-standing tradition of showing these two operas, \"Cavalleria Rusticana,\" by Mascagni, and \"Pagliacci,\" by Leoncavallo, on the same billing. They\'re both quite brief, and in a similar style, so it works. One of the most famous images in all of opera -- Pavarotti putting white clown makeup on while crying and singing a sad, sad song -- is from Pagliacci.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(750,'Philip Roth: Unmasked',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/philip_roth_unmasked/','771270799','2042628',1,'Philip Roth, arguably America\'s greatest living novelist, turns 80 on March 19. In 1959, his collection of short stories, Goodbye, Columbus, put him on the map, and 10 years later his hilarious, ribald best-seller, Portnoy\'s Complaint, gave rise to the first of many Roth-related controversies in which Judaism, sex, the role of women, and the parent-child relationship would take center stage. In candid interviews, the Pulitzer Prize-winner discusses his distinctly unliterary upbringing in Newark, NJ, his admiration for Saul Bellow and Bernard Malamud, his \"brutal and lurid\" first marriage, and how Zuckerman may or may not be his alter-ego. Nathan Englander, Mia Farrow, Jonathan Franzen, and Martin Garbus are among those who talk about the man and his writing. Franzen in particular praises Roth for \"how brave he must have been to have methodically offended everybody and to have exposed parts of himself no one had ever exposed before.\"',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(751,'The Metropolitan Opera: Giulio Cesare',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_metropolitan_opera_giulio_cesare/','771304284',NULL,1,'The opera that conquered London in Handel\'s time comes to the Met in David McVicar\'s inventive production--which triumphed at its Glyndebourne premiere in 2005. The Guardian praised McVicar\'s -- witty, sexy, and tragic post-colonial framing of Handel\'s Caesar and Cleopatra tale, -- which incorporates elements of Baroque theater and 19th-century British imperialism to illuminate the opera\'s ideas of love, war, and empire building. The world\'s leading countertenor, David Daniels, sings the title role opposite Natalie Dessay as an irresistibly exotic Cleopatra. Baroque specialist Harry Bicket conducts.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(752,'The Metropolitan Opera: Giulio Cesare Encore',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_metropolitan_opera_giulio_cesare_encore/','771310580',NULL,1,'The opera that conquered London in Handel\'s time comes to the Met in David McVicar\'s inventive production--which triumphed at its Glyndebourne premiere in 2005. The Guardian praised McVicar\'s --witty, sexy, and tragic post-colonial framing of Handel\'s Caesar and Cleopatra tale,-- which incorporates elements of Baroque theater and 19th-century British imperialism to illuminate the opera\'s ideas of love, war, and empire building. The world\'s leading countertenor, David Daniels, sings the title role opposite Natalie Dessay as an irresistibly exotic Cleopatra. Baroque specialist Harry Bicket conducts.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(753,'An Evening With Crystal Pite: Nederlands Dans Theater',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/an_evening_with_crystal_pite_nederlands_dans_theater/','771322505',NULL,1,'Renowned for her flowing, organic, and poetic style, Crystal Pite has succeeded in bringing her surprising and innovative dance approach to a wide audience. Fascinated by familiar storylines of love, conflict and loss, and the body\'s role in providing the illustrative shape of those stories, in Pite\'s vision, life is an epic tale which she strives to reflect in her ballets through the viewer\'s own tale.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(754,'Silver Circle',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/silver_circle/','771325241','1748199',1,'At the center of corruption is the Federal Reserve who has gained enormous amounts of control over America\'s economy, with disastrous effects beginning to show. Standing opposite, is the band of Rebels who have vowed to take back the freedom they once knew...and they won\'t go down without a fight. Monetary mayhem. Explosions. Romance. Silver Circle plans to take indie animation to a whole other level. (c) Official Site',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(755,'Fight Club',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fight_club/','13153','0137523',1,NULL,'Solid acting, amazing direction, and elaborate production design make Fight Club a wild ride.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/48/11164849_mob.jpg'),(756,'Cloverfield',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cloverfield/','770673272','1060277',1,NULL,'A sort of Blair Witch Project crossed with Godzilla, Cloverfield is economically paced, stylistically clever, and filled with scares.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168927_mob.jpg'),(757,'Coraline',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/coraline/','770680446','0327597',1,NULL,'With its vivid stop-motion animation combined with Neil Gaiman\'s imaginative story, Coraline is a film that\'s both visually stunning and wondrously entertaining.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/16/10891629_mob.jpg'),(758,'Cirque du Freak: The Vampire\'s Assistant',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/vampires_assistant/','770767597','0450405',1,NULL,'This overstuffed, scattershot vampire flick suffers from poor characterization and an unwieldy mix of scares and chuckles.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/12/17/11121754_mob.jpg'),(759,'Sex and the City',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sex_and_the_city/','770680567','1000774',1,NULL,'Sex and the City loses steam in the transition to the big screen, but will still thrill fans of the show.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/83/84/10838483_mob.jpg'),(760,'Shrek Forever After (Shrek 4)',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shrek_4/','770810590','0892791',1,'A domesticated Shrek hatches a plan to recapture his mojo and discovers what life in Far Far Away land would have been like had he never existed in this final chapter of the popular animated film series. There used to be a time when the villagers would run in terror at the mere mention of the name Shrek, but these days the big green ogre is married to Princess Fiona and raising triplets. Maintaining your fierce public persona is no simple task when you\'re juggling infants and changing diapers, so when Shrek realizes that nobody is afraid of him anymore he recruits mischief-maker Rumpelstiltskin to restore his once-mighty roar. Unfortunately for Shrek, that plan hits an unexpected hitch. As a result, the morose monster takes a trip into an alternate-universe Far Far Away land where there is no Shrek, and Rumpelstiltskin reigns. There, Donkey spends his days hauling carts, and a portly Puss in Boots prefers lounging to swashbuckling. Perhaps with a little extra effort, Shrek will be able to regain his status as top ogre in town and still have his happily ever after, too. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','While not without its moments, Shrek Forever After too often feels like a rote rehashing of the franchise\'s earlier entries.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/12/76/11127605_mob.jpg'),(761,'Clash of the Titans',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/clash_of_the_titans_2010/','770805266','0800320',1,'The 1981 mythological fantasy adventure Clash of the Titans is resurrected in this remake from Incredible Hulk director Louis Leterrier. Discovered at sea as an infant by a weary fisherman, demigod Perseus (Sam Worthington) grows up with no real knowledge of his celestial origins until his watchful guardian, Io (Gemma Arterton), informs him that he is the offspring of Zeus (Liam Neeson). When Zeus\' brother Hades (Ralph Fiennes) casually wipes out Perseus\' family, the grieving son vows to show the gods just what kind of damage humankind can inflict on its creators. Before long, Perseus and a small group of soldiers are venturing out into the desert in order to find a way to stop the Kraken, a terrifying force of nature that an indignant Hades has vowed to unleash upon man should they fail to offer up beloved princess Andromeda (Alexa Davalos) as a sacrifice. Along the way, the soldiers encounter a trio of frightening witches with second sight, contend with Hades\' devoted servant Calibos (Jason Flemyng), battle giant scorpions, and come face to face with Medusa (Natalia Vodianova), the dreaded gorgon whose gaze has the power to turn men into stone. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','An obviously affectionate remake of the 1981 original, Louis Leterrier\'s Clash of the Titans doesn\'t offer enough visual thrills to offset the deficiencies of its script.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/71/11167122_mob.jpg'),(762,'Cars',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cars/','155655062','0317219',1,NULL,'While the story may not reach the high standards of Toy Story and The Incredibles, viewers of all ages will marvel at the technical brilliance of the animation and come away satisfied.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/92/20/10922005_mob.jpg'),(763,'Cop Out',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cop_out/','770805261','1385867',1,'Bruce Willis and Tracy Morgan team up for the Warner Bros. police buddy movie Cop Out in this Kevin Smith-directed production. From a script by Robb and Mark Cullen, the story centers around police detectives Jimmy (Willis), a no-B.S. divorced dad, and Paul (Morgan), a crazy-talking loose cannon. Despite nine years as partners, the two lawmen can still sometimes seem like polar opposites -- especially when Paul\'s unpredictable antics get them suspended without pay. Already strapped for cash and trying to pay for his daughter\'s wedding, Jimmy decides to sell a rare baseball card that\'s worth tens of thousands. Unfortunately, when the collector\'s shop is robbed and the card vanishes with the crook, Paul and Jimmy end up going rogue, tracking down the card and the drug ring behind its theft, all on their own time, and without any backup -- except for each other. ~ Cammila Albertson, Rovi','Cop Out is a cliched buddy action/comedy that suffers from stale gags and slack pacing.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/95/25/10952541_mob.jpg'),(764,'The Da Vinci Code',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/da_vinci_code/','155654983','0382625',1,NULL,'What makes Dan Brown\'s novel a best seller is evidently not present in this dull and bloated movie adaptation of The Da Vinci Code.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/31/42/314213_mob.jpg'),(765,'Fred Claus',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1175076-fred_claus/','650942914','0486583',1,NULL,'A slew of talent is wasted in this contrived and overly sentimental Christmas film, which can\'t quite get the balance between slapstick humor and sentimental family moments.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/86/17/10861789_mob.jpg'),(766,'Click',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/click/','155655187','0389860',1,NULL,'This latest Adam Sandler vehicle borrows shamelessly from It\'s A Wonderful Life and Back To The Future, and fails to produce the necessary laughs that would forgive such imitation.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/98/10889889_mob.jpg'),(767,'The Spiderwick Chronicles',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spiderwick_chronicles/','770669821','0416236',1,NULL,'The Spiderwick Chronicles is an entertaining children\'s adventure, with heart and imagination to spare.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/93/69/42/9369420_mob.jpg'),(768,'Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/harry_potter_and_the_chamber_of_secrets/','10031','0295297',1,NULL,'Though perhaps more enchanting for younger audiences, Chamber of Secrets is nevertheless both darker and livelier than its predecessor, expanding and improving upon the first film\'s universe.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/87/11168797_mob.jpg'),(769,'The Cabin in the Woods',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_cabin_in_the_woods/','770785486','1259521',1,'Five friends go to a remote cabin in the woods. Bad things happen. If you think you know this story, think again. From fan favorites Joss Whedon and Drew Goddard comes The Cabin in the Woods, a mind blowing horror film that turns the genre inside out. -- (C) Lionsgate','The Cabin in the Woods is an astonishing meta-feat, capable of being funny, strange, and scary -- frequently all at the same time.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/41/11164153_mob.jpg'),(770,'Children of Men',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/children_of_men/','326459204','0206634',1,NULL,'Children of Men works on every level: as a violent chase thriller, a fantastical cautionary tale, and a sophisticated human drama about societies struggling to live. This taut and thought-provoking tale may not have the showy special effects normally found in movies of this genre, but you won\'t care one bit after the story kicks in, about a dystopic future where women can no longer conceive and hope lies within one woman who holds the key to humanity\'s survival. It will have you riveted.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/27/04/67/2704676_mob.jpg'),(771,'The Golden Compass',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/his_dark_materials_the_golden_compass/','494046103','0385752',1,NULL,'Without the bite or the controversy of the source material, The Golden Compass is reduced to impressive visuals overcompensating for lax storytelling.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/86/11168632_mob.jpg'),(772,'Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakquel',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10009926-alvin_and_the_chipmunks_2/','770805259','1231580',1,NULL,'This Squeakquel may entertain the kiddies, but it\'s low on energy and heavily reliant on slapstick humor.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/93/88/10938869_mob.jpg'),(773,'Journey 2: The Mysterious Island',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/journey_to_the_center_of_the_earth_2_3d/','771042281','1397514',1,'In this follow-up to the 2008 worldwide hit Journey to the Center of the Earth, the new 3D family adventure Journey 2: The Mysterious Island begins when young Sean Anderson (Josh Hutcherson, reprising his role from the first film) receives a coded distress signal from a mysterious island where no island should exist. It\'s a place of strange life forms, mountains of gold, deadly volcanoes, and more than one astonishing secret. Unable to stop him from going, Sean\'s new stepfather, Hank (Dwayne Johnson), joins the quest. Together with a helicopter pilot (Luis Guzman) and his beautiful, strong-willed daughter (Vanessa Hudgens), they set out to find the island, rescue its lone inhabitant and escape before seismic shockwaves force the island under the sea and bury its treasures forever. -- (C) Official Site','Aggressively unambitious, Journey 2 might thrill tween viewers, but most others will find it too intense for young audiences and too cartoonishly dull for adults.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/54/11165487_mob.jpg'),(774,'Sex and the City 2',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sex_and_the_city_2/','770805765','1261945',1,'The stars of the hit HBO series reunite with original writer/producer/director Michael Patrick King to deliver this sequel that finds the ladies venturing outside New York City for the adventure of a lifetime. Carrie (Sarah Jessica Parker), Charlotte (Kristin Davis), and Miranda (Cynthia Nixon) are all married now, but they\'re still up for a little fun in the sun. When Samantha (Kim Cattrall) gets the chance to visit one of the most extravagant vacation destinations on the planet and offers to bring them all along, they surmise that a women-only retreat may be the perfect excuse to eschew their responsibilities and remember what life was like before they decided to settle down. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Straining under a thin plot stretched to its limit by a bloated running time, Sex and the City 2 adds an unfortunate coda to the long-running HBO series.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/12/47/11124787_mob.jpg'),(775,'Couples Retreat',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/couples_retreat/','770803584','1078940',1,NULL,'Despite a talented cast and some reliably pleasant interplay between Jon Favreau and Vince Vaughn, Couples Retreat leaves viewers stranded in an arid, mirthless comedy.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/12/67/11126761_mob.jpg'),(776,'Changeling',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1191742_changeling/','770677185','0824747',1,NULL,'Beautifully shot and well-acted, Changeling is a compelling story that unfortunately gives in to convention too often.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/86/09/10860981_mob.jpg'),(777,'Confessions of a Shopaholic',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/confessions_of_a_shopaholic/','770679228','1093908',1,NULL,'This middling romantic comedy underutilizes a talented cast and delivers muddled messages on materialism and conspicuous consumption.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/40/10884041_mob.jpg'),(778,'The Covenant',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/covenant/','287865019','0475944',1,NULL,'The Covenant plays out like a teen soap opera, full of pretty faces, wooden acting, laughable dialogue, and little suspense.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/23/86/16/2386162_mob.jpg'),(779,'The Haunting in Connecticut',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1188732-haunting_in_connecticut/','770682442','0492044',1,NULL,'Though it features a few scares and some creepy atmosphere, The Haunting in Connecticut ultimately relies too much on familiar horror cliches to achieve its goals.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/14/64/11146446_mob.jpg'),(780,'Law Abiding Citizen',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/law_abiding_citizen/','770804709','1197624',1,NULL,'Unnecessarily violent and unflinchingly absurd, Law Abiding Citizen is plagued by subpar acting and a story that defies reason.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/72/10897297_mob.jpg'),(781,'Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pirates_of_the_caribbean_on_stranger_tides/','770855546','1298650',1,'Johnny Depp returns to his iconic role of Captain Jack Sparrow in an action-packed adventure. Crossing paths with the enigmatic Angelica (Penelope Cruz), he\'s not sure if it\'s love-or if she\'s a ruthless con artist who\'s using him to find the fabled Fountain of Youth. When she forces him aboard the \"Queen Anne\'s Revenge,\" the ship of the legendary pirate Blackbeard (Ian McShane), Jack finds himself on an unexpected adventure in which he doesn\'t know whom to fear more: Blackbeard or Angelica, with whom he shares a mysterious past. -- (C) Disney','It\'s shorter and leaner than the previous sequel, but this Pirates runs aground on a disjointed plot and a non-stop barrage of noisy action sequences.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/67/11156760_mob.jpg'),(782,'Crank 2: High Voltage',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crank_high_voltage/','770740096','1121931',1,NULL,'Crank: High Voltage delivers on its promises: a fast-paced, exciting thrill ride that doesn\'t take itself too seriously.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/41/10884139_mob.jpg'),(783,'The Chronicles of Narnia: The Voyage of the Dawn Treader',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chronicles_of_narnia_the_voyage_of_the_dawn_treader/','770671153','0980970',1,'Upon returning to Narnia to join Prince Caspian for a voyage on the majestic royal vessel known as The Dawn Treader, Lucy, Edmund, and their cousin Eustace encounter merfolk, dragons, dwarves, and a wandering band of lost warriors. As the edge of the world draws near, their remarkable adventure at sea sails toward an exciting, yet uncertain, conclusion. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Its leisurely, businesslike pace won\'t win the franchise many new fans, but Voyage of the Dawn Treader restores some of the Narnia franchise\'s lost luster with strong performances and impressive special effects.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/45/11154523_mob.jpg'),(784,'Four Christmases',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/four_christmases/','770683011','0369436',1,NULL,'Despite a strong cast, this sour holiday comedy suffers from a hackneyed script.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/64/10876473_mob.jpg'),(785,'Michael Clayton',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/michael_clayton/','770671488','0465538',1,NULL,'Michael Clayton is one of the most sharply scripted films of 2007, with an engrossing premise and faultless acting. Director Tony Gilroy succeeds not only in capturing the audience\'s attention, but holding it until the credits roll.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/39/11163967_mob.jpg'),(786,'Captain America: The First Avenger',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/captain-america/','770739679','0458339',1,'Captain America: The First Avenger will focus on the early days of the Marvel Universe when Steve Rogers (Chris Evans) volunteers to participate in an experimental program that turns him into the Super Soldier known as Captain America. As Captain America, Rogers joins forces with Bucky Barnes (Sebastian Stan) and Peggy Carter (Hayley Atwell) to wage war on the evil HYDRA organization, led by the villainous Red Skull (Hugo Weaving.) -- (C) Paramount','With plenty of pulpy action, a pleasantly retro vibe, and a handful of fine performances, Captain America is solidly old-fashioned blockbuster entertainment.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/83/11158339_mob.jpg'),(787,'Good Luck Chuck',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/good_luck_chuck/','528347193','0452625',1,NULL,'A shortage of laughs and an undercurrent of mean-spiritedness undermine Good Luck Chuck, squandering a decent premise on gross-out humor and shopworn slapstick.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/99/46/33/9946331_mob.jpg'),(788,'Cruel Intentions',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cruel_intentions/','16563','0139134',1,NULL,'Even in a slick package and an attractive cast, the movie succumbs to bad acting and a bad script.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/12/58/11125862_mob.jpg'),(789,'X-Men: First Class',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/x_men_first_class/','771041145','1270798',1,'X-Men: First Class unveils the epic beginning of the X-Men saga - and a secret history of the Cold War and our world at the brink of nuclear Armageddon. As the first class discovers, harnesses, and comes to terms with their formidable powers, alliances are formed that will shape the eternal war between the heroes and villains of the X-Men universe. -- (C) Fox','With a strong script, stylish direction, and powerful performances from its well-rounded cast, X-Men: First Class is a welcome return to form for the franchise.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/79/11157925_mob.jpg'),(790,'The Crazies',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1205380-crazies/','770805222','0455407',1,'Sahara director Breck Eisner teams with screenwriters Ray Wright (Pulse) and Scott Kosar (The Texas Chainsaw Massacre) to give George A. Romero\'s underrated 1973 shocker a shiny new makeover in this update starring Timothy Olyphant and Radha Mitchell. Perform a Google search on \"small-town America,\" and eventually you\'ll stumble across Ogden Marsh, a picturesque hamlet situated a safe distance from the nearest big city, and full of friendly faces. The citizens of Ogden Marsh are happy, albeit unremarkable people, but they\'re about to discover just how fragile their warm slice of the American dream really is. When a mysterious toxin transforms the locals into murderous maniacs, it\'s up to Sheriff David Dutton (Olyphant) to find out why a man who was once an upstanding citizen would attempt to massacre the local youth baseball team, and a caring father would burn his beloved family alive. Within hours the town has descended into total chaos, and the government has ordered it quarantined. Anyone who attempts to escape will be shot on sight, whether they\'re infected or not. Realizing that their only hope for survival is to fight through the madness that has consumed their once-quiet town, Sheriff Dutton, his pregnant wife, Judy (Mitchell), his deputy Russell (Joe Anderson), and frightened medical center assistant Becca (Danielle Panabaker) wage an epic struggle to discover the source of this malevolent scourge while fending off their infected friends and neighbors. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Tense, nicely shot, and uncommonly intelligent, The Crazies is a horror remake that, unusually, works.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/93/48/10934852_mob.jpg'),(791,'Cloud Atlas',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cloud_atlas_2012/','771310572','1371111',1,'Cloud Atlas explores how the actions and consequences of individual lives impact one another throughout the past, the present and the future. Action, mystery and romance weave dramatically through the story as one soul is shaped from a killer into a hero and a single act of kindness ripples across centuries to inspire a revolution in the distant future. Each member of the ensemble appears in multiple roles as the stories move through time. -- (C) Warner Bros.','Its sprawling, ambitious blend of thought-provoking narrative and eye-catching visuals will prove too unwieldy for some, but the sheer size and scope of Cloud Atlas are all but impossible to ignore.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/87/11168701_mob.jpg'),(792,'Chernobyl Diaries',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chernobyl_diaries/','771269700','2244781',1,'Chernobyl Diaries is an original story from Oren Peli, who first terrified audiences with his groundbreaking thriller, Paranormal Activity. The film follows a group of six young vacationers who, looking to go off the beaten path, hire an \"extreme\" tour guide. Ignoring warnings, he takes them into the city of Pripyat, the former home to the workers of the Chernobyl nuclear reactor, but a deserted town since the disaster more than 25 years ago. After a brief exploration of the abandoned city, however, the group soon finds themselves stranded, only to discover that they are not alone... -- (C) Warner Bros.','Despite an interesting premise and spooky atmospherics, Chernobyl Diaries is mostly short on suspense and originality.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/67/11166784_mob.jpg'),(793,'No Country for Old Men',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/no_country_for_old_men/','770669872','0477348',1,NULL,'Bolstered by powerful lead performances from Javier Bardem, Josh Brolin, and Tommy Lee Jones, No Country for Old Men finds the Coen brothers spinning cinematic gold out of Cormac McCarthy\'s grim, darkly funny novel.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/86/81/10868132_mob.jpg'),(794,'Journey to the Center of the Earth',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10008588-journey_3d/','770674856','0373051',1,NULL,'Modern visuals and an old fasioned storyline make this family adventure/comedy a fast-paced, kitschy ride.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/25/10882502_mob.jpg'),(795,'World Trade Center',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/world_trade_center/','248007780','0469641',1,NULL,'As a visually stunning tribute to lives lost in tragedy, World Trade Center succeeds unequivocally, and it is more politically muted than many of Stone\'s other works.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168981_mob.jpg'),(796,'The Karate Kid',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/karate_kid_2010/','770813677','1155076',1,'When a 12-year-old from Detroit moves to China with his mother and incurs the wrath of the class bully at his new school, he makes an unlikely ally in the form of his aging maintenance man, a kung fu master who teaches him the secrets to self-defense. Upon arriving at his new school, Dre Parker (Jaden Smith) develops a powerful crush on pretty classmate Mei Ying. The feeling is mutual, although the cultural divide between Dre and Mei Ying makes a friendship unlikely, and romance impossible. When cruel classmate and kung fu prodigy Cheng learns of Dre\'s feelings for Mei Ying, he harasses and humiliates the young outsider in front of the entire school. With no one to turn to for help, Dre confides his fears in kindly maintenance man Mr. Han (Jackie Chan), a kung fu master who knows that serenity and maturity -- not punches and power -- are the true keys to mastering the martial arts. As Dre prepares to face down his intimidating tormentor, he begins to realize that the real fight is just beginning. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','It may not be as powerful as the 1984 edition, but the 2010 Karate Kid delivers a surprisingly satisfying update on the original.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/12/21/11122168_mob.jpg'),(797,'Catch Me If You Can',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/catch_me_if_you_can/','10662','0264464',1,NULL,'Steven Spielberg turns in another hit, with help from a strong performance by Leonardo DiCaprio, in this stylish, breezily entertaining, and surprisingly sweet story of real-life wunderkind con artist Frank Abagnale.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/12/11151205_mob.jpg'),(798,'Captivity',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/captivity/','535227372','0374563',1,NULL,'Lacking scares or psychological insight, Captivity is a distasteful entry in the \'torture porn\' subgenre.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/94/10889481_mob.jpg'),(799,'When a Stranger Calls',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/when_a_stranger_calls/','14662876','0455857',1,NULL,'What\'s fitting punishment for running up the phone bill? Why have that person baby sit; that\'ll teach them. Or better yet, make that person through this poorly acted, fright-free remake of the 1979 movie of the same name. Camilla Belle is a looker, but she got nothing on Carol Kane, the actress who originally played the part, when it comes to range. The final straw is that the payoff isn\'t worth the tedium that comes before. Just hang up on this one.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/92/11/10921175_mob.jpg'),(800,'Crank',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crank/','276994403','0479884',1,NULL,'It\'s a film about a guy injected with Speed... wait, there\'s no bus. It\'s a film about a guy who has to kick a bunch of squirmy butt to stay alive... wait, no snakes or planes here. But it is a film about doing lots of drugs and pulling lots of punches, and it entertains accordingly.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/87/49/10874942_mob.jpg'),(801,'Charlie Wilson\'s War',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/charlie_wilsons_war/','770673565','0472062',1,NULL,'Charlie Wilson\'s War manages to entertain and inform audiences, thanks to its witty script and talented cast of power players.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/61/60/10616034_mob.jpg'),(802,'Alvin and the Chipmunks',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1184827-alvin_and_the_chipmunks/','770673145','0952640',1,NULL,'Though cutely rendered, Alvin and the Chipmunks suffers from bland potty humor and a rehashed kids\' movie formula.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/97/66/56/9766563_mob.jpg'),(803,'Walk Hard: The Dewey Cox Story',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/walk_hard/','770675029','0841046',1,NULL,'A parody that pokes fun at rock stars and reductive biopics alike, this comedy sings in large part because of stellar performances and clever original music.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/74/10897410_mob.jpg'),(804,'Charlotte\'s Web',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/charlottes_web/','376862102','0413895',1,NULL,'Kids will be entertained by the straightforward plot and cute animals, and adults will be charmed by how quiet and humble the production is, a fine translation of E.B. White\'s genteel prose.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168926_mob.jpg'),(805,'It\'s Complicated',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1208806-its_complicated/','770814954','1230414',1,NULL,'Despite fine work by an appealing cast, It\'s Complicated is predictable romantic comedy fare, going for broad laughs instead of subtlety and nuance.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/12/07/11120778_mob.jpg'),(806,'A Clockwork Orange',1971,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/clockwork_orange/','15694',NULL,1,NULL,'Disturbing and thought-provoking, A Clockwork Orange is a cold, dystopian nightmare with a very dark sense of humor.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/80/11168026_mob.jpg'),(807,'Killing Them Softly',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/killing_them_softly/','771225277','1764234',1,'Three dumb guys who think they\'re smart rob a Mob protected card game, causing the local criminal economy to collapse. Brad Pitt plays the enforcer hired to track them down and restore order. Killing Them Softly also features Richard Jenkins, James Gandolfini, Ray Liotta, Scoot McNairy, Ben Mendelsohn, and Vincent Curatola. Max Casella, Trevor Long, Slaine and Sam Shepard also make appearances. -- (C) Weinstein','Killing Them Softly is a darkly comic, visceral thriller that doubles as a cautionary tale on capitalism, whose message is delivered with sledgehammer force.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/69/11166941_mob.jpg'),(808,'Casablanca',1942,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1003707-casablanca/','10056','0034583',1,NULL,'An undisputed masterpiece and perhaps Hollywood\'s quintessential statement on love and romance, Casablanca has only improved with age, boasting career-defining performances from Humphrey Bogart and Ingrid Bergman.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/81/11168101_mob.jpg'),(809,'Chicken Little',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chicken_little/','9043','0371606',1,NULL,'In its first non-Pixar CGI venture, Disney expends more effort in the technical presentation than in crafting an original storyline.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/04/250491_mob.jpg'),(810,'Crash',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1144992-crash/','12','0375679',1,NULL,'A raw and unsettling morality piece on modern angst and urban disconnect, Crash examines the dangers of bigotry and xenophobia in the lives of interconnected Angelenos.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/24/97/249717_mob.jpg'),(811,'Wallace & Gromit: The Curse of the Were-Rabbit',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wallace_and_gromit_curse_of_the_wererabbit/','8565','0312004',1,NULL,'The Curse of the Were-Rabbit is a subtly touching and wonderfully eccentric adventure featuring Wallace and Gromit.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/02/250296_mob.jpg'),(812,'Coach Carter',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/coach_carter/','10295','0393162',1,NULL,'Like a good point guard, Samuel L. Jackson is the clear leader on the floor in a film that critics say transcends its formula trappings to be inspirational. However, some have said the film is too preachy and too long.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168929_mob.jpg'),(813,'The Crow',1994,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crow/','15519','0109506',1,NULL,'Filled with style and dark, lurid energy, The Crow is an action-packed visual feast that also has a soul in the performance of the late Brandon Lee.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/93/21/10932156_mob.jpg'),(814,'Constantine',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/constantine/','12977','0360486',1,NULL,'Despite solid production values and an intriguing premise, Constantine lacks the focus of another spiritual shoot-em-up, The Matrix.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/67/11166720_mob.jpg'),(815,'Curious George',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1153951-curious_george/','19049940','0381971',1,NULL,'Curious George is a bright, sweet, faithful adaptation of the beloved children\'s books.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/94/34/10943485_mob.jpg'),(816,'Clerks II',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/clerks_2/','190815877','0424345',1,NULL,'Clerks II dishes up much of the graphic humor and some of the insight that made the 1994 original a cult hit.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/93/69/10936947_mob.jpg'),(817,'Street Fighter: The Legend of Chun-Li',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/street_fighter_the_legend_of_chun_li/','770781883','0891592',1,NULL,'The combination of a shallow plot and miscast performers renders Street Fighter: The Legend of Chun Li a perfectly forgettable video game adaptation.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/12/45/11124512_mob.jpg'),(818,'Cinderella Man',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cinderella_man/','670','0352248',1,NULL,'With grittiness and an evocative sense of time and place, Cinderella Man is a powerful underdog story. And Ron Howard and Russell Crowe prove to be a solid combination.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/24/97/249797_mob.jpg'),(819,'Chicago',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chicago/','10061','0299658',1,NULL,'A rousing and energetic adaptation of the Broadway musical, Chicago succeeds on the level pure spectacle, but provides a surprising level of depth and humor as well.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/38/253893_mob.jpg'),(820,'The Passion of the Christ',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/passion_of_the_christ/','12891','0335345',1,NULL,'The graphic details of Jesus\' torture make the movie tough to sit through and obscure whatever message it is trying to convey.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/13/50/11135040_mob.jpg'),(821,'John Carter',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/john_carter/','770801433','0401729',1,'From filmmaker Andrew Stanton comes John Carter-a sweeping action-adventure set on the mysterious and exotic planet of Barsoom (Mars). John Carter is based on a classic novel by Edgar Rice Burroughs, whose highly imaginative adventures served as inspiration for many filmmakers, both past and present. The film tells the story of war-weary, former military captain John Carter (Taylor Kitsch), who is inexplicably transported to Mars where he becomes reluctantly embroiled in a conflict of epic proportions amongst the inhabitants of the planet, including Tars Tarkas (Willem Dafoe) and the captivating Princess Dejah Thoris (Lynn Collins). In a world on the brink of collapse, Carter rediscovers his humanity when he realizes that the survival of Barsoom and its people rests in his hands. -- (C) Walt Disney','While John Carter looks terrific and delivers its share of pulpy thrills, it also suffers from uneven pacing and occasionally incomprehensible plotting and characterization.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/39/11163924_mob.jpg'),(822,'Catch and Release',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/catch_and_release/','387348368','0395495',1,NULL,'A romantic dramedy with boring, stock characters and contrived situations.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/46/91/33/4691337_mob.jpg'),(823,'Ice Age: Continental Drift',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ice_age_continental_drift/','771041816','1667889',1,'Scrat\'s nutty pursuit of the cursed acorn, which he\'s been after since the dawn of time, has world-changing consequences - a continental cataclysm that triggers the greatest adventure of all for Manny, Diego and Sid. In the wake of these upheavals, Sid reunites with his cantankerous Granny, and the herd encounters a ragtag menagerie of seafaring pirates determined to stop them from returning home. -- (C) Official Site','Ice Age: Continental Drift 3D has moments of charm and witty slapstick, but it often seems content to recycle ideas from the previous films.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/75/11167513_mob.jpg'),(824,'Chimpanzee',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chimpanzee_2012/','770740017','0364242',1,'In theaters Earth Day 2012, Disneynature\'s newest True Life Adventure introduces Oscar, a baby chimp whose playful curiosity and zest for discovery light up the African forest until a twist of fate leaves Oscar to fend for himself with a little help from an unexpected ally. -- (C) Disneynature','Chimpanzee often anthropomorphizes its subjects, but it\'s a beautifully filmed, remarkably intimate look at the lives of a family of primates.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/10/11161097_mob.jpg'),(825,'Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade',1989,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/indiana_jones_and_the_last_crusade/','23531','0097576',1,NULL,'Lighter and more comedic than its predecessor, Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade returns the series to the brisk serial adventure of Raiders, while adding a dynamite double act between Harrison Ford and Sean Connery.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/91/96/10919621_mob.jpg'),(826,'Star Wars: The Clone Wars',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/clone_wars/','770683913','1185834',1,NULL,'Mechanical animation and a less-than stellar script make The Clone Wars a pale shadow of George Lucas\' once great franchise.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/13/24/11132487_mob.jpg'),(827,'The Constant Gardener',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/constant_gardener/','5625','0387131',1,NULL,'The Constant Gardener is a smart, gripping, and suspenseful thriller with rich performances from the leads.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/00/250092_mob.jpg'),(828,'College Road Trip',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/college_road_trip/','770680564','0997047',1,NULL,'Filled with shrill gags and middling slapstick, College Road Trip is woefully short on comic imagination.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/83/94/10839445_mob.jpg'),(829,'Crazy Heart',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crazy_heart/','770801608','1263670',1,NULL,'Thanks to a captivating performance from Jeff Bridges, Crazy Heart transcends its overly familiar origins and finds new meaning in an old story.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/92/65/10926559_mob.jpg'),(830,'One Flew Over the Cuckoo\'s Nest',1975,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/one_flew_over_the_cuckoos_nest/','12965','0073486',1,NULL,'The onscreen battle between Jack Nicholson and Louise Fletcher serves as a personal microcosm of the culture wars of the 1970s -- and testament to the director\'s vision that the film retains its power more than three decades later.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/81/11168107_mob.jpg'),(831,'Chocolat',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1103080-chocolat/','10047','0241303',1,NULL,'Chocolat is a charmingly light-hearted fable with a lovely performance by Binoche.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/24/34/10243432_mob.jpg'),(832,'Along Came Polly',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/along_came_polly/','10982','0343135',1,NULL,'Though the supporting actors are funny, Stiller and Aniston don\'t make a believable couple, and the gross-out humor is gratuitous.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/89/41/10894152_mob.jpg'),(833,'Extremely Loud & Incredibly Close',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/extremely_loud_and_incredibly_close/','771247182','0477302',1,'Oskar (Thomas Horn) is convinced that his father (Tom Hanks), who died in the 9/11 attacks on the World Trade Center, has left a final message for him hidden somewhere in the city. Feeling disconnected from his grieving mother (Sandra Bullock) and driven by a relentlessly active mind that refuses to believe in things that can\'t be observed, Oskar begins searching New York City for the lock that fits a mysterious key he found in his father\'s closet. His journey through the five boroughs takes him beyond his own loss to a greater understanding of the observable world around him. -- (C) Warner Bros','Extremely Loud & Incredibly Close has a story worth telling, but it deserves better than the treacly and pretentious treatment director Stephen Daldry gives it.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/41/11164141_mob.jpg'),(834,'Source Code',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/source_code/','771174105','0945513',1,'When decorated soldier Captain Colter Stevens (Jake Gyllenhaal) wakes up in the body of an unknown man, he discovers he\'s part of a mission to find the bomber of a Chicago commuter train. In an assignment unlike any he\'s ever known, he learns he\'s part of a government experiment called the Source Code, a program that enables him to cross over into another man\'s identity in the last 8 minutes of his life. With a second, much larger target threatening to kill millions in downtown Chicago, Colter re-lives the incident over and over again, gathering clues each time, until he can solve the mystery of who is behind the bombs and prevent the next attack. -- (C) Summit','Finding the human story amidst the action, director Duncan Jones and charming Jake Gyllenhaal craft a smart, satisfying sci-fi thriller.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/64/11156441_mob.jpg'),(835,'Casanova',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1156246-casanova/','24475','0402894',1,NULL,'This frothy, oddly bloodless film does a disservice to the colorful life of the real Casanova.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/31/18/311809_mob.jpg'),(836,'Howl\'s Moving Castle',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/howls_moving_castle/','75428742','0347149',1,NULL,'Exquisitely illustrated by master animator Miyazaki, Howl\'s Moving Castle will delight children with its fantastical story and touch the hearts and minds of older viewers as well.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/37/11163753_mob.jpg'),(837,'Sunshine Cleaning',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sunshine_cleaning/','770682576','0862846',1,NULL,'Despite a sometimes overly familiar plot, Sunshine Cleaning benefits from the lively performances of its two stars.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/88/11168848_mob.jpg'),(838,'Cidade de Deus (City of God)',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/city_of_god/','12927','0317248',1,NULL,'A shocking and disturbing, but always compelling look at life in the slums of Rio de Janiero.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/26/72/267221_mob.jpg'),(839,'Cars 2',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cars_2/','770805427','1216475',1,'Star racecar Lightning McQueen (Owen Wilson) and the incomparable tow truck Mater (Larry the Cable Guy) take their friendship to exciting new places in Cars 2 when they head overseas to compete in the first-ever World Grand Prix to determine the world\'s fastest car. But the road to the championship is filled with plenty of potholes, detours and hilarious surprises when Mater gets caught up in an intriguing adventure of his own: international espionage. Mater finds himself torn between assisting Lightning McQueen in the high-profile race and towing the line in a top-secret mission orchestrated by master British super spy Finn McMissile (Michael Caine) and the stunning spy-in-training Holley Shiftwell (Emily Mortimer). -- (C) Disney','Cars 2 is as visually appealing as any other Pixar production, but all that dazzle can\'t disguise the rusty storytelling under the hood.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/64/11156447_mob.jpg'),(840,'The Campaign',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_campaign/','771258806','1790886',1,'When long-term congressman Cam Brady (Will Ferrell) commits a major public gaffe before an upcoming election, a pair of ultra-wealthy CEOs plot to put up a rival candidate and gain influence over their North Carolina district. Their man: naive Marty Huggins (Zach Galifianakis), director of the local Tourism Center. At first, Marty appears to be the unlikeliest possible choice but, with the help of his new benefactors\' support, a cutthroat campaign manager and his family\'s political connections, he soon becomes a contender who gives the charismatic Cam plenty to worry about. As Election Day closes in, the two are locked in a dead heat, with insults quickly escalating to injury until all they care about is burying each other, in this mud-slinging, back-stabbing, home-wrecking comedy. -- (C) Warner Bros.','Its crude brand of political satire isn\'t quite as smart or sharp as one might hope in an election year, but The Campaign manages to generate a sufficient number of laughs thanks to its well-matched leads.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/72/11167275_mob.jpg'),(841,'Cold Mountain',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cold_mountain/','12931','0159365',1,NULL,'The well-crafted Cold Mountain has an epic sweep and captures the horror and brutal hardship of war.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/26/72/267229_mob.jpg'),(842,'Cowboys & Aliens',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cowboys_and_aliens/','770863875','0409847',1,'1875. New Mexico Territory. A stranger (Craig) with no memory of his past stumbles into the hard desert town of Absolution. What he discovers is that the people of Absolution don\'t welcome strangers, and nobody makes a move on its streets unless ordered to do so by the iron-fisted Colonel Dolarhyde (Ford). It\'s a town that lives in fear. But Absolution is about to experience fear it can scarcely comprehend as the desolate city is attacked by marauders from the sky. Now, the stranger they rejected is their only hope for salvation. As this gunslinger slowly starts to remember who he is and where he\'s been, he realizes he holds a secret that could give the town a fighting chance against the alien force. -- (C) Official Site','Daniel Craig and Harrison Ford are as dependably appealing as ever, but they\'re let down by director Jon Favreau\'s inability to smooth Cowboys & Aliens\' jarring tonal shifts.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/36/11163635_mob.jpg'),(843,'Cast Away',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cast_away/','12777','0162222',1,NULL,'Flawed but fascinating, Cast Away offers an intelligent script, some of Robert Zemeckis\' most mature directing, and a showcase performance from Tom Hanks.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/48/11164876_mob.jpg'),(844,'Space Chimps',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1195801-space_chimps/','770729335','0482603',1,NULL,'Space Chimps\' cheap animation and overabundance of monkey puns feels especially dated in a post-Wall-E world.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/86/17/10861787_mob.jpg'),(845,'The Santa Clause 3: The Escape Clause',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/santa_clause_3/','353654309','0452681',1,NULL,'Playing Jack Frost as an evil cross between Liza Minnelli and Liberace, Martin Short is a welcome presence, but this tired series continues drawing from its bag of bland gags and dumb slapstick.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/29/42/66/2942662_mob.jpg'),(846,'The Town',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_town/','770814363','0840361',1,'Boston bank robber Doug MacRay (Ben Affleck) falls for a woman his gang had previously taken hostage after feigning a chance meeting with her to ensure that she can\'t identify them in Affleck\'s adaptation of author Chuck Hogan\'s novel Prince of Thieves. The son of a tough Charlestown, MA thief, Doug passed on his chance to walk the straight and narrow in favor of becoming a career bank robber. Not only is Doug\'s crew one of the most ruthless in Boston, but they\'re also one of the best; they never leave a trace of evidence, and always make a clean break. Over the years, Doug\'s fearless partners in crime have become something of a surrogate family to him; Jem (Jeremy Renner), the most dangerous of the bunch, is the closest thing Doug has ever had to a brother. But a divide begins to open between the two career criminals when Jem takes bank manager Claire Keesey (Rebecca Hall) hostage during a particularly tense heist, and the group subsequently discovers that she hails from their own tight-knit suburb. When Jem proposes that the gang make an effort to find out just how much Claire recalls about the crime, Doug fears that his volatile partner may do more harm than good and volunteers himself for the job. Later, Doug turns on the charm while pretending to bump into Claire by chance, and becomes convinced that she doesn\'t suspect him of being the same man who just robbed her bank. As the feds turn up the heat on the gang, Doug finds himself falling for Claire, and searching desperately for a means of cutting his ties to his criminal past. But with each passing day, Jem grows increasingly suspicious of Doug\'s true motivations. Now caught between two worlds with no chance of turning back, Doug realizes that his only hope for finding a happy future is to betray the only family he\'s ever known. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Tense, smartly written, and wonderfully cast, The Town proves that Ben Affleck has rediscovered his muse -- and that he\'s a director to be reckoned with.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/67/11166732_mob.jpg'),(847,'Miss Congeniality 2 - Armed and Fabulous',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/miss_congeniality_2/','10300','0385307',1,NULL,'Sandra Bullock is still as appealing as ever; too bad the movie is not pageant material.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/55/05/36/5505367_mob.jpg'),(848,'Charlie\'s Angels - Full Throttle',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/charlies_angels_full_throttle/','17226','0305357',1,NULL,'Eye candy for those who don\'t require a movie to have a plot or for it to make sense.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/13/33/11133370_mob.jpg'),(849,'Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crouching_tiger_hidden_dragon/','10267','0190332',1,NULL,'The movie that catapulted Ang Lee into the ranks of upper echelon Hollywood filmmakers, Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon features a deft mix of amazing martial arts battles, beautiful scenery, and tasteful drama.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/49/254902_mob.jpg'),(850,'Carrie',1976,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1003625-carrie/','15878','0074285',1,NULL,'Carrie is a horrifying look at supernatural powers, high school cruelty, and teen angst -- and it brings us one of the most memorable and disturbing prom scenes in history.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/28/14/281415_mob.jpg'),(851,'Chronicle',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chronicle/','771239389','1706593',1,'Three high school students make an incredible discovery, leading to their developing uncanny powers beyond their understanding. As they learn to control their abilities and use them to their advantage, their lives start to spin out of control, and their darker sides begin to take over. -- (C) Official Site','Chronicle transcends its found-footage gimmick with a smart script, fast-paced direction, and engaging performances from the young cast.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/30/11163017_mob.jpg'),(852,'Collateral',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/collateral/','12909','0369339',1,NULL,'Driven by director Michael Mann\'s trademark visuals and a lean, villainous performance from Tom Cruise, Collateral is a stylish and compelling noir thriller.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/93/72/10937228_mob.jpg'),(853,'Crazy, Stupid, Love.',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/771203531/','771203531','1570728',1,'At fortysomething, straight-laced Cal Weaver (Steve Carell) is living the dream-good job, nice house, great kids and marriage to his high school sweetheart. But when Cal learns that his wife, Emily (Julianne Moore), has cheated on him and wants a divorce, his \"perfect\" life quickly unravels. Worse, in today\'s single world, Cal, who hasn\'t dated in decades, stands out as the epitome of un-smooth. Now spending his free evenings sulking alone at a local bar, the hapless Cal is taken on as wingman and protege to handsome, thirtysomething player Jacob Palmer (Ryan Gosling). -- (C) Warner Bros','It never lives up to the first part of its title, but Crazy, Stupid, Love\'s unabashed sweetness -- and its terrifically talented cast -- more than make up for its flaws.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/36/11163666_mob.jpg'),(854,'Charlie St. Cloud',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/charlie_st_cloud/','770859139','1438254',1,'A young man forms a unique connection to the afterlife after surviving the tragic car accident that claimed his younger brother in this supernatural drama starring Zac Efron, based on the best-selling book by author Ben Sherwood. Charlie St. Cloud (Efron) is an experienced sailor from the Pacific Northwest who has just earned a scholarship that will take him far from home. The light of his mother\'s life, Charlie and his little brother, Sam (Charlie Tahan), are driving late at night when they\'re involved in a deadly car accident that kills Sam and leaves Charlie forever changed. In the aftermath of the accident, Charlie is wracked with guilt, convinced that if he had just been more careful behind the wheel, Sam would still be alive today. When Charlie begins seeing visions of his younger brother that are just as real as if Sam is actually standing before him, his friends and neighbors all start to think he\'s losing his mind. Shortly thereafter, Charlie\'s former high-school classmate Tess (Amanda Crew) returns to town unannounced, and together the two old acquaintances forge the foundation of a meaningful romance. But before Charlie can move on with his life he\'ll have to first let go of his past, and bid his beloved brother Sam one final, heartfelt farewell. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Zac Efron gives it his all, but Charlie St. Cloud is too shallow and cloying to offer much more than eye candy for his fans.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/10/11151021_mob.jpg'),(855,'Lara Croft - Tomb Raider',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lara_croft_tomb_raider/','10375','0146316',1,NULL,'Angelina Jolie is perfect for the role of Lara Croft, but even she can\'t save the movie from a senseless plot and action sequences with no emotional impact.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168952_mob.jpg'),(856,'Adam Sandler\'s Eight Crazy Nights',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/adam_sandlers_eight_crazy_nights/','11186','0271263',1,NULL,'Sandler returns to his roots in this nauseating concoction filled with potty humor and product placements.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/93/56/10935638_mob.jpg'),(857,'The Hot Chick',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hot_chick/','10976','0302640',1,NULL,'The Hot Chick\'s one-note concept gets stretched thin, and a lot of the jokes fall flat.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/84/258410_mob.jpg'),(858,'Coyote Ugly',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/coyote_ugly/','10913','0200550',1,NULL,'Well, the women in this film are incredibly attractive and flaunt that fact quite a lot. Unfortunatly, that\'s all there is to the film. The script is almost as big a joke as the charactors, and everything else follows the same path. If you\'re looking for a tease then see this flick, otherwise stay as far away as possible.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/81/258105_mob.jpg'),(859,'Cry-Baby',1990,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cry-baby/','10100','0099329',1,NULL,'John Waters\' musical ode to the teen rebel genre is infectious and gleefully camp, providing star Johnny Depp with the perfect vehicle in which to lampoon his pin-up image.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/55/36/05/5536059_mob.jpg'),(860,'The Texas Chainsaw Massacre',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/texas_chainsaw_massacre/','13328','0324216',1,NULL,'An unnecessary remake that\'s more gory and less scary than the original.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/13/31/11133149_mob.jpg'),(861,'Cassandra\'s Dream',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cassandras_dream/','749215709','0795493',1,NULL,'Colin Farrell and Tom Wilkinson act up a storm in Cassandra\'s Dream, but Woody Allen\'s heavy-handed symbolism and foreshadowing drains the plot of all tension.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/06/15/10061520_mob.jpg'),(862,'Ever After: A Cinderella Story',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ever_after_a_cinderella_story/','11509','0120631',1,NULL,'Ever After is a sweet, frothy twist on the ancient fable, led by a solid turn from star Barrymore.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/50/11165010_mob.jpg'),(863,'Confessions of a Teenage Drama Queen',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/confessions_of_a_teenage_drama_queen/','10634','0361467',1,NULL,'Sloppily assembled fluff that won\'t have much of interest for anyone who isn\'t a preteen girl.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/02/10880251_mob.jpg'),(864,'For a Good Time, Call...',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/for_a_good_time_call/','771266667','1996264',1,'The reserved Lauren and the irrepressible Katie are polar opposites... and past enemies. But when both come up short on the funds needed to afford their dream New York City apartment a mutual friend re-introduces them and they reluctantly agree to room together. These apartment-mates have nothing in common - until Lauren discovers that Katie is working as a phone-sex operator, and recognizes a good business opportunity. But as their business partnership takes off, their newfound friendship finds unexpected challenges that may leave them both, as they say, hanging on the telephone. -- (C) Focus','Brisk, funny, and sweetly raunchy, For a Good Time, Call... adds to the recent string of R-rated female comedies while serving as an overdue coming out party for the charming Ari Graynor.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/79/11167939_mob.jpg'),(865,'Cadillac Records',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cadillac_records/','770796579','1042877',1,NULL,'What Cadillac Records may lack in originality, it more than makes up for in strong performances and soul-stirring music.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/94/10889479_mob.jpg'),(866,'Willy Wonka and the Chocolate Factory',1971,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/willy_wonka_and_the_chocolate_factory/','9897','0067992',1,NULL,'Willy Wonka and the Chocolate Factory is strange yet comforting, full of narrative detours that don\'t always work but express the film\'s uniqueness.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/80/11168085_mob.jpg'),(867,'Alvin and the Chipmunks: Chipwrecked',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/alvin_and_the_chipmunks_chipwrecked_2011/','771219444','1615918',1,'The vacationing Chipmunks and Chipettes are turning a luxury cruise liner into their personal playground, until they become \'chipwrecked\' on a remote island. As the \'Munks and Chipettes try various schemes to find their way home, they accidentally discover their new turf is not as deserted as it seems. -- (C) Official Site','Lazy, rote, and grating, Chipwrecked is lowest-common-denominator family entertainment that\'s strictly for the very, very, very young at heart.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/12/11161263_mob.jpg'),(868,'Contraband',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/contraband_2012/','771224339','1524137',1,'Chris Farraday (Mark Wahlberg) long ago abandoned his life of crime, but after his brother-in-law, Andy (Caleb Landry Jones), botches a drug deal for his ruthless boss, Tim Briggs (Giovanni Ribisi), Chris is forced back into doing what he does best- running contraband-to settle Andy\'s debt. Chris is a legendary smuggler and quickly assembles a crew with the help of his best friend, Sebastian (Ben Foster), for one final run to Panama and back, hoping to return with millions in counterfeit bills. Things quickly fall apart and with only hours to reach the cash, Chris must use his rusty skills to successfully navigate a treacherous criminal network of brutal drug lords, cops and hit men before his wife, Kate (Kate Beckinsale), and sons become their target. -- (C) Official Site','It\'s more entertaining than your average January action thriller, but that isn\'t enough to excuse Contraband\'s lack of originality and unnecessarily convoluted plot.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/51/11165161_mob.jpg'),(869,'The Chronicles of Riddick',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chronicles_of_riddick/','17007','0296572',1,NULL,'As an action movie, Riddick offers some thrills, but as a sequel to Pitch Black, it\'s a disappointment.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/45/10884541_mob.jpg'),(870,'Clueless',1995,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/clueless/','11124',NULL,1,NULL,'A funny and clever reshaping of Emma, Clueless offers a soft satire that pokes as much fun at teen films as it does at the Beverly Hills glitterati.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168928_mob.jpg'),(871,'Lara Croft Tomb Raider - The Cradle of Life',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lara_croft_tomb_raider_the_cradle_of_life/','10579','0325703',1,NULL,'Though the sequel is an improvement over the first movie, it\'s still lacking in thrills.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/82/13/10821386_mob.jpg'),(872,'Martian Child',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/martian_child/','387335433','0415965',1,NULL,'Despite some charms, overt emotional manipulation and an inconsistent tone prevents Martian Child from being the heartfelt dramedy it aspires to be.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/17/78/10177873_mob.jpg'),(873,'The Comebacks',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/comebacks/','770672999','0790804',1,NULL,'Full of groin-centric humor and tired sports cliches, The Comebacks is poor even by parody movie standards.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/18/33/10183342_mob.jpg'),(874,'Contagion',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/contagion_2011/','771041155','1598778',1,'Contagion follows the rapid progress of a lethal airborne virus that kills within days. As the fast-moving epidemic grows, the worldwide medical community races to find a cure and control the panic that spreads faster than the virus itself. At the same time, ordinary people struggle to survive in a society coming apart. -- (C) Warner Bros.','Tense, tightly plotted, and bolstered by a stellar cast, Contagion is an exceptionally smart -- and scary -- disaster movie.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/36/11163665_mob.jpg'),(875,'The Texas Chainsaw Massacre',1974,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1021112-texas_chainsaw_massacre/','14466','0072271',1,NULL,'Thanks to a smart script and documentary-style camerawork, The Texas Chainsaw Massacre achieves start-to-finish suspense, making it a classic in low-budget exploitation cinema.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/27/47/274725_mob.jpg'),(876,'Dazed and Confused',1993,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dazed_and_confused/','13761','0106677',1,NULL,'Featuring an excellent ensemble cast, a precise feel for the 1970s, and a killer soundtrack, Dazed and Confused is a funny, affectionate, and clear-eyed look at high school life.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/40/11164087_mob.jpg'),(877,'The Color Purple',1985,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/color_purple/','10141','0088939',1,NULL,'A sentimental tale that reveals great emotional truths in American history.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/80/11168034_mob.jpg'),(878,'A Christmas Story',1983,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1004151-christmas_story/','10030','0085334',1,NULL,'Both warmly nostalgic and darkly humorous, A Christmas Story deserves its status as a holiday perennial.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/99/11159941_mob.jpg'),(879,'Capote',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1151898-capote/','8267','0379725',1,NULL,'Philip Seymour Hoffman\'s riveting central performance guides a well-constructed retelling of the most sensational and significant period in author Truman Capote\'s life.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/02/250220_mob.jpg'),(880,'Citizen Kane',1941,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/citizen_kane/','10074','0033467',1,NULL,'Orson Welles\'s epic tale of a publishing tycoon\'s rise and fall is entertaining, poignant, and inventive in its storytelling, earning its reputation as a landmark achievement in film.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/93/41/10934161_mob.jpg'),(881,'How the Grinch Stole Christmas',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/how_the_grinch_stole_christmas/','10401','0170016',1,NULL,'Jim Carrey shines as the Grinch. Unfortunately, it\'s not enough to save this movie. You\'d be better off watching the TV cartoon.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/55/255591_mob.jpg'),(882,'Charlie\'s Angels',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/charlies_angels/','11062','0160127',1,NULL,'The story and plot are nothing to write home about, but the movie has enough action and campy fun to entertain the skeptics.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/13/33/11133373_mob.jpg'),(883,'The Count of Monte Cristo',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1110288-count_of_monte_cristo/','10118','0245844',1,NULL,'Though it may not reach for any new artistic heights, The Count of Monte Cristo is an old-fashioned yet enjoyable swashbuckler.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/12/83/11128345_mob.jpg'),(884,'Daddy Day Camp',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/daddy_day_camp/','566051689','0462244',1,NULL,'Daddy Day Camp relies too heavily on bodily functions for comedic effect, resulting in plenty of gags but no laughs.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/91/79/10917946_mob.jpg'),(885,'Sixteen Candles',1984,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sixteen_candles/','15348','0088128',1,NULL,'Significantly more mature than the teen raunch comedies that defined the era, Sixteen Candles is shot with compassion and clear respect for his characters and their hang-ups.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/27/90/279006_mob.jpg'),(886,'Cabin Fever',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1125409-cabin_fever/','13729','0303816',1,NULL,'More gory than scary, Cabin Fever is satisfied with paying homage to genre conventions rather than reinventing them.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/04/10890498_mob.jpg'),(887,'This Christmas',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/this_christmas/','770676786','0937375',1,NULL,'This Christmas features strong performances and a sharp portrayal of family dynamics, but relies too heavily on holiday movie cliches.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/86/75/10867510_mob.jpg'),(888,'Chicken Run',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chicken_run/','9394','0120630',1,NULL,'Chicken Run has all the charm of Nick Park\'s Wallace & Gromit, and something for everybody. The voice acting is fabulous, the slapstick is brilliant, and the action sequences are spectacular.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/86/71/10867195_mob.jpg'),(889,'Little Children',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/little_children/','314387182','0404203',1,NULL,'Little Children takes a penetrating look at suburbia and its flawed individuals with an unflinching yet humane eye.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/63/40/10634003_mob.jpg'),(890,'Capitalism: A Love Story',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/capitalism_a_love_story/','770811421','1232207',1,NULL,'Love him or hate him, Capitalism captures Michael Moore in his muckraking element -- with all the Moore-centric showmanship that entails.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/89/82/10898292_mob.jpg'),(891,'RoboCop',1987,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1017712-robocop/','18016','0093870',1,NULL,'While over-the-top and gory, Robocop is also a surprisingly smart sci-fi flick that uses ultraviolence to disguise its satire of American culture.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/29/03/290309_mob.jpg'),(892,'Caddyshack',1980,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/caddyshack/','16431','0080487',1,NULL,'Though unabashedly crude and juvenile, Caddyshack nevertheless scores with its classic slapstick, unforgettable characters, and endlessly quotable dialogue.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/55/04/75/5504753_mob.jpg'),(893,'Harold & Kumar Go to White Castle',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/harold_and_kumar_go_to_white_castle/','16982','0366551',1,NULL,'The likable leads and subversion of racial stereotypes elevate Harold and Kumar above the typical stoner comedy.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/14/72/11147225_mob.jpg'),(894,'North Country',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/north_country/','8841','0395972',1,NULL,'Though sometimes melodramatic and formulaic, North Country is nonetheless a rousing, powerful story of courage and humanity.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/03/250394_mob.jpg'),(895,'Cosmopolis',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cosmopolis/','771225278','1480656',1,'New York City, not-too-distant-future: Eric Packer, a 28 year-old finance golden boy dreaming of living in a civilization ahead of this one, watches a dark shadow cast over the firmament of the Wall Street galaxy, of which he is the uncontested king. As he is chauffeured across midtown Manhattan to get a haircut at his father\'s old barber, his anxious eyes are glued to the yuan\'s exchange rate: it is mounting against all expectations, destroying Eric\'s bet against it. Eric Packer is losing his empire with every tick of the clock. Meanwhile, an eruption of wild activity unfolds in the city\'s streets. Petrified as the threats of the real world infringe upon his cloud of virtual convictions, his paranoia intensifies during the course of his 24-hour cross-town odyssey. Packer starts to piece together clues that lead him to a most terrifying secret: his imminent assassination. -- (C) Official Site','Though some may find it cold and didactic, Cosmopolis benefits from David Cronenberg\'s precise direction, resulting in a psychologically complex adaptation of Don DeLillo\'s novel.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/41/11164165_mob.jpg'),(896,'A Prairie Home Companion',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/prairie_home_companion/','155655082','0420087',1,NULL,'The final film by the great Robert Altman, A Prairie Home Companion, the big screen adaptation of Garrison Keillor\'s radio broadcast, showcases plenty of the director\'s strengths: it\'s got a gigantic cast and plenty of quirky acting and dialogue. Much like the radio show, Companion features clever jokes, rousing tunes, and endearing characters. With strong work from Lindsay Lohan, Meryl Streep, Kevin Kline, and Tommy Lee Jones, it\'s a worthy swan song from one of the cinema\'s best.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/78/59/785962_mob.jpg'),(897,'Jeepers Creepers 2',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jeepers_creepers_2/','13400','0301470',1,NULL,'Jeepers Creepers 2 is competently made, but it doesn\'t have the scares of the original.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/95/36/10953695_mob.jpg'),(898,'Jeepers Creepers',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jeepers_creepers/','13360','0263488',1,NULL,'Jeepers Creepers has a promising start. Unfortunately, the tension and suspense quickly deflates into genre cliches as movie goes on.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/95/36/10953697_mob.jpg'),(899,'Miss Congeniality',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/miss_congeniality/','10560','0212346',1,NULL,'Though critics say Bullock is funny and charming, she can\'t overcome a bad script that makes the movie feel too much like a fluffy, unoriginal sitcom.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/55/05/33/5505338_mob.jpg'),(900,'Layer Cake',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/layer_cake/','16153','0375912',1,NULL,'A stylized, electric British crime thriller.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/55/28/552840_mob.jpg'),(901,'Casa de mi padre',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/casa_de_mi_padre/','771205913','1702425',1,'Armando Alvarez (Will Ferrell) has lived and worked on his father\'s ranch in Mexico his entire life. As the ranch encounters financial difficulties, Armando\'s younger brother Raul (Diego Luna) shows up with his new fiancee, Sonia (Genesis Rodriguez). It seems that Raul\'s success as an international businessman means the ranch\'s troubles are over as he pledges to settle all debts his father has incurred. But when Armando falls for Sonia, and Raul\'s business dealings turn out to be less than legit, all hell breaks loose as they find themselves in a war with Mexico\'s most feared drug lord, the mighty Onza (Gael Garcia Bernal). -- (C) Pantelion Films','Thinly written and not as funny as it needs to be, Casa de mi Padre would have worked better as a fake trailer or short film; stretched to feature length, it wears out its welcome far too quickly.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/29/11162945_mob.jpg'),(902,'Chasing Amy',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chasing_amy/','13118','0118842',1,NULL,'Chasing Amy explores gender roles, sexual mores, and the limits of friendship with a mixture of sensitivity, raw honesty, and director/screenwriter Kevin Smith\'s signature raunchy humor.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/26/82/268201_mob.jpg'),(903,'City of Ember',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/city_of_ember/','770681833','0970411',1,NULL,'City of Ember is visually arresting, and boasts a superb cast, but is sadly lacking in both action and adventure.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/95/10889518_mob.jpg'),(904,'Catwoman',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/catwoman/','10994','0327554',1,NULL,'Halle Berry is the lone bright spot, but even she can\'t save this laughable action thriller.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/55/35/14/5535142_mob.jpg'),(905,'Dude, Where\'s My Car?',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dude_wheres_my_car/','12758','0242423',1,NULL,'The movie isn\'t funny, the plot is too thin, and the production values feel more like a TV sitcom than a movie.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/48/11164859_mob.jpg'),(906,'A Very Harold & Kumar Christmas',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/very_harold_and_kumar_christmas/','771041051','1268799',1,'Following years of growing apart, Harold Lee (Cho) and Kumar Patel (Penn) have replaced each other with new friends and are preparing for their respective Yuletide celebrations. But when a mysterious package mistakenly arrives at Kumar\'s door on Christmas Eve, his attempt to redirect it to Harold\'s house ends with the \"high grade\" contents-and Harold\'s father-in-law\'s prize Christmas tree-going up in smoke. With his in-laws out of the house for the day, Harold decides to cover his tracks, rather than come clean. Reluctantly embarking on another ill-advised journey with Kumar through New York City, their search for the perfect replacement tree takes them through party heaven-and almost blows Christmas Eve sky high. -- (C) Warner Bros','Still raunchy, still irreverent, and still hit-and-miss, this Harold & Kumar outing also has a Christmas miracle: The audience gets to see the sweeter side of the duo.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/36/11163672_mob.jpg'),(907,'Daddy Day Care',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/daddy_day_care/','10928','0317303',1,NULL,'Daddy Day Care does its job of babysitting the tots. Anyone older will probably be bored.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/81/258196_mob.jpg'),(908,'Case 39',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/case_39/','770680570','0795351',1,'In CASE 39, family services social worker Emily Jenkins (Renee Zellweger) thinks she has seen it all... until she meets 10-year old Lilith Sullivan (Jodelle Ferland) and the child\'s cruel and dangerous parents. Her worst fears are confirmed when the parents try to harm Lily, their only daughter. Frightened for her life, Emily enlists the help of Detective Mike Barron (Ian McShane) and takes Lily in while she continues the search for the perfect foster family. Just as it seems as though Lily is on her way to a more loving home, under the guidance of Emily and psychiatrist (Bradley Cooper), dark forces surrounding this young girl come to light and, little do they know, their attempts to protect her will only bring on greater horror... -- (C) Paramount','Director Christian Alvert has a certain stylish flair, but it\'s wasted on Case 39\'s frightless, unoriginal plot.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/20/11152034_mob.jpg'),(909,'Cinderella',1950,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1004186-cinderella/','9371','0042332',1,NULL,'The rich colors, sweet songs, adorable mice and endearing (if suffering) heroine make Cinderella a nostalgically lovely charmer.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/06/250619_mob.jpg'),(910,'Hard Candy',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hard_candy/','147302867','0424136',1,NULL,'Disturbing, controversial, but entirely engrossing, Hard Candy is well written with strong lead performances, especially that of newcomer Ellen Page. A movie that stays with the viewer long after leaving the theater.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/31/40/314001_mob.jpg'),(911,'Cats & Dogs: The Revenge of Kitty Galore',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cats_and_dogs_the_revenge_of_kitty_galore/','770805223','1287468',1,'The epic struggle for control of planet Earth continues in this sequel to the 2001 comedy that confirmed everyone\'s worst suspicions about our furry four-legged companions. A former top spy for the clandestine feline espionage bureau MEOWS, Kitty Galore is determined to rule the world and finally gain the upper paw over her canine rivals. But when an unforeseen threat appears, cats and dogs must band together to defeat a common foe. Chris O\'Donnell and 30 Rock\'s Jack McBrayer head up the cast of the production, with scripting duties being handled by Brother Bear\'s Ron J. Friedman and Steve Bencich. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Dull and unfunny, this inexplicable sequel offers little more than the spectacle of digitally rendered talking animals with celebrity voices.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/12/06/11120621_mob.jpg'),(912,'The Children of Huang Shi',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/children_of_huang_shi/','528394726','0889588',1,NULL,'This beautifully photographed but dramatically flat war drama recounts an important chapter in history with little cinematic freshness.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/91/61/10916194_mob.jpg'),(913,'Cats & Dogs',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cats_and_dogs/','11574','0239395',1,NULL,'A great concept, but the movie fails to develop the characters and some of the jokes are hit-or-miss.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/92/10889221_mob.jpg'),(914,'The Collector',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1214027-collector/','770811108','0844479',1,NULL,'Increasingly tedious displays of gore makes this torture porn home-invasion-horror more programmatic than provocative.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/89/02/10890239_mob.jpg'),(915,'Dark City',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dark_city/','13011',NULL,1,NULL,'Stylishly gloomy, Dark City offers a polarizing whirl of arresting visuals and noirish action.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/67/89/73/6789737_mob.jpg'),(916,'College',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1191620-college/','770683838','0844671',1,NULL,'A pale imitation of the raunchy college frat of old, College aims low and misses.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/90/11169098_mob.jpg'),(917,'Alex Cross',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/alex_cross/','771229596','1694020',1,'Alex Cross follows the young homicide detective/psychologist (Tyler Perry), from the worldwide best-selling novels by James Patterson, as he meets his match in a serial killer (Matthew Fox). The two face off in a high-stakes game of cat and mouse, but when the mission gets personal, Cross is pushed to the edge of his moral and psychological limits in this taut and exciting action thriller. -- (C) Lionsgate','Tyler Perry and Matthew Fox do their best, but they\'re trampled by Rob Cohen\'s frustrating direction and a tasteless, lazily written screenplay.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/92/11169204_mob.jpg'),(918,'Crossroads',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1112549-crossroads/','11336','0275022',1,NULL,'A cliched and silly pop star vanity project, Crossroads is strictly for Britney fans only.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/94/50/10945037_mob.jpg'),(919,'Trouble with the Curve',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trouble_with_the_curve/','771268582','2083383',1,'Gus Lobel (Clint Eastwood) has been one of the best scouts in baseball for decades, but, despite his efforts to hide it, age is starting to catch up with him. Nevertheless, Gus-who can tell a pitch just by the crack of the bat-refuses to be benched for what may be the final innings of his career. He may not have a choice. The front office of the Atlanta Braves is starting to question his judgment, especially with the country\'s hottest batting phenom on deck for the draft. The one person who might be able to help is also the one person Gus would never ask: his daughter, Mickey (Amy Adams), an associate at a high-powered Atlanta law firm whose drive and ambition has put her on the fast track to becoming partner. Against her better judgment, and over Gus\'s objections, Mickey joins him on his latest scouting trip to North Carolina, jeopardizing her own career to save his. -- (C) Warner Bros.','Though predictable and somewhat dramatically underwhelming, Trouble with the Curve benefits from Clint Eastwood\'s grizzled charisma and his easy chemistry with a charming Amy Adams.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/74/11167431_mob.jpg'),(920,'Cool Runnings',1993,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1046227-cool_runnings/','10237','0106611',1,NULL,'Cool Runnings rises above its formulaic sports-movie themes with charming performances, light humor, and uplifting tone.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/47/254718_mob.jpg'),(921,'What Dreams May Come',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/what_dreams_may_come/','11789','0120889',1,NULL,'An insubstantial plot overshadows the beautiful, surreal scenery.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/24/262404_mob.jpg'),(922,'Centurion',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/centurion/','770809514','1020558',1,'CENTURION is set during the war between Roman soldiers and Pict tribesmen during the 2nd century Roman conquest of Britain. Michael Fassbender stars as Quintus Dias, Roman centurion and son of a legendary gladiator who leads a group of soldiers on a raid of a Pict camp to rescue a captured general (Dominic West). The son of the Pict leader is murdered during the raid, and the Romans find themselves hunted by a seemingly unstoppable group of the Pict\'s most vicious and skilled warriors, led by a beautiful and deadly tracker (Olga Kurylenko), and hell bent on revenge.-- (C) Magnolia','It\'s a bloody geyser of Neil Marshall\'s typically stylish B-movie action, but Centurion is too focused on hacking and slashing to deliver original dialogue or interesting characters.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/13/63/11136308_mob.jpg'),(923,'Close Encounters of the Third Kind',1977,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/close_encounters_of_the_third_kind/','10443','0075860',1,NULL,'Close Encounters\' most iconic bits (the theme, the mashed-potato sculpture, etc.) have been so thoroughly absorbed into the culture that it\'s easy to forget that its treatment of aliens as peaceful beings rather than warmongering monsters was somewhat groundbreaking in 1977.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/94/47/10944789_mob.jpg'),(924,'The Change-Up',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_change_up/','771041150','1488555',1,'Growing up together, Mitch (Ryan Reynolds) and Dave (Jason Bateman) were inseparable best friends, but as the years have passed they\'ve slowly drifted apart. While Dave is an overworked lawyer, husband and father of three, Mitch has remained a single, quasi-employed man-child who has never met a responsibility he liked. Following a drunken night out together, Mitch and Dave\'s worlds are turned upside down when they wake up in each other\'s bodies and proceed to freak the &*#@ out. Despite the freedom from their normal routines and habits, the guys soon discover that each other\'s lives are nowhere near as rosy as they once seemed. -- (C) Universal Pictures','There\'s a certain amount of fun to be had from watching Bateman and Reynolds play against type, but it isn\'t enough to carry The Change-Up through its crude humor and formulaic plot.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/72/11157218_mob.jpg'),(925,'Cyrus',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cyrus/','770856624','1336617',1,'Directed by mumblecore stalwarts Jay and Mark Duplass, Cyrus stars John C. Reilly as John, a middle-aged lonely divorced guy who, as the film opens, gets dragged to a party by his remarried ex-wife (Catherine Keener) -- who remains his best friend. After a few clumsy, drunken passes at a variety of women, John encounters Molly (Marisa Tomei), an attractive single-mom who finds John\'s social awkwardness appealing. They hit it off, and quickly begin a tender new relationship. Problems soon arise in the form of Cyrus (Jonah Hill), Molly\'s twentysomething son, who has an off-puttingly close relationship to his mom. Soon the jealous Cyrus sets about trying to break them up, and John must figure out how to deal with this unhinged and unexpected rival. ~ Perry Seibert, Rovi','While it may strike some viewers as slight, Cyrus is a successful hybrid of mainstream production values and the mumblecore ideals of directors Jay and Mark Duplass.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/11/97/11119720_mob.jpg'),(926,'Master and Commander: The Far Side of the World',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/master_and_commander_the_far_side_of_the_world/','10125','0311113',1,NULL,'Russell Crowe\'s rough charm is put to good use in this masterful adaptation of Patrick O\'Brian\'s novel.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/41/254198_mob.jpg'),(927,'Monte Carlo',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/monte_carlo_2011/','771202906','1067774',1,'Three graduates fulfill their dreams of vacationing in Paris. They accidentally find themselves in a lavish world, where they live like royalty and experience romance. But at the end of their journey, they discover the true magic of friendship. -- 20th Century Fox','Although it has its charming moments, Monte Carlo is mostly silly, predictable stuff that never pushes beyond the boundaries of formula.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/76/11157604_mob.jpg'),(928,'Crossover',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crossover/','287864892','0473024',1,NULL,'This heartfelt but incompetent, cliche-ridden sports picture is the cinematic equivalent of an airball.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/84/07/10840774_mob.jpg'),(929,'Wolf Creek',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wolf_creek/','24474','0416315',1,NULL,'Though Wolf Creek is effectively horrific, it is still tasteless exploitation.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/80/10888029_mob.jpg'),(930,'The Cell',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_cell_2000/','13516','0209958',1,NULL,'The Cell offers disturbing, stunning eye candy, but it is undermined by a weak and shallow plotline that offers nothing new.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/27/01/270120_mob.jpg'),(931,'Intolerable Cruelty',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/intolerable_cruelty/','11037','0138524',1,NULL,'Though more mainstream than other Coen films, there are still funny oddball touches, and Clooney and Zeta-Jones sizzle like old-time movie stars.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/55/36/85/5536851_mob.jpg'),(932,'Lust, Caution',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lust_caution/','512902931','0808357',1,NULL,'Ang Lee\'s Lust, Caution is a tense, sensual and beautifully-shot espionage film.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/86/08/10860817_mob.jpg'),(933,'Along Came a Spider',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/along_came_a_spider/','13471','0164334',1,NULL,'Derivative and contains too many implausible situations.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/41/10894154_mob.jpg'),(934,'The Condemned',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/condemned/','512887037','0443473',1,NULL,'The Condemned is a morally ambiguous, exceedingly violent and mostly forgettable action film.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/52/53/61/5253611_mob.jpg'),(935,'Orange County',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/orange_county/','10724','0273923',1,NULL,'Smarter than the average teen movie, but a little on the unmemorable side.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168961_mob.jpg'),(936,'Cashback',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cashback/','552835835','0460740',1,NULL,'An unlikable protagonist, messy editing, and gratuitous nudity might make audiences ask for their cash back.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/91/21/03/9121037_mob.jpg'),(937,'Colombiana',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/colombiana/','771205891','1657507',1,'In the action film Colombiana, Zoe Saldana plays Cataleya, a young woman who has grown up to be an assassin after witnessing the murder of her parents as a child. Turning herself into a professional killer and working for her uncle, she remains focused on her ultimate goal: to hunt down and get revenge on the mobster responsible for her parents\' deaths. -- (C) Sony Pictures','Zoe Saldana has the chops but she\'s taken out by erratic and sloppy filmmaking.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/36/11163650_mob.jpg'),(938,'Sky Captain and the World of Tomorrow',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sky_captain/','10053','0346156',1,NULL,'Sky Captain and the World of Tomorrow is slim on plot and characterization, but the visuals more than make up for it.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/23/10892374_mob.jpg'),(939,'The City of Lost Children (La Cite des Enfants Perdus)',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/city_of_lost_children/','13050','0112682',1,NULL,'Not all of its many intriguing ideas are developed, but The City of Lost Children is an engrossing, disturbing, profoundly memorable experience.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/78/267824_mob.jpg'),(940,'Cocaine Cowboys',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10007598-cocaine_cowboys/','314103660','0380268',1,NULL,'As frenetic, thrilling, and lacking in subtletly as its drug of focus...and just as likely to prompt some hard questions after it\'s gone.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/87/98/10879811_mob.jpg'),(941,'House of 1000 Corpses',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/house_of_1000_corpses/','12901','0251736',1,NULL,'There\'s an abundance of gore in this derivative horror movie, but little sense or wit.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/45/10894585_mob.jpg'),(942,'L.A. Confidential',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/la_confidential/','12956','0119488',1,NULL,'Taut pacing, brilliantly dense writing and Oscar-worthy acting combine to produce a smart, popcorn-friendly thrill ride.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/87/11168703_mob.jpg'),(943,'Carnage',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/carnage/','771240424','1692486',1,'Carnage is a razor sharp, biting comedy centered on parental differences. After two boys duke it out on a playground, the parents of the \"victim\" invite the parents of the \"bully\" over to work out their issues. A polite discussion of childrearing soon escalates into verbal warfare, with all four parents revealing their true colors. None of them will escape the carnage. -- (C) Sony Pictures Classics','It isn\'t as compelling on the screen as it was on the stage, but Carnage makes up for its flaws with Polanski\'s smooth direction and assured performances from Winslet and Foster.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/13/11161344_mob.jpg'),(944,'The Cave',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cave/','5617','0402901',1,NULL,'Despite its stylized and impressive sets, this horror-monster movie mish-mash suffers from endless cliches and wildly implausible plotlines.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/22/10882223_mob.jpg'),(945,'Cool Hand Luke',1967,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cool_hand_luke/','18102','0061512',1,NULL,'Though hampered by Stuart Rosenberg\'s direction, Cool Hand Luke is held aloft by a stellar script and one of Paul Newman\'s most indelible performances.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/98/11159869_mob.jpg'),(946,'Arthur Christmas',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/arthur_christmas/','771025662','1430607',1,'The 3D, CG-animated family comedy Arthur Christmas, an Aardman production for Sony Pictures Animation, at last reveals the incredible, never-before seen answer to every child\'s question: \'So how does Santa deliver all those presents in one night?\' The answer: Santa\'s exhilarating, ultra-high-tech operation hidden beneath the North Pole. But at the heart of the film is a story with the ingredients of a Christmas classic - a family in a state of comic dysfunction and an unlikely hero, Arthur, with an urgent mission that must be completed before Christmas morning dawns. -- (C) Sony Pictures','Aardman Animations broadens their humor a bit for Arthur Christmas, a clever and earnest holiday film with surprising emotional strength.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/74/11167404_mob.jpg'),(947,'Sympathy for Lady Vengeance',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sympathy_for_lady_vengeance/','149086041','0451094',1,NULL,'Stylistically flashy and gruesomely violent, Sympathy for Lady Vengeance fits in nicely with the other two films of Park\'s revenge trilogy.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/05/10890561_mob.jpg'),(948,'Fever Pitch (The Perfect Catch)',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fever_pitch/','23','0332047',1,NULL,'While not a home run, Fever Pitch has enough charm and on-screen chemistry between the two leads to make it a solid hit.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/24/97/249737_mob.jpg'),(949,'Dr. Seuss - The Cat in the Hat',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cat_in_the_hat/','12422','0312528',1,NULL,'Filled with double entendres and potty humor, this Cat falls flat.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/53/265308_mob.jpg'),(950,'The Core',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/core/','11233','0298814',1,NULL,'A B-movie with its tongue planted firmly in cheek, The Core is so unintentionally (intentionally?) bad that it\'s a hoot.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/84/02/10840223_mob.jpg'),(951,'The Company Men',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the-company-men/','770820081','1172991',1,'Bobby Walker (Ben Affleck) is living the American dream: great job, beautiful family, shiny Porsche in the garage. When corporate downsizing leaves him and co-workers Phil Woodward (Chris Cooper) and Gene McClary (Tommy Lee Jones) jobless, the three men are forced to re-define their lives as men, husbands, and fathers. <br /><br /> Bobby soon finds himself enduring enthusiastic life coaching, a job building houses for his brother-in-law (Kevin Costner) which does not play to his executive skill set, and perhaps the realization that there is more to life than chasing the bigger, better deal. With humor, pathos, and keen observation, writer-director John Wells (the creator of \"ER\") introduces us to the new realities of American life. -- (C) Weinstein','It might be hard for most viewers to identify with The Company Men\'s well-heeled protagonists, but writer/director John Wells uses their plight to make universally resonant points -- and gets the most out of his excellent cast.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/31/11153150_mob.jpg'),(952,'Cedar Rapids',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cedar_rapids_2010/','771193483','1477837',1,'To call insurance agent Tim Lippe (Ed Helms), \"naive\" is a gross understatement. He\'s never left his small hometown. He\'s never stayed at a hotel. And he\'s never experienced anything like Cedar Rapids, Iowa. Sent to represent his company at the annual insurance convention, Tim is soon distracted by three convention veterans (John C. Reilly, Anne Heche and Isiah Whitlock Jr.) who will show him the ropes and push his boundaries. For a guy who plays everything by the book, this convention will be anything but conventional -- (C) Fox Searchlight','It\'s as conventional as its Midwestern setting, but Cedar Rapids boasts a terrific cast and a script that deftly blends R-rated raunch and endearing sweetness.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/47/11154775_mob.jpg'),(953,'Jesus Camp',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jesus_camp/','314101917','0486358',1,NULL,'Evangelical indoctrination is given an unflinching, even-handed look in this utterly worthwhile documentary.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/91/79/10917947_mob.jpg'),(954,'One Missed Call',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/one_missed_call/','770674406','0479968',1,NULL,'One of the weakest entries in the J-horror remake sweepstakes, One Missed Call is undone by bland performances and shopworn shocks.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/16/10891634_mob.jpg'),(955,'Snow Cake',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/snow_cake/','326396726','0448124',1,NULL,'Sigourney Weaver gracefully undertakes a difficult role, while the rest of the cast lifts the histrionic plot into something worthwhile.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/34/10/56/3410563_mob.jpg'),(956,'Center Stage',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/center_stage/','10234','0210616',1,NULL,'Critics say that if you\'re willing to suffer through soap opera-like dialogue and plot to see some excellent dancing, this movie is for you. Otherwise, you might be better off renting Fame.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/47/254713_mob.jpg'),(957,'Creation',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1205717-creation/','770800781','0974014',1,NULL,'This Charles Darwin biopic is curiously dispassionate, but Creation contains some of director Jon Amiel\'s best work, and Paul Bettany\'s performance is not to be missed.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/94/36/10943696_mob.jpg'),(958,'Chinatown',1974,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chinatown/','12883','0071315',1,NULL,'As bruised and cynical as the decade that produced it, this noir classic benefits from Robert Towne\'s brilliant screenplay, director Roman Polanski\'s steady hand, and wonderful performances from Jack Nicholson and Faye Dunaway.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/19/10871921_mob.jpg'),(959,'Crossing Over',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crossing_over/','770679612','0924129',1,NULL,'Crossing Over is flagrant and heavy-handed about a situation that deserves more deliberate treatment, and joins its characters with coincidences that strain believability.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/76/10887646_mob.jpg'),(960,'National Lampoon\'s Christmas Vacation',1989,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/national_lampoons_christmas_vacation/','10856','0097958',1,NULL,'While Christmas Vacation may not be the most disciplined comedy, it\'s got enough laughs and good cheer to make for a solid seasonal treat.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/42/11154289_mob.jpg'),(961,'Mutant Chronicles',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mutant_chronicles/','770681656','0490181',1,NULL,'Bad acting, poor CGI and clunky script mean this sci-fi thriller is lacking in all departments including the thrills.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/84/95/10849585_mob.jpg'),(962,'Confessions of a Dangerous Mind',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/confessions_of_a_dangerous_mind/','13421','0270288',1,NULL,'Rockwell is spot-on as Barris, and Clooney directs with entertaining style and flair.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/84/10878465_mob.jpg'),(963,'Warlords (Tau ming chong)',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/warlords-2007/','770673133','0913968',1,NULL,'Slightly stodgy historical Chinese epic with impressive battles.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/93/96/10939605_mob.jpg'),(964,'Control',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/control/','770671983','0421082',1,NULL,'Control is a work of art, thanks to its evocative black and white cinematography and sensational performances from Sam Riley and Samantha Morton. Even those not familiar with Joy Division can still appreciate the beauty of the film.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/89/36/92/8936921_mob.jpg'),(965,'Star Trek - First Contact',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/star_trek_first_contact/','11853','0117731',1,NULL,'While fans of the series will surely appreciate it, First Contact is exciting, engaging, and visually appealing enough to entertain Star Trek novices.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/85/10888599_mob.jpg'),(966,'Creepshow',1982,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/creepshow/','13487','0083767',1,NULL,'It\'s uneven, as anthologies often are, but Creepshow is colorful, frequently funny, and treats its inspirations with infectious reverence.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/27/00/270002_mob.jpg'),(967,'Chloe',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10011774-chloe/','770813273','1352824',1,'An untrusting wife attempts to prove that her husband is cheating by hiring an escort to seduce him, inadvertently endangering her entire family in the process. Catherine (Julianne Moore) is a respected doctor, and her husband, David (Liam Neeson), is a dedicated music professor. They\'ve been married for years and have a teenage son together, but lately the passion has faded from their romance. The morning after David misses his flight home -- and the elaborate surprise birthday party Catherine had planned to celebrate his return -- Catherine finds a text message on his phone that leads her to believe her husband is sleeping with a female student. Her suspicions grow over the following weeks, and when Catherine has a run-in with an escort named Chloe (Amanda Seyfried), she hires the ravishing blonde to test her husband\'s fidelity. After each encounter with David, Chloe reports back to Catherine with all the sordid details. But the further the experiment goes, the less clear Chloe\'s motivations for taking part in it become, and the more the untrusting wife begins to fear that the situation has spiraled out of control. Directed by Atom Egoyan (The Sweet Hereafter, Ararat), this erotic thriller is a remake of Anne Fontaine\'s French film Nathalie..., and was adapted by Erin Cressida Wilson. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Despite its promising pedigree and a titillating premise, Chloe ultimately fails to deliver the heat -- or the thrills -- expected of a sexual thriller.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/92/77/10927726_mob.jpg'),(968,'The Conspirator',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_conspirator/','771194947','0968264',1,'In the wake of Abraham Lincoln\'s assassination, seven men and one woman are arrested and charged with conspiring to kill the President, Vice President, and Secretary of State. The lone woman charged, Mary Surratt (Wright) owns a boarding house where John Wilkes Booth (Toby Kebbell) and others met and planned the simultaneous attacks. Against the ominous back-drop of post-Civil War Washington, newly-minted lawyer, Frederick Aiken (McAvoy), a 28-year-old Union war-hero, reluctantly agrees to defend Surratt before a military tribunal. Aiken realizes his client may be innocent and that she is being used as bait and hostage in order to capture the only conspirator to have escaped a massive manhunt, her own son, John (Johnny Simmons). As the nation turns against her, Surratt is forced to rely on Aiken to uncover the truth and save her life. -- (C) Official Site','The Conspirator is well cast and tells a worthy story, but many viewers will lack the patience for Redford\'s deliberate, stagebound approach.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/57/11155718_mob.jpg'),(969,'The Manchurian Candidate',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/manchurian_candidate/','14500','0368008',1,NULL,'While not the classic its predecessor is, this update is well-acted and conjures a chilling resonance.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/55/35/35/5535356_mob.jpg'),(970,'Strangers with Candy',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1152191-strangers_with_candy/','155655225','0369994',1,NULL,'Occasionally funny, but little more than a jumbled, overextended episode of the TV show. Still, Candy devotees won\'t be disappointed.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/39/22/1039223_mob.jpg'),(971,'Christmas with the Kranks',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/christmas_with_the_kranks/','10018','0388419',1,NULL,'A mirthless movie as fresh as last year\'s fruit cake, Christmas with the Kranks is a coarse, garish comedy that promotes conformity.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/27/10882789_mob.jpg'),(972,'Code Name: The Cleaner',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/code_name_the_cleaner/','459358075','0462229',1,NULL,'Code Name: The Cleaner is a limp action/comedy flick that alternates between lame, worn-out jokes and cheesy martial arts.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/40/44/08/4044085_mob.jpg'),(973,'Dickie Roberts - Former Child Star',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dickie_roberts_former_child_star/','11727','0325258',1,NULL,'A so-so David Spade comedy with a few laughs.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/21/262102_mob.jpg'),(974,'Country Strong',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/country_strong/','771203530','1555064',1,'Soon after a rising young singer-songwriter (Hedlund) gets involved with a fallen, emotionally unstable country star (Paltrow), the pair embarks on a career resurrection tour helmed by her husband/manager (McGraw) and featuring a beauty-queen-turned-singer (Meester). Between concerts, romantic entanglements and old demons threaten to derail them all. -- (C) Columbia','The cast gives it their all, and Paltrow handles her songs with aplomb, but Country Strong\'s cliched, disjointed screenplay hits too many bum notes.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/43/11154324_mob.jpg'),(975,'Larry Crowne',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/larry_crowne/','771199080','1583420',1,'Until he was downsized, affable, amiable Larry Crowne (Tom Hanks) was a superstar team leader at the big-box company where he\'s worked since his time in the Navy. Underwater on his mortgage and unclear on what to do with his suddenly free days, Larry heads to his local college to start over. There he becomes part of a colorful community of outcasts, also-rans and the overlooked all trying to find a better future for themselves...often moving around town in a herd of scooters. In his public-speaking class, Larry develops an unexpected crush on his teacher Mercedes Tainot (Julia Roberts), who has lost as much passion for teaching as she has for her husband. -- (C) Universal Pictures','Despite the relaxed, easy chemistry of stars Tom Hanks and Julia Roberts, Larry Crowne is surprisingly bland and conventional.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/77/11157716_mob.jpg'),(976,'Choke',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/choke/','770682478','1024715',1,NULL,'While bolstered by strong performances from Sam Rockwell and Anjelica Huston, Choke struggles to capture the tone of Chuck Palahniuk\'s novel.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/85/09/10850932_mob.jpg'),(977,'Who\'s Your Caddy?',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/whos_your_caddy/','770673012','0785077',1,NULL,'Who\'s Your Caddy? is unoriginal, unfunny, and just plain forgettable.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie