p://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1037581-cape_fear/','13137','0101540',1,NULL,'Smart and stylish, Cape Fear is a gleefully mainstream shocker from Martin Scorsese, with a terrifying Robert De Niro peformance.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/93/72/10937223_mob.jpg'),(996,'Like Crazy',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/like_crazy/','771224180','1758692',1,'A love story is both a physical and emotional tale, one that can be deeply personal and heartbreaking for an audience to experience. Director Drake Doremus\' film Like Crazy beautifully illustrates how your first real love is as thrilling and blissful as it is devastating. When a British college student (Felicity Jones) falls for her American classmate (Anton Yelchin) they embark on a passionate and life-changing journey only to be separated when she violates the terms of her visa. Like Crazy explores how a couple faces the real challenges of being together and of being apart. -- (C) Paramount','It has the schmaltzy trappings of my romantic films, but Like Crazy allows its characters to express themselves beyond dialogue, crafting a true, intimate study.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/91/11169147_mob.jpg'),(997,'The Ten Commandments',1956,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1021015-ten_commandments/','9686','0049833',1,NULL,'Bombastic and occasionally silly but extravagantly entertaining, Cecil B. DeMille\'s all-star spectacular is a muscular retelling of the great Bible story.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168921_mob.jpg'),(998,'Last Chance Harvey',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/last_chance_harvey/','770784001','1046947',1,NULL,'Last Chance Harvey is an above-average story that graduates to potent romantic drama based on the chemistry and charm of its top-notch performers.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/53/11155396_mob.jpg'),(999,'Aqua Teen Hunger Force Colon Movie Film for Theatres',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/aqua_teen_hunger_force_colon_movie_film_for_theatres/','491975117','0455326',1,NULL,'The non sequitur humor of Aqua Teen Hunger Force will surely appeal to its built-in fanbase, but for the uninitiated, the premise wears thin.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/61/11/86/6111861_mob.jpg'),(1000,'Curse of the Golden Flower',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/curse_of_the_golden_flower/','420147807','0473444',1,NULL,'Melodrama, swordplay, and CG armies -- fans of martial arts epic will get what they bargain for, though the baroque art direction can be both mesmerizing and exhaustively excessive.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/92/10889211_mob.jpg'),(1001,'Miller\'s Crossing',1990,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/millers_crossing/','12945','0100150',1,NULL,'Though possibly more notable for its distinctive style than an airtight story, this Coen brothers take on the classic gangster flick features sharp dialogue, impressive cinematography, and a typically quirky cast of characters.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/73/267312_mob.jpg'),(1002,'The Cold Light of Day',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_cold_light_of_day/','771224090','1366365',1,'Will Shaw (Henry Cavill) goes to Spain for a weeklong sailing vacation with his family but his whole world turns upside down when the family is kidnapped by intelligence agents hell-bent on recovering a mysterious briefcase and Will suddenly finds himself on the run. -- (C) Summit Entertainment',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/37/11163765_mob.jpg'),(1003,'Che: Part One (The Argentine)',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1221112-che/','770675137','0892255',1,NULL,'Though lengthy and at times plodding, Soderbergh\'s vision and Benicio Del Toro\'s understated performance ensure that Che always fascinates.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/49/10884940_mob.jpg'),(1004,'Chasing Liberty',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chasing_liberty/','11153',NULL,1,NULL,'Formulaic comfort food for the teen crowd.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/17/10891706_mob.jpg'),(1005,'The Chumscrubber',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chumscrubber/','2772','0406650',1,NULL,'This derivative poke at suburbia falls short of delivering a scathing indictment of upper middle-class disconnect.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/24/99/249913_mob.jpg'),(1006,'Casino Royale',1967,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1003722-casino_royale/','18316','0061452',1,NULL,'A goofy, dated parody of spy movie cliches, Casino Royale squanders its all-star cast on a meandering, mostly laugh-free script.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/12/81/11128112_mob.jpg'),(1007,'Clash of the Titans',1981,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/clash_of_the_titans/','10212','0082186',1,NULL,'A goofy, old-school sword-and-sandal epic, Clash of the Titans mines Greek mythology for its story and fleshes it out with Ray Harryhausen\'s charmingly archaic stop-motion animation techniques.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/28/11152887_mob.jpg'),(1008,'Who Killed the Electric Car?',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/who_killed_the_electric_car/','170572378','0489037',1,NULL,'A searing indictment of big business and greed, Who Killed The Electric Car? is a well-tuned doc that simultaneously entertains and enrages.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/39/26/1039266_mob.jpg'),(1009,'Cliffhanger',1993,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1044214-cliffhanger/','16194','0106582',1,NULL,'While it can\'t escape comparisons to the movies it borrows from, Cliffhanger is a tense, action-packed thriller and a showcase for the talents that made Sylvester Stallone a star.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/70/11157076_mob.jpg'),(1010,'Celeste and Jesse Forever',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/celeste_and_jesse_forever/','771266291','1405365',1,'Celeste (Rashida Jones) and Jesse (Andy Samberg) met in high school, married young and are growing apart. Now thirty, Celeste is the driven owner of her own media consulting firm, Je