 life is undeniably disturbing, but Dustin Hoffman and Jon Voight\'s performances make it difficult to turn away.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/51/10885192_mob.jpg'),(1033,'Heavenly Creatures',1994,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/heavenly_creatures/','22544','0110005',1,NULL,'Dark, stylish, and captivating, Heavenly Creatures signals both the auspicious debut of Kate Winslet and the arrival of Peter Jackson as more than just a cult director.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/90/75/10907555_mob.jpg'),(1034,'Crimson Tide',1995,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crimson_tide/','13167','0112740',1,NULL,'Boasting taut, high energy thrills and some cracking dialogue courtesy of an uncredited Quentin Tarantino, Crimson Tide finds director Tony Scott near the top of his action game.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/26/84/268417_mob.jpg'),(1035,'Space Cowboys',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/space_cowboys/','10873','0186566',1,NULL,'While the plot is overly cliched, the suberb acting by the stars (especially the tense interactions between Clint Eastwood and Tommy Lee Jones) and the spectacular special effects make this a movie worth seeing.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/79/257904_mob.jpg'),(1036,'The Santa Clause',1994,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/santa_clause/','12344','0111070',1,NULL,'The Santa Clause is utterly undemanding, but it\'s firmly rooted in the sort of good old-fashioned holiday spirit missing from too many modern yuletide films.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/50/265000_mob.jpg'),(1037,'Captain Corelli\'s Mandolin',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/captain_corellis_mandolin/','14200','0238112',1,NULL,'The cinematography is gorgeous, but the movie plays it fast and loose with history and the novel it was adapted from. Mostly, the movie fails because the romance between the leads strains credulity and the story is largely uninvolving.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/94/83/10948332_mob.jpg'),(1038,'Wild Child',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10008678-wild_child/','770680383','1024255',1,NULL,'More mild than wild. This tween comedy mess falls flat on its face due to poor characters, poor direction and poor jokes.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/84/90/10849053_mob.jpg'),(1039,'Cache (Hidden)',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1153493-cache/','24470','0387898',1,NULL,'A creepy French psychological thriller that commands the audience\'s attention throughout.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/31/17/311798_mob.jpg'),(1040,'Chariots of Fire',1981,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chariots_of_fire/','10818','0082158',1,NULL,'Decidedly slower and less limber than the Olympic runners at the center of its story, the film nevertheless manages to make effectively stirring use of its spiritual and patriotic themes.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/81/11168143_mob.jpg'),(1041,'Changing Lanes',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/changing_lanes/','13986','0264472',1,NULL,'Though some may find its conclusion unsatisfying, Changing Lanes is a tense, well-crafted exploration of meaty ethical dilemmas.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/28/31/10283104_mob.jpg'),(1042,'The Collection',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_collection_2012/','771312085','1748227',1,'When Elena\'s (Emma Fitzpatrick) friends take her to a secret party at an undisclosed location, she never imagined she would become the latest victim of The Collector, a psychopathic killer. The Collector kidnaps and transports her to an abandoned hotel he\'s transformed into his own private maze of torture and death. Upon learning of his daughter\'s disappearance, Elena\'s wealthy father (Christopher McDonald) hires a group of mercenaries to retrieve her from the vicious grips of The Collector. These mercenaries coerce Arkin (Josh Stewart), the only man to have escaped the wrath of this heinous monster, to lead them through the gruesome labyrinth. Now, Arkin finds himself fighting for his own life in order to save Elena. -- (C) Official Site','The Collection offers more grisly thrills and twisted humor than its predecessor; in other words, fun for genre fans, but unpleasant for anyone else.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/69/11166931_mob.jpg'),(1043,'The Crocodile Hunter - Collision Course',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crocodile_hunter_collision_course/','11746','0305396',1,NULL,'Aside from the unnecessary plot about a downed US spy satellite, there\'s not much difference between the movie and the TV show.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/91/77/10917789_mob.jpg'),(1044,'Urban Legends: Final Cut',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/urban_legends_final_cut/','15289','0192731',1,NULL,'This teen horror movie brings nothing new to an already exhausted genre. And it\'s bad. Really bad.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/94/63/10946361_mob.jpg'),(1045,'Comedy Central Roast of Charlie Sheen',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/comedy_central_roast_of_charlie_sheen/','771257874',NULL,1,'It\'s Charlie Sheen\'s turn to step in to the celebrity hot seat for the latest installment of The Comedy Central Roast.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1046,'But I\'m A Cheerleader',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/but_im_a_cheerleader/','14580','0179116',1,NULL,'Critics think that But I\'m a Cheerleader could have been better. The acting is stiff at times and the plot is surprisingly unoriginal.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/27/53/275310_mob.jpg'),(1047,'The Chorus (Les Choristes)',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chorus_les_choristes/','10152','0372824',1,NULL,'While predictable, this low-key heartwarmer manages to be uplifting without overdoing the sentiment.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/61/21/10612171_mob.jpg'),(1048,'Coriolanus',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/coriolanus_2010/','771204667','1372686',1,'Caius Martius \'Coriolanus\' (Ralph Fiennes), a revered and feared Roman General is at odds with the city of Rome and his fellow citizens. Pushed by his controlling and ambitious mother Volumnia (Vanessa Redgrave) to seek the exalted and powerful position of Consul, he is loath to ingratiate himself with the masses whose votes he needs in order to secure the office. When the public refuses to support him, Coriolanus\'s anger prompts a riot that culminates in his expulsion from Rome. The banished hero then allies himself with his sworn enemy Tullus Aufidius (Gerard Butler) to take his revenge on the city. -- (C) Weinstein Co','Visceral and visually striking, Ralph Fiennes\' Coriolanus proves Shakespeare can still be both electrifying and relevant in a modern context.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/94/11159402_mob.jpg'),(1049,'Margin Call',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/margin_call/','771225052','1615147',1,'Set in the high-stakes world of the financial industry, Margin Call is an entangling thriller involving the key players at an investment firm during one perilous 24-hour period in the early stages of the 2008 financial crisis. When an entry-level analyst unlocks information that could prove to be the downfall of the firm, a roller-coaster ride ensues as decisions both financial and moral catapult the lives of all involved to the brink of disaster. Writer/director J.C. Chandor\'s enthralling first feature is a stark and bravely authentic portrayal of the financial industry and its denizens as they confront the decisions that shape our global future. -- (C) Roadside Attractions','Smart, tightly wound, and solidly acted, Margin Call turns the convoluted financial meltdown of \'08 into gripping, thought-provoking drama.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/04/11160411_mob.jpg'),(1050,'Candy',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/candy/','286584162','0424880',1,NULL,'Stars Heath Ledger and Abbie Cornish look better than they should as heroin addicts, and their characters are too absorbed and self-pitying to be totally compelling.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/35/10883510_mob.jpg'),(1051,'The Cove',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1208882-cove/','770802994','1313104',1,NULL,'Though decidedly one-sided, The Cove is an impeccably crafted, suspenseful expose of the covert slaughter of dolphins in Japan.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/80/10888094_mob.jpg'),(1052,'An American Carol',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/an_american_carol/','770789096','1190617',1,NULL,'An American Carol suffers not so much from its perceived political bias, but from the fact that it simply is not very funny.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/72/10877241_mob.jpg'),(1053,'200 Cigarettes',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/200_cigarettes/','14561','0137338',1,NULL,'A clumsy and scattered comedy with a poorly executed script.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/27/52/275211_mob.jpg'),(1054,'Ip Man 2: Legend of the Grandmaster',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ip_man_2_legend_of_the_grandmaster/','771040112','1386931',1,'International megastar Donnie Yen reprises his iconic role as the real-life kung fu grandmaster Ip Man in this martial arts spectacular. After escaping the Japanese occupation of his hometown of Fo Shan, China, Ip Man and his family have arrived in Hong Kong, which is living under the iron fist of British colonial rule. Ip wants to support his family by opening up a martial arts academy to teach his unique Wing Chun style. But a corrupt cabal of Hong Kong martial arts masters, led by Hung Chun-nam (the legendary Sammo Hung), refuses to allow Ip to teach until he proves himself - and prove himself he does, in an intense series of fights against the masters showcasing a dazzling variety of martial arts styles, culminating in a highly anticipated brawl between Ip and Hung atop a rickety table. But even after gaining the respect of the masters, Ip\'s troubles are far from over. Hong Kong under British rule is a world of corruption, and when a Western-style boxer named Taylor \"Twister\" Milos comes to town to entertain the British upper-class, and insults both Chinese martial arts and the native citizens in a horrifically violent way, Ip must step up and fight for the honor of both his kung fu and the Chinese people. Forced by honor to enter a brutal \"King of the Ring\" boxing match against Twister, it\'s East versus West in an amazing, knock-down drag-out fight to the finish, the likes of which have never been seen on-screen before. Presented in the original, un-dubbed and uncut, international version that\'s been breaking box-office records across Asia, Ip Man 2: Legend of the Grandmaster is a throwback to the golden age of Hong Kong martial arts cinema that will delight kung fu fans and newcomers alike. -- (C) Well Go USA and Variance',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/46/11154623_mob.jpg'),(1055,'The Human Centipede (First Sequence)',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/human_centipede/','770817002','1467304',1,NULL,'Grotesque, visceral and hard to (ahem) swallow, this surgical horror doesn\'t quite earn its stripes because the gross-outs overwhelm and devalue everything else.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/95/55/10955551_mob.jpg'),(1056,'Joyeux Noel (Merry Christmas)',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/joyeux_noel/','49249009','0424205',1,NULL,'The poignant humanity on display in Joyeux Noel makes its sentimentality forgivable.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/31/28/312815_mob.jpg'),(1057,'Supercop (Police Story 3) (Ging chaat goo si 3: Chiu kap ging chaat)',1992,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/supercop/','147524239','0104558',1,NULL,'Blending hand-to-hand combat with breathtaking stunts and slapstick comedy, Supercop reminds us why Jackie Chan is one of the world\'s great entertainers.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/86/39/10863979_mob.jpg'),(1058,'The Promise (Master of Crimson Armor) (Wu ji)',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1