 Filmmaker Rodman Flender\'s resulting documentary, Conan O\'Brien Can\'t Stop, is an intimate portrait of an artist trained in improvisation, captured at the most improvisational time of his career. It offers a window into the private writers room and rehearsal halls as O\'Brien\'s \"half-assed show\" (his words) is almost instantly assembled and mounted to an adoring fan base. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/77/11157713_mob.jpg'),(1064,'Catfish',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/catfish/','770856706','1584016',1,'In late 2007, filmmakers Ariel Schulman and Henry Joost sensed a story unfolding as they began to film the life of Ariel\'s brother, Nev. They had no idea that their project would lead to the most exhilarating and unsettling months of their lives. A reality thriller that is a shocking product of our times, Catfish is a riveting story of love, deception and grace within a labyrinth of online intrigue.-- (C) Official Site','Catfish may tread the line between real-life drama and crass exploitation a little too unsteadily for some viewers\' tastes, but its timely premise and tightly wound mystery make for a gripping documentary.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/18/11151834_mob.jpg'),(1065,'Glee: The 3D Concert Movie',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/glee_the_3d_concert_movie/','771242069','1922612',1,'The multi-generational phenomenon that has inspired millions to embrace their inner-Gleek will soon bring them together to experience Glee a whole new way. -- (C) Official Site','The unconverted will remain just as perplexed as ever, but for gleeful Gleeks, The 3D Concert Movie delivers exactly what it promises.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/93/11159304_mob.jpg'),(1066,'Cirque Du Soleil: Worlds Away 3D',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cirque_du_soleil_worlds_away_3d/','771270612','1792647',1,'From the big top to the big screen, visionary filmmaker James Cameron and director Andrew Adamson (Shrek, Narnia) invite you and your family on an all new 3D adventure: Cirque du Soleil Worlds Away. A young couple who is separated, must journey through the astonishing and dreamlike worlds of Cirque du Soleil to find each other, as audiences experience the immersive 3D technology that will allow them to leap, soar, swim, and dance with the performers. This Holiday Season, Cirque du Soleil brings their world to your city! -- (C) Paramount',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/72/11167255_mob.jpg'),(1067,'Coco Chanel & Igor Stravinsky',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/coco_chanel_and_igor_stravinsky/','770808836','1023441',1,NULL,'It\'s well-acted and beautifully filmed, but Jan Kounen\'s dramatization of the affair between his famous subjects is curiously short on passion.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/95/32/10953269_mob.jpg'),(1068,'Spirit - Stallion of the Cimarron',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spirit_stallion_of_the_cimarron/','9502','0166813',1,NULL,'A visually stunning film that may be too predictable and politically correct for adults, but should serve children well.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/36/11153650_mob.jpg'),(1069,'Diminished Capacity',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/diminished_capacity/','770682046','1007950',1,NULL,'This low-key comedy about memory loss offers mild pleasures but is too bland to fully resonate.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/84/96/10849656_mob.jpg'),(1070,'Cemetery Junction',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cemetery_junction/','770811375','1196204',1,'Playing out against the glamorous backdrop of Reading, England, during the 1970s, Cemetery Junction (a nod to the stretch of road of the same name) focuses on a small group of colorful characters who work for an insurance company. Written, directed, and produced by Ricky Gervais and Stephen Merchant, the film marks the duo\'s first collaboration for the big screen and features a cast that includes the likes of Ralph Fiennes, Emily Watson, and Gervais himself. ~ Rovi','It fails to challenge the well-established conventions of its storyline, but Cemetery Junction benefits from the genuine warmth of its script, as well as its refusal to give in to cheap nostalgia.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/95/28/10952874_mob.jpg'),(1071,'Romance and Cigarettes',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1159262-romance_and_cigarettes/','147454363','0368222',1,NULL,'This movie musical aims for fun and modern, but Romance and Cigarettes is too scattered and uneven to achieve either.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/38/47/86/3847867_mob.jpg'),(1072,'Scrooge (A Christmas Carol)',1951,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1004126-christmas_carol/','18404','0044008',1,NULL,'The 1951 adaptation of Charles Dickens\' timeless classic is perhaps the most faithful film version -- and Alastair Sim\'s performance as Scrooge is not to be missed.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/92/45/10924541_mob.gif'),(1073,'The Crow - Salvation',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crow_salvation/','14199','0132910',1,NULL,'The Crow: Salvation adds nothing new to the series and is plagued by bad acting and dialogue.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/93/21/10932155_mob.jpg'),(1074,'Un Conte de Noel (A Christmas Tale)',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10009929-a_christmas_tale/','770768817','0993789',1,NULL,'A sharp black comedy about a chaotic family holiday gathering, A Christmas Tale is always involving, thanks to an impressive ensemble cast.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/88/11168852_mob.jpg'),(1075,'Cocoon',1985,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cocoon/','11112','0088933',1,NULL,'Though it may be too sentimental for some, Ron Howard\'s supernatural tale of eternal youth is gentle and heartwarming, touching on poignant issues of age in the process.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/91/259100_mob.jpg'),(1076,'Chapter 27',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1193377-chapter_27/','460291595','0488988',1,NULL,'Despite Jared Leto\'s committed performance, Chapter 27 fails to penetrate to mind of Mark David Chapman, John Lennon\'s killer.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/40/53/41/4053410_mob.jpg'),(1077,'Larry the Cable Guy: Health Inspector',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/larry_the_cable_guy_health_inspector/','147058736','0462395',1,NULL,'An aggressively lowbrow vehicle for its titular star, this gross-out comedy fails to \"git-r-done.\"','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/31/37/313794_mob.jpg'),(1078,'Camp Rock 2: The Final Jam',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/camp-rock-2/','771202156','1252380',1,'The kids at Camp Rock enter into a musical battle with the aspiring chart-toppers at nearby Camp Star in this lively sequel to Camp Rock starring Demi Lovato and The Jonas Brothers. Summertime is here, and for Mitchie (Lovato) that means another opportunity to make music with friends, and get reacquainted with talented young rocker Shane Gray (Joe Jonas), who\'s just returned from a world tour with his band Connect 3. But things get complicated when Axel Turner (Daniel Kash), a former band-mate of Camp Rock founder Brown Cesario (Daniel Fathers), opens up Camp Star in a bid to lure the most talented young artists to his side of the lake. And while the kids at Camp Star have access to all the most expensive and high-tech recording equipment, the kids at Camp Rock possess the drive to succeed no matter what challenges stand in their way. When the camp owners schedule a battle of the bands to determine which camp will stay in business, Mitchie begins preparing for the show that will launch her to stardom, and save Camp Rock in the process. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/13/73/11137382_mob.jpg'),(1079,'Cave of Forgotten Dreams',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cave_of_forgotten_dreams/','771208642','1664894',1,'Cave of Forgotten Dreams follows an exclusive expedition into the nearly inaccessible Chauvet Cave in France, home to the most ancient visual art known to have been created by man. It\'s an unforgettable cinematic experience that provides a unique glimpse of the pristine artwork dating back to human hands over 30,000 years ago - almost twice as old as any previous discovery. -- (c) IFC Films','Hauntingly filmed and brimming with Herzog\'s infectious enthusiasm, Cave of Forgotten Dreams is a fascinating triumph.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/03/11160362_mob.jpg'),(1080,'Courage Under Fire',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/courage_under_fire/','16796','0115956',1,NULL,'An emotional and intriguing tale of a military officer who must review the merits of a fallen officer while confronting his own war demons. Effectively depicts the terrors of war as well as its heartbreaking aftermath.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/47/11164782_mob.jpg'),(1081,'Crocodile Dundee in Los Angeles',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crocodile_dundee_in_los_angeles/','11532','0231402',1,NULL,'A family movie without toilet jokes, but there\'s nothing that haven\'t seen before.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/26/11/261123_mob.jpg'),(1082,'Cold Creek Manor',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cold_creek_manor/','14962','0331468',1,NULL,'The plot of Cold Creek Manor is too predictable and contrived to generate suspense.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/86/99/10869965_mob.jpg'),(1083,'Chasing Mavericks',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chasing_mavericks/','771257653','1629757',1,'Chasing Mavericks is the inspirational true story of real life surfing phenom Jay Moriarity (played by newcomer Jonny Weston). When 15 year old Jay discovers that the mythic Mavericks surf break, one of the biggest waves on Earth, is not only real, but exists just miles from his Santa Cruz home, he enlists the help of local legend Frosty Hesson (played by Gerard Butler) to train him to survive it. As Jay and Frosty embark on their quest to accomplish the impossible, they form a unique friendship that transforms both their lives, and their quest to tame Mavericks becomes about far more than surfing. Chasing Mavericks was made with the help of some of the biggest names in the surfing world, and features some of the most mind-blowing real wave footage ever captured on film. -- (C) Official Site','It\'s sweet, gentle, and affably modest, but Chasing Mavericks is ultimately pulled under by an unconvincing script and a puzzling lack of energy.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/82/11168294_mob.jpg'),(1084,'White Christmas',1954,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1023543-white_christmas/','18069','0047673',1,NULL,'It may be too sweet for some, but this unabashedly sentimental holiday favorite is too cheerful to resist.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/29/04/290499_mob.jpg'),(1085,'Club Dread',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/club-dread/','15772','0331953',1,NULL,'Comedy is too hit-or-miss is this slasher spoof.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/98/10899802_mob.jpg'),(1086,'L\'Enfant (The Child)',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/enfant/','126518660','0456396',1,NULL,'The Dardennes continue to excel at presenting works of rigorous naturalism, with detached observations of authentic characters that nevertheless resonate with complex moral issues.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/84/10898421_mob.jpg'),(1087,'The Lost City',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10002516-lost_city/','152552647','0343996',1,NULL,'Its heart is in the right place, but what starts as a promising exercise devolves into an overlong, unevenly directed disappointment.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/14/23/11142384_mob.jpg'),(1088,'Oliver & Company',1988,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/oliver_and_company/','9542','0095776',1,NULL,'Oliver & Company is a decidedly lesser effort in the Disney canon, with lackluster songs, stiff animation, and a thoroughly predictable plot.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/15/251504_mob.jpg'),(1089,'Don\'t Come Knocking',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dont_come_knocking/','112770461','0377800',1,NULL,'The cinematography conjures beautifully evocative landscapes, but aside from that, the film is meandering and pointless.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/89/84/10898416_mob.jpg'),(1090,'Summer Catch',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/summer_catch/','11127','0234829',1,NULL,'Cliched and predictable, Summer Catch is a reminder of better films.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/91/259191_mob.jpg'),(1091,'Che: Part Two (Guerrilla)',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/che_part_two/','770686043','0374569',1,NULL,'The second part of Soderbergh\'s biopic is a dark, hypnotic and sometimes frustrating portrait of a warrior in decline, with a terrific central performance from Del Toro.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/12/10881201_mob.jpg'),(1092,'The Cooler',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cooler/','13608','0318374',1,NULL,'A small movie elevated by superb performances.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/27/05/270598_mob.jpg'),(1093,'Drive Me Crazy',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/drive_me_crazy/','11140','0164114',1,NULL,'Unoriginal story.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/92/259215_mob.jpg'),(1094,'Cronos',1993,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cronos/','14970','0104029',1,NULL,'Guillermo del Toro\'s unique feature debut is not only gory and stylish, but also charming and intelligent.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/27/72/277211_mob.jpg'),(1095,'Confidence',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/confidence/','14362','0310910',1,NULL,'While it may not be the best con in town, the movie still manages to entertain with its colorful cast.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/09/80/10098040_mob.jpg'),(1096,'This Is Not a Film',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/this_is_not_a_film_2011/','771243297','1667905',1,'This clandestine documentary, shot partially on an iPhone and smuggled into France in a cake for a last-minute submission to Cannes, depicts the day-to-day life of acclaimed director Jafar Panahi (Offside, The Circle) during his house arrest in his Tehran apartment. While appealing his sentence - six years in prison and a 20 year ban from filmmaking - Panahi is seen talking to his family and lawyer on the phone, discussing his plight with Mirtahmasb and reflecting on the meaning of the art of filmmaking. -- (C) Palisades Tartan','Through simple means and filming, This is Not a Film presents a vital political statement and a snapshot of life in Iran as enemy of the state.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/37/11163759_mob.jpg'),(1097,'The White Countess',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/white_countess/','24467','0384686',1,NULL,'High production values and fine performances get bogged down by a lifeless story that fails to engage the viewer.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/51/17/511748_mob.jpg'),(1098,'The King of Comedy',1983,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1011623-king_of_comedy/','10861','0085794',1,NULL,'Largely misunderstood upon its release, The King of Comedy today looks eerily prescient, and features a fine performance by Robert DeNiro as a strangely sympathetic psychopath.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/78/257817_mob.jpg'),(1099,'Love Don\'t Cost a Thing',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/love_dont_cost_a_thing/','11693','0337592',1,NULL,'A stale, unnecessary remake of Can\'t Buy Me Love.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/55/28/29/5528294_mob.jpg'),(1100,'Casino Jack',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/casino-jack/','770814722','1194417',1,'Two-time Academy Award Winner Kevin Spacey gives the performance of a lifetime in CASINO JACK, a riotous new film starring Spacey as a man hell bent on acquiring all that the good life has to offer. He plays in the same game as the highest of rollers and resorts to awe-inspiring levels of conning, scheming and fraudulent antics to get what he wants. Inspired by true events that are too over-the-top for even the wildest imaginations to conjure, CASINO JACK lays bare the wild excesses and escapades of Jack Abramoff. Aided by his business partner Michael Scanlon (Barry Pepper), Jack parlays his clout over some of the world\'s most powerful men with the goal of creating a personal empire of wealth and influence. When the two enlist a mob-connected buddy (Jon Lovitz) to help with one of their illegal schemes, they soon find themselves in over their heads, entrenched in a world of mafia assassins, murder and a scandal that spins so out of control that it makes worldwide headlines. Directed by George Hickenlooper (FACTORY GIRL, THE MAN FROM ELYSIAN FIELDS), CASINO JACK returns Spacey to the type of role that made him famous - a cool-headed, articulate snake charmer whose wild ambitions knows no limits or boundaries. The film also stars Kelly Preston and Rachelle Lefevre and is produced by Gary Howsam, Bill Marks and George Vitetzakis from an original screenplay by Norman Snider. Executive Producers are Richard Rionda Del Castro, Lewin Webb, Donald Zuckerman, Dana Brunetti, Patricia Eberle, Warren Nimchuk, Angelo Paletta and Domenic Serafino. The Associate Producer is Rick Chad. -- (C) Art Takes Over','Kevin Spacey turns in one of his stronger performances, but Casino Jack is a disappointingly uneven fictionalized account of a fascinating true story.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/41/11154140_mob.jpg'),(1101,'The Counterfeiters',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_counterfeiters_2007/','770676882','0813547',1,NULL,'The Counterfeiters is a gripping account of one prisoner\'s moral dilemma, superbly portrayed by Karl Markovics.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/83/79/10837983_mob.jpg'),(1102,'For Your Consideration',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1159169-for_your_consideration/','384067821','0470765',1,NULL,'As the object of satire gets bigger the jokes become thinner, and Christopher Guest isn\'t as droll or insightful here than when he was lampooning smaller subjects.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/02/11150245_mob.jpg'),(1103,'Confetti',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/confetti/','287865282','0427089',1,NULL,'This improvised mockumentary has its funny and even sweet moments, but it\'s not as witty or sharp as Christopher Guest\'s offerings.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/04/21/2504210_mob.jpg'),(1104,'Ten Canoes',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ten_canoes/','287379464','0466399',1,NULL,'Ten Canoes combines adventure, comedy, and anthropology to explore an Aborigine folk tale both fallibly human and legendary. Helmer Rolf de Heer depicts a barely represented oral tradition with a clean style.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/94/57/10945754_mob.jpg'),(1105,'A Cat in Paris',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_cat_in_paris/','771217935','1673702',1,'Dino is a pet cat that leads a double life. By day he lives with Zoe, a little mute girl whose mother, Jeanne, is a detective in the Parisian police force. But at night he sneaks out the window to work with Nico - a slinky cat burglar with a big heart, whose fluid movements are poetry in motion - as he evades captors and slips and swishes from rooftop to rooftop across the Paris skyline. The cat\'s two worlds collide when young Zoe decides to follow Dino on his nocturnal adventures - and falls into the hands of Victor Costa, a blustery gangster planning the theft of a rare statue.Now cat and cat burglar must team up to save Zoe from the bumbling thieves, leading to a thrilling acrobatic finale on top of Notre Dame. -- (C) GKIDS','A Cat in Paris depicts a stylish, imaginative world with a wonderful soundtrack and Hitchcockian overtones.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/59/11165903_mob.jpg'),(1106,'The Great Muppet Caper',1981,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/great_muppet_caper/','9768','0082474',1,NULL,'The Great Muppet Caper is overplotted and uneven, but the appealing presence of Kermit, Miss Piggy and the gang ensure that this heist flick is always breezily watchable.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/15/10881575_mob.jpg'),(1107,'Ghosts of Cite Soleil',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ghosts_of_cite_soleil/','385329392','0479046',1,NULL,'Asger Leth risked his life to bring audiences this rare and gritty glimpse at Haitian gangs, poverty and politics.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/87/18/91/8718914_mob.jpg'),(1108,'Nitro Circus: The Movie 3D',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nitro_circus_the_movie_3d_2012/','771310839','1815852',1,'The show follows Travis and the Nitro Circus Crew as they travel around the world setting up outrageous stunts and pushing the human body to the limit, constantlylooking to innovate the world of action sports. Travis\' compound in Annapolis houses a full motocross course, foampits and a homemade waterslide carved into a hill creating a self contained extreme sports circus. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/58/11165845_mob.jpg'),(1109,'Dead Man on Campus',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dead_man_on_campus/','13424','0118301',1,NULL,'Not much of a story.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/87/18/10871827_mob.jpg'),(1110,'Rare Exports: A Christmas Tale',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/rare_exports/','771200719','1401143',1,'It\'s the eve of Christmas in northern Finland, and an \'archeological\' dig has just unearthed the real Santa Claus. But this particular Santa isn\'t the one you want coming to town. When the local children begin mysteriously disappearing, young Pietari and his father Rauno, a reindeer hunter by trade, capture the mythological being and attempt to sell Santa to the misguided leader of the multinational corporation sponsoring the dig. Santa\'s elves, however, will stop at nothing to free their fearless leader from captivity. What ensues is a wildly humorous nightmare - a fantastically bizarre polemic on modern day morality. RARE EXPORTS: A CHRISTMAS TALE is a re-imagining of the most classic of all childhood fantasies, and is a darkly comic gem soon to be required perennial holiday viewing. -- (C) Oscilloscope','Rare Exports is an unexpectedly delightful crossbreed of deadpan comedy and Christmas horror.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/12/11161217_mob.jpg'),(1111,'The Corporation',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/corporation/','16973','0379225',1,NULL,'The Corporation is a satisfyingly dense, thought-provoking rebuttal to some of capitalism\'s central arguments.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/93/78/10937865_mob.jpg'),(1112,'Get Carter',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1100569-get_carter/','15255','0208988',1,NULL,'A remake that doesn\'t approach the standard of the original, Get Carter will likely leave viewers confused and unsatisfied. Also, reviews are mixed concerning Stallone\'s acting.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/27/85/278597_mob.jpg'),(1113,'Cidade dos Homens (City of Men)',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cidade_dos_homens/','770677320','0870090',1,NULL,'Brutal and unflinching, City of Men is both a harrowing look at Brazil\'s favela life, and a touching tale of youths rushed into adulthood.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/83/85/10838542_mob.jpg'),(1114,'Certified Copy (Copie Conforme)',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/certified_copy/','771042185','1020773',1,'Juliette Binoche won the Best Actress prize in Cannes for her performance in this playful and provocative romantic drama from legendary auteur Abbas Kiarostami (TASTE OF CHERRY, THE WIND WILL CARRY US), his first feature made outside of Iran. Binoche plays a gallery owner living in a Tuscan village who attends a lecture by a British author (opera star William Shimell) on authenticity and fakery in art. Afterward, she invites him on a tour of the countryside, during which he is mistaken for her husband. They keep up the pretense and continue on their afternoon out, discussing love, life and art, and increasingly behaving like a long-married couple. But are they play-acting on a whim, or is there more to their seemingly new relationship than meets the eye? -- (C) IFC','The main stars are absolutely perfect in this absorbing, existential drama that dissects human relationships.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/61/11156107_mob.jpg'),(1115,'The Emperor\'s Club',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/emperors_club/','11168','0283530',1,NULL,'Though Kline is excellent in his portrayal of Hundert, the movie is too dull and sentimental to distinguish itself from other titles in its genre.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/93/259391_mob.jpg'),(1116,'Compliance',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/compliance_2012/','771267239','1971352',1,'Becky and Sandra aren\'t the best of friends. Sandra is a middle-aged manager at a fast-food restaurant; Becky is a teenaged counter girl who really needs the job. One stressful day (too many customers and too little bacon), a police officer calls, accusing Becky of stealing money from a customer\'s purse, which she vehemently denies. Sandra, overwhelmed by her managerial responsibilities, complies with the officer\'s orders to detain Becky. This choice begins a nightmare that tragically blurs the lines between expedience and prudence, legality and reason. -- (C) Magnolia','Anchored by smart, sensitive direction and strong performances, Complicance is a ripped-from-the-headlines thriller that\'s equal parts gripping and disturbing.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/57/11165767_mob.jpg'),(1117,'Clockstoppers',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/clockstoppers/','11933','0157472',1,NULL,'A pleasant diversion for the young teens, but a waste of time for anyone older.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/84/11/10841188_mob.jpg'),(1118,'Criminal',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10003276-criminal/','14750','0362526',1,NULL,'If you saw Nine Queens, it may feel redundant, but the snappy performances make it fun to watch.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/90/40/10904033_mob.jpg'),(1119,'44 Inch Chest',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/44_inch_chest/','770807379','0914837',1,NULL,'An actor\'s movie with a strong cast, 44 Inch Chest can\'t quite redeem its static plotting and tonal shifts.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/26/10882663_mob.jpg'),(1120,'The Strange Case Of Angelica',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_strange_case_of_angelica_2010/','771205009','1282153',1,'The new film from master filmmaker Manoel de Oliveira, The Strange Case of Angelica is a magical tale about a young photographer who falls madly in love with a woman he can never have, except in his dreams. Late one night, Isaac is summoned by a wealthy family to take the last photograph of a young bride, Angelica, who mysteriously passed away. Arriving at their estate, Isaac is struck by Angelica\'s beauty, but when he looks through his lens, something strange happens - the young woman appears to come to life. From that moment, Isaac will be haunted by Angelica day and night. -- (C) Cinema Guild',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/47/11154714_mob.jpg'),(1121,'The Cake Eaters',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the-cake-eaters/','770685471','0418586',1,NULL,'Though light on theme and craftsmanship, The Cake Eaters relies on fine performances and brisk direction to provide an affecting tale of small-town life.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/86/80/10868046_mob.jpg'),(1122,'Darling Companion',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/darling_companion/','771209745','1730687',1,'Beth (Diane Keaton) saves a bedraggled lost dog from the side of the freeway on a wintry day in Denver. Struggling with her distracted, self-involved husband Joseph (Kevin Kline) and an empty nest at home, Beth forms a special bond with the rescued animal. When Joseph loses the dog after their daughter\'s (Elisabeth Moss) wedding at their vacation home in the Rockies, Beth, distraught and angry with Joseph, enlists the help of the few remaining guests (Dianne Wiest, Richard Jenkins, Mark Duplass) and a mysterious woman (Ayelet Zurer) in a frantic search. -- (C) Sony Classics',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/40/11164034_mob.jpg'),(1123,'Mother and Child',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mother_and_child/','770799466','1121977',1,'Writer/director Rodrigo Garca (Nine Lives) teams with executive producer Alejandro Gonzlez Irritu to craft this drama highlighting the powerful bond between a mother and her son. It\'s been years since Karen (Annette Bening) gave her daughter, Elizabeth, up for adoption, and the decision to abandon her child has always haunted her. Upon meeting laid-back Paco (Jimmy Smits), Karen permits her anxiety and mistrust to get the best of her. On the surface it appears that Elizabeth (Naomi Watts) is none the worse for never knowing her biological mother; she\'s a fast-talking lawyer who\'s just landed a high-profile job at a firm fronted by Paul (Samuel L. Jackson), though her unsavory penchant for exploiting others is about to blow up in her face. Meanwhile, maternal-minded baker Lucy (Kerry Washington) longs to experience the joys of motherhood, eventually deciding that adoption is the best bet to start a family with her husband, Joseph (David Ramsey). ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Though it occasionally veers into unnecessary melodrama, Mother and Child benefits from a stellar cast and writer-director Rodrigo Garcia\'s finely detailed, bravely unsentimental script.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/13/32/11133215_mob.jpg'),(1124,'Chopper',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chopper/','14000','0221073',1,NULL,'Eric Bana\'s performance as the charming but twisted Chopper is the highlight of this disturbing portrait about Australia\'s notorious author/criminal.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/27/25/272516_mob.jpg'),(1125,'Surviving Christmas',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/surviving_christmas/','10805','0252028',1,NULL,'Surviving Christmas is unpleasant characters attacking each other for 90 minutes before delivering a typical, hollow anti-consumerist message','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/56/19/48/5619486_mob.jpg'),(1126,'Chasing Ice',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chasing_ice_2012/','771267237','1579361',1,'Acclaimed National Geographic photographer James Balog was once a skeptic about climate change. But through his Extreme Ice Survey, he discovers undeniable evidence of our changing planet. In Chasing Ice, Balog deploys revolutionary time-lapse cameras to capture a multi-year record of the world\'s changing glaciers. His hauntingly beautiful videos compress years into seconds and capture ancient mountains of ice in motion as they disappear at a breathtaking rate. Traveling with a team of young adventurers across the brutal Arctic, Balog risks his career and his well-being in pursuit of the biggest story facing humanity. As the debate polarizes America, and the intensity of natural disasters ramps up globally, Chasing Ice depicts a heroic photojournalist on a mission to deliver fragile hope to our carbon-powered planet. -- (C) Submarine',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/71/11167188_mob.jpg'),(1127,'The Cook, the Thief, His Wife & Her Lover',1989,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cook_the_thief_his_wife_and_her_lover/','14895','0097108',1,NULL,'This romantic crime drama may not be to everyone\'s taste, but The Cook, the Thief, His Wife & Her Lover is an audacious, powerful film.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/27/68/276824_mob.jpg'),(1128,'The Human Centipede II (Full Sequence)',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_human_centipede_ii/','771205845','1530509',1,'Tom Six\'s internationally controversial follow-up to the original cult smash, The Human Centipede: Full Sequence ups the ante with a brute force unparalleled in motion pictures today. -- (C) IFC Films','The Human Centipede II (Full Sequence) attempts to weave in social commentary but as the movie wears on, it loses its ability to repulse and shock and ends up obnoxious and annoying.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/06/11160659_mob.jpg'),(1129,'Chocolate',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10010208-chocolate/','770686154','1183252',1,NULL,'Chocolate is a bizarre martial arts flick, with a slushy plot, an unusual protagonist, and breathtaking stunts.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/91/11169118_mob.jpg'),(1130,'A Civil Action',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/civil_action/','10500','0120633',1,NULL,'Intelligent and unconventional.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/60/256024_mob.jpg'),(1131,'Conversations With Other Women',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/conversations_with_other_women/','248007841','0435623',1,NULL,'The chemistry between stars Helena Bonham Carter and Aaron Eckhart carries this intimate tale of middle-aged romance.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/89/81/10898112_mob.jpg'),(1132,'King of California',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/king_of_california/','528360394','0388182',1,NULL,'A quirky and often touching comedy about a mature teenager and her manic depressive father, King of California is a charming tale of familial relations and treasure hunting.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/98/90/89/9890896_mob.jpg'),(1133,'Meek\'s Cutoff',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/meeks_cutoff/','771203826','1518812',1,'The year is 1845, the earliest days of the Oregon Trail, and a wagon train of three families has hired mountain man Stephen Meek to guide them over the Cascade Mountains. Claiming to know a shortcut, Meek leads the group on an unmarked path across the high plain desert, only to become lost in the dry rock and sage. Over the coming days, the emigrants face the scourges of hunger, thirst and their own lack of faith in one another\'s instincts for survival. When a Native American wanderer crosses their path, the emigrants are torn between their trust in a guide who has proven himself unreliable and a man who has always been seen as a natural born enemy. -- (C) Oscilloscope','Moving at a contemplative speed unseen in most westerns, Meek\'s Cutoff is an effective, intense journey of terror and survival in the untamed frontier.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/57/11155788_mob.jpg'),(1134,'Catch That Kid',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/catch_that_kid/','11722','0337917',1,NULL,'An unimaginative heist movie aimed strictly at the preteen set.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/47/11164714_mob.jpg'),(1135,'Corky Romano',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/corky_romano/','11512','0250310',1,NULL,'Corky Romano continues the trend of bad movies featuring SNL members. The jokes are tired and unfunny, and the slapstick feels forced.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/26/10/261023_mob.jpg'),(1136,'Code Unknown (Code inconnu: Recit incomplet de divers voyages)',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/code_unknown/','20825','0216625',1,NULL,'Though challengingly cryptic at times, Code Unknown still manages to resonate.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/30/36/303693_mob.jpg'),(1137,'The Rabbi\'s Cat',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_rabbis_cat/','771235475','1355638',1,'Based on the best-selling graphic novel by Joann Sfar, The Rabbi\'s Cat tells the story of a rabbi and his talking cat - a sharp-tongued feline philosopher brimming with scathing humor and a less than pure love for the rabbi\'s voluptuous teenage daughter. Algeria in the 1930s is an intersection of Jewish, Arab and French culture. A cat belonging to a widowed rabbi and his beautiful daughter, Zlabya, eats the family parrot and miraculously gains the ability to speak. Along with the power of speech comes unparalleled sardonic wit, and the cat - and filmmaker Sfar - spare no group or individual as they skewer faith, tradition and authority in a provocative exploration of (among other things) God, lust, death, phrenology, religious intolerance, interspecies love, and the search for truth. Rich with the colors, textures, flavors and music of Mediterranean Africa, the film embarks on a cross continent adventure from the tiled terraces, fountains, quays and cafes of colonial Algiers to Maghrebi tent camps, dusty trading outposts, and deep blue Saharan nights in search of a lost Ethiopian city. (c) GKids',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/77/11157737_mob.jpg'),(1138,'Daltry Calhoun',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/secret_life_of_daltry_calhoun/','7978','0339642',1,NULL,'Watching grass grow would likely be more entertaining than this dull, slight feature about a sod salesman.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/89/83/10898327_mob.jpg'),(1139,'Rudo y Cursi',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/rudo_y_cursi/','770800777','0405393',1,NULL,'Despite its fair share of sports movie cliches, Rudo y Cursi marks an auspicious directing debut for Carlos Cuaron, and features strong performances from Garcia Bernal and Luna.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/86/78/10867842_mob.jpg'),(1140,'You Can Count On Me',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/you_can_count_on_me/','13769','0203230',1,NULL,'You Can Count On Me may look like it belongs on the small screen, but the movie surprises with its simple yet affecting story. Beautifully acted and crafted, the movie will simply draw you in.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/27/13/271397_mob.jpg'),(1141,'Out Cold',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/out_cold/','12847','0253798',1,NULL,'A party movie that substitutes surfs for snow, Out Cold will leave viewers just that with its gross-out humor and sophomoric plot.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/18/78/38/1878389_mob.jpg'),(1142,'Last Ounce of Courage',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/last_ounce_of_courage/','771310119','2359137',1,'Last Ounce of Courage is the story of a grieving father inspired by his grandson to take a stand for faith and freedom against a tide of apathy and vanishing liberty. Alongside fellow citizens of courage, faith, and integrity, he is a champion for the cherished principles we the people hold dear. A tale of family bonds and free expression, the film seeks to encourage all Americans to take a stand and raise their voices in support of their beliefs. Last Ounce of Courage and Veritas are proud to partner with StandUSA, an online community for American values, in standing up for the ideals of faith, family, and freedom in a pivotal time for our country. StandUSA, along with its partners and affiliates, encourages all Americans to take the inspirational message of the film to heart and let it spur them to raise their voices in support of freedom. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/65/11166578_mob.jpg'),(1143,'Changing Times (Les Temps Qui Changent)',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10006130-changing_times/','326299390','0399738',1,NULL,'A restless mix of cultural and emotional turmoil provides the backdrop for this exhilarating and uncomfortable story about the consistancy of long lost love.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/29/08/85/2908858_mob.jpg'),(1144,'Primary Colors',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/primary_colors/','12462','0119942',1,NULL,'Well acted and suprisingly funny.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/87/54/10875476_mob.jpg'),(1145,'Syndromes and a Century (Sang sattawat)',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/syndromes_and_a_century/','351527694','0477731',1,NULL,'Despite having little in the way of narrative, Apichatpong Weerasethakul\'s Syndromes is a poignant and mesmerizing memoir.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/89/77/10897767_mob.jpg'),(1146,'My Country, My Country',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/my_country_my_country/','248007668','0810983',1,NULL,'This war documentary offers a valuable look at Iraqi life under the U.S. occupation, and finds a compelling central subject