becomes obsessed with her new favorite girl. Consumed with jealousy, Di encourages the group to bully their team mate and they chase her out of the school. When Fiamma is made to return the girls are forced to try and get along with Fiamma and as they open up to her they too begin to warm to the charms that so captivated Miss G. In an attempt to put their differences aside - the diving team and Fiamma plan a secret midnight party to celebrate the feast of St. Agnes; a ritualistic celebration that is both innocent and erotic. A night that begins with high spirits soon takes a turn that will change the girls\' lives forever as Miss G interrupts the evening and takes a drunken Fiamma away to her room... -- (C) IFC','Atomospheric but not much else, Cracks is a formless film in search of compelling drama.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/56/11155689_mob.jpg'),(1151,'What\'s the Worst That Could Happen?',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/whats_the_worst_that_could_happen/','12802','0161083',1,NULL,'Talented cast is squandered by an uninvolving script filled with unfunny gags.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/83/80/10838013_mob.jpg'),(1152,'Chandni Chowk To China',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chandni_chowk_to_china/','770800803','1091229',1,NULL,'A thin plot is disguised by high octane dancing and action in this Bollywood crossover comedy.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/87/76/10877678_mob.jpg'),(1153,'Clean',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1156587-clean/','155654817','0388838',1,NULL,'In one of her best roles, Cheung gives a believable and arresting performance as a recovering addict.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/89/10888941_mob.jpg'),(1154,'So Close',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/so_close/','14143','0300620',1,NULL,'This HK actioner oozes with style.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/27/32/273210_mob.jpg'),(1155,'Castlevania',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/castlevania/','770785501','0488982',1,'This movie focuses on the origin of the eternal struggle between the Belmont clan and Lord Dracula.',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/85/47/10854785_mob.jpg'),(1156,'Heaven Can Wait',1978,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1009427-heaven_can_wait/','11133','0077663',1,NULL,'A throwback to the high-gloss screwball comedies of the 1940s, Heaven Can Wait beguiles with seamless production values and great comic relief from Charles Grodin and Dianne Cannon.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/86/72/10867228_mob.jpg'),(1157,'Looking for Comedy in the Muslim World',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/looking_for_comedy_in_the_muslim_world/','2864432','0433116',1,NULL,'Although the premise seems ripe for laughs, Albert Brooks isn\'t ruthless or clever enough to pull it off.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/91/36/10913654_mob.jpg'),(1158,'CJ7',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cj7/','770682295','0940709',1,NULL,'Eccentric and sweet, Stephen Chow\'s latest is charming, but too strangely and slackly plotted to work as a whole.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/86/83/10868373_mob.jpg'),(1159,'The Mosquito Coast',1986,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mosquito_coast/','11308','0091557',1,NULL,'Harrison Ford capably tackles a tough, unlikable role, producing a fascinating and strange character study.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/95/11159526_mob.jpg'),(1160,'Il conformista (The Conformist)',1970,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/conformist/','136193252','0065571',1,NULL,'A commentary on fascism and beauty alike, Bernadro Bertolucci\'s The Conformist is acclaimed for its sumptuous visuals and extravagant, artful cinematography.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/31/35/313515_mob.jpg'),(1161,'XXX: The Return of Xander Cage',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/xxx-the-return-of-xander-cage/','770805755','1293847',1,'Vin Diesel re-teams with Rob Cohen on the third installment of their extreme spy film franchise. Screenwriting duties will be handled by Terminator Salvation writers Michael Ferris and John Brancato, with Cohen once again directing. Samuel L. Jackson returns to play Diesel\'s boss, Agent Augustus Gibbons. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1162,'The Class',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_class/','770770023','1068646',1,NULL,'Energetic and bright, this hybrid of documentary style and dramatic plotting looks at the present and future of France through the interactions of a teacher and his students in an inner city high school.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/26/10882622_mob.jpg'),(1163,'Crooked Arrows',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crooked_arrows/','771304937','1954352',1,'A mixed-blood Native American, Joe Logan, eager to modernize his reservation, must first prove himself to his father, the traditionalist Tribal Chairman, by rediscovering his spirit. He is tasked with coaching the reservation\'s high school lacrosse team which competes against the better equipped and better trained players of the elite Prep School League. Joe inspires the Native American boys and teaches them the true meaning of tribal pride. Ignited by their heritage and believing in their new-found potential, coach and team climb an uphill battle to the state championship finals against their privileged prep school rivals...will they win? -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/45/11164597_mob.jpg'),(1164,'Henry\'s Crime',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/henrys_crime_2010/','771195234','1220888',1,'Working the night shift as a toll collector on a lonely stretch of highway in Buffalo, New York, Henry (KEANU REEVES) is a man seemingly without ambition, dreams or purpose; a man sleepwalking his way through life. He gets his wakeup call early one morning when he becomes an unwitting participant in an ill-conceived bank heist. Rather than give up the names of the real culprits, Henry takes the fall and goes to jail. There, he meets the irrepressible Max (JAMES CAAN), a con man who\'s grown far too comfortable with the familiarity and security of his \'idyllic\' life behind bars, but one who also helps plant an idea in Henry\'s mind which will change his life forever: for a man to find his purpose, he must first have a dream. Upon his release one year later, Henry finds his purpose. Having done the time, he decides he may as well do the crime. Discovering a long forgotten bootlegger\'s tunnel which runs from the very same bank to a theater across the alleyway, he convinces the reluctant Max to file for his long overdue parole -- and then recruits his former cellmate to help stage a robbery. Their plan is simple: by infiltrating the theater and its current production of Chekhov\'s, The Cherry Orchard, the unlikely duo will buy just enough time to dig their way to the adjacent bank vault and drive off with their loot. Unfortunately that plan also includes Henry taking the lead role in the play, where he finds himself slowly falling for the production\'s mercurial leading lady, Julie (VERA FARMIGA). By turns wry, off-beat, and simply hilarious, HENRY\'S CRIME is the heartwarming story of a man who finds his purpose in life. And then finds his destiny. -- (C) Moving Pictures','Supporting actors Vera Farmiga and James Caan give the movie a little heft, but Henry\'s Crime is an otherwise predictable heist/comedy with slow pacing.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/62/11156235_mob.jpg'),(1165,'The Original Kings of Comedy',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/original_kings_of_comedy/','13160','0236388',1,NULL,'If you want lots of laughs and don\'t mind some profanity, The Original Kings of Comedy can deliver.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/14/72/11147213_mob.jpg'),(1166,'Connie And Carla',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/connie_and_carla/','11082','0345074',1,NULL,'The two female leads, as well as energitic musical numbers, enliven an otherwise silly reworking of Billy Wilder\'s Some Like It Hot.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/89/258917_mob.jpg'),(1167,'El Cantante',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/el_cantante/','371354217','0458522',1,NULL,'El Cantante adheres to the most basic conventions of the musical biopic, rendering it indistinguishable from others of its ilk.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/87/41/10874186_mob.jpg'),(1168,'Two Can Play That Game',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/two_can_play_that_game/','13627','0269341',1,NULL,'As a romantic comedy, Two Can Play That Game is more mean-spirited than romantic. Also, some critics say the movie is misogynistic in its attitudes and has too many blatant product placements.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/87/89/10878916_mob.jpg'),(1169,'Legend of the Fist: The Return of Chen Zhen',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/legend_of_the_fist_the_return_of_chen_zhen/','771207926','1456661',1,'Legendary Kung Fu hero Chen Zhen is an iconic cultural mainstay in China and Hong Kong, having spawned both record-breaking feature films and a TV series. Over the years, martial arts legends such as Bruce Lee (FIST OF FURY) and Jet Li (FIST OF LEGEND) have played the popular hero. In LEGEND OF THE FIST: THE RETURN OF CHEN ZHEN, Donnie Yen continues this rich historical legacy, but with a brand new take on the urban legend. In 1920s China, the nation is divided by infighting. Japan has become the most powerful force in Asia, taking over Northern Shanghai. With the city torn in half by international conflict, the popular nightclub \"Casablanca\" has become a hotbed of spies, mobsters, English officials and the Japanese military- all looking to gain control of the country, with little regard for what happens to its citizens. Into this den of intrigue enters Chen Zhen (Donnie Yen), who has returned to China after fighting alongside the Allied forces in Europe, bringing some dark secrets from his past along with him. During the day, he\'s known as \"Ku\", and appears to be just another wealthy playboy. But at night, he takes to the street as a masked warrior, determined to subvert the Japanese invasion while becoming entangled with the sultry Kiki (Played by Shu Qi), who has a dangerous secret of her own. When his past catches up to him, Zhen is faced with near impossible odds- but his skills are formidable, and he\'s up to the challenge. Combining the best of today\'s martial arts and superhero action with the classic spy thrillers of the past (and a healthy dollop of film noir on top), LEGEND OF THE FIST is the rare action film that truly gives the audience something they\'ve never seen before. --(c) Variance',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/62/11156246_mob.jpg'),(1170,'Chaos Theory',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chaos_theory/','770679810','0460745',1,NULL,'Ryan Reynolds and Emily Mortimer do what they can, but ultimately Chaos Theory is an overly conventional dramedy.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/46/11164647_mob.jpg'),(1171,'The Contender',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1100998-contender/','16856','0208874',1,NULL,'Critics say this political thriller is solidly made, with top-notch performances, screenplay, and direction for about two third of the film. Unfortunately, the ending almost tank the whole movie.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/28/54/285405_mob.jpg'),(1172,'In the Cut',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/in_the_cut/','17077','0199626',1,NULL,'Ryan is very good playing against type, but Campion\'s good-looking thriller is far from thrilling.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/63/26/12/6326125_mob.jpg'),(1173,'The Concert (Le concert)',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/le-concert/','770852280','1320082',1,'Twenty-five years after losing his position as the conductor of the Bolshoi Orchestra for his refusal to fire the Jewish musicians, a once-famous musical director attempts to stage a late-career comeback. Andrei Semoinovitch Filipov (Aleksei Guskov) was at the top of his game when the Soviet regime ended his career. More than two decades later, he\'s working as a janitor in the same theater where he once conducted. In his spare time, Andrei and his wife stage mock communist demonstrations to entertain the locals. When Andrei happens across an invitation to Paris\' famed Theatre du Chatelet, he contacts his old orchestra friends in hopes of staging a performance that will bring the crowd to their feet for a standing ovation. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/14/82/11148250_mob.jpg'),(1174,'Small Time Crooks',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/small_time_crooks/','11792','0196216',1,NULL,'Woody Allen rises from his recent slump with Small Time Crooks. A simple, funny movie, Crooks proves Allen still has the touch that made his name synonymous with off-beat comedy.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/26/24/262409_mob.jpg'),(1175,'Come Early Morning',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/come_early_morning/','390467926','0457308',1,NULL,'A quiet but moving film anchored by the unexpected depth of Ashley Judd\'s performance.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/33/28/64/3328642_mob.jpg'),(1176,'Cavite',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1162654-cavite/','166583385','0428303',1,NULL,'A gritty, low-budget thriller, Cavite takes us on a heart-pounding ride through the seedy Filipino underworld.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/47/18/471820_mob.jpg'),(1177,'Croupier',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/croupier/','17214','0159382',1,NULL,'The writer slumming for human truths and real experience is a common enough story, but this cool-headed and slick thriller provides a gut-churningly compelling backdrop to a look at our darker sides.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/28/68/286811_mob.jpg'),(1178,'Color Me Kubrick',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/colour-me-kubrick/','265868862','0376543',1,NULL,'Colour Me Kubrick has a fascinating premise, but provides little insight into Kubrick and the man who impersonated him.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/86/96/10869625_mob.jpg'),(1179,'The 9th Company (9 rota)',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the-9th-company/','569877577','0417397',1,'Fedor Bondarchuk, the son of noted Russian filmmaker Sergei Bondarchuk, debuts as a director with the harrowing and relentless military drama 9th Company, set between 1988 and 1989 at the tail end of the U.S.S.R. Afghani war (the Soviet equivalent of Vietnam). The picture opens in Krasnoyarsk, Siberia, in late 1988, when military trainees Petrovsky, Ryaba, Chugun, Stas, Pinochet, Lyutev and Vorobyev are whipped into shape at a training camp by the brutal, sadistic commander, Warrant Officer Dygalo - prior to being sent off to the front lines. After several one-by-one dalliances with the local whore, Snow White, and a cautionary lecture on the history, geography and culture of Afghanistan (which most of the men sleep through), the trainees head off to battle - first to the Bagram air base, then to the Afghani province of Khost to secure supply lines. But nothing can begin to prepare them for the brutal devastation into which they are plunged, or the relentless tide of slaughter that scatters thousands of Soviet victims in its wake. ~ Nathan Southern, Rovi',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/53/33/14/5333141_mob.jpg'),(1180,'Cat People',1942,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1003757-cat_people/','185962182','0034587',1,NULL,'Influential noir director Jacques Tourneau infused this sexy, moody horror film with some sly commentary about the psychology and the taboos of desire.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/20/86/15/2086154_mob.jpg'),(1181,'The Curse of the Jade Scorpion',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/curse_of_the_jade_scorpion/','11829','0256524',1,NULL,'The writing for Scorpion is not as sharp as Woody Allen\'s previous movies as most of the jokes fall flat.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/26/262600_mob.jpg'),(1182,'The Central Park Five',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_central_park_five_2012/','771307293','2380247',1,'In 1989, five black and Latino teenagers were arrested and charged for brutally attacking and raping a white female jogger in Central Park. News media swarmed the case, calling it \"the crime of the century.\" But the truth about what really happened didn\'t become clear until after the five had spent years in prison for a crime they didn\'t commit. With THE CENTRAL PARK FIVE, this story of injustice finally gets the telling it deserves. Based on Sarah Burns\' best-selling book and co-directed by her husband David McMahon and father, the beloved doc filmmaker Ken Burns, this incendiary film tells the riveting tale of innocent young men scapegoated for a heinous crime, and serves as a mirror for our times. (c) IFC Films',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/74/11167457_mob.jpg'),(1183,'The Truth About Charlie',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/truth_about_charlie/','98836435','0270707',1,NULL,'Newton has star quality, but this exercise in style can\'t hold a candle to the original.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/84/10888428_mob.jpg'),(1184,'Carandiru',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/carandiru/','13862','0293007',1,NULL,'A gritty, poignant, and shocking prison movie.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/27/18/271817_mob.jpg'),(1185,'Camp',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/camp/','10614','0342167',1,NULL,'Campy comedy that squeaks by on its charms.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/28/10882881_mob.jpg'),(1186,'Goodbye, Children (Au Revoir Les Enfants)',1987,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/au_revoir_les_enfants/','60560683','0092593',1,NULL,'Louis Malle\'s autobiographical tale of a childhood spent in a WWII boarding school is a beautifully realized portrait of friendship and youth.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/27/11152770_mob.jpg'),(1187,'Hitler\'s Children',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hitlers_children_2012/','771306408','2359085',1,'This documentary is about the descendants of the most powerful figures in the Nazi regime: men and women who were left a legacy that permanently associates them with one of the greatest crimes in history. What is it like for them to have grown up with a name that immediately raises images of murder and genocide? How do they cope with the fact that they are the children of ... literally, not just metaphorically.',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/71/11167119_mob.jpg'),(1188,'A Midnight Clear',1992,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1039575-1039575-midnight_clear/','13520','0102443',1,NULL,'Beautifully filmed and wonderfully acted, A Midnight Clear is a holiday war film in search of a wider audience.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/27/01/270191_mob.jpg'),(1189,'Comic-Con: Episode IV - A Fan\'s Hope',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/comic_con_episode_iv_a_fans_hope/','771251569','1605782',1,'Comic-Con Episode IV: A Fan\'s Hope--a film by Morgan Spurlock explores this amazing cultural phenomenon by following the lives of five attendees as they descend upon the ultimate geek mecca at San Diego Comic-Con 2010. One on one interviews with Comic-Con veterans who have turned their passions into professions include Stan Lee, Joss Whedon, Frank Miller, Kevin Smith, Matt Groening, Seth Rogen, Eli Roth and others are shared throughout the film along with up close and up front coverage of all the panels, parades, photos, costumes, crowds and camaraderie that make up one of the largest fan gatherings in the U.S. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/38/11163865_mob.jpg'),(1190,'Caramel',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/caramel/','770676269','0825236',1,NULL,'Caramel is both an astute cultural study, and a charming comedic drama from a talented newcomer.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/04/22/10042278_mob.jpg'),(1191,'Chugyeogja (The Chaser)',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chaser/','770686074','1190539',1,NULL,'A frantic and taut Korean serial killer thriller. One classy, if bloody and messy, gut wrencher of a movie.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/85/52/10855238_mob.jpg'),(1192,'Celebrity',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1084868-celebrity/','14798','0120533',1,NULL,'Entertaining, but too scattered.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/27/63/276393_mob.jpg'),(1193,'Flammen & Citronen (Flame & Citron) (The Flame and the Lemon)',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/flammen_and_citronen/','770728092','0920458',1,NULL,'The true story of the Danish resistance in WW2, though lengthy and sprawling, is gripping and competently made.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/87/26/10872620_mob.jpg'),(1194,'Real Women Have Curves',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/real_women_have_curves/','11387','0296166',1,NULL,'Even though Real Women is another coming-of-age tale, it\'s a real charmer.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/86/58/10865811_mob.jpg'),(1195,'On a Clear Day',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1156415-on_a_clear_day/','140952642','0410400',1,NULL,'Another blue-collar inspirational feel-good British dramedy, On A Clear Day succeeds on the strength of lead actor Peter Mullan\'s performance and Gaby Dellal\'s competent direction.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/83/10898389_mob.jpg'),(1196,'Laurel Canyon',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/laurel_canyon/','13908','0298408',1,NULL,'Though the movie itself is flawed, McDormand is fantastic as Jane.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/52/10885223_mob.jpg'),(1197,'Les Parapluies de Cherbourg (The Umbrellas of Cherbourg)',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/umbrellas_of_cherbourg/','22029','0058450',1,NULL,'Jacques Demy elevates the basic drama of everyday life into a soaring opera full of bittersweet passion and playful charm, featuring a timeless performance from Catherine Deneuve.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/30/89/308923_mob.jpg'),(1198,'House of Sand (Casa de Areia)',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/casa_de_areia/','190816482','0456875',1,NULL,'Beautifully filmed with wonderful performances, this Brazilian tale deftly explores the passage of time and prolonged isolation in several decades of a mother and daughter relationship.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/86/91/10869184_mob.jpg'),(1199,'OSS 117: Le Caire Nid d\'Espions (OSS 117: Cairo, Nest of Spies)',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1197120-oss_117_cairo_nest_of_spies/','285386768','0464913',1,NULL,'This clever spy spoof plays politics and movie conventions for laughs and features a great turn by Jen Dujardin as a smarmy-suave nouveau-Bond.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/35/65/72/3565726_mob.jpg'),(1200,'Chico & Rita',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chico_and_rita/','771208474','1235830',1,'Cuba, 1948. Chico is a young piano player with big dreams. Rita is a beautiful singer with an extraordinary voice. Music and desire unite them as they chase their dreams and each other from Havana to New York to Paris, Hollywood and Las Vegas. With an original soundtrack by legendary Cuban pianist and five-time Grammy-winning composer Bebo Valdes, Chico & Rita captures a defining moment in the evolution of history and jazz, and features the music of (and animated cameos by) Thelonious Monk, Charlie Parker, Cole Porter, Dizzy Gillespie, Woody Herman, Tito Puente, Chano Pozo, and others. -- (C) GKIDS',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/33/11163390_mob.jpg'),(1201,'Chalet Girl',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chalet_girl/','771201465','1487118',1,'Pretty tomboy Kim (Felicity Jones) used to be a champion skateboarder, but now she flips burgers to support herself and her dad. Opportunity comes knocking when she flukes a winter-long catering job in one of the plushest ski chalets in the Alps. At first, Kim is baffled by this bizarre new world of posh people, vintage champagne, epic mountains and waist deep powder. Then Kim discovers snowboarding, and her natural talent soon sees her training for the end-of-season competition, with a chance to win major prize money. But before she can become a champion again, Kim needs to overcome her deepest fears - and figure out what\'s going on with Jonny (Ed Westwick), her boss\' handsome but apparently unavailable son. -- (C) IFC','Chalet Girl is light comedic fun geared for teenage girls, featuring a charming performance from Felicity Jones.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/07/11160781_mob.jpg'),(1202,'The Company',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1128345-company/','13468','0335013',1,NULL,'Its deliberately unfocused narrative may frustrate some viewers, but The Company finds Altman gracefully applying his distinctive eye to the world of dance.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/85/24/10852432_mob.jpg'),(1203,'The Crime of Padre Amaro',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crime_of_padre_amaro/','13356','0313196',1,NULL,'Though melodramatic, El Crimen del Padre Amaro\'s critique of the Catholic church is a timely one.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/50/10895046_mob.jpg'),(1204,'13 Conversations About One Thing',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/thirteen_conversations_about_one_thing/','14167','0268690',1,NULL,'Thirteen Conversations About One Thing is an intelligent and poignant look at lives intersecting.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/37/88/10378897_mob.jpg'),(1205,'Charlotte Gray',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/charlotte_gray/','11916','0245046',1,NULL,'A dull adaptation of Sebastian Faulk\'s novel despite gorgeous cinematography and Cate Blanchett\'s best efforts.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/30/263010_mob.jpg'),(1206,'The Cat\'s Meow',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cats_meow/','12118','0266391',1,NULL,'The Cat\'s Meow is a deliciously evoked period piece and whodunit.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/26/39/263991_mob.jpg'),(1207,'My Kid Could Paint That',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/my_kid_could_paint_that/','528361220','0912592',1,NULL,'Director Amir Bar-Lev grapples with exposing the authenticity of four-year-old Marla\'s paintings at the sake of burdening her publicly shamed family to transfixing results.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/96/22/13/9622137_mob.jpg'),(1208,'Cyberbully',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cyberbully/','771249032','1930315',1,'A teenage girl (Emily Osment) falls prey to online bullying and retreats from spending time with her family and friends. Soon the tormenting pushes her toward the edge, and her mom (Kelly Rowan) takes the troubling issue to authorities. ~ Jennifer Sankowski, Rovi',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/05/11160516_mob.jpg'),(1209,'Chop Shop',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chop_shop/','770682646','0990404',1,NULL,'Filled with excellent performances, Ramin Bahrani\'s deft sophomore effort is a heartfelt, hopeful neorealist look at the people who live in the gritty underbelly of New York City.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/85/03/10850366_mob.jpg'),(1210,'The Comedy',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_comedy/','771266294','2112293',1,'On the cusp of inheriting his father\'s estate, Swanson (Tim Heidecker, \"Tim & Eric Awesome Show, Great Job!\") is a man with unlimited options. An aging hipster in Brooklyn, he spends his days in aimless recreation with like-minded friends (\"Tim & Eric\" co-star Eric Wareheim, LCD Soundsystem frontman James Murphy and comedian Gregg Turkington a.k.a.\"Neil Hamburger\") in games of comic irreverence and mock sincerity. As Swanson grows restless of the safety a sheltered life offers him, he tests the limits of acceptable behavior, pushing the envelope in every way he can. Heidecker\'s deadpan delivery cleverly masks a deep desire for connection and sense in the modern world. The Comedy wears its name on its sleeve, but director Rick Alverson\'s powerful and provocative character study touches a darkness behind the humor that resonates with viewers long after the story ends.',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/88/11168802_mob.jpg'),(1211,'The Fox & the Child',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_fox_and_the_child_2007/','770681648','0756648',1,NULL,'Jackanory-esque voiceover from Winslet lends a syrupy tone to this mawkish and slow, but beautifully shot, human/beastie buddy movie.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/86/81/10868131_mob.jpg'),(1212,'Private Fears in Public Places (Coeurs)',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/private_fears_in_public_places/','351527197','0498120',1,NULL,'The premise isn\'t anything new, but director Alain Resnais\' attention to detail and smooth camerawork gives this movie a delicate edge.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/92/42/10924224_mob.jpg'),(1213,'Chill Factor',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chill_factor/','15886','0163579',1,NULL,'Claiming it fails on every level, critics had almost nothing good to say about this movie.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/89/85/10898575_mob.gif'),(1214,'I Capture the Castle',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/i_capture_the_castle/','13959','0300015',1,NULL,'A handsome and charming adaptation of the novel.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/89/47/10894704_mob.jpg'),(1215,'You Can\'t Take It with You',1938,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1024312-you_cant_take_it_with_you/','17136','0030993',1,NULL,'It\'s predictably uplifting fare from Frank Capra, perhaps the most consciously uplifting of all great American directors -- but thanks to immensely appealing performances and a nimble script, You Can\'t Take It With You is hard not to love.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/91/55/10915585_mob.jpg'),(1216,'Le Mepris (Contempt)',1963,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/contempt/','19272','0057345',1,NULL,'This powerful work of essential cinema joins \"meta\" with \"physique,\" casting Brigite Bardot and director Godard\'s inspiration Fritz Lang.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/93/40/10934024_mob.jpg'),(1217,'Fantastic Planet',1973,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fantastic_planet/','12113','0070544',1,NULL,'Fantastic Planet is an animated epic that is by turns surreal and lovely, fantastic and graceful.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/94/96/10949678_mob.jpg'),(1218,'About Cherry',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/about_cherry/','771309282','1945062',1,'Cherry is about Angelina (Ashley Hinshaw), an 18-year-old girl on the verge of finishing high school. Angelina\'s family life is difficult. Her mother (Lili Taylor) is an alcoholic and her step-father is violent and unpredictable. One morning her boyfriend (Jonny Weston) suggests she take naked pictures for money. She balks at first but then does the photo shoot, using the money to run-off with her best friend (Dev Patel) to San Francisco. In San Francisco, while cocktailing in a strip club, Angelina meets Frances (James Franco) a well-off lawyer who offers to introduce her to a different kind of world, a place full of expensive dresses and fancy parties. But that world is not as perfect as it first appears and Frances has problems of his own. At the same time Angelina, using the moniker Cherry, has begun exploring the San Francisco porn industry under the direction of Margaret (Heather Graham) a former performer turned adult film director. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/60/11166076_mob.jpg'),(1219,'Circumstance',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/771228738/','771228738','1684628',1,'Atafeh and her brother, Mehran, have grown up privileged, in a home filled with music, art, and intellectual curiosity. While Atafeh dreams of fame and adventure, and she and her best friend, Shireen, explore Tehran\'s underground scene with youthful exuberance and determination to be themselves, her brother returns home from drug rehab, renounces his former decadent life, and replaces his once obsessive practice of classical music with more destructive pursuits. -- (C) Roadside Attractions','A thought-provoking, insightful look into Iranian youth culture.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/84/11158479_mob.jpg'),(1220,'City of Life and Death',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/city_of_life_and_death/','770810520','1124052',1,'Within the scope of Asian history, few events carry the ugly and sickening connotations of the Rape of Nanking. Japanese forces invaded that Chinese city on December 9, 1937, and in the six weeks to follow, soldiers raped thousands of women and annihilated hundreds of thousands of innocent civilians. Director Lu Chuan directs this black-and-white docudrama account of that horrifying six-week period, with the benefit of an ensemble cast that includes Hideo Nakaizumi as a conscience-stricken Japanese soldier, Fan Wei as the aid to a German humanitarian worker, and Gao Yuanyuan as the head of a refugee camp. Lu relays the events directly and straightforwardly, with a careful avoidance of sensationalism and excessive sentimentality, and uses the chronicle to meditate on the insanity of war for all of those involved. ~ Nathan Southern, Rovi',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/88/11168819_mob.jpg'),(1221,'CSA: Confederate States of America',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/csa_confederate_states_of_america/','243336303','0389828',1,NULL,'Through the eyes of a British \"documentary\", this film takes a satirically humorous, and sometimes frightening, look at the history of an America where the South won the Civil War.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/15/53/07/1553077_mob.jpg'),(1222,'Capturing the Friedmans',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/capturing_the_friedmans/','133039637','0342172',1,NULL,'A haunting depiction of a disintegrating family, and a powerful argument on the elusiveness of truth.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/93/45/10934558_mob.jpg'),(1223,'Cairo Time',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cairo_time/','770817176','0896529',1,NULL,'Though potentially too slowly paced for some, Cairo Time lingers long after the closing credits, largely due to a wonderful performance by Patricia Clarkson.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/90/11169076_mob.jpg'),(1224,'Killer of Sheep: The Charles Burnett Collection',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/killer_of_sheep/','700941685','0076263',1,NULL,'By turns funny, sad, and profound, Killer of Sheep offers a sympathetic and humane glimpse into inner-city life.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/59/10895986_mob.jpg'),(1225,'The Silent House',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_silent_house/','771040732','1646973',1,'Laura and her father Wilson settle down in an old farmhouse to make some repairs and update it prior to its sale. But after they spend the night there, things start to get strange. Laura hears a sound that gets louder and louder on the upper floor of the house. Wilson goes up to see what is going on while she remains downstairs, waiting for her father\'s return.',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/70/11157039_mob.jpg'),(1226,'Crazy Love',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/crazy_love_2007/','528345208','0790706',1,NULL,'Crazy Love\'s subjects and story are so compelling that they overcome the doc\'s dry, talking heads format.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/53/69/10536956_mob.jpg'),(1227,'La Fille Coupee en Deux (The Girl Cut in Two) (A Girl Cut in Two)',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/girl_cut_in_two/','770676929','0901485',1,NULL,'Nouvelle Vague master Claude Chabrol balances subtle stabs of humor and biting class criticism to explore a love story and the seedier side of the haute bourgeois.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/92/44/10924441_mob.jpg'),(1228,'Wing Commander',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wing_commander/','11724','0131646',1,NULL,'The low budget may explain Wing Commander\'s cheesy special effects, but can\'t excuse the lame dialogue or the movie\'s obsessive reliance on sci-fi cliches.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/50/11165098_mob.jpg'),(1229,'Foreign Correspondent',1940,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/foreign_correspondent/','18812','0032484',1,NULL,'Alfred Hitchcock\'s Foreign Correspondent features a winning combination of international intrigue, comic relief, and some of the legendary director\'s most memorable set pieces.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/99/05/70/9905707_mob.jpg'),(1230,'Saints and Soldiers: Airborne Creed',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/saints_and_soldiers_airborne_creed/','771266783','2082415',1,'On August 15, 1944 the 517th Parachute Regimental Combat Team (PRCT) jumped over the south of France. Their mission was to support and protect the Allied Troops marching to Berlin. Landing in enemy territory, they fell under immediate attack. In their effort to complete the mission and rendez-vous with their unit, three isolated paratroopers come across a group of French resistants in desperate need. They decide to help liberate some of the captive Partisans. Doing so they risk their lives in an effort to live the Airborne Creed. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/43/11164373_mob.jpg'),(1231,'A Midsummer Night\'s Sex Comedy',1982,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/midsummer_nights_sex_comedy/','11629','0084329',1,NULL,'It may not Woody Allen\'s best work, but the frothy, fun A Midsummer Night\'s Sex Comedy is still worth a look.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/17/10881707_mob.jpg'),(1232,'Cape of Good Hope',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cape_of_good_hope/','9180','0398830',1,NULL,'This little South African film takes a different approach -- putting politics in the background and ordinary people front and center. Overall, it\'s a heartwarming effort.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/83/10898394_mob.jpg'),(1233,'Les Enfants du Paradis (Children of Paradise)',1945,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/children-of-paradise/','19218','0037674',1,NULL,'Strong performances abound, and Carne\'s wit and grace are evident in this masterful (if long) French epic.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/29/61/296100_mob.jpg'),(1234,'Cradle Will Rock',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cradle_will_rock/','14150','0150216',1,NULL,'Witty and provocative.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/27/32/273223_mob.jpg'),(1235,'Constantine 2',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/constantine-2/','770783453','1071873',1,'Caught in the middle of the war between Angels and Demons, John Constantine must find a way to stop Demons from possessing the bodies of innocent people and becoming half-breeds.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1236,'O Homem Que Copiava (The Man Who Copied)',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/man_who_copied/','14645','0367859',1,NULL,'Though it has some nice moments, The Man Who Copied spins out of control by the second half and wears out its welcome.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/27/56/275616_mob.jpg'),(1237,'La Graine et le Mulet (The Secret of the Grain) (Couscous)',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10009066-la_graine_et_le_mulet/','770682245','0487419',1,NULL,'A complex portrait of an immigrant family, The Secret of the Grain is a sprawling, intimate film with many fine performances.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/83/83/10838338_mob.jpg'),(1238,'The Clearing',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/clearing/','14327','0331952',1,NULL,'Though it has an excellent cast, this emotionally detached movie is the kind that one admires more than enjoys.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/27/41/274102_mob.jpg'),(1239,'Snow Falling on Cedars',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/snow_falling_on_cedars/','11251','0120834',1,NULL,'Though Snow Falling on Cedars is beautiful to look at, critics say the story becomes dull and tedious to sit through.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/46/10884605_mob.jpg'),(1240,'Dixie Chicks: Shut Up and Sing',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shut_up_and_sing/','355028133',NULL,1,NULL,'Though ostensibly an intimate look at the Dixie Chicks after their 2003 anti-Bush remark, the film achieves broader relevance by exploring how media, politics, and celebrities intertwine.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/30/19/24/3019240_mob.jpg'),(1241,'Citadel',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/citadel_2012/','771270449','1641975',1,'Tommy Cowley lives a quiet life in a decaying apartment complex with his highly pregnant wife. The couple is attacked one day by a group of hooded young thugs, and after a shocking act of violence, Tommy is left to raise his newborn daughter alone. So shaken by the events that he\'s developed extreme agoraphobia, Tommy alternates days hiding out indoors in his new flat from imagined threats and intense therapy sessions aimed at bringing him back to normalcy. When the same hooded gang, seemingly intent on kidnapping his daughter, begins terrorizing his life again, he\'s torn between his paralyzing fear and protective parental instinct. With the help of a vigilante priest who has uncovered the genesis of this ruthless, potentially supernatural gang, Tommy must overcome his fears and venture into the heart of the abandoned tower block known as the CITADEL to save his family.',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/68/11166897_mob.jpg'),(1242,'I Want Someone to Eat Cheese With',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/i_want_someone_to_eat_cheese_with/','770672886','0391229',1,NULL,'This quirky romantic comedy\'s realistic depiction of a lonely guy looking for love is sure to please fans of Curb Your Enthusiasm\'s Jeff Garlin.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/65/10886536_mob.jpg'),(1243,'Three Days of the Condor',1975,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/three_days_of_the_condor/','12933','0073802',1,NULL,'This post-Watergate thriller captures the paranoid tenor of the times, thanks to Syndey Pollock\'s taut direction and excellent performances from Robert Redford and Faye Dunaway.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/26/72/267291_mob.jpg'),(1244,'Brooklyn Castle',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/brooklyn_castle_2012/','771271065','1800266',1,'Brooklyn Castle is the remarkable and improbable true story of I.S. 318 in Brooklyn. The school, where 65% of students live below the federal poverty level, has the highest ranked junior high chess team in the nation. The heart of the film is the engaging young students who populate the team: Rochelle, who has the goal of becoming the first female African-American chess master; Pobo, the team\'s charismatic leader; Justus, an entering student who must manage the high expectations that come with achieving master status at an early age; Alexis, who feels the pressure of his immigrant parents\' desire for him to realize the American dream; Patrick, who uses chess to help overcome his ADHD; and James, the young rapping maestro and budding chess talent; among several others. -- (C) Official Site','Brooklyn Castle is a warm, engaging, and even uplifting documentary about chess-playing whiz kids.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/67/11166757_mob.jpg'),(1245,'Caos Calmo (Quiet Chaos)',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/quiet_chaos/','770684842','0929412',1,NULL,'An understated and thoughtful insight into grief and despair, with a stellar turn from Nanni Moretti.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/90/11169080_mob.jpg'),(1246,'Easy Money',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/easy_money_2012/','770856726','1291652',1,'Lower-class business student JW (Joel Kinnaman) falls in love with a sexy heiress while living a double life mingling with Stockholm\'s wealthy elite. To keep up the facade of his lifestyle, he\'s lured into a world of crime. Jorge is a petty fugitive on the run from both the police and Serbian mafia. He hopes that brokering a massive cocaine deal will allow him to escape for good. Mafia enforcer Mrado is on the hunt for Jorge, but his efforts are complicated when he\'s unexpectedly saddled with caring for his young daughter. As JW\'s journey ventures deeper into the dark world of organized crime, the fate of all three men becomes entangled and ends with a dramatic struggle for life and death. -- (C) Weinstein',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/57/11165716_mob.jpg'),(1247,'Bill Cunningham New York',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bill_cunningham_new_york_2010/','771205733','1621444',1,'\"We all get dressed for Bill,\" says Vogue editrix Anna Wintour. The \"Bill\" in question is 80+ New York Times photographer Bill Cunningham. For decades, this Schwinn-riding cultural anthropologist has been obsessively and inventively chronicling fashion trends and high society charity soirees for the Times Style section in his columns \"On the Street\" and \"Evening Hours.\" Documenting uptown fixtures (Wintour, Tom Wolfe, Brooke Astor, David Rockefeller-who all appear in the film out of their love for Bill), downtown eccentrics and everyone in between, Cunningham\'s enormous body of work is more reliable than any catwalk as an expression of time, place and individual flair. In turn, Bill Cunningham New York is a delicate, funny and often poignant portrait of a dedicated artist whose only wealth is his own humanity and unassuming grace. -- (C) Zeitgeist films','Suffused with happiness and modest charm, Bill Cunningham New York offers a touching, gently humorous portrait of its subject without invading his jealously guarded privacy.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/57/11155759_mob.jpg'),(1248,'Stay Cool',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stay_cool/','770783621','1235807',1,'Henry McCarthy (Mark Polish), the 30-something author of the popular 80s-themed novel How Lionel Got Me Laid, returns to his suburban hometown of Sacramento to deliver the commencement speech at his former high school. Despite his success as an author Henry\'s return home has sparked all of the youthful dreams, desires and particularly disappointments he\'s never quite gotten over, specifically his unrequited affection for the girl who is now the local pharmacist: the elusive Scarlet Smith (Winona Ryder). Between run-ins with the outcast friends he left behind Big Girl (Sean Astin) and Wino (Josh Holloway), the school principal (Chevy Chase) and a seductive senior, Shasta O\'Neil (Hilary Duff) who clearly has the hots for him, Henry is sent spinning through a time warp that incites all the old emotions and challenges of the world he grew up in. -- (C) Initiate Productions',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/02/11160219_mob.jpg'),(1249,'Memories of Murder (Salinui chueok)',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/memories-of-murder/','17410','0353969',1,NULL,'Memories of Murder blends the familiar crime genre with social satire and comedy, capturing the all-too human desperation of its key characters.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/92/26/10922621_mob.jpg'),(1250,'Los Cronocrimenes (Timecrimes)',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/time_crimes/','770679312','0480669',1,NULL,'Timecrimes is a low-budget thriller that\'s well-crafted and loaded with dark humor and bizarre twists.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/87/72/10877206_mob.jpg'),(1251,'The Vertical Ray of the Sun (At the Height of Summer) (Mua he chieu thang dung)',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/vertical_ray_of_the_sun/','11899','0224578',1,NULL,'The Vertical Ray of the Sun is gorgeously, poetically composed, lulling the viewer into its story of everyday life.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/14/31/11143156_mob.jpg'),(1252,'The Color Wheel',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_color_wheel/','771263121','1734548',1,'The Color Wheel is the story of JR, an increasingly transient aspiring news-anchor, as she forces her disappointing younger brother Colin to embark on a road trip to move her belongings out of her professor-turned-lover\'s apartment. Problem is, these grown up kids do not get along, and are both too obnoxious to know better. Chaos and calamity are not far behind her beat up Honda Accord. Too bad that nobody else in the world can stand either of them. Not Colin\'s neglectful girlfriend, nor JR\'s former high school friends, nor strangers they clash with at pretty much every step of their hopeless and increasingly infuriating voyage of frustration, failure and jerks. It can only be a matter of time before JR and Colin arrive at the strangest and most unsettling of resolutions and put to rest their decades of animosity, half-baked sibling rivalry and endless bickering. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/51/11165172_mob.jpg'),(1253,'Comedian',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/comedian/','13300','0328962',1,NULL,'Comedian is an insightful look at the hard work of creating comedy.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/91/269100_mob.jpg'),(1254,'Dao huo xian (City Without Mercy) (Flash Point) (Fuse) (The Signal)',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/flash_point/','770673130','0992911',1,NULL,'Flash Point features some nice mindless martial-arts action, but too much of the already thin story treads familiar ground.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/64/10876433_mob.jpg'),(1255,'The Claim',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/claim/','16067','0218378',1,NULL,'Though it sometimes feels cold and detached, The Claim is evocative, beautifully shot, and full of understated performances.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/28/22/282225_mob.jpg'),(1256,'The Grace Card',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_grace_card/','771208003','1544600',1,'This earnest evangelical drama draws inspiration from the Bible verse Hebrews 4:16 (\"We will find grace to help us when we need it\") in its tale of a police officer named Bill \"Mac\" McDonald (Michael Joiner) whose life is shattered (and his faith severely challenged) when he loses his son in a tragic accident. Eighteen years of rage and hostility ensue, marked by rapidly crumbling relationships with his family members and strained relationships on the force. Events reach a fever pitch, however, when Mac gets partnered up in the squad car with Sam Wright (Michael Higgenbottom), an African-American ordained minister-turned-cop with a loving and supportive family. Despite the many obstacles standing in the way, the men gradually work toward overcoming their differences and helping one another. ~ Nathan Southern, Rovi','Tailored for a very specific audience, The Grace Card delivers its noble religious message via implausible plot twists and preachy dialogue.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/58/11155858_mob.jpg'),(1257,'Turtles Can Fly (Lakposhtha ham parvaz mikonand)',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/turtles_can_fly/','10444','0424227',1,NULL,'Set in Iraq after the fall of Saddam, Turtles Can Fly is being hailed as extraordinary, moving, and lyrical.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/70/23/10702313_mob.jpg'),(1258,'Carlos',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/carlos_2010/','771253374',NULL,1,NULL,'Despite its hefty running time, Carlos moves along briskly, thanks to an engaging story, exotic locales, and a breakout performance by Edgar Ramirez.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/35/11153533_mob.jpg'),(1259,'Cafe de Flore',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cafe_de_flore/','771235393','1550312',1,'Cafe de Flore is a love story about people separated by time and place but connected in profound and mysterious ways. Atmospheric, fantastical, tragic and hopeful, the film chronicles the parallel fates of Jacqueline, a young mother with a disabled son in 1960s Paris, and Antoine, a recently divorced, successful DJ in present day Montreal. What binds the two stories together is love - euphoric, obsessive, tragic, youthful, timeless love. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/67/11166710_mob.jpg'),(1260,'The Corruptor',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/corruptor/','14666','0142192',1,NULL,'This uninspiring cop thriller doesn\'t measure up to Chow Yun-Fat\'s Hong Kong work.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/27/57/275717_mob.jpg'),(1261,'Lady Chatterley',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10008097-lady_chatterley/','770671300','0459880',1,NULL,'Tasteful, poetic, yet sexually forthright, Lady Chatterley skillfully translates its source novel\'s high-art erotica onto the big screen.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/12/63/11126329_mob.jpg'),(1262,'Cowgirls n\' Angels',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cowgirls_n_angels/','771247485','1894561',1,'Ida, a feisty and rebellious young girl, dreams of one day finding her father, a rodeo rider, whose identity her mom has kept from her. While searching for her dad at a local rodeo, Ida meets the Sweethearts of the Rodeo, a team of young female trick riders run by cowboy legend Terence Parker. Terence discovers that Ida is the grand-daughter of a friend who passed away years before, so he decides to help her. Ida joins the Sweethearts and embarks with them on a tour of rodeos throughout the west. Ida hopes to find her father, but she discovers much more, including a love for horses that redefines her life. -- (C) Sense and Sensibility Ventures',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/31/11163179_mob.jpg'),(1263,'Journey to the Center of the Earth',1959,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1011256-journey_to_the_center_of_the_earth/','9427','0052948',1,NULL,'A silly but fun movie with everything you\'d want from a sci-fi blockbuster -- heroic characters, menacing villains, monsters, big sets and special effects.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/48/11164810_mob.jpg'),(1264,'Donnie Darko',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/donnie_darko/','12889','0246578',1,NULL,'Richard Kelly\'s debut feature Donnie Darko is a daring, original vision, packed with jarring ideas and intelligence and featuring a remarkable performance from Jake Gyllenhaal as the troubled title character.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/44/11164487_mob.jpg'),(1265,'The Day After Tomorrow',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/day_after_tomorrow/','10154','0319262',1,NULL,'A ludicrous popcorn flick filled with clunky dialogues, but spectacular visuals save it from being a total disaster.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/43/254313_mob.jpg'),(1266,'50 First Dates',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/50_first_dates/','10192','0343660',1,NULL,'Gross-out humor overwhelms the easy chemistry between Adam Sandler and Drew Barrymore, who bring some energy and yucks to this tale of a girl with short-term memory loss and the guy who tries to get her to love him.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/32/11153208_mob.jpg'),(1267,'Save the Last Dance',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/save_the_last_dance/','10398',NULL,1,NULL,'This teen romance flick feels like a predictable rehashing of other movies.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/16/90/48/1690480_mob.jpg'),(1268,'The Twilight Saga: New Moon',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/twilight_saga_new_moon/','770801331','1259571',1,NULL,'The Twilight Saga\'s second installment may satisfy hardcore fans of the series, but outsiders are likely to be turned off by its slow pace, relentlessly downcast tone, and excessive length.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/95/40/10954019_mob.jpg'),(1269,'Live Free or Die Hard',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/live_free_or_die_hard/','494020502','0337978',1,NULL,'Live Free or Die Hard may be preposterous, but it\'s an efficient, action-packed summer popcorn flick with thrilling stunts and a commanding performance by Bruce Willis. Fans of the previous Die Hard films will not be disappointed.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/93/34/10933482_mob.jpg'),(1270,'Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows - Part 1',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/harry_potter_and_the_deathly_hallows_part_1/','770672991','0926084',1,'The first installment of the two-film adaptation of Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows follows Harry (Daniel Radcliffe), Ron (Rupert Grint), and Hermione (Emma Watson) as they search for the pieces of Voldemort\'s (Ralph Fiennes) soul that he extracted from his being and hid in obscure locations both far and wide. If the trio is unable to locate and destroy them all, Voldemort will remain immortal. Despite their long friendship, a combination of dark forces, romantic tensions, and long-held secrets threaten to sabotage the mission. David Yates directs. ~ Tracie Cooper, Rovi','It can\'t help but feel like the prelude it is, but Deathly Hallows: Part I is a beautifully filmed, emotionally satisfying penultimate installment for the Harry Potter series.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/36/11163674_mob.jpg'),(1271,'Zero Dark Thirty',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/zero_dark_thirty/','771249562','1790885',1,'For a decade, an elite team of intelligence and military operatives, working in secret across the globe, devoted themselves to a single goal: to find and eliminate Osama bin Laden. Zero Dark Thirty reunites the Oscar winning team of director-producer Kathryn Bigelow and writer-producer Mark Boal (The Hurt Locker) for the story of history\'s greatest manhunt for the world\'s most dangerous man. -- (C) Official Site','Gripping, suspenseful, and brilliantly crafted, Zero Dark Thirty dramatizes the hunt for Osama bin Laden with intelligence and an eye for detail.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/75/11167541_mob.jpg'),(1272,'Disturbia',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/disturbia/','554237964','0486822',1,NULL,'Aside from its cliched resolution, Disturbia is a tense, subtle thriller with a noteworthy performance from Shia LaBeouf.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/67/10886753_mob.jpg'),(1273,'Star Trek Into Darkness',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/star_trek_into_darkness/','771190753','1408101',1,'The Star Trek franchise continues with this follow-up to 2009\'s J.J. Abrams-directed reboot. Abrams and Bryan Burk handle producing duties on the sci-fi production, from a script by Damon Lindelof and the writing team of Roberto Orci and Alex Kurtzman. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/78/11167865_mob.jpg'),(1274,'The Dark Knight Rises',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_dark_knight_rises/','771041731','1345836',1,'It has been eight years since Batman vanished into the night, turning, in that instant, from hero to fugitive. Assuming the blame for the death of D.A. Harvey Dent, the Dark Knight sacrificed everything for what he and Commissioner Gordon both hoped was the greater good. For a time the lie worked, as criminal activity in Gotham City was crushed under the weight of the anti-crime Dent Act. But everything will change with the arrival of a cunning cat burglar with a mysterious agenda. Far more dangerous, however, is the emergence of Bane, a masked terrorist whose ruthless plans for Gotham drive Bruce out of his self-imposed exile. But even if he dons the cape and cowl again, Batman may be no match for Bane.. -- (C) Warner Bros.','The Dark Knight Rises is an ambitious, thoughtful, and potent action film that concludes Christopher Nolan\'s franchise in spectacular fashion.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/78/11167835_mob.jpg'),(1275,'Thor: The Dark World',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/thor_the_dark_world/','771247277','1981115',1,'Marvel\'s \"Thor: The Dark World\" continues the big-screen adventures of Thor, the Mighty Avenger, as he battles to save Earth and all the Nine Realms from a shadowy enemy that predates the universe itself. In the aftermath of Marvel\'s \"Thor\" and \"Marvel\'s The Avengers,\" Thor fights to restore order across the cosmos...but an ancient race led by the vengeful Malekith returns to plunge the universe back into darkness. Faced with an enemy that even Odin and Asgard cannot withstand, Thor must embark on his most perilous and personal journey yet, one that will reunite him with Jane Foster and force him to sacrifice everything to save us all. Starring Chris Hemsworth, Natalie Portman, Tom Hiddleston, Stellan Skarsgard, Idris Elba, Christopher Eccleston, Adewale Akinnuoye-Agbaje, Kat Dennings, Ray Stevenson, Zachary Levi, Tadanobu Asano, and Jaimie Alexander with Rene Russo and Anthony Hopkins as Odin, Marvel\'s \"Thor: The Dark World\" is directed by Alan Taylor, produced by Kevin Feige, from a story by Don Payne (credit not final) and screenplay by Christopher Yost and Christopher Markus & Stephen McFeely (credit not final) and is based on Marvel\'s classic Super Hero Thor, who first appeared in the comic book \"Journey into Mystery \" #83 in August, 1962. Marvel\'s \"Thor: The Dark World\" continues the big-screen adventures of Thor, the Mighty Avenger, as he battles to save Earth and all the Nine Realms from a shadowy enemy that predates the universe itself. (c) Disney',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1276,'District 9',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/district_9/','770805203','1136608',1,NULL,'Technically brilliant and emotionally wrenching, District 9 has action, imagination, and all the elements of a thoroughly entertaining science-fiction classic.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/94/46/10944698_mob.jpg'),(1277,'Slumdog Millionaire',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/slumdog_millionaire/','770770017','1010048',1,NULL,'Visually dazzling and emotionally resonant, Slumdog Millionaire is a film that\'s both entertaining and powerful.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/86/47/10864783_mob.jpg'),(1278,'How to Train Your Dragon 2',2014,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/how_to_train_your_dragon_2/','771040382','1646971',1,'DreamWorks Animation returns to the world of dragons and Vikings in this sequel to their successful 2010 outing How to Train Your Dragon. The original film followed the exploits of a Viking chief\'s son, who must capture a dragon in order to mark his passage into manhood and prove his worthiness to the tribe. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1279,'A Good Day To Die Hard',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_good_day_to_die_hard/','771257607','1606378',1,'John McClane (Bruce Willis) heads to Russia in this fifth installment of the Die Hard film series. Skip Woods (The A-Team) provides the script, with Max Payne\'s John Moore directing. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/83/11168351_mob.jpg'),(1280,'Despicable Me 2',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/despicable_me_2/','771245727','1690953',1,'Universal Pictures presents this sequel to the wildly successful 2010 animated picture following Gru (voiced by Steve Carell), the ex-scheming evildoer-turned-parental figure, from animation company Illumination Entertainment. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/39/11163934_mob.jpg'),(1281,'Evil Dead',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_evil_dead_2013/','771264989','1288558',1,'In the much anticipated remake of the 1981 cult-hit horror film, five twenty-something friends become holed up in a remote cabin. When they discover a Book of the Dead, they unwittingly summon up dormant demons living in the nearby woods, which possess the youngsters in succession until only one is left intact to fight for survival.',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/77/11167764_mob.jpg'),(1282,'The Hobbit: The Desolation Of Smaug',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_hobbit_the_desolation_of_smaug/','771315407','1170358',1,'The second in a trilogy of films adapting the enduringly popular masterpiece The Hobbit, by J.R.R. Tolkien, The Hobbit: The Desolation of Smaug continues the adventure of the title character Bilbo Baggins (Martin Freeman) as he journeys with the Wizard Gandalf (Ian McKellan) and thirteen Dwarves, led by Thorin Oakenshield (Richard Armitage) on an epic quest to reclaim the lost Dwarf Kingdom of Erebor.(c) WB',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1283,'John Dies at the End',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/john_dies_at_the_end/','771256250','1783732',1,'It\'s a drug that promises an out-of-body experience with each hit. On the street they call it Soy Sauce, and users drift across time and dimensions. But some who come back are no longer human. Suddenly a silent otherworldly invasion is underway, and mankind needs a hero. What it gets instead is John and David, a pair of college dropouts who can barely hold down jobs. Can these two stop the oncoming horror in time to save humanity? No. No, they can\'t. -- (C) Official Site','Some will find the darkly funny, genre-bending incoherence of John Dies at the End charming; some will feel its zany antics and gore lead to an unsatisfying payoff.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/71/11167149_mob.jpg'),(1284,'Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows - Part 2',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/harry_potter_and_the_deathly_hallows_part_2_2011/','770687943','1201607',1,'Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows - Part 2, is the final adventure in the Harry Potter film series. The much-anticipated motion picture event is the second of two full-length parts. In the epic finale, the battle between the good and evil forces of the wizarding world escalates into an all-out war. The stakes have never been higher and no one is safe. But it is Harry Potter who may be called upon to make the ultimate sacrifice as he draws closer to the climactic showdown with Lord Voldemort. It all ends here. -- (C) Warner Bros','Thrilling, powerfully acted, and visually dazzling, Deathly Hallows Part II brings the Harry Potter franchise to a satisfying -- and suitably magical -- conclusion.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/36/11163675_mob.jpg'),(1285,'The ABCs of Death',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_abcs_of_death/','771269389','1935896',1,'Twenty-six directors. Twenty-six ways to die. The ABC\'s OF DEATH is perhaps the most ambitious anthology film ever conceived with productions spanning fifteen countries and featuring segments directed by over two dozen of the world\'s leading talents in contemporary genre film. Inspired by children\'s educational books, the motion picture is comprised of twenty-six individual chapters; each helmed by a different director assigned a letter of the alphabet. The directors were then given free reign in choosing a word to create a story involving death. Provocative, shocking, funny and ultimately confrontational, THE ABC\'s OF DEATH is the definitive vision of modern horror diversity. (c) Magnolia',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/42/11164272_mob.jpg'),(1286,'Ice Age: Dawn of the Dinosaurs (Ice Age 3)',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1194515-ice_age_dawn_of_the_dinosaurs/','770681481','1080016',1,NULL,'The third Ice Age film has some excellent animation, but its story is tired and monotonous.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/93/89/10938903_mob.jpg'),(1287,'Drag Me to Hell',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/drag_me_to_hell/','770785298','1127180',1,NULL,'Sam Raimi returns to top form with Drag Me to Hell, a frightening, hilarious, delightfully campy thrill ride.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/88/11168866_mob.jpg'),(1288,'Dead Man Down',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dead_man_down_2013/','771310807','2101341',1,'Niels Arden Oplev, the acclaimed director of the original The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo, makes his American theatrical debut with the new action thriller, DEAD MAN DOWN. Colin Farrell and Noomi Rapace star as two strangers who are irresistibly drawn to one another by their mutual desire for revenge. The film co-stars Academy Award (R) nominee Terrence Howard and Dominic Cooper, from a screenplay by J.H.Wyman (Fringe). (c) Film District',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/86/11168630_mob.jpg'),(1289,'Dark Skies',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dark_skies_2013/','771317035','2387433',1,'From the producer of Paranormal Activity, Insidious, and Sinister comes Dark Skies: a supernatural thriller that follows a young family living in the suburbs. As husband and wife Daniel and Lacey Barret witness an escalating series of disturbing events involving their family, their safe and peaceful home quickly unravels. When it becomes clear that the Barret family is being targeted by an unimaginably terrifying and deadly force, Daniel and Lacey take matters in their own hands to solve the mystery of what is after their family. Written and Directed by Scott Stewart (PRIEST, LEGION) Starring: Keri Russell, Josh Hamilton, Dakota Goyo, Kadan Rockett and J.K. Simmons (c) Weinstein',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/87/11168752_mob.jpg'),(1290,'Dirty Energy',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dirty_energy/','771270636','2071449',1,'On April 20th, 2010, the Deepwater Horizon drilling rig exploded off the Gulf of Mexico taking the lives of 11 workers and sank as millions of barrels of oil poured into the ocean creating one of the worst environmental disasters in history. The fate of the Gulf is still largely unknown. Dirty Energy tells the personal story of those directly affected by the spill and how they are still struggling to rebuild their lives amidst the economic devastation and long-term health risks.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1291,'The Dark Tower',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_dark_tower_2012/','771208934','1648190',1,'Director Ron Howard brings Stephen King\'s most beloved series to life with this first chapter chronicling gunslinger Roland Deschain\'s journey to find an ever-elusive tower in an alternate dimension filled with fantastical creatures and characters directly connected with many of the author\'s most famous works. The feature film will be followed by two sequels, each of which will be bridged by two television series. Akiva Goldsman (Da Vinci Code, Batman & Robin) provides the screenplay. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1292,'A Dark Truth',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_dark_truth/','771314713','2083379',1,'Andy Garcia plays a former CIA operative turned political talk show host, who is hired by a corporate whistle blower to expose her company\'s cover-up of a massacre in a South American village. When he arrives, he is plunged into a violent and chaotic situation, with the military cracking down on a group of protesters led by a pair of activists (Eva Longoria and Forrest Whitaker). The ever-increasing depletion of earth\'s natural resource of water serves as the backdrop for this tense environmental thriller. (c) Magnolia',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/68/11166873_mob.jpg'),(1293,'Upside Down',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/upside_down_2012/','771266656','1374992',1,'Ever since Adam (Jim Sturgess) and Eden (Kirsten Dunst) fell in love as teens, their bond has faced astronomical odds. The pair are separated not just by social class and a political system bent on keeping them apart, but also by a freak planetary condition: they live on twinned worlds with gravities that pull in opposite directions-he on the poverty-stricken planet below, she on the wealthy, exploitative world above. Their budding but illicit romance screeches to a tragic halt when interplanetary-border patrol agents catch them and Eden suffers an apparently fatal fall. But when, ten years later, Adam learns she is alive and working at a vast corporation whose towering headquarters connects their planets, he sets out on a dangerous quest to infiltrate the company and the upper world to reconnect with her. UPSIDE DOWN is a visually stunning romantic adventure that poses the question: what if love was stronger than gravity?(c) Millenium',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/90/11169026_mob.jpg'),(1294,'Angels & Demons',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1189217-angels_and_demons/','770676132','0808151',1,NULL,'Angels and Demons is a fast-paced thrill ride, and an improvement on the last Dan Brown adaptation, but the storyline too often wavers between implausible and ridiculous, and does not translate effectively to the big screen.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/94/10879477_mob.jpg'),(1295,'Frozen',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/frozen_2013/','771246543','2294629',1,'Featuring the voices of Kristen Bell and Idina Menzel, \"Frozen\" is the coolest comedy-adventure ever to hit the big screen. When a prophecy traps a kingdom in eternal winter, Anna, a fearless optimist, teams up with extreme mountain man Kristoff and his sidekick reindeer Sven on an epic journey to find Anna\'s sister Elsa, the Snow Queen, and put an end to her icy spell. Encountering mystical trolls, a funny snowman named Olaf, Everest-like extremes and magic at every turn, Anna and Kristoff battle the elements in a race to save the kingdom from destruction. (c) Disney',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1296,'Officer Down',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/officer_down/','771319211','1925479',1,'One year ago, dirty cop Detective Callahan (Dorff) was shot in a drug bust gone wrong and saved by a stranger, giving Callahan a second chance to clean up his life. But when the stranger finally comes forward, seeking revenge against the men responsible for a string of assaults on young women at a local strip club, Callahan must go rogue to find the attacker in an effort to hide how his own past played a part in these crimes. His desperation to find the attacker and cover his tracks takes him down a violent road of deception and fraud. Can he play the \"good cop\" and track down the assailant, while still keeping his reputation clean?',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/82/11168249_mob.jpg'),(1297,'Day of the Falcon',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/day_of_the_falcon/','771235386','1701210',1,'Starring Antonio Banderas (Desperado), Mark Strong (Zero Dark Thirty), Freida Pinto (Slumdog Millionaire) and Tahar Rahim (The Eagle), Day of the Falcon is a soaring epic of honor, greed, betrayal and love from award-winning director Jean-Jacques Annaud (Enemy at the Gates). After years of bloody conflict, the leaders of two rival kingdoms reluctantly agree to end the fighting. But when oil is discovered between their territories, the war is re-ignited. Now it is up to their children - young lovers who have married in hopes of bringing the families together - to find a way to end the violence and bring peace to the land. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/91/11169170_mob.jpg'),(1298,'Dead Sushi',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/deddo_sushi/','771314033','2396429',1,'Keiko (Rina Takeda) is the daughter of a legendary sushi chef. Hoping to follow in his footsteps, she enters into training under her father\'s guidance. His kung fu-like regime is rigid, pushing her to impossible mental and physical limits and Keiko, unable to bear the strain, runs away from home. Finding work at a rural hot springs inn, she is dismayed to find that her co-workers are an eccentric lot who have it in for the new girl. Complicating matters is the arrival of a group of employees from Komatsu Pharmaceutical there to sample the inn\'s famous specialty sushi. Following them in pursuit of revenge is Yamada (Kentaro Shimazu), a medical researcher betrayed by the Komatsu president. Disgruntled and seeking revenge, Yamada injects the hotel sushi with a drug that not only brings it to life, but also turns it into ferocious, bloodthirsty killers! (c) Office Walker',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/87/11168731_mob.jpg'),(1299,'Love Is All You Need',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/love_is_all_you_need/','771315449','1854236',1,'When a female quarterback falls in love with a journalist they are harassed after their relationship becomes public as the world is overwhelmingly homosexual and heterosexuality is the exception.',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/73/11167371_mob.jpg'),(1300,'The Good Dinosaur',2014,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_good_dinosaur/','771306093','1979388',1,'What if the cataclysmic asteroid that forever changed life on Earth actually missed the planet completely and giant dinosaurs never became extinct? This hilarious, heartfelt and original tale is directed by Bob Peterson (co-director/writer, \"Up;\" writer, \"Finding Nemo\") and produced by John Walker (\"The Incredibles,\" \"The Iron Giant\").',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1301,'Oscar Nominated Documentary Shorts',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/oscar_nominated_documentary_shorts/','771267477',NULL,1,'Inocente - (directors: Sean Fine and Andrea Nix, USA) An intensely personal and vibrant coming of age documentary about a young artist\'s fierce determination to never surrender to the bleakness of her surroundings. At 15, Inocente refuses to let her dream of becoming an artist be caged by her life as an undocumented immigrant forced to live homeless for the last nine years. Inocente is both a timeless story about the transformative power of art and a timely snapshot of the new face of homelessness in America -- children. King\'s Point - (director: Sari Gilman, USA) Kings Point tells the stories of five seniors living in a typical American retirement resort-men and women who came to Florida decades ago with their spouses by their sides and their health intact, and now find themselves grappling with love, loss and the universal desire for human connection. Mondays at Racine - (director: Cynthia Wade, USA) Every third Monday of the month, in brassy Long Island, sisters Cynthia and Rachel open up their hair salon, called Racine, and offer free beauty services for women undergoing chemotherapy. The sisters are determined to give women who are losing their hair, eyebrows and eyelashes a sense of normalcy and dignity in a traumatic and uncertain time. The story of what hair means in our culture quickly unfolds into an unexpected look at womanhood, marriage and survival. Open Heart - (director: Keif Davidson, USA) Eight Rwandan children leave their families behind to embark on a life-or-death journey seeking high-risk heart surgery in Sudan. Their hearts ravaged by a treatable disease from childhood strep throat, the kids have only months to live. Open Heart reveals the intertwined endeavors of Dr. Emmanuel Rusingiza, Rwanda\'s lone government cardiologist, as he fights to save the lives of his young patients, and Dr. Gino Strada, the Salam Center\'s head surgeon who must convince Sudanese President Omar Al-Bashir\'s government to keep Africa\'s only link to life-saving cardiac surgery free of charge for the millions who need it. Redemption - (directors: Jon Alpert & Matthew O\'Neill, USA) In the documentary Redemption, filmmakers Jon Alpert & Matthew O\'Neill closely follow this growing army of New Yorkers whose treasures are in the trash. The film is a chance to meet the marginalized masses we often rush past on our way to catch a bus or make a meeting. They are poor but proud New Yorkers - people who don\'t ask for a handout - people whose hands rake through the discards of our lives - building their lives one nickel at a time. -- (C) Shorts International',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/90/11169047_mob.jpg'),(1302,'Disconnect',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/disconnect_2013/','771312103',NULL,1,'Murderball director Henry Alex Rubin explores the destructive potential of the internet in this ensemble drama starring Jason Bateman, Hope Davis, and Alexander Skarsgard. His marriage dissolving before his very eyes, a former Marine (Skarsgard) ruins his credit by gambling online as his wife (Paula Patton) strikes up an intimate relationship on a popular social networking site. When identity theft puts their life savings at risk, the couple tracks down the man (Michael Nyqvust) they believe is responsible for the crime. Meanwhile, an introverted teenage goth ({Jonah Bobo}) becomes the victim of a humiliating prank when his two biggest tormentors pose as the girl he likes, trick him into exposing his true identity online. When the prank leads to tragedy, the young victim\'s mother (Davis) is overwhelmed by grief as her husband (Bateman) explodes with rage. Later, an ambitious TV reporter\'s quest to expose an online prostitution racket has unexpected repercussions for the frightened young man at the center of the growing controversy. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1303,'It\'s a Disaster',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/its_a_disaster/','771309897','1995341',1,'Four couples meet for Sunday brunch only to discover they are stuck in a house together as the world may be about to end.',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/56/11165615_mob.jpg'),(1304,'Greenwich Village: Music That Defined a Generation',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/greenwich_village_music_that_defined_a_generation/','771318925','1941541',1,'GREENWICH VILLAGE: MUSIC THAT DEFINED A GENERATION is a feature-length documentary about the Greenwich Village music scene and how it sparked everlasting political, social and cultural changes. For the first time, the greatest singer-songwriters, authors and performers from Greenwich Village reflect on how they collectively became the voice of a generation. Through poignant interviews, rare archival footage and new live performances, GREENWICH VILLAGE: MUSIC THAT DEFINED A GENERATION tells a story about community, courage and most importantly - music. (c) Official Site',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/85/11168586_mob.jpg'),(1305,'The Taste of Money',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_taste_of_money/','771307453','2106670',1,'In a mansion on the outskirts of Seoul lives one of South Korea\'s richest families. Although nominally headed by a prominent businessman, it\'s his wife Madame Baek who\'s really in control. Her personal secretary, a handsome young man newly introduced to the world of power, deals with the family\'s immoral-and frequently illegal-activities while he waits for his own opportunity to make it rich. But everything changes when an affair upsets the household\'s balance of power, and an unexpected arrest threatens to expose the family\'s tawdriest secrets. (c) IFC',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/85/11168596_mob.jpg'),(1306,'Walking With Dinosaurs 3D',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/walking_with_dinosaurs_3d/','771249781',NULL,1,'For the first time in movie history, audiences will truly see and feel what it was like when dinosaurs ruled the Earth. WALKING WITH DINOSAURS is the ultimate immersive experience, utilizing state of the art 3D to put audiences in the middle of a thrilling and epic prehistoric world, where an underdog dino triumphs to become a hero for the ages.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1307,'Delivery Man',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/delivery_man/','771320475','2387559',1,'From DreamWorks Pictures comes \"Delivery Man\", the story of affable underachiever David Wozniak, whose mundane life is turned upside down when he finds out that he fathered 533 children through sperm donations he made twenty years earlier. In debt to the mob, rejected by his pregnant girlfriend, things couldn\'t look worse for David when he is hit with a lawsuit from 142 of the 533 twenty-somethings who want to know the identity of the donor. As David struggles to decide whether or not he should reveal his true identity, he embarks on a journey that leads him to discover not only his true self but the father he could become as well. (c) Disney',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1308,'No Good Deed',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/no_good_deed_2013/','771271279',NULL,1,'Idris Elba stars as a cryptic man who\'s granted access into an ex-D.A.\'s house after posing as a broken down motorist in this home invasion thriller from director Sam Miller. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1309,'Die Hard Marathon',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/die_hard_marathon/','771324790',NULL,1,'Yipee-Ki-Yay, \"Die Hard\" movie fans - the celebrated action movie series is returning to the big screen for one day only, on Wednesday, February 13th. Attendees can catch the first four movies in the franchise - \"Die Hard,\" \"Die Hard 2,\" \"Die Hard with a Vengeance\" and \"Live Free or Die Hard\" - plus a special advance showing of the newest chapter, \"A Good Day to Die Hard\" - all for one low price.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1310,'Please Subscribe: A Documentary About Youtubers',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/please_subscribe_a_documentary_about_youtubers_2013/','771324525','2368182',1,'Please Subscribe is a documentary that explains the phenomenon of some of the most influential and unique content creators raising the bar on Youtube and for online media in general. Through a series of intimate narrative vignettes, the film explores the different journeys taken by some of the medium\'s top creators to get where they are today. The film focuses on one main question that is \"What makes a YouTuber?\" Ask anyone in the community and they will each provide a different answer. No one thing makes a YouTuber, but rather it\'s the journey these creators have taken to pave their own unique path.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1311,'Mumia: Long Distance Revolutionary',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mumia_long_distance_revolutionary/','771321115','2005276',1,'Before he was convicted of murdering a policeman in 1981 and sentenced to die, Mumia Abu-Jamal was a gifted journalist and brilliant writer. Now after more than 30 years in prison and despite attempts to silence him, Mumia is not only still alive but continuing to report, educate, provoke and inspire. (c) First Run',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/76/11167628_mob.jpg'),(1312,'Night Across the Street',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/night_across_the_street/','771307321','1876360',1,'On the verge of a forced retirement, Don Celso, an elderly office worker begins to relive both real and imagined memories from his life - a trip to the movies as a young boy with Beethoven, listening to tall tales from Long John Silver, a brief stay in a haunted hotel. Stories hide within stories and the thin line between imagination and reality steadily erodes, opening up a marvelous new world of personal remembrance and fantastic melodrama. In this playfully elegiac film, loosely adapted from the fantastical short stories of Chilean writer Hernan del Solar, Raul Ruiz (MYSTERIES OF LISBON) has crafted a final masterwork on his favorite subjects: fiction, history and life itself. (c) Cinema Guild',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168920_mob.jpg'),(1313,'Safe Haven: The Underground Railroad During The Vietnam War',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/safe_haven_the_underground_railroad_during_the_vietnam_war/','771243843',NULL,1,'A young woman escaping her past moves to a small North Carolina town and falls for a loving widowed father, he heals her heart, and helps her escape the danger that threatens her.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1314,'David',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/david_2013/','771325714','2358412',1,'The story revolves around the lives of 3 David\'s in 3 different parts of the world in 3 different eras. 1975 London - 30 year old David works for Iqbal Ghani, a dreaded Mafia don who controls the entire Asian community. He is a protege who is poised to take over the empire until a revelation which changes the course of his future. 1999 Mumbai - 19 year old David is a musician born into a family of devout Christians. A happy go lucky teenager who loses all semblance of his peaceful existence when his family gets dragged into a political issue. 2010 Goa - 40 year old David is a fisherman living in the small fishing village of Betul in Goa. He falls in love with the deaf and mute Roma - the only hitch is that she is engaged to be married to his best friend Peter in 10 days! All 3 David\'s are about to take a step which is going to change their lives forever. 3 lives, 3 destinies connected by 1 name - David. (c) Reliance Big Picture',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/90/11169045_mob.jpg'),(1315,'Sun Don\'t Shine',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sun_dont_shine/','771270482','2023714',1,'Written and directed by actress/filmmaker Amy Seimetz (Tiny Furniture, Upstream Color and Pit Stop), Sun Don\'t Shine follows Crystal (Kate Lyn Sheil) and her boyfriend Leo (Kentucker Audley) on a tense and mysterious road trip through the desolate yet hauntingly beautiful landscape of central Florida. From the outset, the purpose of their journey is unclear, and the motivations behind their heated altercations and shady errands are hazy, but sporadic moments of tenderness illuminate the loving bond between the two that exists underneath their overt tensions. As the couple travels up the Gulf Coast past an endless panorama of mangrove fields, trailer parks, and cookie-cutter housing developments, the disturbing details of their excursion gradually begin to emerge, revealing Crystal\'s sinister past and the couple\'s troubling future. Filmed on location in the environs of Seimetz\'s hometown of St. Petersburg, Florida, Sun Don\'t Shine is a subtly cryptic story driven by the powerful performances of its lead actors and its eerily poetic setting. (c) Factory25',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1316,'Wait Wait... Don\'t Tell Me! Live',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wait_wait_dont_tell_me_live/','771322101',NULL,1,'It\'s Wait Wait... Don\'t Tell Me! like you\'ve never seen it before! Because, well, normally you can\'t see it...it\'s a radio show. A live staging of Wait Wait... Don\'t Tell Me! presented by NCM Fathom Events, NPR, WBEZ-Chicago, and BY Experience, will be beamed to select cinemas across the country on Thursday, May 2nd, 2013. Host Peter Sagal and official judge and scorekeeper Carl Kasell will be joined by panelists Paula Poundstone, Mo Rocca and Tom Bodett to play the quiz in front of a live audience. Carl reading limericks! Celebrity guests answering stupid questions! Faces made for radio! You\'ve heard it in 1D, now see it live in glorious...2D.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1317,'Dreams',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dreams_2013/','771324835','1870375',1,'Mia dreams of singing, Quentin dreams of dancing, Paalo dreams of mending his relationship with his daughter and Alonzo dreams of reconnecting with his family. Though they all have dreams, fragments of abuse and failures from their broken past, make the trek up life\'s hills hard to climb. Set in an urban metropolitan, Chicago area, four different stories are weaved together in an unlikely manner. With notorious criminal and king of the hill, Donte, lurking in the shadows, what will become of our dreamers? Will they be impeded by life\'s difficulties or use these obstacles as stepping stones to achieving their dreams? (c) Official Site',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1318,'The Metropolitan Opera: Francesca Da Rimini',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_metropolitan_opera_francesca_da_rimini/','771304283',NULL,1,'Zandonai\'s compelling opera, inspired by an episode from Dante\'s Inferno, returns in the Met\'s ravishingly beautiful production, last seen in 1986. Dramatic soprano Eva-Maria Westbroek and tenor Marcello Giordani are the doomed lovers. Marco Armiliato conducts.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1319,'Star Trek Into Darkness Fan Sneaks IMAX 3D',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/star_trek_into_darkness_fan_sneaks_imax_3d/','771325815',NULL,1,'When the crew of the Enterprise is called back home, they find an unstoppable force of terror from within their own organization has detonated the fleet and everything it stands for, leaving our world in a state of crisis. With a personal score to settle, Captain Kirk leads a manhunt to a war-zone world to capture a one man weapon of mass destruction. As our heroes are propelled into an epic chess game of life and death, love will be challenged, friendships will be torn apart, and sacrifices must be made for the only family Kirk has left: his crew.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1320,'Dorfman in Love',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dorfman_in_love/','771272399','1665418',1,'Dorfman In Love tells the story of a young single suburbanite unknowingly trapped in her role as caretaker of her unappreciative family, who desperately needs to get her own life. When she volunteers to cat sit at her unrequited love\'s downtown L.A loft, her world, as she knows it, changes forever. In seven days, she meets another man who appreciates her and she not only transforms the mess of a loft but also transforms the mess of herself. Her journey of self-discovery leads her to find her true love. (C) Freestyle',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1321,'Deceptive Practice',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/deceptive_practice/','771322789',NULL,1,'Ricky Jay is a world-renowned magician, historian, collector of antiquarian books and artifacts, and actor (often a mischievous presence in the films of David Mamet and Paul Thomas Anderson) - and a performer who regularly provokes astonishment from even the most jaded audiences. DECEPTIVE PRACTICE traces Jay\'s achievements and influences, from his apprenticeship at age 4 with his grandfather, to such now-forgotten legends as Al Flosso, Slydini, Cardini (\"the best act I ever saw\") and his primary mentors, Dai Vernon and Charlie Miller. Featuring rare footage from his 1970s TV appearances (doing 3-card Monte with Steve Martin on The Dinah Shore Show) and told in Jay\'s inimitable voice, this is a remarkable journey inside the secretive world of magic and the small circle of eccentric geniuses who have mastered it. (c) Film Forum',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1322,'The Metropolitan Opera: Francesca Da Rimini Encore',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_metropolitan_opera_francesca_da_rimini_encore/','771310579',NULL,1,'Zandonai\'s compelling opera, inspired by an episode from Dante\'s Inferno, returns in the Met\'s ravishingly beautiful production, last seen in 1986. Dramatic soprano Eva-Maria Westbroek and tenor Marcello Giordani are the doomed lovers. Marco Armiliato conducts.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1323,'Wait Wait... Don\'t Tell Me! 2nd Showing',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wait_wait_dont_tell_me_2nd_showing/','771322100',NULL,1,'It\'s Wait Wait... Don\'t Tell Me! like you\'ve never seen it before! Because, well, normally you can\'t see it...it\'s a radio show. A live staging of Wait Wait... Don\'t Tell Me! presented by NCM Fathom Events, NPR, WBEZ-Chicago, and BY Experience, will be beamed to select cinemas across the country on Monday, May 7, 2013. Host Peter Sagal and official judge and scorekeeper Carl Kasell will be joined by panelists Paula Poundstone, Mo Rocca and Tom Bodett to play the quiz in front of a live audience. Carl reading limericks! Celebrity guests answering stupid questions! Faces made for radio! You\'ve heard it in 1D, now see it live in glorious...2D.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1324,'An Evening With Sol Leon And Paul Lightfoot: Netherlands Dans Theater',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/an_evening_with_sol_leon_and_paul_lightfoot_netherlands_dans_theater/','771322504',NULL,1,'Welcome to the world of the Netherlands Dans Theater\'s in-house choreographers Sol Leon and Paul Lightfoot. During this evening, they take you with them to their artistic universe. You can see the characteristic style of the successful Spanish-British choreographer duo in the humorous \"SH-Boom\", and enjoy the powerful theatrical \"Same Difference,\" set to music by Philip Glass. The closing performance of \"Shoot the Moon,\" also with the beautiful sounds of Glass, gives you a glimpse into the love lives of several characters.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1325,'Gran Teatre Del Liceu: IL Trovatore Encore',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/gran_teatre_del_liceu_il_trovatore_encore/','771322507',NULL,1,'Verdi\'s Il Trovatore is said to be a sure success - as long as you have the four best singers in the world singing it. This bold, modern production from the historic Barcelona opera house, the Gran Teatre del Liceu, certainly fits the bill! Fiorenza Cedolins, Marco Berti, Luciana D\'Intino and Vittorio Vitelli all shine in this operatic classic, which features the popular \"Anvil Chorus\" hit.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1326,'Notre-dame De Paris: La Scala',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/notre_dame_de_paris_la_scala/','771322516',NULL,1,'Notre-Dame de Paris, inspired by Victor Hugo\'s novel, with music by Maurice Jarre, sets by Rene Allio and the renowned costumes of Yves Saint-Laurent, returns to La Scala after more than ten years since its last performances. Once again it will be celebrating choreographer Roland Petit and the triumph of his vision of performance as a total creation: dance, sets, costumes, music, theatricality...with two of the international ballet world\'s brightest stars: Roberto Bolle and Natalia Osipova.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1327,'Da Thadiya',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/da_thadiya/','771323890',NULL,1,'The love story of an obese youth named Luke John Prakash. Luke comes from a wealthy family and is in love with a girl named Ann Mary Thadikkaran. The evolution of their relationship through various stages forms the crux of the story.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1328,'Once Every Day',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/once_every_day/','771325710',NULL,1,'Highly visual, complexly edited, and without a conventional narrative \'story\', ONCE EVERY DAY nevertheless circles a secret theme as it zeros in on a group of 25 people acting out a series of semi-ritualistic behavior patterns. But their eccentric impulses are aborted in unpredictable ways with each new attempt at action or development. As the film cuts between colored tableaus, bleached-out action sequences, expressionistic black-and-white confrontations, and slow immersion in pure light, we repeatedly hear the voices of the invisible director (Foreman) and his technicians, whispering off-camera instructions and comments to the characters - who are of course \'actors\' as well as disturbed and inhibited human beings. The implicit question of the film becomes: could this be life itself - visibly re-making itself as art? --(c) Anthology Archives',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(1329,'Dear John',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dear_john/','770795974','0989757',1,'Director Lasse Hallstrom and screenwriter Jamie Linden collaborate to adapt author Nicholas Sparks\' novel about a young soldier who falls for an idealistic college girl. Savannah Curtis (Amanda Seyfried) was on spring break when she first met John Tyree (Channing Tatum), who was home on temporary leave. For the smitten soldier it was practically love at first sight. Over the course of the next seven years, when each deployment seemed more treacherous than the last, the love letters that Savannah sent to John were one of the only things that kept him going. However, those loving and heartfelt correspondences would ultimately yield consequences that neither the brave soldier nor his one true love could have ever foreseen. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Built from many of the same ingredients as other Nicholas Sparks tearjerkers, Dear John suffers from its cliched framework, as well as Lasse Hallstrom\'s curiously detached directing.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/91/89/10918984_mob.jpg'),(1330,'The Final Destination',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/final_destination_final_death_trip_3D/','770685807','1144884',1,NULL,'With little of the ingenuity of previous installments, The Final Destination is predictable, disposable horror fare.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/93/73/10937376_mob.jpg'),(1331,'Dark Shadows',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dark-shadows-2010/','770783545','1077368',1,'Barnabas (Johnny Depp) has the world at his feet-or at least the town of Collinsport, Maine. The master of Collinwood Manor, Barnabas is rich, powerful and an inveterate playboy...until he makes the grave mistake of breaking the heart of Angelique Bouchard (Eva Green). A witch, in every sense of the word, Angelique dooms him to a fate worse than death: turning him into a vampire, and then burying him alive. Two centuries later, Barnabas is inadvertently freed from his tomb and emerges into the very changed world of 1972. He returns to Collinwood Manor to find that his once-grand estate has fallen into ruin. The dysfunctional remnants of the Collins family have fared little better, each harboring their own dark secrets. -- (C) Warner Bros.','The visuals are top notch but Tim Burton never finds a consistent rhythm, mixing campy jokes and gothic spookiness with less success than other Johnny Depp collaborations.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/66/11166608_mob.jpg'),(1332,'The Mummy: Tomb of the Dragon Emperor',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mummy_tomb_of_the_dragon_emperor/','770671522','0859163',1,NULL,'With middling CG effects and a distinct lack of fun, The Mummy: Tomb of the Dragon Emperor finds the series past its prime.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/87/58/10875846_mob.jpg'),(1333,'The Imaginarium of Doctor Parnassus',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1190561-imaginarium_of_doctor_parnassus/','770683433','1054606',1,NULL,'Terry Gilliam remains as indulgent as ever, but The Imaginarium of Doctor Parnassus represents a return to the intoxicatingly imaginative, darkly beautiful power of his earlier work, with fine performances to match all the visual spectacle.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/91/88/10918875_mob.jpg'),(1334,'The Departed',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/departed/','314387087','0407887',1,NULL,'Featuring outstanding work from an excellent cast that includes Jack Nicholson, Leonardo DiCaprio, and Matt Damon, The Departed is a thoroughly engrossing gangster drama with the gritty authenticity and soupy morality that has infused director Martin Scorsese\'s past triumphs.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/67/11166721_mob.jpg'),(1335,'Dr. Seuss\' Horton Hears a Who!',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/horton-hears-a-who2008/','770669822','0451079',1,NULL,'Horton Hears A Who! is both whimsical and heartwarming, and is the rare Dr. Seuss adaptation that stays true to the spirit of the source material.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/86/39/10863903_mob.jpg'),(1336,'Edge of Darkness',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/edge_of_darkness/','770797691','1226273',1,'Casino Royale\'s Martin Campbell returns to familiar territory with this adaptation of his own 1985 BBC miniseries -- a mystery starring Mel Gibson as a detective looking into his political-activist daughter\'s death and uncovering layers of governmental conspiracies in the process. William Monahan (The Departed) provides the screenplay for the GK Films production, co-starring Ray Winstone and Danny Huston. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi','For better and for worse, Edge of Darkness offers vintage Mel Gibson, working within the familiar framework of a bloody revenge thriller.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/13/31/11133139_mob.jpg'),(1337,'30 Days of Night',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/30_days_of_night/','512923951','0389722',1,NULL,'While 30 Days of Night offers a few thrills, it ultimately succumbs to erratic execution.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/18/32/10183253_mob.jpg'),(1338,'Valentine\'s Day',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/valentines_day_2010/','770805766','0817230',1,'Gary Marshall\'s ensemble romantic comedy Valentine\'s Day follows nearly two dozen people as they find and lose love in all its many forms over the course of the title holiday. The numerous characters include a very busy florist (Ashton Kutcher) and his schoolteacher best friend (Jennifer Garner). She\'s having an affair with a married doctor (Patrick Dempsey). Meanwhile, a businessman (Bradley Cooper) and a military captain (Julia Roberts) on leave share a long conversation during an international flight. There\'s also an elderly couple (Hector Elizondo and Shirley MacLaine) who are caring for their elementary school-age grandson, who is pining for a classmate and missing his mother. The huge cast also includes Jamie Foxx as a local TV personality, Topher Grace, Queen Latifah, and Anne Hathaway. ~ Perry Seibert, Rovi','Eager to please and stuffed with stars, Valentine\'s Day squanders its promise with a frantic, episodic plot and an abundance of rom-com cliches.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/12/75/11127550_mob.jpg'),(1339,'Dan in Real Life',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dan_in_real_life/','770674525','0480242',1,NULL,'The fine performances elevate Dan in Real Life beyond its sentimental plot.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/95/90/60/9590608_mob.jpg'),(1340,'Django Unchained',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/django_unchained_2012/','771245718','1853728',1,'Set in the South two years before the Civil War, Django Unchained stars Jamie Foxx as Django, a slave whose brutal history with his former owners lands him face-to-face with German-born bounty hunter Dr. King Schultz (Christoph Waltz). Schultz is on the trail of the murderous Brittle brothers, and only Django can lead him to his bounty. Honing vital hunting skills, Django remains focused on one goal: finding and rescuing Broomhilda (Kerry Washington), the wife he lost to the slave trade long ago. Django and Schultz\'s search ultimately leads them to Calvin Candie (Leonardo DiCaprio), the proprietor of \"Candyland,\" an infamous plantation. Exploring the compound under false pretenses, Django and Schultz arouse the suspicion of Stephen (Samuel L. Jackson), Candie\'s trusted house slave. -- (C) Weinstein','Bold, bloody, and stylistically daring, Django Unchained is another incendiary masterpiece from Quentin Tarantino.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/75/11167576_mob.jpg'),(1341,'You Don\'t Mess with the Zohan',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10008759-you_don\'t_mess_with_the_zohan/','770671938','0960144',1,NULL,'You Don\'t Mess With the Zohan features intermittent laughs, and will please Sandler diehards, but after awhile the leaky premise wears thin.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/86/19/10861952_mob.jpg'),(1342,'Alpha Dog',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/alpha_dog/','343353088','0426883',1,NULL,'A glossy yet unflinching portrait of violent, hedonistic teenagers. Bruce Willis and Sharon Stone chew the scenery, while Justin Timberlake gives a noteworthy performance.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/36/10883691_mob.jpg'),(1343,'Dreamgirls',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dreamgirls/','358047697','0443489',1,NULL,'Dreamgirls\' simple characters and plot hardly detract from the movie\'s real feats: the electrifying performances and the dazzling musical numbers.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168935_mob.jpg'),(1344,'John Tucker Must Die',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/john_tucker_must_die/','190816360','0455967',1,NULL,'This derivitive teen comedy tries to go for cute when it could use more bite.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/26/10872657_mob.jpg'),(1345,'The Devil Wears Prada',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_devil_wears_prada/','155655228','0458352',1,NULL,'A rare film that surpasses the quality of its source novel, this Devil is a witty expose of New York\'s fashion scene, with Meryl Streep in top form and Anne Hathaway more than holding her own.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/89/84/10898435_mob.jpg'),(1346,'Final Destination 3',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/final_destination_3/','19049941','0414982',1,NULL,'Final Destination 3 is more of the same: gory and pointless, with nowhere new to go.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/93/47/10934756_mob.jpg'),(1347,'500 Days of Summer',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/500_days_of_summer/','770801801','1022603',1,NULL,'A clever, offbeat romantic comedy, 500 Days of Summer is refreshingly honest and utterly charming.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/89/13/10891315_mob.jpg'),(1348,'Tenacious D in: The Pick of Destiny',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tenacious_d_in_the_pick_of_destiny/','314096471','0365830',1,NULL,'Tenacious D fan will find this movie hilarious; everybody else will see only a low-brow concept movie and a small assembly of jokes stretched past the 100 minute mark.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/28/07/61/2807614_mob.jpg'),(1349,'Did You Hear About the Morgans?',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1213718-did_you_hear_about_the_morgans/','770805258','1314228',1,NULL,'It gets a certain amount of mileage out of the inherent likability of its stars, but with an unfunny script and a lack of onscreen chemistry, Did You Hear About the Morgans? falls flat.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/92/05/10920552_mob.jpg'),(1350,'DOA: Dead or Alive',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/doa_dead_or_alive/','301427003','0398913',1,NULL,'With a ridiculous plot and comical acting, checking one\'s brain at the door is required before watching DOA: Dead or Alive.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/93/50/10935009_mob.jpg'),(1351,'Fun With Dick and Jane',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fun_with_dick_and_jane/','24466','0369441',1,NULL,'This muddled comedy has a few laughs, but never sustains a consistent tone.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/31/17/311794_mob.jpg'),(1352,'The Day the Earth Stood Still',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/day_the_earth_stood_still/','770675291','0970416',1,NULL,'Heavy on special effects, but without a coherent story at its base, The Day the Earth Stood Still is subpar re-imagining of the 1951 science-fiction classic.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/87/31/10873108_mob.jpg'),(1353,'27 Dresses',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/27_dresses/','770669912','0988595',1,NULL,'The filmmakers perfectly follow the well-worn romantic comedy formula, rendering 27 Dresses cliched and mostly forgettable.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/70/11/10701195_mob.jpg'),(1354,'Despicable Me',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1214097-despicable_me/','770805190','1323594',1,'A mysterious criminal mastermind has stolen one of the pyramids in Egypt, sparking a fit of jealous envy in evil genius Gru (Steve Carell), who hasn\'t managed to make headlines since he and his minions swiped the Times Square JumboTron years back. Ever since Gru was a little boy, he dreamed of going to the moon. Now, if Gru can just build a rocket and get his hands on a powerful shrink-ray, he can cement his reputation as the greatest thief who ever lived by stealing the Earth\'s satellite right out of the sky. But immediately after Gru heists the shrink-ray, the cunning super-nerd Vector (Jason Segel) swoops in and snatches it right out of his hands. Now, in order to claim the moon, Gru must first reacquire the weapon from Vector. Armed with the knowledge that his nemesis has a mean sweet tooth, Gru adopts cookie-selling orphans Margo (Miranda Cosgrove), Agnes (Elsie Fisher), and Edith (Dana Gaier) and commissions a new line of cookie robots from the evil Dr. Nefario (Russell Brand), his personal weapons specialist. But as Gru and his diminutive yellow minions prepare to carry out the biggest heist in history, something strange happens. Gru discovers that the three little girls who have come into his life are much more than simple pawns. They actually seem to care about Gru, and it turns out the scheming evildoer makes a pretty good father. When Gru realizes that his upcoming moon mission clashes with a ballet performance by the girls, he must decide what\'s more important -- being a present parent or cementing his nefarious reputation once and for all. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Borrowing heavily (and intelligently) from Pixar and Looney Tunes, Despicable Me is a surprisingly thoughtful, family-friendly treat with a few surprises of its own.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/88/11168864_mob.jpg'),(1355,'Duplicity',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/duplicity_2009/','770683997','1135487',1,NULL,'Duplicity is well-crafted, smart, and often funny, but it\'s mostly more cerebral than visceral and features far too many plot twists.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/94/10889485_mob.jpg'),(1356,'How to Train Your Dragon',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1194522-how_to_train_your_dragon/','770782733','0892769',1,'The son of a Viking chief must capture a dragon in order to mark his passage into manhood and prove his worthiness to the tribe in directors Chris Sanders and Dean DeBlois\' adaptation of Cressida Cowell\'s popular children\'s book. Gerard Butler, America Ferrera, Jonah Hill, Jay Baruchel, and Christopher Mintz-Plasse provide voices for the DreamWorks Animation production. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Boasting dazzling animation, a script with surprising dramatic depth, and thrilling 3-D sequences, How to Train Your Dragon soars.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/22/11152298_mob.jpg'),(1357,'The Fast and the Furious: Tokyo Drift',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fast_and_the_furious_tokyo_drift/','155655113','0463985',1,NULL,'Eye-popping driving sequences coupled with a limp story and flat performances make this Drift an adequate follow-up to the previous Fast and Furious installments. Strictly for the racing crowd and fans of the first two films.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/88/11168870_mob.jpg'),(1358,'Date Night',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/date_night/','770808107','1279935',1,'This action comedy tells the tale of mild-mannered married couple Phil (Steve Carell) and Claire (Tina Fey), who fear their relationship may be falling into a stale rut. During their weekly date night, they impetuously steal a dinner reservation, which leads to a case of mistaken identity. Turns out the reservation was for a pair of thieves, and now a number of unsavory characters want Phil and Claire killed. If they can survive a wacky life-threatening night, they may just rediscover the passion missing from their marriage. Directed by Shawn Levy, the film co-stars Mark Wahlberg, James Franco, and Kristen Wiig. ~ Perry Seibert, Rovi','An uneasy blend of action and comedy, Date Night doesn\'t quite live up to the talents of its two leads, but Steve Carell and Tina Fey still manage to shine through most of the movie\'s flaws.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/93/37/10933732_mob.jpg'),(1359,'Date Movie',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1155470-date_movie/','19049972','0466342',1,NULL,'In an attempt to parody rom-com cliches, Date Movie ultimately makes a mockery of itself, with juvenile toilet humor and empty pop culture references.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/31/27/312710_mob.jpg'),(1360,'Deja Vu',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/deja_vu/','387273864','0453467',1,NULL,'Tony Scott tries to combine action, science fiction, romance, and explosions into one movie, but the time travel conceit might be too preposterous and the action falls apart under scrutiny.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/32/89/62/3289629_mob.jpg'),(1361,'You, Me and Dupree',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/you_me_and_dupree/','190815618','0463034',1,NULL,'A rather generic entry into the arrested development subgenre, with themes borrowed from other more successful and funnier films. Dupree wears out its welcome.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/17/61/33/1761334_mob.jpg'),(1362,'Defiance',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10009458-defiance/','770682436','1034303',1,NULL,'Professionally made but artistically uninspired, Ed Zwick\'s story of Jews surviving WWII in the Belarus forest lacks the emotional punch of the actual history.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/87/76/10877622_mob.jpg'),(1363,'Napoleon Dynamite',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/napoleon_dynamite/','10007','0374900',1,NULL,'A charming, quirky, and often funny comedy.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/92/76/10927695_mob.jpg'),(1364,'Death Race',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/death_race/','770671911','0452608',1,NULL,'Mindless, violent, and lightning-paced, Death Race is little more than an empty action romp.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/81/10888107_mob.jpg'),(1365,'Dance Flick',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dance_flick/','770799335','1153706',1,NULL,'Dance Flick scores a few laughs thanks to the Wayans brothers\' exuberance, but it\'s ultimately a scattershot collection of gags without much direction.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/92/12/10921279_mob.jpg'),(1366,'The Dictator',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_dictator_2012/','771219982','1645170',1,'The heroic story of a North African dictator who risks his life to ensure that democracy would never come to the country he so lovingly oppressed. -- (C) Paramount','Wildly uneven but consistently provocative, The Dictator is a decent entry in the poli-slapstick comedy genre.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168933_mob.jpg'),(1367,'Old Dogs',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10009596-old_dogs/','770785550','0976238',1,NULL,'Its cast tries hard, but Old Dogs is a predictable, nearly witless attempt at physical comedy and moral uplift that misses the mark on both counts.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/92/71/10927146_mob.jpg'),(1368,'Dredd',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dredd/','771207918','1343727',1,'The future America is an irradiated waste land. On its East Coast, running from Boston to Washington DC, lies Mega City One- a vast, violent metropolis where criminals rule the chaotic streets. The only force of order lies with the urban cops called \"Judges\" who possess the combined powers of judge, jury and instant executioner. Known and feared throughout the city, Dredd (Karl Urban) is the ultimate Judge, challenged with ridding the city of its latest scourge - a dangerous drug epidemic that has users of \"Slo-Mo\" experiencing reality at a fraction of its normal speed. -- (C) Lionsgate','Fueled by bombastic violence and impressive special effects, rooted in self-satire and deadpan humor, Dredd 3D is a rare example of a remake that actually works.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/82/11168284_mob.jpg'),(1369,'Die Hard',1988,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/die_hard/','16351','0095016',1,NULL,'Its many imitators (and sequels) have never come close to matching the taut thrills of the definitive holiday action classic.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/47/11164776_mob.jpg'),(1370,'Knight & Day',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/knight_and_day/','770820013','1013743',1,'A single girl en route to a family wedding gets swept up in a fight between a rogue government agent and the FBI in this globe-trotting action comedy from director James Mangold (Walk the Line, 3:10 to Yuma). June Havens (Cameron Diaz) is preparing to board a flight back home for her sister\'s wedding when she literally bumps into Roy Miller (Tom Cruise) in the middle of a busy airport. A few minutes later, they\'re making small talk on the plane when June excuses herself to the bathroom, and all hell breaks loose in the fuselage. By the time June emerges Roy has killed everybody on board, including the pilots. After crash-landing the plane in a darkened cornfield, Roy tells June that she should expect a visit from government agents, but warns her that by cooperating with them she risks almost certain death. The following day, Roy\'s prediction comes true when June is confronted by an imposing gang of government spooks who come under heavy fire while bombarding her with questions about her mysterious traveling companion. Suddenly, Roy is back, and he\'s once again whisking June away to safety. But what do the agents want, and why do they insist that Roy is the one to be feared, and not them? Before long the girl who never traveled far from home is off on a wild adventure that will take her from the tropics to Austria, France, and Spain. Somewhere amidst all of the confusion and gunfire, June begins to forge a bond with Roy. Unfortunately, it\'s never quite clear whether her unpredictable protector is one of the good guys or the bad guys, and by the time Roy reveals that he\'s attempting to protect a valuable new energy source, there\'s no time for questions. Paul Dano, Viola Davis, Peter Sarsgaard, Maggie Grace, and Marc Blucas co-star. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','It\'s pure formula, but thanks to its breezy pace and a pair of charming performances from Tom Cruise and Cameron Diaz, Knight and Day offers some agreeably middle-of-the-road summer action.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/14/43/11144395_mob.jpg'),(1371,'The Girl Next Door',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1130343-girl_next_door/','14679','0265208',1,NULL,'The movie borrows heavily from Risky Business, though Hirsch and Cuthbert are appealing leads.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/12/56/11125663_mob.jpg'),(1372,'The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_girl_with_the_dragon_tattoo/','771202144','1568346',1,'The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo is the first film in Columbia Pictures\' three-picture adaptation of Stieg Larsson\'s literary blockbuster The Millennium Trilogy. Directed by David Fincher and starring Daniel Craig and Rooney Mara, the film is based on the first novel in the trilogy, which altogether have sold 50 million copies in 46 countries and become a worldwide phenomenon. -- (C) Sony','Brutal yet captivating, The Girl With the Dragon Tattoo is the result of David Fincher working at his lurid best with total role commitment from star Rooney Mara.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/39/11163974_mob.jpg'),(1373,'28 Days Later',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/28_days_later/','14347','0289043',1,NULL,'28 Days Later is both a terrifying zombie movie and a sharp political allegory.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/55/37/32/5537323_mob.jpg'),(1374,'Dr Seuss\' The Lorax',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_lorax/','771193269','1482459',1,'The 3D-CGI feature Dr. Seuss\' The Lorax is an adaptation of Dr. Seuss\' classic tale of a forest creature who shares the enduring power of hope. The animated adventure follows the journey of a boy as he searches for the one thing that will enable him to win the affection of the girl of his dreams. To find it he must discover the story of the Lorax, the grumpy yet charming creature who fights to protect his world. -- (C) Universal','Dr. Seuss\' The Lorax is cute and funny enough but the moral simplicity of the book gets lost with the zany Hollywood production values.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/74/11167427_mob.jpg'),(1375,'Transformers: Dark of the Moon',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/transformers_dark_of_the_moon/','771223136','1399103',1,'Shia LaBeouf returns as Sam Witwicky in Transformers: Dark of the Moon. When a mysterious event from Earth\'s past erupts into the present day it threatens to bring a war to Earth so big that the Transformers alone will not be able to save us. -- (C) Paramount','Its special effects -- and 3D shots -- are undeniably impressive, but they aren\'t enough to fill up its loud, bloated running time, or mask its thin, indifferent script.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/91/11169150_mob.jpg'),(1376,'Shaun of the Dead',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shaun_of_the_dead/','12873','0365748',1,NULL,'Shaun of the Dead cleverly balances scares and witty satire, making for a bloody good zombie movie with loads of wit.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/99/21/86/9921865_mob.jpg'),(1377,'Dodgeball - A True Underdog Story',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dodgeball_a_true_underdog_story/','16981','0364725',1,NULL,'Proudly profane and splendidly silly, Dodgeball is a worthy spiritual successor to the goofball comedies of the 1980s.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/94/04/10940443_mob.jpg'),(1378,'Daredevil',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/daredevil/','11118','0287978',1,NULL,'Passable if derivative as entertainment, Ben Affleck fits the role but the film is not up to par with recent superhero films.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/50/11165002_mob.jpg'),(1379,'Earth (Disneynature\'s Earth) (Planet Earth)',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1197228-earth/','770672740','0393597',1,NULL,'With its spectacular and extensive footage, Earth is both informative and entertaining.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/92/40/10924053_mob.jpg'),(1380,'The Tale of Despereaux',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tale_of_despereaux/','770682016','0420238',1,NULL,'Despite its striking visuals, The Tale of Despereaux as a story feels familiar and unimaginative.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/87/41/10874160_mob.jpg'),(1381,'Terminator 2: Judgment Day',1991,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/terminator_2_judgment_day/','14016','0103064',1,NULL,'T2 features thrilling action sequences and eye-popping visual effects, but what takes this sci-fi/ action landmark to the next level is the depth of the human (and cyborg) characters.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/94/47/10944701_mob.jpg'),(1382,'Dead Silence',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dead_silence/','562878940','0455760',1,NULL,'More tasteful than recent slasher flicks, but Dead Silence is undone by boring characters, bland dialogue, and an unnecessary and obvious twist ending.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/92/35/10923568_mob.jpg'),(1383,'The Seeker: The Dark Is Rising',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/seeker_the_dark_is_rising/','770676133',NULL,1,NULL,'The magic of the book is lost in translation with The Seeker, due to its clumsy plot and lack of heart.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/87/47/10874735_mob.jpg'),(1384,'How to Lose a Guy in 10 Days',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/how_to_lose_a_guy_in_10_days/','10435','0251127',1,NULL,'Good premise, dull execution.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168947_mob.jpg'),(1385,'Daddy\'s Little Girls',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/daddys_little_girls/','462957579','0778661',1,NULL,'Daddy\'s Little Girls boasts fine performances and a poignant message, but is ultimately let down by amateurish filmmaking.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/66/10876637_mob.jpg'),(1386,'Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom',1984,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/indiana_jones_and_the_temple_of_doom/','23530','0087469',1,NULL,'It may be too \"dark\" for some, but Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom remains an ingenious adventure spectacle that showcases one of Hollywood\'s finest filmmaking teams in vintage form.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/92/11/10921138_mob.jpg'),(1387,'Doubt',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/doubt/','770771570','0918927',1,NULL,'Doubt succeeds on the strength of its top-notch cast, who successfully guide the film through the occasional narrative lull.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/40/10884051_mob.jpg'),(1388,'Dawn of the Dead',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dawn_of_the_dead/','17051','0363547',1,NULL,'A kinetic, violent and surprisingly worthy remake of George Romero\'s horror classic that pays homage to the original while working on its own terms.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/28/60/286018_mob.jpg'),(1389,'40 Days and 40 Nights',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/40_days_and_40_nights/','13850','0243736',1,NULL,'As romantic comedies go, 40 Days and 40 Nights is smutty, sexist, and puerile.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/27/17/271796_mob.jpg'),(1390,'Due Date',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/due-date/','770814359','1231583',1,'Director Todd Phillips re-teams with his break-out Hangover star Zach Galifianakis for this road movie concerning a soon-to-be father (played by Robert Downey Jr.) and his cross-country trip to make it back in time for his baby\'s birth -- with the only roadblock being the dubious passenger (Galifianakis) who\'s along for the ride. Michelle Monaghan and Jamie Foxx co-star in the Warner Bros./Legendary Pictures production. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi','Shamelessly derivative and only sporadically funny, Due Date doesn\'t live up to the possibilities suggested by its talented director and marvelously mismatched stars.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/67/11166722_mob.jpg'),(1391,'Get Rich or Die Tryin\'',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/get_rich_or_die_tryin/','9175','0430308',1,NULL,'While it may be based upon 50 Cent\'s own life experiences, Get Rich Or Die Tryin\' is too similar to many other rags-to-riches stories to resonate.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/05/250501_mob.jpg'),(1392,'Definitely, Maybe',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1174278-definitely_maybe/','770674772','0832266',1,NULL,'With a clever script and charismatic leads, Definitely, Maybe is a refreshing entry into the romantic comedy genre.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/83/81/10838102_mob.jpg'),(1393,'Are We Done Yet?',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/are_we_done_yet/','462989368','0422774',1,NULL,'Are We Done Yet? plays it way too safe with generic slapstick and uninspired domestic foibles.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/63/32/95/6332952_mob.jpg'),(1394,'Requiem for a Dream',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/requiem_for_a_dream/','17949','0180093',1,NULL,'Though the movie may be too intense for some to stomach, the wonderful performances and the bleak imagery are hard to forget.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/29/00/290095_mob.jpg'),(1395,'Dragon Wars',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dragon_wars/','770675215','0372873',1,NULL,'Dragon Wars\' special effects can\'t make up for an unfocused script and stale acting.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/21/10892161_mob.jpg'),(1396,'Meet Dave',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/meet_dave/','770728557','0765476',1,NULL,'Easy gags and slack direction drag this occasionally clever alien-out-of-planet comedy down to unimaginative lows.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/86/17/10861791_mob.jpg'),(1397,'The Nanny Diaries',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nanny_diaries/','630695026',NULL,1,NULL,'The Nanny Diaries\' miscast lead and unrealistic, one-dimensional characters make this class satire far less effective than it should\'ve been.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/80/10878037_mob.jpg'),(1398,'House of Flying Daggers',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/house_of_flying_daggers/','10034','0385004',1,NULL,'The visual splendor of the movie makes up for the weak story.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/89/29/10892903_mob.jpg'),(1399,'Nancy Drew',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nancy_drew/','475364640','0479500',1,NULL,'Emma Roberts is bubbly and charming as Nancy Drew, the junior detective. But despite her best efforts, Nancy Drew still lacks excitement, surprise, and compelling secondary characters.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/42/46/30/4246302_mob.jpg'),(1400,'Domino',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/domino/','8760','0097224',1,NULL,'The life story of model-turned- bounty-hunter Domino Harvey struggles to get out of this overwrought and excessive biopic.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/03/250313_mob.jpg'),(1401,'Taxi Driver',1976,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/taxi_driver/','16625','0075314',1,NULL,'A must-see film for movie lovers, this Martin Scorsese masterpiece is as hard-hitting as it is compelling, with Robert De Niro at his best.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/78/11157877_mob.jpg'),(1402,'Mr. Deeds',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mr_deeds/','11234','0280590',1,NULL,'This update of Capra doesn\'t hold a candle to the original, and even on its own merits, Mr. Deeds is still indifferently acted and stale.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/97/259704_mob.jpg'),(1403,'Driving Lessons',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1167633-driving_lessons/','247553502','0446687',1,NULL,'Though it has charm, Driving Lessons is a middling offering in the genre where the youngster coming of age meets a quirky senior who teaches valuable lessons about life.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/86/17/10861778_mob.jpg'),(1404,'Diary of a Wimpy Kid',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/diary_of_a_wimpy_kid/','770808106','1196141',1,'Hapless preteen Greg Heffley (Zachary Gordon) endures bullies, swirlies, morons, and wedgies while navigating the treacherous world of middle school and recording his traumas in his personal journal in this family-oriented comedy inspired by author Jeff Kinney\'s best-selling series of illustrated novels. Try as he might, Greg just can\'t understand who thought it was a good idea to place kids who haven\'t even hit their first growth spurt in the same school as kids who get a five-o\'clock shadow by lunch time. Realizing that he\'ll have to get creative if he hopes to survive until high school, Greg concocts a series of get-cool-quick schemes that all go hopelessly awry. Despite the fact that he\'s viewed as a dork by his peers, Greg never loses hope that someday, when all is said and done, he\'ll be able to look back on his middle school experiences and laugh. Steve Zahn and Rachael Harris co-star in this comedy from Hotel for Dogs director Thor Freudenthal. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Unlike its bestselling source material, Diary of a Wimpy Kid fails to place a likable protagonist at the center of its middle-school humor -- and its underlying message is drowned out as a result.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/95/36/10953698_mob.jpg'),(1405,'Kung Fu Panda 2',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kung_fu_panda_the_kaboom_of_doom/','770805426','1302011',1,'In Kung Fu Panda 2, Po is now living his dream as The Dragon Warrior, protecting the Valley of Peace alongside his friends and fellow kung fu masters, The Furious Five. But Po\'s new life of awesomeness is threatened by the emergence of a formidable villain, who plans to use a secret, unstoppable weapon to conquer China and destroy kung fu. Po must look to his past and uncover the secrets of his mysterious origins; only then will he be able to unlock the strength he needs to succeed. -- (C) Dreamworks','The storyline arc may seem a tad familiar to fans of the original, but Kung Fu Panda 2 offers enough action, comedy, and visual sparkle to compensate.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/66/11156693_mob.jpg'),(1406,'Dinner for Schmucks',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dinner_for_schmucks/','770807431','0427152',1,'An ambitious executive accepts an invitation from his boss to attend a dinner party where high-powered professionals make fun of unsuspecting dimwits in this remake of Francis Veber\'s 1998 comedy The Dinner Game. Upwardly mobile executive Tim (Paul Rudd) has just landed his company an extremely wealthy Swiss client when his boss, Lance (Bruce Greenwood), invites him to an exclusive, yet unusually mean-spirited dinner party where each of the high-powered executives brings a guest to make fun of. Recognizing that his long-awaited promotion is finally within reach, Tim begins to have second thoughts about participating in the elaborate charade when his longtime girlfriend, Julie (Stephanie Szostak), the successful curator at a local art gallery, voices intense disdain for the idea. The following day, Tim is looking for a way out of the dinner when fate throws the perfect guest right in front of his luxury car. Barry (Steve Carell) is a sweet but dim-witted IRS agent with an unusual hobby: he creates elaborate dioramas featuring stuffed mice. His latest project is \"The Last Supper,\" and he\'s just put the finishing touches on a tiny mouse Jesus to set at the center of the table. Tim knows that Barry is his ticket to a big corner office on the seventh floor, but the closer the party looms, the more he realizes that his bumbling new acquaintance isn\'t just an idiot, but also is a magnet for chaos. ~ Rovi','It doesn\'t honor its source material -- or its immensely likable leads -- as well as it should, but Dinner for Schmucks offers fitfully nourishing comedy.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/95/55/10955547_mob.jpg'),(1407,'Independence Day',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1071806-independence_day/','11591','0116629',1,NULL,'The plot is thin and so is character development, but as a thrilling, spectacle-filled summer movie, Independence Day delivers.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/47/11164744_mob.jpg'),(1408,'Die Another Day',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/die_another_day/','10530','0246460',1,NULL,'Its action may be bit too over-the-top for some, but Die Another Day is lavishly crafted and succeeds in evoking classic Bond themes from the franchise\'s earlier installments.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/93/34/10933478_mob.jpg'),(1409,'Dumb and Dumber',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dumb_and_dumber/','10194','0109686',1,NULL,'A relentlessly stupid comedy elevated by its main actors: Jim Carrey goes bonkers and Jeff Daniels carries himself admirably in an against-type performance.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/45/254516_mob.jpg'),(1410,'Final Destination 2',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/final_destination_2/','13166','0309593',1,NULL,'This sequel is little more than an excuse to stage elaborate, gory scenes of characters getting killed off.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/35/84/22/3584220_mob.jpg'),(1411,'Final Destination',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/final_destination/','13223','0195714',1,NULL,'Despite a panel of X-Files\' alums at the helm and a promising premise, flighty performances and poor execution keep Final Destination from ever taking off.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/87/268708_mob.jpg'),(1412,'Doomsday',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/doomsday/','770673000','0483607',1,NULL,'Doomsday is a pale imitation of previous futuristic thrillers, minus the cohesive narrative and charismatic leads.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/88/11168865_mob.jpg'),(1413,'The Descent',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/descent/','75557905','0435625',1,NULL,'Deft direction and strong performances from its all-female cast guide The Descent, a riveting, claustrophobic horror film. In this low-budget import from Scotland, director Neil Marshall has masterfully created a spelunking nightmare, which doubles as a compelling meditation on morality, vengeance, and the depths to which we might go for survival.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/14/69/11146933_mob.jpg'),(1414,'Aladdin',1992,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1042582-aladdin/','9383',NULL,1,NULL,'A highly entertaining entry in Disney\'s \"second golden age,\" Aladdin is beautifully drawn, with near-classic songs and a cast of scene-stealing characters.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/93/64/10936428_mob.jpg'),(1415,'Dawn of the Dead',1978,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1005339-dawn_of_the_dead/','13306','0077402',1,NULL,'One of the most compelling and entertaining zombie films ever, Dawn of the Dead perfectly blends pure horror and gore with social commentary on bourgeois society.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/38/11153820_mob.jpg'),(1416,'Death at a Funeral',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/death_at_a_funeral_2010/','770805752','1321509',1,'Frank Oz\'s 2007 black comedy Death at a Funeral is given the remake treatment with an urban spin in this Chris Rock-produced production. When a dysfunctional clan reuintes to mourn the passing of the family patriarch, a respectful funeral quickly turns into an all-out fiasco marked by bitter resentment, blackmail attempts, and scandalous revelations. Dean Craig penned the script for director Neil LaBute (The Wicker Man), with Martin Lawrence, Tracy Morgan, and Danny Glover co-starring. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi','It\'s amusing and it assembles a talented cast, but Neil LaBute\'s surprisingly faithful remake of the 2007 Frank Oz dramedy ultimately falls short of the original.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/12/18/11121845_mob.jpg'),(1417,'The Dukes of Hazzard',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dukes_of_hazzard/','1971','0377818',1,NULL,'A dumb, goofy, and vacuous adaptation of a TV show where plot is simply an excuse to string together the car chases.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/45/11164565_mob.jpg'),(1418,'Derailed',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/derailed/','9177','0398017',1,NULL,'With miscast stars, a ludicrous plot and an obvious twist, Derailed embodies its name all too aptly.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/05/250504_mob.jpg'),(1419,'Queen of the Damned',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/queen_of_the_damned/','13541','0238546',1,NULL,'A muddled and campy MTV-styled vampire movie with lots of eye candy and bad accents.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/91/48/10914808_mob.jpg'),(1420,'Rescue Dawn',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/rescue_dawn/','573372752','0462504',1,NULL,'Director Werner Herzog has once again made a compelling tale of man v.s nature, and Christian Bale completely immerses himself in the role.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/87/30/52/8730522_mob.jpg'),(1421,'Kiki\'s Delivery Service',1989,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kikis_delivery_service/','9447','0280835',1,NULL,'Kiki\'s Delivery Service is a heartwarming, gorgeously-rendered tale of a young witch discovering her place in the world.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/94/88/10948823_mob.jpg'),(1422,'Dogma',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dogma/','13107','0120655',1,NULL,'Provocative and audacious, Dogma is an uneven but thoughtful religious satire that\'s both respectful and irreverent.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/26/81/268119_mob.jpg'),(1423,'Oceans (Disneynature\'s Oceans)',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10011268-oceans/','770805763','0765128',1,NULL,'Oceans adds another visually stunning chapter to the Disney Nature library.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/04/79/11047971_mob.jpg'),(1424,'Doom',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/doom/','8839','0419706',1,NULL,'Sure to please fans of the video game, but lacking in plot and originality to please other moviegoers.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/03/250391_mob.jpg'),(1425,'Training Day',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/training_day/','12997','0139654',1,NULL,'The ending may be less than satisfying, but Denzel Washington reminds us why he\'s such a great actor in this taut and brutal police drama.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/91/83/10918353_mob.jpg'),(1426,'Hotel for Dogs',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hotel_for_dogs/','770682080','0785006',1,NULL,'Hotel for Dogs may appeal to children and dog lovers, but it\'s ultimately contrived, predictable, and simplistic.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/39/11153917_mob.jpg'),(1427,'The Spy Next Door',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spy_next_door/','770807290','1273678',1,'Reminiscent of Kindergarten Cop, with a dash of Spy Kids, The Spy Next Door blends together an entertaining mixture of family fun and martial-arts comedy styling to form a familiar story that once again reminds us that even hardened action heroes have a soft side. Jackie Chan stars as Bob Ho, an international spy on loan to the CIA who gives up his job in hopes of leading a so-called normal life with his next-door-neighbor girlfriend and her rambunctious brood. There\'s nothing in Spy that the audience hasn\'t seen before from similarly themed incarnations (think The Pacifier), but, fans will appreciate director Brian Levant\'s homage to Jackie Chan\'s past Hong Kong movie blockbusters -- most notably, Police Story and The Legend of Drunken Master -- during the opening credit sequence, which is fitting considering many of the action sequences are derivative of those films.The main story centers on Bob\'s relationship with artsy single mom Gillian (Amber Valletta) and her three kids: precocious teenage stepdaughter Farren (Madeline Carroll), nerdy middle child Ian (Will Shadley), and adorably energetic Nora (Alina Foley). After an emergency sends Gillian away to Denver, Bob steps up and offers to watch the kids while she\'s gone. Ill-equipped to handle a situation that\'s clearly over his head, Bob utilizes his spy skills and gadgets -- video watch, GPS tracking, x-ray glasses -- to gain control over the situation in hopes of winning over the kid\'s affection, but when an old enemy escapes from prison and threatens his potential family, Bob must return to his 007 world of international espionage to protect them.Admittedly, there\'s a certain level of cheese in this film, especially when it comes to the Boris-and-Natasha-style villains, Poldark (Magnus Scheving) and Creel (Katherine Boecher), whose silly Russian stereotyped performances and running joke about American fashion unabashedly border on cringe-worthy territory. Not to mention, the thinly plotted storyline involving brainiac Ian, who accidentally downloads a top-secret formula for oil-eating ooze created by the bad guys, which propels the main action of the film. Adding to the pile are the supporting cast members: George Lopez as the traitorous CIA agent, Glaze, and Billy Ray Cyrus as CIA agent and Bob\'s BFF Colton James, who lends folksy witticisms like \"As gone as rum cake at an AA meeting.\"Even so, Chan\'s charm wins out in the end, and The Spy Next Door\'s most effective sequences involve Bob\'s attempts to bond with the kids -- from taking little Nora shopping for a Halloween costume to helping Ian with school bullies and girls. These comedic moments more or less overshadow an otherwise simplistic narrative, and the audience can\'t help but smile to themselves every time Chan appears onscreen. Die-hard fans might miss the era of classic kick-ass Hong Kong action films, but Spy manages to fill that void as an entertaining alternative that kids and parents alike will enjoy. ~ Alaina O\'Connor, Rovi','Lacking a script funny enough to cover up for Jackie Chan\'s fading physical gifts, The Spy Next Door fails on every conceivable level.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/92/77/10927764_mob.jpg'),(1428,'Drive',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/drive_2011/','771224338','0780504',1,'Ryan Gosling stars as a Los Angeles wheelman for hire, stunt driving for movie productions by day and steering getaway vehicles for armed heists by night. Though a loner by nature, Driver can\'t help falling in love with his beautiful neighbor Irene (Carey Mulligan), a vulnerable young mother dragged into a dangerous underworld by the return of her ex-convict husband Standard (Oscar Isaac). After a heist intended to pay off Standard\'s protection money spins unpredictably out of control, Driver finds himself driving defense for the girl he loves, tailgated by a syndicate of deadly serious criminals. But when he realizes that the gangsters are after more than the bag of cash in his trunk-that they\'re coming straight for Irene and her son-Driver is forced to shift gears and go on offense. -- (C) FilmDistrict','A hyper-stylized blend of striking imagery and violence, Drive represents a fully realized vision of arthouse action.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/36/11163653_mob.jpg'),(1429,'Death Sentence',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/death_sentence/','770672423','0804461',1,NULL,'A nonsensical plot and an absurd amount of violence make this revenge pic gratuitous and overwrought.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/91/47/09/9147092_mob.jpg'),(1430,'The Darjeeling Limited',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/darjeeling_limited/','770670652','0838221',1,NULL,'With the requisite combination of humor, sorrow and outstanding visuals, The Darjeeling Limited will satisfy Wes Anderson fans.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/95/78/33/9578332_mob.jpg'),(1431,'The Great Debaters',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/great_debaters/','770679318',NULL,1,NULL,'A wonderful cast and top-notch script elevate The Great Debaters beyond a familiar formula for a touching, uplifting drama.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/70/08/10700830_mob.jpg'),(1432,'The Rum Diary',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/The-Rum-Diary/','770768030','0376136',1,'Based on the debut novel by Hunter S. Thompson. Tiring of the noise and madness of New York and the crushing conventions of late Eisenhower-era America, Paul Kemp (Johnny Depp) travels to the pristine island of Puerto Rico to write for a local newspaper, run by downtrodden editor Lotterman (Richard Jenkins). Adopting the rum-soaked life of the island, Paul soon becomes obsessed with Chenault (Amber Heard), the wildly attractive Connecticut-born fiancee of Sanderson (Aaron Eckhart). Sanderson is one of a growing number of American entrepreneurs who are determined to convert Puerto Rico into a capitalist paradise in service of the wealthy. When Kemp is recruited by Sanderson to write favorably about his latest unsavory scheme, the journalist is presented with a choice: to use his words for the corrupt businessmen\'s financial benefit, or use them to take the bastards down. -- (C) FilmDistrict','It\'s colorful and amiable enough, and Depp\'s heart is clearly in the right place, but The Rum Diary fails to add sufficient focus to its rambling source material.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/10/11161094_mob.jpg'),(1433,'Next Day Air',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/next_day_air/','770802045','1097013',1,NULL,'Rife with half-baked jokes and excessive violence, Next Day Air is an uninspired stoner comedy.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/87/64/10876428_mob.jpg'),(1434,'Delta Farce',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/delta_farce/','544060052','0800003',1,NULL,'Too afraid to be a real satire of the Iraq War, Delta Farce instead devolves into a reprehensible, unfunny mix of slapstick, gay panic, and flatulence jokes.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/75/10887545_mob.jpg'),(1435,'Diary of a Wimpy Kid: Dog Days',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/diary_of_a_wimpy_kid_dog_days/','771251499','2023453',1,'During his summer vacation, \"Wimpy Kid\" Greg Heffley, the hero of the phenomenally successful book series, hatches a plan to pretend he has a job at a ritzy country club - which fails to keep him away from the season\'s dog days, including embarrassing mishaps at a public pool and a camping trip that goes horribly wrong. -- (C) 20th Century Fox','Overly familiar and a bit too reliant on slapstick, the sitcom-like Dog Days fails to improve upon previous installments and will likely appeal to few outside its target audience.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/79/11167902_mob.jpg'),(1436,'Dirty Dancing - Havana Nights',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/havana_nights/','10470','0338096',1,NULL,'Cheesy, unnecessary remake.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/91/46/10914657_mob.jpg'),(1437,'Dark Water',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dark_water/','1968','0382628',1,NULL,'All the atmospherics in Dark Water can\'t make up for the lack of genuine scares.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/12/84/11128476_mob.jpg'),(1438,'Disaster Movie',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/disaster_movie/','770768860','1213644',1,NULL,'Returning to their seemingly bottomless well of flatulence humor, racial stereotypes, and stale pop culture gags, Friedberg and Seltzer have produced what is arguably their worst Movie yet.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/73/10877361_mob.jpg'),(1439,'Tyler Perry\'s Good Deeds',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tyler_perrys_good_deeds/','771243948','1885265',1,'A successful, wealthy businessman, Wesley Deeds (Tyler Perry) has always done what\'s expected of him, whether it\'s assuming the helm of his father\'s company, tolerating his brother\'s misbehavior at the office or planning to marry his beautiful but restless fiancee, Natalie (Gabrielle Union). But Wesley is jolted out of his predictable routine when he meets Lindsey (Thandie Newton), a down-on-her-luck single mother who works on the cleaning crew in his office building. When he offers to help her get back on her feet, the chance encounter with someone so far outside his usual circle ignites something in Wesley. This one good deed may finally spark his courage to exchange the life that\'s expected of him for the life he\'s always really wanted. -- (C) Lionsgate','Tyler Perry\'s craftmanship as a director continues to improve, but his stories are still the same ol\' hoary, pretentious melodramas.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/13/11161340_mob.jpg'),(1440,'The Shaggy Dog',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shaggy_dog/','93101407','0393735',1,NULL,'This Disney retread has neither inspiration nor originality, but may please moviegoers under the age of ten.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/89/84/10898411_mob.jpg'),(1441,'Dorian Gray',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1200873-dorian_gray/','770785505','1235124',1,NULL,'Despite a lavish and polished production, Dorian Gray is tame and uninspired with a lifeless performance by Ben Barnes in the title role.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/35/11153562_mob.jpg'),(1442,'Red Dragon',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/red_dragon/','13084','0289765',1,NULL,'Competently made, but everything is a bit too familiar.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/80/268012_mob.jpg'),(1443,'Dead Poets Society',1989,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dead_poets_society/','10138','0097165',1,NULL,'Affecting performances from the young cast and a genuinely inspirational turn from Robin Williams grant Peter Weir\'s college drama top honors.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/58/40/10584083_mob.jpg'),(1444,'Limitless',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/limitless/','771036677','1219289',1,'Aspiring author Eddie Morra (Cooper) is suffering from chronic writer\'s block, but his life changes instantly when an old friend introduces him to NZT, a revolutionary new pharmaceutical that allows him to tap his full potential. Soon Eddie takes Wall Street by storm, parlaying a small stake into millions. His accomplishments catch the eye of mega-mogul Carl Van Loon (De Niro),who invites him to help broker the largest merger in corporate history. But they also bring Eddie to the attention of people willing to do anything to get their hands on his stash of NZT. With his life in jeopardy and the drug\'s brutal side effects grinding him down, Eddie dodges mysterious stalkers, a vicious gangster and an intense police investigation as he attempts to hang on to his dwindling supply long enough to outwit his enemies.-- (C) Relativity','Although its script is uneven, Neil Burger directs Limitless with plenty of visual panache, and Bradley Cooper makes for a charismatic star.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/61/11156184_mob.jpg'),(1445,'From Dusk Till Dawn',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/from_dusk_till_dawn/','12984','0116367',1,NULL,'A pulpy crime drama/vampire film hybrid, From Dusk Till Dawn is an uneven but often deliriously enjoyable B-movie.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/62/82/01/6282011_mob.jpg'),(1446,'Why Did I Get Married Too',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/why_did_i_get_married_too/','770805268','1391137',1,'This sequel to Tyler Perry\'s Why Did I Get Married reunites the cast from that earlier movie, again playing a group of eight friends who take an annual week-long vacation with each other. As they reconnect, Sheila (Jill Scott) discovers that her ex-husband, Mike, is planning to wreck her new marriage. Their troubles lead to the others facing some uncomfortable truths about their own relationships. The film co-stars Janet Jackson, Malik Yoba, Michael Jai White, and Louis Gossett Jr. ~ Perry Seibert, Rovi','It\'s bolstered by a strong performance from Janet Jackson, but ultimately, Tyler Perry\'s Why Did I Get Married Too? doesn\'t add anything new to Perry\'s melodramatic formula.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/12/14/11121415_mob.jpg'),(1447,'Deception',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10009724-deception/','770680663','0800240',1,NULL,'Deception is a middling, predictable potboiler with mediocre dialogue and ludicrous plot twists.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/62/10876257_mob.jpg'),(1448,'The Descendants',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_descendants_2011/','771236985','1033575',1,'From Alexander Payne, the creator of the Oscar-winning Sideways, set in Hawaii, The Descendants is a sometimes humorous, sometimes tragic journey for Matt King (George Clooney) an indifferent husband and father of two girls, who is forced to re-examine his past and embrace his future when his wife suffers a boating accident off of Waikiki. The event leads to a rapprochement with his young daughters while Matt wrestles with a decision to sell the family\'s land handed down from Hawaiian royalty and missionaries. -- (C) Fox Searchlight','Funny, moving, and beautifully acted, The Descendants captures the unpredictable messiness of life with eloquence and uncommon grace.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/77/11157747_mob.jpg'),(1449,'The Princess Diaries 2 - Royal Engagement',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/princess_diaries_2_royal_engagement/','9454','0368933',1,NULL,'Anne Hathaway and Julie Andrews bring charm and elegance to the movie, but there\'s not enough material for them to work with in this sequel.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/28/11152832_mob.jpg'),(1450,'A Scanner Darkly',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/scanner_darkly/','190815509','0405296',1,NULL,'A faithful adaptation of Philip K. Dick\'s novel, A Scanner Darkly takes the viewer on a visual and mind-blowing journey into the author\'s conception of a drug-addled and politically unstable world.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/84/10898442_mob.jpg'),(1451,'Red Dawn',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/red_dawn_2012/','770820295','1234719',1,'In Red Dawn, a city in Washington state awakens to the surreal sight of foreign paratroopers dropping from the sky - shockingly, the U.S. has been invaded and their hometown is the initial target. Quickly and without warning, the citizens find themselves prisoners and their town under enemy occupation. Determined to fight back, a group of young patriots seek refuge in the surrounding woods, training and reorganizing themselves into a guerrilla group of fighters. Taking inspiration from their high school mascot, they call themselves the Wolverines, banding together to protect one another, liberate their town from its captors, and take back their freedom. -- (C) Official Site','The rebooted Red Dawn lacks the original\'s topicality, but at least pays tribute in delivering the same short shrift to character development and general logic.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/82/11168296_mob.jpg'),(1452,'In the Name of the King: A Dungeon Siege Tale',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/in-the-name-of-the-king-a-dungeon-siege-tale/','770670801','0460780',1,NULL,'Featuring mostly wooden performances, laughable dialogue, and shoddy production values, In the Name of the King fulfills all expectations of an Uwe Boll film.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/48/11164835_mob.jpg'),(1453,'Drillbit Taylor',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/drillbit_taylor/','770674040','0817538',1,NULL,'Owen Wilson\'s charms can\'t save Drillbit Taylor, an unfunny, overly familiar bullied-teen comedy.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/84/11/10841187_mob.jpg'),(1454,'Mulholland Drive',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mulholland_dr/','12960','0166924',1,NULL,'Mulholland Drive makes little sense, even for a Lynch film, but its dreamlike imagery is mesmerizing, and Watts delivers a great performance.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/74/267404_mob.jpg'),(1455,'28 Days',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/28_days/','10914','0191754',1,NULL,'Even though 28 Days is tackling a difficult subject, it comes off light and superficial, and maybe even a little preachy.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/85/04/10850487_mob.jpg'),(1456,'Must Love Dogs',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/must_love_dogs/','2118','0417001',1,NULL,'Despite good work from its likable leads, the romantic comedy Must Love Dogs is too predictable.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/87/23/10872352_mob.jpg'),(1457,'Sex Drive',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sex_drive/','770680691','1135985',1,NULL,'Sex Drive has some hilarious moments and is well made for a raunchy teen film, but will appeal to few beyond that demographic.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/87/99/10879900_mob.jpg'),(1458,'Sleep Dealer',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sleep_dealer/','770682569','0804529',1,NULL,'Sleep Dealer\'s depth and energy are almost enough to overcome a shaky screenplay and pedestrian acting.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/25/10892545_mob.jpg'),(1459,'The Duchess',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10009493-duchess/','770680512','0864761',1,NULL,'While The Duchess treads the now-familiar terrain of the corset-ripper, the costumes look great and Keira Knightley\'s performance is stellar in this subtly feminist, period drama.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/85/97/10859746_mob.jpg'),(1460,'American Dreamz',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/american_dreamz/','150164931','0465142',1,NULL,'This overly silly satire aims at too many targets with arrows too dull to make relevant social commentary.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/31/40/314020_mob.jpg'),(1461,'The Devil\'s Advocate',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/devils_advocate/','22536','0118971',1,NULL,'Though it is ultimately somewhat undone by its own lofty ambitions, The Devil\'s Advocate is a mostly effective blend of supernatural thrills and character exploration.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/83/07/830796_mob.jpg'),(1462,'Miss Pettigrew Lives for a Day',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/miss_pettigrew_lives_for_a_day/','770674707','0970468',1,NULL,'Miss Pettigrew is a breezy period comedy carried by the strong performances of Amy Adams and Frances McDormand.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/83/87/10838710_mob.jpg'),(1463,'The Water Horse: Legend of the Deep',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/water_horse/','770671492',NULL,1,NULL,'The Water Horse is a fine family film. It takes a classic tale and infuses it with extra imagination, sly humor, heart, and inventive special effects.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/89/68/67/8968672_mob.jpg'),(1464,'Love and Other Drugs',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/love-and-other-drugs/','770856056','0758752',1,'Handsome and charming pharmaceutical rep Jamie (Jake Gyllenhaal) falls head over heels for radiant free spirit Maggie (Anne Hathaway), and together the two people who never thought they would fall in love discover that their intense chemistry is more powerful than any drug on the market. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','It\'s a pleasure to see Hollywood produce a romance this refreshingly adult, but Love and Other Drugs struggles to find a balance between its disparate plot elements.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/28/11152817_mob.jpg'),(1465,'Joe Dirt',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/joe_dirt/','10877','0245686',1,NULL,'If you fall within the target audience of Joe Dirt, you may find it funny. Otherwise, the jokes will seem like a tired retread.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/79/257912_mob.jpg'),(1466,'The Dilemma',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_dilemma/','771041141','1578275',1,'Vince Vaughn and Kevin James headline an all-star comedy from director Ron Howard and producer Brian Grazer about a man who finds out that what you don\'t say to a friend is just as important as what you do. Jennifer Connelly, Winona Ryder, Channing Tatum and Queen Latifah join them in The Dilemma, a story of how far you can bend a brotherly bond before it snaps. Since college, confirmed bachelor Ronny (Vaughn) and happily married Nick (James) have been through thick and thin. Now partners in an auto design firm, the two pals are vying to land a dream project that would launch their company. With Ronny\'s girlfriend, Beth (Connelly), and Nick\'s wife, Geneva (Ryder), by their sides, they\'re unbeatable. But Ronny\'s world is turned upside down when he inadvertently sees Geneva out with another man and makes it his mission to get answers. As the amateur investigation dissolves his world into comic mayhem, he learns that Nick has a few secrets of his own. Now, with the clock ticking and pressure mounting on the biggest presentation of their careers, Ronny must decide how and when he will reveal the truth to his best friend. -- (C) Universal','It boasts a likable cast and an interesting premise, but The Dilemma can\'t decide what to do with them; the result is an uneven blend of cheesy slapstick and surprisingly dark comedy.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/50/11155059_mob.jpg'),(1467,'Punch-Drunk Love',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/punchdrunk_love/','13508','0272338',1,NULL,'Odd, touching, and unique, Punch-Drunk Love is also delightfully funny, utilizing Adam Sandler\'s comic persona to explore the life of a lonely guy who finds love.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/27/01/270105_mob.jpg'),(1468,'I Still Know What You Did Last Summer',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/i_still_know_what_you_did_last_summer/','14749','0130018',1,NULL,'Boring; predictable.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/02/10890281_mob.jpg'),(1469,'Evil Dead 2',1987,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/evil-dead-2/','98831005','0092991',1,NULL,'Evil Dead 2\'s increased special effects and slapstick-gore makes it as good -- if not better -- than the original.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/51/02/510275_mob.jpg'),(1470,'The Evil Dead',1981,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the-evil-dead/','16969','0083907',1,NULL,'This classic low budget horror film combines just the right amount of gore and black humor, giving The Evil Dead an equal amount of thrills and laughs.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/75/11167510_mob.jpg'),(1471,'Around the World in 80 Days',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/around_the_world_in_80_days/','11425','0327437',1,NULL,'Hit-and-miss family fare that bares only the slightest resemblance to Verne\'s novel.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/14/86/11148613_mob.jpg'),(1472,'The Deer Hunter',1978,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/deer_hunter/','12994','0077416',1,NULL,'Its greatness is blunted by its length and one-sided point of view, but the film\'s weaknesses are overpowered by Michael Cimino\'s sympathetic direction and a series of heartbreaking performances from Robert De Niro, Meryl Streep, and Christopher Walken.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/75/267592_mob.jpg'),(1473,'Dances With Wolves',1990,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dances_with_wolves/','12772','0099348',1,NULL,'A grand, sweeping epic with inarguably noble intentions and arresting cinematography, but one whose center, arguably, is not as weighty as it should be.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/81/11168108_mob.jpg'),(1474,'Dreamcatcher',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dreamcatcher/','13790','0285531',1,NULL,'An incoherent and overly long creature feature.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/27/14/271497_mob.jpg'),(1475,'Marmaduke',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/marmaduke/','770814362','1392197',1,'When advertising exec Phil Winslow (Lee Pace) gets an offer to head the account for a California-based dog-food company, he uproots his wife (($Judy Greer}), three kids, and their beloved Great Dane, Marmaduke (voiced by Owen Wilson), from Kansas to the Sunshine State. Once there, the big canine befriends a group of mutts at the local dog park, but after a surfing competition brings Marmaduke celebrity, he turns his back on his new pals. Eventually, a disaster helps the oversized hound and Phil learn about the importance of family and friendship. ~ Perry Seibert, Rovi','Dull and unfunny, Marmaduke offers family filmgoers little more than another round of talking animals and scatological humor.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/17/11151743_mob.jpg'),(1476,'Going the Distance',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10012042-going_the_distance/','770808364','1322312',1,'Erin\'s (Drew Barrymore) wry wit and unfiltered frankness charm newly single Garrett (Justin Long) over beer, bar trivia and breakfast the next morning. Their chemistry sparks a full-fledged summer fling, but neither expects it to last once Erin heads home to San Francisco and Garrett stays behind for his job in New York City. But when six weeks of romping through the city inadvertently become meaningful, neither is sure they want it to end. And while Garrett\'s friends Box (Jason Sudeikis) and Dan (Charlie Day) joke about his pre-flight calorie-cutting and his full-time relationship with his cell phone, they don\'t like losing their best drinking buddy to yet another rocky romance. At the same time, Erin\'s high-strung, overprotective married sister, Corinne (Christina Applegate), wants to keep Erin from heading down an all-too-familiar road. But despite the opposite coasts, the nay-saying friends and family, and a few unexpected temptations, the couple just might have found something like love, and with the help of a lot of texting, sexting and late-night phone calls, they might actually go the distance.-- (C) Warner Bros','It\'s timelier and a little more honest than most romantic comedies, but Drew Barrymore and Justin Long\'s screen chemistry doesn\'t make up for Going the Distance\'s overall flatness.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/14/76/11147668_mob.jpg'),(1477,'The Wedding Date',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wedding_date/','10051','0372532',1,NULL,'Critics are leaving The Wedding Date at the alter, calling it shopworn, bland, and lightweight.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/89/24/10892423_mob.jpg'),(1478,'Our Family Wedding',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/our_family_wedding/','770816443','1305583',1,'Forest Whitaker and Carlos Mencia headline this culture-clash comedy centered on the conflict between two headstrong fathers whose children are about to be married. With just two weeks to go before the big day, the disagreeable dads struggle to put aside their differences long enough to plan the perfect wedding. America Ferrera, Regina King, and Fred Armisen co-star. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Our Family Wedding is a mirthless, contrived affair that does little with its promising premise and talented cast.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/95/38/10953867_mob.jpg'),(1479,'102 Dalmatians',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/102_dalmatians/','9606','0211181',1,NULL,'This sequel to the live-action 101 Dalmatians is simply more of the same. Critics say it also drags in parts, potentially boring children, and that it\'s too violent for a G-rated movie.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/86/73/10867358_mob.jpg'),(1480,'The Devil\'s Rejects',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/devils_rejects/','2133','0395584',1,NULL,'Zombie has improved as a filmmaker since \"House of 1000 Corpses\" and will please fans of the genre, but beware -- the horror is nasty, relentless, and sadistic.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/24/99/249905_mob.jpg'),(1481,'Dolphin Tale',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dolphin_tale/','771205892','1564349',1,'Dolphin Tale is inspired by the amazing true story of a brave dolphin and the compassionate strangers who banded together to save her life. Swimming free, a young dolphin is caught in a crab trap, severely damaging her tail. She is rescued and transported to the Clearwater Marine Hospital, where she is named Winter. But her fight for survival has just begun. Without a tail, Winter\'s prognosis is dire. It will take the expertise of a dedicated marine biologist, the ingenuity of a brilliant prosthetics doctor, and the unwavering devotion of a young boy to bring about a groundbreaking miracle-a miracle that might not only save Winter but could also help scores of people around the world. -- (C) Warner Bros','Wisely dialing down the schmaltz, Dolphin Tale is earnest, sweet, and well-told, a rare family film that both kids and parents can enjoy.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/36/11163667_mob.jpg'),(1482,'101 Dalmatians',1961,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/101_dalmatians/','9417','0055254',1,NULL,'With plenty of pooches and a memorable villain (Cruella De Vil), this is one of Disney\'s most enduring, entertaining animated films.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/53/11155339_mob.jpg'),(1483,'Lords of Dogtown',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lords_of_dogtown/','671','0355702',1,NULL,'Lords of Dogtown, while slickly made and edited, lacks the depth and entertaining value of the far superior documentary on the same subject, Dogtown and Z-Boys.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/55/36/80/5536806_mob.jpg'),(1484,'Night of the Living Dead',1968,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1015052-night_of_the_living_dead/','50375489','0063350',1,NULL,'George A. Romero\'s debut set the template for the zombie film, and features tight editing, realistic gore, and a sly political undercurrent.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/38/11153823_mob.jpg'),(1485,'Downfall (Der Untergang)',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/downfall/','12853',NULL,1,NULL,'Downfall is an illuminating, thoughtful and detailed account of Hitler\'s last days.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/89/40/10894056_mob.jpg'),(1486,'The Princess Diaries',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/princess_diaries/','9627','0247638',1,NULL,'A charming, if familiar, makeover movie for young teenage girls.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/44/10894429_mob.jpg'),(1487,'Final Destination 5',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/final_destination_5/','771202196','1622979',1,'In Final Destination 5, Death is just as omnipresent as ever, and is unleashed after one man\'s premonition saves a group of coworkers from a terrifying suspension bridge collapse. But this group of unsuspecting souls was never supposed to survive, and, in a terrifying race against time, the ill-fated group frantically tries to discover a way to escape Death\'s sinister agenda. -- (C) Warner Bros','It\'s still only for the gore-thirsty faithful, but Final Destination 5 represents a surprising return to form for the franchise.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/36/11163668_mob.jpg'),(1488,'Devil',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/771203480/','771203480',NULL,1,'Five strangers trapped in an elevator realize that one of them is the Devil in this thriller from director John E. Dowdle (Quarantine) and screenwriter Brian Nelson (Hard Candy, 30 Days of Night). The first installment of \"The Night Chronicles,\" a film series in which up-and-coming filmmakers bring to life stories conceived by M. Night Shyamalan, Devil opens to find five Philadelphia office workers filing into the elevator of an inner-city office building. But a typical day at the office takes a sudden detour into terror when the elevator becomes stuck between floors, and the passengers discover that the Devil does exist, and he\'s standing right before them. As emergency workers work frantically to free them, secrets are revealed and the passengers realize their only hope for survival is to confront their darkest sins in front of the others. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','It\'s better than many of the other films M. Night Shyamalan has been associated with, but Devil never gets more than a few low-budget thrills out of its fiendishly promising premise.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/53/11155329_mob.jpg'),(1489,'One Day',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/771206468/','771206468','1563738',1,'After one day together - July 15th, 1988, their college graduation - Emma Morley (Anne Hathaway) and Dexter Mayhew (Jim Sturgess) begin a friendship that will last a lifetime. She is a working-class girl of principle and ambition who dreams of making the world a better place. He is a wealthy charmer who dreams that the world will be his playground. For the next two decades, key moments of their relationship are experienced over several July 15ths in their lives. Together and apart, we see Dex and Em through their friendship and fights, hopes and missed opportunities, laughter and tears. Somewhere along their journey, these two people realize that what they are searching and hoping for has been there for them all along. As the true meaning of that one day back in 1988 is revealed, they come to terms with the nature of love and life itself. -- (C) Focus Features','Despite some fresh narrative twists, One Day lacks the emotion, depth, or insight of its bestselling source material.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/57/11155740_mob.jpg'),(1490,'Shall We Dance',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shall_we_dance/','10228','0358135',1,NULL,'The cast is warmly appealing, but with the loss of cultural context and addition of big-name celebrities, this American version loses the nuances of the original.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/84/66/10846607_mob.jpg'),(1491,'The Darkest Hour',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_darkest_hour/','771204356','1093357',1,'The Darkest Hour is the story of five young people who find themselves stranded in Moscow, fighting to survive in the wake of a devastating alien attack. The 3D thriller highlights the classic beauty of Moscow alongside mind-blowing special effects. -- (C) Summit',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/13/11161345_mob.jpg'),(1492,'The Devil Inside',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_devil_inside/','771240536','1560985',1,'In 1989, emergency responders received a 9-1-1 call from Maria Rossi (Suzan Crowley) confessing that she had brutally killed three people. 20 years later, her daughter Isabella (Fernanda Andrade) seeks to understand the truth about what happened that night. She travels to the Centrino Hospital for the Criminally Insane in Italy where her mother has been locked away to determine if her mother is mentally ill or demonically possessed. When she recruits two young exorcists (Simon Quarterman and Evan Helmuth) to cure her mom using unconventional methods combining both science and religion, they come face-to-face with pure evil in the form of four powerful demons possessing Maria. Many have been possessed by one; only one has been possessed by many. -- (C) Paramount Insurge','The Devil Inside is a cheap, choppy unscary mess, featuring one of the worst endings in recent memory.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168932_mob.jpg'),(1493,'The Next Three Days',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/next_three_days/','770873457','1458175',1,'His wife convicted of a murder she swears she did not commit, a college professor plots to break her out of prison in this thriller starring Russell Crowe and Liam Neeson. John Brennan (Crowe) and his wife, Lara (Elizabeth Banks), were happily married and raising a family when their lives fell apart in the blink of an eye. Lara has been charged with murder, and despite every effort to prove her innocence, the judge sentences her to an extended prison sentence. Meanwhile, on the outside, John files multiple appeals while struggling to raise their children and maintain his career. Lara\'s future starts to look especially grim, however, after the final appeal is rejected, and she admits that she\'d rather commit suicide than spend the rest of her life behind bars. Determined to save his wife after the justice system fails her, John seeks the advice of ex-convict Damon Pennington (Liam Neeson), who staged his own daring prison escape, in order to draw up an airtight plan. Later, John prepares to put his life on the line for the woman he loves, and sets the plan into motion with the knowledge that one false move could be their last. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Russell Crowe and Elizabeth Banks give it their all, but their solid performances aren\'t quite enough to compensate for The Next Three Days\' uneven pace and implausible plot.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/27/11152771_mob.jpg'),(1494,'The Pirates Who Don\'t Do Anything: A VeggieTales Movie',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pirates_who_dont_do_anything_a_veggietales_movie/','770670770','0475998',1,NULL,'This Veggietale should please the youngest crowds, but the silly script will tire the more discerning viewer.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/80/70/10807062_mob.jpg'),(1495,'Night Watch (Nochnoi Dozor)',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1148279-night_watch/','19049986','0403358',1,NULL,'This Russian horror/fantasy film pits darkness and light against each other using snazzy CGI visuals to create an extraordinary atmosphere of a dank, gloomy city wrestling with dread.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/22/60/07/2260074_mob.jpg'),(1496,'The House of the Devil',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/house_of_the_devil/','770806327','1172994',1,NULL,'Though its underlying themes are familiar, House of the Devil effectively sheds the loud and gory cliches of contemporary horror to deliver a tense, slowly building throwback to the fright flicks of decades past.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/89/54/10895415_mob.jpg'),(1497,'Land of the Dead',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/land_of_the_dead/','1785','0418819',1,NULL,'George A. Romero\'s latest entry in his much-vaunted Dead series is not as fresh as his genre-inventing original, Night of the Living Dead. But Land of the Dead does deliver on the gore and zombies-feasting-on-flesh action.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/24/98/249809_mob.jpg'),(1498,'Let the Right One In',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/let_the_right_one_in/','770687125','1139797',1,NULL,'Let the Right One In reinvigorates the seemingly tired vampire genre by effectively mixing scares with intelligent storytelling.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/92/37/10923703_mob.jpg'),(1499,'Dumb and Dumberer: When Harry Met Lloyd',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dumb_and_dumberer_when_harry_met_lloyd/','11624','0329028',1,NULL,'This lame prequel induces more groans than laughs. Rent the original instead.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/55/35/64/5535640_mob.jpg'),(1500,'Drumline',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/drumline/','10577','0303933',1,NULL,'Essentially a sports movie with drums, the energetic Drumline somehow manages to make the familiar seem fresh.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/48/11164851_mob.jpg'),(1501,'Firehouse Dog',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/firehouse_dog/','486314988','0476995',1,NULL,'Firehouse Dog\'s cute premise is ruined with endless fart and poop jokes, and an overlong run time.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/49/98/28/4998280_mob.jpg'),(1502,'Waist Deep',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/waist_deep/','155655200','0456020',1,NULL,'A well-meaning B-movie that suffers from a cliche-ridden script and poorly drawn characters that fail to inspire much sympathy.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/45/20/452090_mob.jpg'),(1503,'Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs',1937,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1048445-snow_white_and_the_seven_dwarfs/','9380',NULL,1,NULL,'With its involving story and characters, vibrant art, and memorable songs, Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs set the animation standard for decades to come.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/91/50/10915008_mob.jpg'),(1504,'Double Jeopardy',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1093614-double_jeopardy/','13437','0150377',1,NULL,'A talented cast fails to save this unremarkable thriller.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/97/269724_mob.jpg'),(1505,'Dumbo',1941,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dumbo/','9384','0033563',1,NULL,'Dumbo packs plenty of story into its brief runtime, along with all the warm animation and wonderful music you\'d expect from a Disney classic.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/53/11155336_mob.jpg'),(1506,'Dr. Dolittle 2',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dr_dolittle_2/','11120','0240462',1,NULL,'Although there are laughs to be had in Dr. Dolittle 2, its preoccupation with toilet humor and Murphy\'s restrained performance makes this a missed opportunity.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/47/11164721_mob.jpg'),(1507,'Romeo Must Die',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/romeo_must_die/','13447','0165929',1,NULL,'In his second Hollywood movie, Jet Li impresses. Unfortunately, when he\'s not on screen, the movie slows to a crawl. Though there\'s some spark between Jet and Aaliyah, there isn\'t any threat of a fire. And as impressive as the action sequences are, some critics feel they are over-edited.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/26/98/269803_mob.jpg'),(1508,'How Do You Know',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/how_do_you_know/','771201460','1341188',1,'Director James L. Brooks returns to the helm for this ensemble comedy starring Reese Witherspoon, Jack Nicholson, Paul Rudd, and Owen Wilson, which centers on the story of a passionate athlete who finds herself romantically torn between a narcissistic baseball star and a straight-laced businessman. As far back as Lisa (Witherspoon) can remember, her life has been defined by sports. Then, in the blink of an eye, she\'s cut from the team. With her identity in crisis as she attempts to regain her footing in life, Lisa begins dating Matty (Wilson), a Major League Baseball pitcher and notorious womanizer. Meanwhile, terminally honest businessman George (Rudd) finds himself on the road to financial ruin or worse after being wrongly implicated in a financial crime. As George struggles to clear his name and reconcile his turbulent relationship with his father, Charles (Nicholson), a chance meeting with Lisa at the lowest point in both of their lives leaves him optimistic that things may work out after all. Meanwhile, Lisa and George both realize that the only thing that\'s certain about the future is that we never know what fate has in store for us. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','How Do You Know boasts a quartet of likeable leads -- and they deserve better than this glib, overlong misfire from writer/director James L. Brooks.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/41/11154128_mob.jpg'),(1509,'Dr. No',1962,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dr_no/','10684','0055928',1,NULL,'Featuring plenty of the humor, action, and escapist thrills the series would become known for, Dr. No kicks off the Bond franchise in style.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/69/256991_mob.jpg'),(1510,'Mou gaan dou (Infernal Affairs)',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/infernal_affairs/','13489','0338564',1,NULL,'Smart and engrossing, this is one of Hong Kong\'s better cop thrillers.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/55/33/32/5533327_mob.jpg'),(1511,'The Debt',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1211195-debt/','770815579','1226753',1,'The espionage thriller begins in 1997, as shocking news reaches retired Mossad secret agents Rachel (Helen Mirren) and Stephan (Tom Wilkinson) about their former colleague David (Ciaran Hinds). All three have been venerated for decades by their country because of the mission that they undertook back in 1966, when the trio (portrayed, respectively, by Jessica Chastain, Marton Csokas, and Sam Worthington tracked down Nazi war criminal Vogel (Jesper Christensen) in East Berlin. At great risk, and at considerable personal cost, the team\'s mission was accomplished - or was it? The suspense builds in and across two different time periods, with startling action and surprising revelations. -- (C) Focus','Its time-shifting narrative creates distracting casting problems, but ultimately, The Debt is a smart, well-acted entry in a genre that could use more like it.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/75/11157527_mob.jpg'),(1512,'For a Few Dollars More (Per Qualche Dollaro in Piu)',1965,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/for_a_few_dollars_more/','60565656','0059578',1,NULL,'With Clint Eastwood in the lead, Ennio Morricone on the score, and Sergio Leone\'s stylish direction, For a Few Dollars More earns its recognition as a genre classic.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/15/95/75/1595754_mob.jpg'),(1513,'The Damned United',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/damned_united/','770802240','1226271',1,NULL,'Better than your average football pic, Damned United is carried by another star turn from Michael Sheen as Brian Clough.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/07/11150731_mob.jpg'),(1514,'Tomorrow Never Dies',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tomorrow_never_dies/','11715','0120347',1,NULL,'A competent, if sometimes by-the-numbers entry to the 007 franchise, Tomorrow Never Dies may not boast the most original plot but its action sequences are genuinely thrilling.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/91/35/10913520_mob.jpg'),(1515,'The Motorcycle Diaries (Diarios de Motocicleta)',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/motorcycle_diaries/','12867','0318462',1,NULL,'The Motorcycle Diaries is heartfelt and profound in its rendering of the formative experiences that turn Ernesto \"Che\" Guerva into a famous revolutionary.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/94/15/10941510_mob.jpg'),(1516,'World\'s Greatest Dad',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1213731-worlds_greatest_dad/','770802334','1262981',1,NULL,'World\'s Greatest Dad is a risky, deadpan, dark comedy that effectively explores the nature of posthumous cults of celebrity.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/31/10883147_mob.jpg'),(1517,'A Fistful of Dollars (Per un Pugno di Dollari)',1964,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fistful_of_dollars/','13370','0058461',1,NULL,'With Akira Kurosawa\'s Yojimbo as his template, Sergio Leone\'s A Fistful of Dollars helped define a new era for the Western and usher in its most iconic star, Clint Eastwood.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/94/269416_mob.jpg'),(1518,'Day Watch',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/day_watch/','271509844','0409904',1,NULL,'Day Watch is frequently cheesy but it offers enough twists, surprises, and inventive action sequences to maintain viewer interest.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/48/11164821_mob.jpg'),(1519,'Death at a Funeral',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/death_at_a_funeral/','770669823',NULL,1,NULL,'Death At A Funeral is a rousing British farce, with enough slapstick silliness to overcome its faults.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/92/77/10927714_mob.jpg'),(1520,'The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_girl_with_the_dragon_tattoo_2009/','770798724','1132620',1,NULL,'Its graphic violence and sprawling length will prove too much for some viewers to take, but Noomi Rapace\'s gripping performance makes The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo an unforgettable viewing experience.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/12/17/11121773_mob.jpg'),(1521,'I Hate Valentine\'s Day',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/i_hate_valentines_day/','770806884','0762105',1,NULL,'This boilerplate comedy lacks ingenuity or humor and features mediocre dialogue that sounds less like conversation and more like stand-up shtick.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/12/75/11127560_mob.jpg'),(1522,'Drive Angry',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/drive-angry/','770858012','1502404',1,'Nicolas Cage headlines this high-octane thriller as Milton, a hard-case felon who breaks out of Hell to prevent the cult that murdered his daughter from sacrificing his infant granddaughter to Satan on the night of the full moon. With just three days to go before the ritual killing, Milton crosses paths with knockout waitress Piper (Amber Heard), who steals her cheating ex-boyfriend\'s vintage Charger and joins him on his quest to save the Earth from the forces of darkness. With Piper\'s help and a mean set of wheels to keep them moving, they may have a shot at taking down diabolical cult leader Jonah King (Billy Burke) before he achieves his malevolent goal. But should Jonah get the opportunity to make his dark sacrifice, he will become the most powerful man alive and all of humanity will suffer. Unfortunately for Milton, the cops are quickly closing in, and the Devil\'s determined minion, \"The Accountant\" (William Fichtner), will stop at nothing to drag him back down to Hell. With each passing minute, Milton\'s last shot at redemption is fading, and the fate of the entire world inches ever closer to infernal darkness. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','It may deliver the over-the-top action pieces, but Drive Angry prefers to work safely within grindhouse formula than do something truly unique.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/37/11153713_mob.jpg'),(1523,'Dream House',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dream_house_2011/','771204354','1462041',1,'Successful publisher Will Atenton (Daniel Craig) quit a job in New York City to relocate his wife, Libby (Rachel Weisz), and two girls to a quaint New England town. But as they settle into their new life, they discover their perfect home was the murder scene of a mother and her children. And the entire city believes it was at the hands of the husband who survived. When Will investigates the tragedy, his only lead comes from Ann Paterson (Naomi Watts), a neighbor who was close to the family that died. As Will and Ann piece together the disturbing puzzle, they discover that the story of the last man to leave Will\'s dream house will be just as horrifying to the one who came next. -- (C) Universal Pictures','Dream House is punishingly slow, stuffy, and way too obvious to be scary.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/36/11163637_mob.jpg'),(1524,'A Dangerous Method',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_dangerous_method/','771203681','1571222',1,'Seduced by the challenge of an impossible case, the driven Dr. Carl Jung (Michael Fassbender) takes the unbalanced yet beautiful Sabina Spielrein (Keira Knightley) as his patient in A Dangerous Method. Jung\'s weapon is the method of his master, the renowned Sigmund Freud (Viggo Mortensen). Both men fall under Sabina\'s spell. -- (C) Sony Pictures Classics','A provocative historical fiction about the early days of psychoanalysis, A Dangerous Method is buoyed by terrific performances by Michael Fassbender, Keira Knightley, and Viggo Mortensen.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/10/11161096_mob.jpg'),(1525,'Dracula 2000',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dracula_2000/','13199',NULL,1,NULL,'This retelling trys to offer a different spin on the origin of Dracula. Unfortunately, there\'s nothing here audiences haven\'t seen before.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/26/85/268599_mob.jpg'),(1526,'That Thing You Do!',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/that_thing_you_do/','10233','0117887',1,NULL,'A light, sweet, and thoroughly entertaining debut for director Tom Hanks, That Thing You Do! makes up in charm what it lacks in complexity.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/47/11164757_mob.jpg'),(1527,'Unleashed (Danny the Dog)',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1145385-unleashed/','13','0342258',1,NULL,'Jet Li gets to emote in some emotionally awkward scenes, but the gritty fight sequences come through in what is Li\'s best English language film.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/24/97/249719_mob.jpg'),(1528,'Doctor Zhivago',1965,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1006037-doctor_zhivago/','10116','0059113',1,NULL,'It may not be the best of David Lean\'s epics, but Dr. Zhivago is still brilliantly photographed and sweepingly romantic.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/80/11168025_mob.jpg'),(1529,'Stephanie Daley',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stephanie_daley/','405589595','0483812',1,NULL,'The premise has all the trappings of melodrama, but the excellent performances give the characters complexity and emp