usician is worthy of being called a \"genius,\" this document of his life is crafted with sincere respect and is fascinating to watch.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/59/10895946_mob.jpg'),(1655,'Dirty Girl',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dirty_girl_2011/','771235026','1107319',1,'Dirty Girl is the story of Danielle (Juno Temple), the dirty girl of Norman High School in Norman, Oklahoma, circa 1987. When Danielle\'s misbehavior gets her banished to a remedial class, she is paired on a parenting project with Clarke (Jeremy Dozier), an innocent closet-case with no friends. Danielle is determined to get to California to find the father she\'s never met, and Clarke is desperate to escape being sent to military school by his homophobic dad. Together, the mismatched misfits light out for California, and discover each other and themselves through a funny and serendipitous friendship. -- (C) Weinstein',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/05/11160584_mob.jpg'),(1656,'The Great Mouse Detective',1986,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the-great-mouse-detective/','9493','0091149',1,NULL,'The Great Mouse Detective may not rank with Disney\'s classics, but it\'s an amiable, entertaining picture with some stylishly dark visuals.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/12/251227_mob.jpg'),(1657,'Darkness',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/darkness/','17278','0273517',1,NULL,'Yet another predictable variation on the hoary old haunted-house movie, Darkness is an illogical, portentous mess.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/28/71/287119_mob.jpg'),(1658,'Dragonslayer',1981,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dragonslayer/','10449','0082288',1,NULL,'An atypically dark Disney adventure, Dragonslayer puts a realistic spin -- and some impressive special effects -- on a familiar tale.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/58/255808_mob.jpg'),(1659,'Watership Down',1978,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/watership_down/','10301','0078480',1,NULL,'Aimed at adult