sors, Return of the Jedi remains an entertaining sci-fi adventure and a fitting end to the classic trilogy.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/94/47/10944709_mob.jpg'),(1869,'Edward Scissorhands',1990,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/edward_scissorhands/','10019','0099487',1,NULL,'The first collaboration between Johnny Depp and Tim Burton, Edward Scissorhands is a magical modern fairy tale with gothic overtones and a sweet center.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/44/11164473_mob.jpg'),(1870,'Employee of the Month',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/employee_of_the_month/','338671160','0424993',1,NULL,'Employee of the Month features mediocre performances, few laughs, and a lack of satiric bite.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/28/18/36/2818365_mob.jpg'),(1871,'A Nightmare on Elm Street',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nightmare_on_elm_street_2010/','770785488','1179056',1,'Platinum Dunes revives the Nightmare on Elm Street franchise with this reworking of slasher film legend Freddy Krueger, a deceased child killer who torments the dreams of the teenagers of Springwood, OH. Jackie Earle Haley picks up the killer\'s mantle from series veteran Robert Englund with the reboot from music-video director Samuel Bayer. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi','Visually faithful but lacking the depth and subversive twists that made the original so memorable, the Nightmare on Elm Street remake lives up to its title in the worst possible way.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/95/40/10954017_mob.jpg'),(1872,'Mr. Magorium\'s Wonder Emporium',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mr_magoriums_wonder_emporium/','594225106','0457419',1,NULL,'Mr. Magorium\'s Wonder Emporium\'s title is much more fun that the film itself, as the colorful visuals and talented players can\'t make up for a bland story.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/87/52/10875231_mob.jpg'),(1873,'Red Eye',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1149496-1149496-red_eye/','5078','0421239',1,NULL,'With solid performances and tight direction from Wes Craven, Red Eye is a brisk, economic thriller.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/68/11156845_mob.jpg'),(1874,'The Eye',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10008606-eye/','712377385','0406759',1,NULL,'Featuring wooden performances and minimal scares, The Eye is another tedious remake of an Asian horror film.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/84/47/10844773_mob.jpg'),(1875,'Eternal Sunshine Of The Spotless Mind',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/eternal_sunshine_of_the_spotless_mind/','12860','0338013',1,NULL,'Propelled by Charlie Kaufman\'s smart, imaginative script and Michel Gondry\'s equally daring directorial touch, Eternal Sunshine is a twisty yet heartfelt look at relationships and heartache.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/55/05/71/5505718_mob.jpg'),(1876,'Lemony Snicket\'s A Series of Unfortunate Events',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lemony_snicket/','10045','0339291',1,NULL,'The film adaptation of the popular books is winning raves for its set design and a wry comic charm that mitigates some morbid images. However, some have panned the film as smug and overcooked.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168954_mob.jpg'),(1877,'My Super Ex-Girlfriend',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/my_super_ex_girlfriend/','190816028','0465624',1,NULL,'My Super Ex=Girlfriend is an only sporadically amusing spoof on the superhero genre that misses the mark with a nerd-turned-superwoman who embodies sexist cliches.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/22/10872241_mob.jpg'),(1878,'A Nightmare on Elm Street',1984,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nightmare_on_elm_street/','13117','0087800',1,NULL,'Wes Craven\'s intelligent premise, combined with the horrifying visual appearance of Freddy Krueger, still causes nightmares to this day.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/96/11159613_mob.jpg'),(1879,'Elizabethtown',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/elizabethtown/','8761