ootage, occasionally recognize their neighbors, or report upon the filmmakers\' efforts to stage fantasies of affluence and well-being, or of Jews treating their less fortunate compatriots with callous disdain. This is a film of enormous import: it documents conditions under which ghetto residents lived and the efforts (however imperfect) of the perpetrators to recast this reality to suggest an entirely different scenario. A FILM UNFINISHED is presented with support from the Joan S. Constantiner Fund for Jewish and Holocaust Film. -- (C) Film Forum','A heartbreaking, haunting historical document, A Film Unfinished excavates particularly horrible chapter of Holocaust history, and in doing so, the film provides a glimpse into the Nazi propaganda machine.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/14/98/11149872_mob.jpg'),(3229,'Uu Kodathara Ulikki Padathara',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/uu_kodathara_ulikki_padathara_2012/','771312345','2401225',1,'Uu Kodathara Ulikki Padathara is a socio-fantasy film and it also deals with life after death. The story revolves around the fort Gandharva Mahal. Balakrishna playing the role of King Narasimha Naidu in this movie.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(3230,'Not Quite Hollywood: The Wild, Untold Story of Ozploitation!',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/not_quite_hollywood/','770783495','0996966',1,NULL,'A raucous, fast-paced celebration of the Ozploitation films that came out of Australia in the 1970s and 1980s.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/13/72/11137217_mob.jpg'),(3231,'Up the Yangtze',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/up_the_yangtze/','770682590','1114277',1,NULL,'Up the Yangtze is a visually stunning meditation about the changes confronting modern China.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/91/11169132_mob.jpg'),(3232,'Ultimate Universe',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ultimate-universe/','770832523',NULL,1,'From the edge of space and time, t