d_in_4d/','771036679','1517489',1,'On the surface, Marissa Cortez Wilson (Jessica Alba) has it all...married to a famous spy hunting television reporter, a new baby and intelligent twin step kids. But in reality, trying to mother Rebecca (Rowan Blanchard) and Cecil (Mason Cook), who clearly don\'t want her around, is her toughest challenge yet. Also, her husband, Wilbur (Joel McHale), wouldn\'t know a spy if he lived with one which is exactly the case - Marissa\'s a retired secret agent. Marissa\'s world is turned upside down when the maniacal Timekeeper (Jeremy Piven) threatens to take over the planet and she\'s called back into action by the head of OSS, home of the greatest spies and where the now-defunct Spy Kids division was created. With a little help from a couple of very familiar Spy Kids, Carmen (Alexa Vega) and Juni Cortez (Daryl Sabara), they just may be able to save the world and possibly bring their family together while they\'re at it. -- (C) Weinstein','Burdened by a rote plot and unfunny scatological humor, All the Time in the World suggests that the Spy Kids franchise has run its course.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/83/11158341_mob.jpg'),(3475,'Timeline',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/timeline/','10365','0300556',1,NULL,'This incoherently plotted addition to the time-travel genre looks and sounds cheesy.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168974_mob.jpg'),(3476,'Take Shelter',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/take_shelter/','771224184','1675192',1,'Curtis LaForche lives in a small Ohio town with his wife Samantha and six-year-old daughter Hannah, who is deaf. Money is tight, and navigating Hannah\'s healthcare and special needs education is a constant struggle. Despite that, Curtis and Samantha are very much in love and their family is a happy one. Then Curtis begins having terrifying dreams about an encroaching, apocalyptic storm. He chooses to keep the disturbance to himself, channeling his anxiety into the obsessive building of a storm shelter in their backyard. But the resulting strain on his marriage and tension within the community doesn\'t compare to Curtis\' private fear of what his dreams may truly signify. Faced with the proposition that his disturbing visions signal disaster of one kind or another, Curtis confides in Samantha, testing the power of their bond against the highest possible stakes. -- (C) Sony Classics','Michael Shannon gives a powerhouse performance and the purposefully subtle filmmaking creates a perfect blend of drama, terror, and dread.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/89/11158902_mob.jpg'),(3477,'They Live',1988,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/they_live/','15716','0096256',1,NULL,'A politically subversive blend of horror and sci fi, They Live is an underrated genre film from John Carpenter.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/28/06/280698_mob.jpg'),(3478,'Trollhunter',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trollhunter/','771217727','1740707',1,'Shot in a verite style, Trollhunter is the story of a group of Norwegian film students that set out to capture real-life trolls on camera after learning their existence has been covered up for years by a government conspiracy. A thrilling and wildly entertaining film, Trollhunter delivers truly fantastic images of giant trolls wreaking havoc on the countryside, with darkly funny adherence to the original Norwegian folklore.\" -- (C) Official Site','A slightly winking mockumentary that manages to be both irreverent and spooky.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/67/11156771_mob.jpg'),(3479,'The Muppets Take Manhattan',1984,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/muppets_take_manhattan/','9472','0087755',1,NULL,'If it\'s not quite as sharp as The Muppet Movie, The Muppets Take Manhattan is still a smart, delightfully old-fashioned tale that follows the formula established by the first two movies -- a madcap adventure assisted by a huge group of human stars.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/11/251125_mob.jpg'),(3480,'A River Runs Through It',1992,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/river_runs_through_it/','10493','0105265',1,NULL,'Tasteful to a fault, this period drama combines a talented cast (including a young Brad Pitt) with some stately, beautifully filmed work from director Robert Redford.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/60/256009_mob.jpg'),(3481,'Janghwa, Hongryeon (A Tale of Two Sisters)',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1143939-1143939-tale_of_two_sisters/','22467','0365376',1,NULL,'Restrained but disturbing, A Tale of Two Sisters is a creepily effective, if at times confusing, horror movie.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/84/07/10840797_mob.jpg'),(3482,'Arctic Tale',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/arctic_tale/','770670842','0488508',1,NULL,'Arctic Tale features breathtaking nature cinematography, but is undone by its over-cutesy narration.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/87/30/65/8730658_mob.jpg'),(3483,'Trade',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1164582-trade/','528392628','0399095',1,NULL,'With an exploitative style that seems more suited for TV shows like CSI, Trade\'s message about the reality of child exploitation is easily lost.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/48/29/58/4829589_mob.jpg'),(3484,'Teeth',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/teeth/','528392454','0780622',1,NULL,'Smart, original, and horrifically funny, Teeth puts a fresh feminist spin on horror movie tropes.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/60/54/10605468_mob.jpg'),(3485,'The Tempest',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tempest/','770805051','1274300',1,'The sorceress Prospera\'s journey spirals through vengeance to forgiveness as she reigns over a magical island, cares for her young daughter, Miranda, and unleashes her powers against shipwrecked enemies in this exciting, masterly mix of romance, tragicomedy and the supernatural.','Director Julie Taymor\'s gender-swapping of roles and some frenzied special effects can\'t quite disguise an otherwise stagey, uninspired take on Shakespeare\'s classic.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/16/11151659_mob.jpg'),(3486,'Lottery Ticket',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10012039-lottery_ticket/','770863869','0979434',1,'A kid from the projects scores the jackpot in the lottery and fights to protect his ticket over the course of a treacherous holiday weekend in this all-star comedy featuring Ice Cube, Charlie Murphy, Terry Crews, and Loretta Devine. With the Fourth of July fast approaching, Kevin Carson (Bow Wow) purchases a pair of lottery tickets and settles down in front of the television to catch the winning numbers. When Kevin realizes he\'s just won 370 million dollars, he knows his neighbors will all come knocking the moment word of his massive windfall gets out. And he\'s right, too; before long, the local thugs are looking to take the ticket by force, and the sexiest girls in the neighborhood are begging to bear his children. Unfortunately for Kevin and his grandma, the lottery-claims office doesn\'t open until Monday, and over the next 72 hours there are more than a million ways the winning ticket could fall into the wrong hands. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','There\'s a worthwhile message at the heart of Lottery Ticket, but it\'s buried under stale humor, tired stereotypes, and obvious cliches.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/95/55/10955537_mob.jpg'),(3487,'The Man Who Knew Too Much',1956,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1013209-man_who_knew_too_much/','10334','0049470',1,NULL,'Remaking his own 1934 film, Hitchcock imbues The Man Who Knew Too Much with picturesque locales and international intrigue, and is helped by a brilliantly befuddled performance from James Stewart.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/71/11157151_mob.jpg'),(3488,'Torque',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1129132-torque/','20512','0329691',1,NULL,'Silly and noisy, Torque is stylish fun for the MTV crowd.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/55/35/33/5535335_mob.jpg'),(3489,'Trading Places',1983,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trading_places/','12898','0086465',1,NULL,'Featuring deft interplay between Eddie Murphy and Dan Dan Aykroyd, Trading Places is an immensely appealing social satire.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168976_mob.jpg'),(3490,'Star Trek - Insurrection',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/star_trek_insurrection/','11889','0120844',1,NULL,'Although not terrible, the sluggishly paced Insurrection plays like an extended episode of the TV series.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/85/10888598_mob.jpg'),(3491,'Take This Waltz',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/take_this_waltz/','771249650','1592281',1,'When Margot (Michelle Williams), 28, meets Daniel (Luke Kirby), their chemistry is intense and immediate. But Margot suppresses her sudden attraction; she is happily married to Lou (Seth Rogen), a cookbook writer. When Margot learns that Daniel lives across the street from them, the certainty about her domestic life shatters. She and Daniel steal moments throughout the steaming Toronto summer, their eroticism heightened by their restraint. Swelteringly hot, bright and colorful like a bowl of fruit, Take This Waltz leads us, laughing, through the familiar, but uncharted question of what long-term relationships do to love, sex, and our images of ourselves. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/43/11164394_mob.jpg'),(3492,'Titan A.E.',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/titan_ae/','10688','0120913',1,NULL,'Great visuals, but the story feels like a cut-and-paste job of other sci-fi movies.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/47/11164767_mob.jpg'),(3493,'Treasure Planet',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/treasure_planet/','10781','0133240',1,NULL,'Though its characterizations are weaker than usual, Treasure Planet offers a fast-paced, beautifully rendered vision of outer space.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/74/257421_mob.jpg'),(3494,'The Treasure of the Sierra Madre',1948,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/treasure_of_the_sierra_madre/','18253','0040897',1,NULL,'Remade but never duplicated, this darkly humorous morality tale represents John Huston at his finest.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/80/11168087_mob.jpg'),(3495,'The Man Who Wasn\'t There',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/man_who_wasnt_there/','15353','0243133',1,NULL,'Stylish but emotionally distant, The Man Who Wasn\'t There is a clever tribute to the film noir genre.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/32/10883293_mob.jpg'),(3496,'Strangers on a Train',1951,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/strangers_on_a_train/','10699','0044079',1,NULL,'A provocative premise and inventive set design lights the way for Hitchcock diabolically entertaining masterpiece.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/93/77/10937755_mob.jpg'),(3497,'Modern Times',1936,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/modern_times/','17958','0027977',1,NULL,'A slapstick skewering of industrialized America, Modern Times is as politically incisive as it is laugh-out-loud hilarious.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/29/01/290109_mob.jpg'),(3498,'Three to Tango',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/three_to_tango/','11714','0144640',1,NULL,'A mediocre episode of Friends has more humor and less offensive gay jokes.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/20/262016_mob.jpg'),(3499,'Tigerland',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tigerland/','14280','0170691',1,NULL,'A great cast and the gritty feel of the film help elevate Tigerland above the familiarity of the subject matter.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/49/11164936_mob.jpg'),(3500,'A Sound of Thunder',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sound_of_thunder/','6361','0318081',1,NULL,'Choppy logic and uneven performances are overshadowed by not-so-special effects that makes the suspension of disbelief a nearly impossible task.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/89/83/10898335_mob.jpg'),(3501,'Twelve',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/twelve-2008/','770807479','1407084',1,'Twelve is the story of 17-year-old White Mike, the privileged son of a restaurant tycoon. His mother succumbed to breast cancer several years before the film begins. White Mike is a drug dealer who has taken his senior year in high school off to sell drugs to his wealthy peers. When he is not selling drugs he is reminiscing of his childhood and philosophizing about a world he feels he is not a part of. The title of the film refers to a new designer drug which the protagonist of the novel, White Mike, sells. The drug is referred to as a cross between cocaine and ecstasy.-- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/12/11151294_mob.jpg'),(3502,'Whatever It Takes',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1095414-whatever_it_takes/','11384','0202402',1,NULL,'Whatever It Takes is another run-of-the-mill teeny-bopper romance flick. Cliche jokes and a tired plot capture few laughs.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/55/12/40/5512408_mob.jpg'),(3503,'Transsiberian',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/transsiberian/','770679862','0800241',1,NULL,'Traditional in form yet effective in execution, this taut thriller updates the \"danger on a train\" scenario with atmospheric sense.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/86/10878637_mob.jpg'),(3504,'Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles III',1993,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/teenage_mutant_ninja_turtles_iii/','11270','0108308',1,NULL,'It\'s a case of one sequel too many for the heroes in a half shell, with a tired time-travel plot gimmick failing to save the franchise from rapidly diminishing returns.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/98/259894_mob.jpg'),(3505,'Micmacs (Micmacs a tire-larigot)',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/micmacs/','770686296','1149361',1,'An underground lair serves as the point of inspiration for this deeply whimsical fantasy comedy (with echoes of Jodorowsky\'s Rainbow Thief) from French cause celebre Jean-Pierre Jeunet (Amelie, The City of Lost Children). The locale is post-9/11 Europe. As arms dealers go head to head with one another in a series of violent skirmishes -- suggesting that an apocalyptic cataclysm may be lingering on the horizon -- the unfortunate Bazil (Dany Boon) still reels from the long-ago death of his father from a roadside bomb, an event that left him orphaned as a boy. Now employed in a low-paying job as a video-store clerk, and still trying to determine how he fits into the scheme of things, he gets hit by a stray bullet from a drive-by shooting and promptly lands in the hospital. Upon release, he finds himself broke and unemployed. Hope soon crops up, however, in the form of Placard (Jean-Pierre Marielle), an ex-convict living in a scrap dump with a motley group of social outcasts -- all of whom welcome Bazil with warmth, compassion, and hospitality. Sure of his place for the first time in his life, Bazil joins forces with them to turn the dump into a lovely underground home, filled to the rafters with extraordinary inventions and sculptures. Soon after, the possibility of revenge against the munitions manufacturers responsible for Bazil\'s dad\'s death presents itself. ~ Nathan Southern, Rovi','It might be a little too whimsical for its own good, but Micmacs delivers more of the inventive silliness that director Jean-Pierre Jeunet is known for.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/12/07/11120749_mob.jpg'),(3506,'Muppet Treasure Island',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/muppet_treasure_island/','9510','0117110',1,NULL,'Though less Muppet-centric than the original trilogy, Muppet Treasure Island is an energetic, cheerful take on Robert Louis Stevenson\'s classic adventure, with typically solid gags.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/15/10881572_mob.jpg'),(3507,'Talk to Her',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/talk_to_her/','13142',NULL,1,NULL,'Another masterful, compassionate work from Pedro Almodovar.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/83/268306_mob.jpg'),(3508,'Where the Truth Lies',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/where_the_truth_lies/','8766',NULL,1,NULL,'The belabored noir plotting feels unbelievable, thus removing any sense of suspense. Also, Lohman is badly miscast.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/83/10898330_mob.jpg'),(3509,'Titus',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/titus/','13294','0120866',1,NULL,'The movie stretches too long to be entertaining despite a strong cast.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/26/90/269029_mob.jpg'),(3510,'Trapped',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1116086-trapped/','14131','0280380',1,NULL,'With its plot about child kidnapping and endangerment, Trapped is an exploitative thriller, more queasy than suspenseful.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/12/22/11122265_mob.jpg'),(3511,'Trust the Man',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trust_the_man/','283051883','0427968',1,NULL,'What aspires to be a sophisticated, unconventional romantic comedy turns out to be a contrivance-filled pretender to other, better films of its genre.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/21/37/19/2137190_mob.jpg'),(3512,'Tekken',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tekken/','770756494','0411951',1,'The year is 2039. World wars have destroyed everything and territories are run by corporations, the mightiest -- and cruelest -- of which is Tekken. Jin Kazama (Jon Foo) witnesses the death of his mother Jun (Tomita) by Tekken in the slums known as Anvil. Vowing vengeance, and armed only with his street smarts and raw fighting skills, he enters a dangerous and potentially deadly combat tournament, where he must defeat the world\'s most elite fighters to become the \"King of the Iron Fist.\" -- (C) Anchor Bay',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/74/11157484_mob.jpg'),(3513,'Teaching Mrs. Tingle',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/teaching_mrs_tingle/','12811','0133046',1,NULL,'As a dark comedy-thriller, this movie lacks humor and thrill.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/66/266698_mob.jpg'),(3514,'The Tigger Movie',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the-tigger-movie/','9475','0220099',1,NULL,'Tigger Movie may lack the technological flash and underlying adult sophistication of other recent animated movies, but it\'s fun and charming.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/12/43/11124383_mob.jpg'),(3515,'Trumbo',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1193303-1193303-trumbo/','770740109','0889671',1,NULL,'Trumbo celebrates the life and work of blacklisted screenwriter Dalton Trumbo with measures of humor and sadness.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/84/42/10844299_mob.jpg'),(3516,'Tokyo Sonata (Tokyo Sonata)',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tokyo_sonata/','770771545','0938341',1,NULL,'J-Horror director Kiyoshi Kurosawa turns successfully to dramedy and gives a unique (and specifically national) perspective to the universal subjects of family and identity.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/87/76/10877627_mob.jpg'),(3517,'Tomboy',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tomboy_2011/','771238362','1847731',1,'A French family with two daughters, 10-year-old Laure and 6-year-old Jeanne, moves to a new neighborhood during the summer holidays. With her Jean Seberg haircut and tomboy ways, Laure is immediately mistaken for a boy by the local kids and passes herself off as Michael. Filmmaker Celine Sciamma brings a light and charming touch to this drama of childhood gender confusion. Zoe Heran as Laure/Michael and Malonn Levanna as Jeanne are nothing less than brilliant. This is a relationship movie: relationships between children, and the even more complicated one between one\'s heart and body. -- (C) Rocket Releasing','In tune with the emotion and tribulations of childhood, Tomboy is a charming movie that treats its main subject with warmth and heart.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/09/11160990_mob.jpg'),(3518,'Angus, Thongs and Perfect Snogging',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/angus_thongs_and_perfect_snogging/','770685222','0963743',1,NULL,'Based on two of British writer Louise Rennison\'s popular books, Angus, Thongs and Perfect Snogging is a pleasant and funny tween comedy, comfortable for UK audiences as well as stateside crowds.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/85/35/10853566_mob.jpg'),(3519,'Timecop',1994,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/timecop/','16855','0111438',1,NULL,'It\'s no Terminator, but for those willing to suspend disbelief and rational thought, Timecop provides limited sci-fi action rewards.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/12/53/11125356_mob.jpg'),(3520,'Sanjuro (Tsubaki Sanjuro)',1962,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sanjuro/','11935','0056443',1,NULL,'Technically impressive and superbly acted, Sanjuro is a funny, action-packed samurai adventure featuring outstanding cinematography and a charismatic performance from Toshiro Mifune.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/39/91/11/3991117_mob.jpg'),(3521,'Pushing Tin',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pushing_tin/','13817','0120797',1,NULL,'Solid performances by the leads, but the generic ending needs help.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/27/16/271610_mob.jpg'),(3522,'Oliver Twist',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10005499-oliver_twist/','12699','0222608',1,NULL,'Polanski\'s version of Dickens\' classic won\'t have audiences asking for more because while polished and directed with skill, the movie\'s a very impersonal experience.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/84/17/10841703_mob.jpg'),(3523,'Starter for 10',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/starter_for_ten/','355028245','0477095',1,NULL,'Starter For 10 is a spirited coming-of-age tale that remains charming and witty even as it veers into darker teritory. The unique setting of a quiz show makes the film wittier than your average romantic comedy.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/09/10870929_mob.jpg'),(3524,'Nothing But the Truth',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nothing_but_the_truth/','770677680','1073241',1,NULL,'A well-crafted political thriller, Nothing But the Truth features a strong cast that helps the real-life drama make an effortless transition to the big screen.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/86/81/10868153_mob.jpg'),(3525,'Tomcats',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tomcats/','14094','0074379',1,NULL,'Why even bother? You already know if you\'re going to see it or not.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/27/29/272998_mob.jpg'),(3526,'Tokyo!',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10010237-tokyo/','770771172','0976060',1,NULL,'An imaginative, if uneven, love letter to a city that signals a great creative enterprise by its three contributing directors.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/87/27/10872791_mob.jpg'),(3527,'Time to Leave (Le Temps Qui Reste)',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/time_to_leave/','190815782','0417189',1,NULL,'A reflective look at our own mortality through the experience of a middle-aged French man, Time To Leave manages to pull at our heart strings without resorting to cliches, and leaves a lasting impression.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/89/10888936_mob.jpg'),(3528,'Mystery Science Theater 3000: The Movie',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mystery_science_theater_3000_the_movie/','12431','0117128',1,NULL,'Mystery Science Theater 3000: The Movie may be thin and uneven, but it\'s hilarious in enough of the right spots to do the show\'s big-screen transition justice.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/13/40/11134021_mob.jpg'),(3529,'Peeping Tom',1960,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/peeping-tom/','19244','0054167',1,NULL,'Peeping Tom is a chilling, methodical look at the psychology of a killer, and a classic work of voyeuristic cinema.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/38/11153833_mob.jpg'),(3530,'Take',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1178444-take/','770687362','0815138',1,NULL,'A story of redemption held together with flashbacks, Take has moments of emotional intensity, but is ultimately undone by preachiness.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/91/50/10915049_mob.jpg'),(3531,'Twelve and Holding (12 and Holding)',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1158234-twelve_and_holding/','155655015','0417385',1,NULL,'This shocking pre-teen drama manages, through realistic performances and a sense of empathy, to avoid exploitation and instead deliver something honest and haunting.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/86/97/10869736_mob.jpg'),(3532,'The Twilight Samurai (Tasogare Seibei)',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/twilight_samurai/','18393','0351817',1,NULL,'Samurai epic as a touching drama.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/92/29/10922967_mob.jpg'),(3533,'Trust',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trust_2010/','771208924','1529572',1,'A family is devastated by a crime committed against a teenage girl in this drama. Annie (Liana Liberato) is 14 years old and growing up in a suburb of Chicago. Annie\'s parents, Will (Clive Owen) and Lynn (Catherine Keener), are loving, but they\'ve been busy with her older brother, Peter (Spencer Curnutt), who is heading off to college, so she spends a lot of time on-line chatting with a boy she met on the Internet, Charlie. Annie has developed a powerful crush on Charlie, and when he asks her to meet face to face, she eagerly agrees. However, Annie is startled to discover that Charlie isn\'t 16 years old, as she was led to believe, but in his mid-thirties (Chris Henry Coffey), and when he talks her into stopping by his hotel room, he sexually assaults her. Humiliated, Annie confides to a friend what happened, and eventually the police are notified; it turns out that \"Charlie\" is a sex offender they\'ve been tracking for months. While Annie is devastated by the experience, her family is just as shocked by what happened, particularly Will, who becomes grimly obsessed with finding the man who raped his daughter. Trust was directed by actor-turned-filmmaker David Schwimmer, representing a significant change from the comedies that made his name. ~ Mark Deming, Rovi','Director David Schwimmer gets some gut-wrenching performances out of his actors but he still lacks the chops to fully ratchet up story tension.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/55/11155572_mob.jpg'),(3534,'Terri',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/terri_2011/','771225867','1687281',1,'A hit at the Sundance 2011 Film Festival, Terri is a moving and often funny film about the relationship between Terri, an oversized teen misfit, and the garrulous but well-meaning vice principal (John C. Reilly) who takes an interest in him. Terri is produced by the team behind Blue Valentine and Half Nelson, and directed by Azazel Jacobs (Momma\'s Man). -- (C) ATO Pictures',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/79/11157916_mob.jpg'),(3535,'Tetro',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tetro/','770805201','0964185',1,NULL,'A complex meditation on family dynamics, Tetro\'s arresting visuals and emotional core compensate for its uneven narrative.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/87/91/10879132_mob.jpg'),(3536,'Swamp Thing',1982,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/swamp_thing/','12160','0084745',1,NULL,'Unabashedly campy -- often to its detriment -- Swamp Thing is not without its charms, among them Adrienne Barbeau as the damsel in distress.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/90/44/10904464_mob.jpg'),(3537,'Alien Trespass',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/alien_trespass/','770802920','1122836',1,NULL,'An earnest attempt to parody campy 1950s sci-fi films, Alien Trespass eventually loses its charm among tedious dialogue and cheesy special effects.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/87/64/10876412_mob.jpg'),(3538,'Tabloid',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tabloid_2010/','771208471','1704619',1,'Thirty years before the antics of Lindsay Lohan and Britney Spears were regular gossip fodder, Miss Wyoming Joyce McKinney made her mark as a tabloid staple ne plus ultra. Morris follows the salacious adventures of this beauty queen with an IQ of 168 whose single-minded devotion to the man of her dreams leads her across the globe, into jail, and onto the front page. Joyce\'s labyrinthine crusade for love takes her through a surreal world of kidnapping, manacled Mormons, risque photography, magic underwear, and celestial sex-until her dream is finally realized in a cloning laboratory in Seoul, South Korea. By turns funny, strange, and disturbing, Tabloid is a vivid portrayal of a phenomenally driven woman whose romantic obsessions and delusions catapult her over the edge into scandal sheet notoriety and an unimaginable life. -- (C) IFC Films','It\'s far from his most thought-provoking work, but Tabloid finds Errol Morris as smart, spirited, and engaging as ever.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/81/11158175_mob.jpg'),(3539,'THR3E',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/thr3e/','474100963','0486028',1,NULL,'Thr3e is a shoddily made, thrill-free thriller that isn\'t half as good as the several movies it borrows from (Adaptation, Saw, Se7en).','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/44/33/18/4433180_mob.jpg'),(3540,'Tyrannosaur',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tyrannosaur/','771224200','1204340',1,'Joseph (Peter Mullan) is an unemployed widower with a drinking problem, a man crippled by his own volatile temperament and furious anger. Hannah (Olivia Colman) is a Christian worker at a charity shop, a respectable woman who seems wholesome and happy. When circumstance brings the pair together, Hannah appears as Joseph\'s guardian angel, tempering his fury and offering him warmth, kindness and acceptance. As their relationship develops, Hannah\'s own secrets are revealed - her husband (Eddie Marsan) is violent and abusive - and Joseph emerges as her unlikely savior. With striking performances and a deeply felt story, actor-turned-writer/director Paddy Considine\'s film is a stunning debut about the emergence of grace and redemption from the least likely of places. -- (C) Strand Releasing','Tyrannosaur is a brutal, frank, and ultimately rewarding story of violent men seeking far-off redemption.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/03/11160387_mob.jpg'),(3541,'Somers Town',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/somers_town/','770771606','1172206',1,NULL,'Shane Meadows hits the spot with this short but sweet slice of good natured comedy, surprisingly, as it\'s essentially an extended black & white advert for a train station.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/80/10888068_mob.jpg'),(3542,'Thunderbirds',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/thunderbirds/','11322','0167456',1,NULL,'Live-action cartoon for kids.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/87/69/10876970_mob.jpg'),(3543,'Tom Jones',1963,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tom_jones/','18019','0057590',1,NULL,'A frantic, irreverent adaptation of the novel, bolstered by Albert Finney\'s courageous performance and arresting visuals.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/29/03/290315_mob.jpg'),(3544,'Tormented',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10011243-tormented/','770807372','1100053',1,NULL,'It relies too heavily on American slasher cliches, but Tormented is a timely, funny, and even somewhat touching entry in the high school horror genre.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/93/95/10939503_mob.jpg'),(3545,'The Piano Teacher (La Pianiste)',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/piano_teacher/','17892','0254686',1,NULL,'Though it makes for rather unpleasant viewing, The Piano Teacher is a riveting and powerful psychosexual drama.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/13/11151355_mob.jpg'),(3546,'Rails & Ties',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10008703-rails_and_ties/','770674038','0822849',1,NULL,'Despite the strong cast, Rails & Ties is an emotionally overwrought, not entirely believable melodrama.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/48/20/10482040_mob.jpg'),(3547,'Twisted',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/twisted/','14784','0315297',1,NULL,'An implausible, overheated potboiler that squanders a stellar cast, Twisted is a cliched, risible whodunit.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/27/63/276304_mob.jpg'),(3548,'The Trip',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_trip_2011/','771230353','1740047',1,'Playing loose versions of themselves, Steve Coogan and Rob Brydon reprise their hilariously fictionalized roles from Tristam Shandy: A Cock and Bull Story and reunite with acclaimed director Michael Winterbottom for an acerbically witty, largely improvised ride through the English countryside. Tapped by The Observer to review fine restaurants throughout the Lake District and Yorkshire Dales, Steve finds himself without a traveling companion after his girlfriend decides not to go at the last minute. After being turned down by everyone else he knows, Steve extends an invitation to Rob, and together the pair attempt to navigate the winding back roads of rural England, impersonating popular celebrities such as Michael Caine, Woody Allen and Liam Neeson (among many others) and bickering along the way. -- (C) IFC','Amiable, funny and sometimes insightful, The Trip works as both a showcase for the enduring chemistry between stars Steve Coogan and Rob Brydon and an unexpected perusal of men entering mid-life crises.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/73/11157369_mob.jpg'),(3549,'One True Thing',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/one_true_thing/','14183','0120776',1,NULL,'Solid performances lift this drama to a higher level.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/46/11164654_mob.jpg'),(3550,'Ashes of Time',1994,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ashes_of_time/','20923','0109688',1,NULL,'Wong Kar Wai\'s redux, with a few slight changes from his 1994 classic, is a feast for the eyes, if a little difficult to follow.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/90/11169097_mob.jpg'),(3551,'The Tree',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_tree_2010/','771202109','1496005',1,'Blindsided with anguish after her husband\'s sudden death, Dawn (Gainsbourg)-along with her four young children-struggles to make sense of life without him. Eight-year-old Simone (unforgettable newcomer Morgana Davies) becomes convinced that her father is whispering to her through the leaves of the gargantuan fig tree that towers over their house. The family is initially comforted by its presence, but then the tree\'s enormous roots slowly begin to encroach on the abode and threaten their fragile existence.... -- (C) Zeitgeist Films','Though it leans rather heavily on its central metaphor, The Tree is a moving and ultimately hopeful meditation on grief with shades of magical realism.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/83/11158304_mob.jpg'),(3552,'The Tenant',1976,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tenant/','13422','0074811',1,NULL,'A rough-edged thriller that lacks the precision of Polanski\'s best work, but makes up for it with its skillful mounting of paranoia, dread, and dark themes.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/87/07/10870718_mob.jpg'),(3553,'Thunderbolt and Lightfoot',1974,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/thunderbolt_and_lightfoot/','13517','0072288',1,NULL,'This likable buddy/road picture deftly mixes action and comedy, and features excellent work from stars Clint Eastwood and Jeff Bridges and first-time director Michael Cimino.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/14/55/11145573_mob.jpg'),(3554,'Sunrise: A Song of Two Humans',1927,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sunrise/','98818519','0018455',1,NULL,'Boasting masterful cinematography to match its well-acted, wonderfully romantic storyline, Sunrise is perhaps the final -- and arguably definitive -- statement of the silent era.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/92/32/923216_mob.jpg'),(3555,'Pootie Tang',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pootie_tang/','11097','0258038',1,NULL,'Based as it is on a short skit, Pootie Tang overstays its welcome.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/90/259010_mob.jpg'),(3556,'The Tailor of Panama',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tailor_of_panama/','14318','0236784',1,NULL,'The Tailor of Panama is a smart, darkly satirical thriller with exuberant performances from Pierce Brosnan and Geoffrey Rush.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/27/40/274026_mob.jpg'),(3557,'The Shape Of Things',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shape_of_things/','14092','0308878',1,NULL,'LaBute returns to his earlier themes of cruelty in relationships, and the results hit hard.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/07/11150743_mob.jpg'),(3558,'13 Tzameti',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/13_tzameti/','298575504','0475169',1,NULL,'This starkly minimalist nail-biter of a thriller relentlessly builds up the tension and keeps the audience guessing.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/87/30/10873098_mob.jpg'),(3559,'The Tall Man',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_tall_man_2012/','771270485','1658837',1,'In an isolated, slowly dying mining town, children are vanishing without a trace - abducted, the townsfolk whisper, by a mysterious entity known locally as \"The Tall Man.\" Town nurse Julia Denning (Jessica Biel) seems skeptical...until her young David disappears in the middle of night. Frantic to rescue the boy, Julia lives every parent\'s darkest nightmare in this twisting, shock-around-each-corner thriller from acclaimed director Pascal Laugier called The Tall Man. -- (C) Image',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/58/11165812_mob.jpg'),(3560,'Inhale',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/inhale/','771208569','1196340',1,'Every day, rising Santa Fe District Attorney Paul Stanton and his wife, Diane, wait for word that there\'s a donor for their daughter, Chloe. Diagnosed with a rare degenerative condition, Chloe is on a long list to receive a double lung transplant. As her health worsens, Paul becomes desperate to save his young child...so desperate that he\'ll risk everything to organize an operation. When Paul learns of a Dr. Novarro who performs transplants in Juarez, Mexico, he heads south in a frantic search for the only man who may be able to save Chloe. But after arriving, he realizes Dr. Novarro\'s medical ring runs deep into a criminal underworld where his patients aren\'t donors - they\'re victims. With his career, his family and his life on the line, Paul finds himself at a critical crossroads: expose a massive, illegal harvesting operation and save the lives of hundreds of children, or save the life of his daughter. -- (C) IFC Films',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/36/11153632_mob.jpg'),(3561,'Is Anybody There?',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/is_there_anybody_there/','770792032','1130088',1,NULL,'Though Michael Caine gives an excellent performance, Is Anybody There? features a cliche-filled story that ultimately falters.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/41/10884140_mob.jpg'),(3562,'Top Hat',1935,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/top_hat/','18352','0027125',1,NULL,'A glamorous and enthralling Depression-era diversion, Top Hat is nearly flawless, with acrobatics by Fred Astaire and Ginger Rogers that make the hardest physical stunts seem light as air.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/13/03/10130383_mob.jpg'),(3563,'Riding Alone for Thousands of Miles',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/riding_alone_for_thousands_of_miles/','287865001','0437447',1,NULL,'Doesn\'t reach the heights of Zhang Yimou\'s best, but this is still a heartwarming tale of love and forgiveness from the acclaimed Chinese director.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/92/20/10922004_mob.jpg'),(3564,'Time After Time',1979,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/time_after_time/','11226','0080025',1,NULL,'With the three principal actors clearly having fun with their roles, Time After Time becomes an amusing, light-hearted fantasy lark.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/92/43/10924387_mob.jpg'),(3565,'The TV Set',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tv_set/','655759887','0473709',1,NULL,'Offering both broad and insider jokes, The TV Set is a sharp satire that will please both the average moviegoers and pop culture aficionados.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/61/76/12/6176124_mob.jpg'),(3566,'They',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1115907-1115907-they/','770682729','0283632',1,NULL,'They fails to sustain the level of creepiness necessary to rise above other movies in the horror genre.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/83/86/10838622_mob.jpg'),(3567,'The Sure Thing',1985,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sure_thing/','12705','0090103',1,NULL,'Though its final outcome is predictable, The Sure Thing is a charming, smartly written, and mature teen comedy featuring a breakout role for John Cusack.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/20/77/15/2077150_mob.jpg'),(3568,'Them (Ils)',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ils/','395114916','0465203',1,NULL,'Suspenseful and tense from start to finish, the French horror film Them proves that a lack of gore doesn\'t mean a dearth of scares.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/91/34/10913458_mob.jpg'),(3569,'Tupac - Resurrection',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tupac_resurrection/','14017','0343121',1,NULL,'There\'s no question where the director\'s loyalty lies in this one-sided tribute; however, Tupac\'s charisma makes this doc an engaging sit.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/92/14/10921402_mob.jpg'),(3570,'Magic Trip',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/magic_trip_2011/','771231858','1235790',1,'In 1964, Ken Kesey, the famed author of \"One Flew Over the Cuckoo\'s Nest,\" set off on a legendary, LSD-fuelled cross-country road trip to the New York World\'s Fair. He was joined by \"The Merry Band of Pranksters,\" a renegade group of counterculture truth-seekers, including Neal Cassady, the American icon immortalized in Kerouac\'s \"On the Road,\" and the driver and painter of the psychedelic Magic Bus. Kesey and the Pranksters intended to make a documentary about their trip, shooting footage on 16MM, but the film was never finished and the footage has remained virtually unseen. With Magic Trip, Oscar-winning director Alex Gibney and Alison Ellwood were given unprecedented access to this raw footage by the Kesey family. They worked with the Film Foundation, HISTORY and the UCLA Film Archives to restore over 100 hours of film and audiotape, and have shaped an invaluable document of this extraordinary piece of American history. --(C) Magnolia Pictures','Magic Trip is overall unenlightening, though there\'s an inherent novelty and joy in seeing the unearthed footage of Ken Kesey and his band of Merry Pranksters.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/74/11157485_mob.jpg'),(3571,'Touchback',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/touchback/','771206182','1628055',1,'Former high school football star turned farmer and family man, Scott Murphy (Brian Presley) finds himself with a unique opportunity to revisit his glory days during the Ohio State championship game where he permanently injured his knee in a game-winning play. Given a second shot at his destiny, Scott seeks counsel from Coach Hand (Kurt Russell), Scott\'s longtime mentor on and off the field, to help him decide whether to let his fate unfold, or follow a path that will change his future. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/38/11163890_mob.jpg'),(3572,'Thunderstruck',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/thunderstruck_2012/','771311086','2041488',1,'NBA superstar Kevin Durant plays himself in this action- packed family film about a basketball star who switches talent with a klutzy 16-year-old fan. When Brian (Taylor Gray) magically switches basketball skills with his hero, Kevin Durant, he becomes the star of his high school team... while Kevin Durant suddenly can\'t make a shot to save his life. But with the playoffs approaching, Brian learns that being a true winner means working hard at your own game, and he tries to make things right in time to prevent a catastrophic end to his hero\'s season. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/72/11167232_mob.jpg'),(3573,'Last Train Home',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/last_train_home-2009/','771035594','1512201',1,NULL,'Last Train Home is a haunting, vivid documentary exploring the human toll of China\'s economic boom in intimate, unforgettable detail.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/07/11150748_mob.jpg'),(3574,'Touch The Sound',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/touch-the-sound/','6929','0424509',1,NULL,'Not only does this documentary introduce viewers to Glennie, it gives them a taste of how she perceives the world.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/01/250102_mob.jpg'),(3575,'The Page Turner (La Tourneuse de pages)',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/page_turner/','380552606','0487503',1,NULL,'Reminiscent of Hitchcock and Chabrol, The Page Turner is elegant yet suspenseful, a revenge potboiler of a high degree.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/33/29/68/3329686_mob.jpg'),(3576,'The Tested',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_tested_2012/','771302911',NULL,1,'A single tragedy sends the lives of three people spinning hopelessly out of control as each struggles to seek meaning and redemption in a world turned upside-down. Julian Varone was an undercover cop who made a terrible mistake. As a result, Darraylynn Warren lay dead in the street. Meanwhile, as Darraylynn\'s despairing mother clings to the memory of her late son, his conflicted brother looks to gangs to provide the support that his fractured family cannot. At the same time, Julian struggles with feelings of intense guilt while preparing to return to work. As unlikely as it seems that these three lost souls could ever come together, the further they each fall the more apparent it becomes that they will need each other to successfully navigate the darkness that now defines their lives. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/56/11165635_mob.jpg'),(3577,'The Tragedy of Othello: The Moor of Venice (Othello)',1952,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the-tragedy-of-othello-the-moor-of-venice-othello1952/','21252','0045251',1,NULL,'This ragged take on Othello may take liberties with the source material, but Orson Welles\' genius never fails to impress.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/92/98/10929883_mob.jpg'),(3578,'L\' Homme du Train (The Man on the Train)',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/man_on_the_train/','15361','0301414',1,NULL,'A lovely, contemplative character study with two wonderful performances at its center.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/39/10893905_mob.jpg'),(3579,'The Trouble with Terkel (Terkel i knibe)',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/terkel-in-trouble-terkel-i-knibe/','335719344','1560987',1,'Terkel is a miserable, unhappy sixth grader who is constantly picked on by two merciless bullies. One day Terkel finds a way to be cool, sadly it involves making fun of his best friends\' sister and his girlfriend, what is a sixth grader to do? Make fun of her and call her a fat pig! When the abuse from Terkel is too much, she throws herself out a window which only makes Terkel more popular. Now dealing with popularity Terkel finds solace is booze, guns and everything American. But then life takes a turn for the weird when he receives strange death threats, unable to confide in his annoying sister or alcoholic uncle Stewart, Terkel turns to his teacher, a stoned out hippie with intentionally hilarious results. Watch this Danish equivalent of South Park in outrageous pixar like animation.-- (C) Indican',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/16/11151625_mob.jpg'),(3580,'Timecode (Time Code)',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/timecode/','15076','0220100',1,NULL,'Not much of a story, but the execution is interesting.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/27/77/277711_mob.jpg'),(3581,'The Turin Horse',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_turin_horse/','771021136','1316540',1,'On January 3, 1889 in Turin, Italy, Friedrich Nietzsche steps out of the doorway of number six, Via Carlo Albert. Not far from him, a cab driver is having trouble with a stubborn horse. The horse refuses to move, whereupon the driver loses his patience and takes his whip to it. Nietzsche puts an end to the brutal scene, throwing his arms around the horse\'s neck, sobbing. After this, he lies motionless and silent for two days on a divan, until he loses consciousness and his mind. Somewhere in the countryside, the driver of the cab lives with his daughter and the horse. Outside, a windstorm rages. Immaculately photographed in Bela Tarr\'s renowned long takes, The Turin Horse is the final statement from a master filmmaker. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/29/11162914_mob.jpg'),(3582,'The Milk of Sorrow (La Teta Asustada)',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/milk_of_sorrow/','770805346','1206488',1,NULL,'Claudia Llosa\'s deliberate pace and abstract storytelling may frustrate some viewers, but there\'s no denying the visual pleasures soaking in The Milk of Sorrow.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/86/11168664_mob.jpg'),(3583,'Trespass',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trespass_2011/','771208334','1674784',1,'In a private, wealthy community, priority is placed on security and no exception is made for the Miller family\'s estate. Behind their pristine walls and manicured gardens, Kyle (Nicolas Cage), a fast-talking businessman, has entrusted the mansion\'s renovation to his stunning wife, Sarah (Nicole Kidman). But between making those big decisions and keeping tabs on their defiant teenage daughter (Liana Liberato), Sarah often finds herself distracted by a young, handsome worker (Cam Gigandet) at their home. Nothing is what it seems, and it will take a group of cold-blooded criminals led by Elias (Ben Mendelsohn), who have been planning a vicious home invasion for months, to bring the Miller family together. Kyle, Sarah and Avery will take the ultimate risk to make it out with their lives - and their family - intact. -- (C) Millenium','Another claustrophobic thriller that Joel Schumacher can churn out in his sleep, Trespass is nasty and aggressive, more unpleasant than entertaining.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/92/11159248_mob.jpg'),(3584,'The Adventures of Ichabod and Mr. Toad',1949,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/adventures_of_ichabod_and_mr_toad/','9376','0041094',1,NULL,'This Disney two-fer may not be the most reverent literary adaptation, but it\'s remarkably crafted and emotionally resonant.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/06/250693_mob.jpg'),(3585,'That\'s What I Am',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/thats_what_i_am/','771234243','1606180',1,'Set in California against the backdrop of the mid-sixties, That\'s What I Am is a coming-of-age story that follows 12-year-old Andy Nichol (Chase Ellison), a bright student who, like most kids his age, will do anything to avoid conflict for fear of suffering overwhelming ridicule and punishment from his junior high school peers. Everyone\'s favorite teacher, Mr. Simon (Ed Harris), pairs Andy with the school\'s biggest outcast and social pariah, Stanley aka \"Big G\" (Alexander Walters), on a critical school project. Sporting thick orange hair, a head too big for his body and ears too big for his head, \"Big G\" has been the object of ridicule since grade school. Before long, Andy will learn that there was truly a method behind Mr. Simon\'s madness as to why he teamed these two up. After a dramatic incident in the schoolyard, teachers and parents rethink their roles in school and society. Principal Kelner (Amy Madigan) suspends a school bully for brutally beating up a female classmate. The vindictive father of the bully makes Mr. Simon the target of a malicious rumor about his sexuality, causing Mr. Simon to question his calling as an educator and mentor to his students. When Andy watches \"Big G\" fearlessly confront the school bully about the incident, a series of events are triggered. Much to Andy\'s surprise, he learns that \"Big G\" is a brilliant, kind, tolerant human being, who as more dignity than anyone Andy has ever encountered. Big G personifies Mr. Simon\'s four word answer on how to obtain world peace: HUMAN DIGNITY + COMPASSION = PEACE. -- (c)Samuel Goldwyn Films',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/70/11157029_mob.jpg'),(3586,'Tyrannosaurus Rex',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tyrannosaurus-rex/','770771675','1185408',1,'A 1970s-set story of an ex-con boxer with self-tendencies who gets caught up in an underground fight ring.',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/91/63/10916340_mob.jpg'),(3587,'Tyson',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1208128-tyson/','770796354','1032821',1,NULL,'A fascinating, emotional, and frank confessional from Iron Mike that sheds a sympathetic light on one of boxing\'s most controversial icons.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/87/65/10876510_mob.jpg'),(3588,'Tony Takitani',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tony_takitani/','359855308','0420260',1,NULL,'Despite its deceptive wispiness, this delicately lovely and melancholy film about loneliness has a haunting power.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/30/25/54/3025547_mob.jpg'),(3589,'Jab Tak Hai Jaan',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jab_tak_hai_jaan/','771314594','2176013',1,'Yash Chopra\'s last labour of love was his dream ever since his last outing as a director with Veer-Zaara. His untimely demise three weeks before the release of his last film makes this film even more special for fans of Yash Chopra and now the title \"Jab Tak Hai Jaan\" (Till my last breath) captures the legend and his passion for cinema. This is Bollywood at its best! The film stars The King of Bollywood - Shah Rukh Khan, Katrina Kaif, and Anushka Sharma. Music is by the Oscar-winning A.R. Rahman and produced by Aditya Chopra. (c) Yash Raj',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/66/11166612_mob.jpg'),(3590,'The Tragedy of Macbeth (Macbeth)',1971,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1012952-macbeth/','13158','0067372',1,NULL,'Roman Polanski\'s Macbeth is unsettling and uneven, but also undeniably compelling.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/26/84/268401_mob.jpg'),(3591,'Touching the Void',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/touching_the_void/','180886728','0379557',1,NULL,'Gripping even though the outcome is known.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/65/08/650851_mob.jpg'),(3592,'Taxidermia',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/taxidermia/','377596921','0410730',1,NULL,'Surreal and visually striking, Taxidermia is, at times, graphic and difficult to watch, but creatively touches on disturbing subjects with imagination and wit.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/79/10887901_mob.jpg'),(3593,'True Legend',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/true_legend/','770814748','1425257',1,'Yuen Woo Ping (The Matrix trilogy, Kill Bill Volumes I and II, Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon and Hero) brings you True Legend, a heart pounding epic about the timeless battle between good and evil. Su Can\'s (Vincent Zhao) respectable life is obliterated when his vengeful brother, Yuan (Andy On), returns from war armed with the deadly Five Venom Fists. Weakened but not destroyed, Su Can learns a never-before-seen form of martial arts: the Drunken Fist. Armed with this new power, he returns home to honor his family through retribution by taking on his brother in a battle to become the ultimate warrior. Packed with distinct fighting styles-including MMA, knife combat and sweeping aerial stunts- and starring martial arts legends Michelle Yeoh, David Carradine and Jay Chou, True Legend has Phillip French of The Observer raving, \"It opens with one of the best action sequences I\'ve ever seen.\" --(c) Indomina Media',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/68/11156801_mob.jpg'),(3594,'The Taming of the Shrew',1967,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1020861-taming_of_the_shrew/','18173',NULL,1,NULL,'It may not be reverent enough for purists, but This Taming of the Shrew is too funny -- and fun -- for the rest of us to resist.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/85/87/10858744_mob.jpg'),(3595,'A Thousand Acres',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/thousand_acres/','14303','0120323',1,NULL,'A Thousand Acres makes disappointingly sudsy stuff out of the source material, but benefits from solid performances by a strong cast.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/70/10887047_mob.jpg'),(3596,'Wild Tigers I Have Known',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wild_tigers_i_have_known/','371357804','0430768',1,NULL,'Beautiful imagery and sharp performances make Wild Tigers a memorable film from first-time director Cam Archer.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/33/28/90/3328903_mob.jpg'),(3597,'Trishna',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trishna_2011/','771253773','1836987',1,'Based on Thomas Hardy\'s classic novel Tess of the D\'Ubervilles, master filmmaker Michael Winterbottom\'s newest film stars Frieda Pinto who soars as Trishna in her most revealing performance yet. Trishna lives with her family in a village in Rajasthan, India\'s largest state. As the eldest daughter, she works in a nearby resort to help pay the bills. Jay (Riz Ahmed) is the wealthy son of a property developer. When he takes up managing a resort at his father\'s request, he meets Trishna at a dance and their fates cross. Jay finds every opportunity to win Trishna\'s affection and she accepts his efforts with shy curiosity. But when the two move to Mumbai and become a couple, Jay\'s deep family bond threaten the young lovers\' bliss. -- (C) IFC',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/53/11165389_mob.jpg'),(3598,'The Wild Thornberrys Movie',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wild_thornberrys_movie/','11231','0282120',1,NULL,'A pleasant enough kids flick that adults may even enjoy.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/96/259698_mob.jpg'),(3599,'Fah talai jone (Tears of the Black Tiger)',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tears_of_the_black_tiger/','475292715','0269217',1,NULL,'With a vibrant pastel color scheme and stylized action sequences, Tears of the Black Tiger is a bizarre, yet thoroughly entertaining Thai western.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/86/88/10868885_mob.jpg'),(3600,'Tape',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tape/','15088','0275719',1,NULL,'Taking place in a hotel room, Tape has the feel of a play, but its engrossing psychodrama allows its stars to shine.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/27/77/277796_mob.jpg'),(3601,'Together (Tillsammans)',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1109600-together/','98820383','0203166',1,NULL,'Managing to be both satirical and warm-hearted in its look at the inhabitants of a commune, Together successfully captures the spirit of a time.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/94/07/10940734_mob.jpg'),(3602,'Women in Trouble',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/women_in_trouble/','770804178','1247704',1,NULL,'Sebastian Gutierrez certainly has an eye for the beauty of the female form, but Women in Trouble lacks a compelling script or point of view to go with its curvaceous visual appeal.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/92/12/10921242_mob.jpg'),(3603,'Them!',1954,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1021186-them/','18157','0047573',1,NULL,'One of the best creature features of the early atomic age, Them! features effectively menacing special effects and avoids the self-parody that would taint later monster movies.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/91/34/10913472_mob.jpg'),(3604,'Tarnation',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tarnation/','17160','0390538',1,NULL,'Using music and home video footage to great effect, Jonathan Caouette has made a very personal and moving film.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/91/97/10919720_mob.jpg'),(3605,'Towelhead',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/towelhead/','770771087','0787523',1,NULL,'This story of politics, race and, sexual awakening has moments that pack a punch, but overall, Towelhead never quite achieves the nuance of helmer Alan Ball\'s television work.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/98/11159845_mob.jpg'),(3606,'It Is No Dream: The Life of Theodor Herzl',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/it_is_no_dream_the_life_of_theodor_herzl/','771311410','2094856',1,'Narrated by Sir Ben Kingsley and featuring Christoph Waltz as the voice of Theodor Herzl, the film examines how Herzl, a well known journalist and playwright, an assimilated Budapest born Jew, horrified by the Dreyfus trial in Paris and the anti-Semitism he saw spreading across Europe, took upon himself the task of attempting to create a Jewish homeland in Palestine against all odds. Over the span of 8 years, Herzl organized and led a worldwide political movement that within 50 years led to the establishment of the state of Israel. The film follows Herzl as he meets with Kings, Prime Ministers, Ambassadors, a Sultan, a Pope and government ministers from Constantinople to St. Petersburg, from Paris to Berlin, from Vienna to Vilna in his quest to build a Jewish nation. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/60/11166087_mob.jpg'),(3607,'Woman on Top',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/woman_on_top/','16908','0206420',1,NULL,'Despite Penelope Cruz\'s beauty and charm, the movie is too tepid to be a romance and too silly to be believable. And the movie is too eager to please with an ending that seems more like a cop out.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/47/11164795_mob.jpg'),(3608,'Illegal Tender',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/illegal_tender/','729680322','0775488',1,NULL,'Lackluster acting and a ridiculous plot make the over-the-top Illegal Tender an unrealistic bust.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/96/45/09/9645093_mob.jpg'),(3609,'Tucker: The Man and His Dream',1988,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tucker_the_man_and_his_dream/','10430','0096316',1,NULL,'Though it may not be as comprehensive as some would like, Francis Ford Coppola\'s cheerful biopic of the failed automotive designer features sparkling direction and a strong central performance from Jeff Bridges.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/57/255709_mob.jpg'),(3610,'Sleep Tight',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sleep_tight/','771200090','1586560',1,'Toiling silently amongst the residents of an everyday Barcelona apartment building, doorman Cesar (Luis Tosar) harbors a dark secret: his sole desire in life is to make others unhappy. When he sets his sights on Clara (Marta Clara), one of his building\'s cheeriest residents, his sick need blossoms into a full-fledged obsession. Embarking on a series of private and physical violations against Clara, Cesar becomes determined to ruin her life by any means. (c) Official Site',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/88/11168804_mob.jpg'),(3611,'Ni na bian ji dian (What Time Is It Over There?)',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/what_time_is_it_there/','20706','0269746',1,NULL,'Though it requires patience to view, What Time Is It There?\'s exploration of loneliness is both elegant and haunting.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/50/11155069_mob.jpg'),(3612,'The Tunnel (Der Tunnel)',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the-tunnel/','19389','0251447',1,NULL,'The Tunnel is both a tension-filled thriller and a riveting history lesson.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/85/69/10856941_mob.jpg'),(3613,'The Tillman Story',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_tillman_story/','770874812','1568334',1,'Pat Tillman gave up his professional football career to join the Army Rangers in 2002 -- and became an instant symbol of patriotic fervor and unflinching duty. But the truth about Pat Tillman is far more complex, and ultimately far more heroic, than the caricature created by the media. And, when the government tried to turn his death into propaganda, they took on the wrong family. From her home in Santa Cruz mountains, Pat\'s mother, Dannie Tillman, led the family\'s crusade to reveal the truth beneath the mythology of their son\'s life and death. \"The Tillman Story\" not only shines a light on the shady aftermath of Pat\'s death and calls to task the entire chain of command but also examines themes as timeless as the notion of heroism itself.','Passionate, angry, and insightful, The Tillman Story offers a revealing portrait of its subject\'s inspiring life and untimely death.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/12/06/11120623_mob.jpg'),(3614,'Hannah Takes the Stairs',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hannah_takes_the_stairs/','764947623','0841108',1,NULL,'Although not terribly focused, Hannah Takes the Stairs contains refreshing realism.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/96/45/17/9645175_mob.jpg'),(3615,'Town & Country',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/town_and_country/','16253','0141907',1,NULL,'Afflicted with extensive re-editing and re-writing, this sex comedy feels confusingly choppy. Also, the main characters are so wealthy and privileged that it\'s difficult to feel sympathy for their problems.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/28/30/283026_mob.jpg'),(3616,'The Awful Truth',1937,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/awful_truth/','18779','0028597',1,NULL,'Great comic direction by Leo McCarrey and memorable onscreen chemistry from stars Cary Grant and Irene Dunne make this screwball comedy a charmer.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/29/39/293993_mob.jpg'),(3617,'L\' Avocat de la Terreur (Terror\'s Advocate)',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10008699-terrors_advocate/','770674534','1032854',1,NULL,'Terror\'s Advocate is a fascinating portrayal of a controversial political figure; both morally unsettling and emotionally gripping.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/12/33/10123317_mob.jpg'),(3618,'Playtime (Play Time)',1967,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/playtime/','20767','0062136',1,NULL,'A remarkable achievement, Playtime\'s packs every scene with sight gags and characters that both celebrates and satirizes the urbanization of modern life.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/30/34/303402_mob.jpg'),(3619,'Better Luck Tomorrow',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/better_luck_tomorrow/','14423','0280477',1,NULL,'A promising work by Lin, the energetic Better Luck Tomorrow is disturbing and thought-provoking.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/84/10888455_mob.jpg'),(3620,'Time of the Wolf',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1132644-time_of_the_wolf/','19527','0324197',1,NULL,'A lean and unsettlingly thriller.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/29/75/297598_mob.jpg'),(3621,'Thin Ice',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/thin_ice_2012/','771265644','1512240',1,'Mickey Prohaska (Greg Kinnear) is a small-time insurance agent looking for a way to jump-start his business, reunite with his estranged wife (Lea Thompson) and escape the frigid Wisconsin weather. This self-proclaimed master of spin believes that salesmanship is about selling a story - all he needs is a sucker willing to buy it. He hits pay dirt with a lonely retired farmer (Alan Arkin) who is sitting on something much bigger than an insurance commission. But Mickey\'s attempt to con the old man spins out of control when a nosy, unstable locksmith (Billy Crudup) with a volatile temper dramatically ups the stakes, trapping him in a madcap spiral of danger, deceit and double-crossing. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/37/11163749_mob.jpg'),(3622,'Tales of the Night',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tales_of_the_night/','771235484','1828229',1,'Tales of the Night is renowned animation auteur Michel Ocelot\'s first foray into 3D animation. A hit at the Berlin Film Festival, the film extends the earlier shadow puppet style of Ocelot\'s Princes and Princesses, with black silhouetted characters set off against exquisitely detailed Day-Glo backgrounds bursting with color and kaleidoscopic patterns - the subtle use of 3D creating a diorama-like effect. The film weaves together six exotic fables each unfolding in a unique locale, from Tibet, to medieval Europe, an Aztec kingdom, the African plains, and even the Land of the Dead. In Ocelot\'s storytelling, history blends with fairytale as viewers are whisked off to enchanted lands full of dragons, werewolves, captive princesses, sorcerers, and enormous talking bees - and each fable ends with its own ironic twist. -- (C) GKIDS',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/66/11166676_mob.jpg'),(3623,'The Three Caballeros',1944,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the-three-caballeros/','9533','0038166',1,NULL,'One of Disney\'s more abstract creations, The Three Caballeros is a dazzling, colorful picture that shows the company at an artistic acme.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/70/10887063_mob.jpg'),(3624,'Don\'t Move (Non ti muovere)',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dont_move/','230347502','0330702',1,NULL,'Sergio Castellitto\'s latest film has a heavy dose of melodrama and is populated with unlikable characters.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/90/74/10907434_mob.jpg'),(3625,'The Burma Conspiracy (Largo Winch (Tome 2))',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_burma_conspiracy/','771229859','1322333',1,'Immediately after selling his late father\'s corporation to found a humanitarian organization, Largo Winch (Tomer Sisley) finds himself the target of some shocking allegations. Now, in order to clear his name, Largo must travel deep into the jungles of Burma and get back in touch with his roots. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(3626,'Biggie and Tupac',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/biggie_and_tupac/','15827','0303356',1,NULL,'This is a compelling documentary, even for those who aren\'t fans of rap.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/90/06/10900681_mob.jpg'),(3627,'The Taste of Others',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_taste_of_others/','770674798','0216787',1,NULL,'The Taste of Others is a fresh, witty comedy about the attraction of opposites. The characters are well-drawn and engaging and their social interactions believable.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/14/86/11148634_mob.jpg'),(3628,'Hidden Colors 2: The Triumph of Melanin',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hidden_colors_2_the_triumph_of_melanin_2012/','771321775','2404572',1,'Hidden Colors 2 is the follow up to the critically acclaimed 2011 documentary about the untold history of people of African and aboriginal descent. This installment of Hidden Colors goes into topics such as: The global African presence The science of melanin The truth about the prison industrial complex How thriving black economic communities were undermined in America The hidden truth about Native Americans And much more Hidden Colors 2 is directed by New York Times best selling author and film producer Tariq Nasheed (Hidden Colors, The Eugenist)',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/76/11167698_mob.jpg'),(3629,'Twilight',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1082855-twilight/','14311','0119594',1,NULL,'It suffers from a frustratingly deliberate pace, but with nuanced performances from Paul Newman, Gene Hackman, Susan Sarandon, and Reese Witherspoon to fall back on, Twilight can\'t help but be compelling.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/78/10887854_mob.jpg'),(3630,'Happy, Texas',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/happy_texas/','10925','0162360',1,NULL,'A smart, light-hearted romantic comedy, Happy, Texas uses its well-written script and exceptional cast to prove there\'s still life left in the fish-out-of-water caper genre.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/50/10885052_mob.jpg'),(3631,'Texas Rangers',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1111103-texas_rangers/','12204','0193560',1,NULL,'As far as westerns go, Texas Rangers is strictly mediocre stuff.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/13/99/11139981_mob.jpg'),(3632,'Aftershocks (Tangshan dadizhen)',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/aftershock_the_imax_experience/','771203903','1393746',1,'Two natural disasters frame a story of a mother, her children and a painful decision that scars them forever in this grand-scale drama from China. In 1976, Li Yuanni (Xu Fan) is living in the city of Tangshan with her two children, seven year old twins Fang Da and Fang Deng. The family\'s life is simple but full of joy until a massive earthquake levels the city and leaves a swath of destruction in its wake. Amidst the wreckage, Li Yuanni discovers both Fang Da and Fang Deng are caught under a concrete slab, and if enough is broken to rescue one of the children, it would tip the balance and crush the other. Li Yuanni is asked which child should be saved, and she impulsively answers her son Fang Da. The boy is rescued, but the effort costs him his arm; meanwhile, the daughter Fang Deng is left for dead but miraculously survives, and is eventually adopted by another family without Li Yuanni\'s knowledge. The mother is forced to live with the shame of her decision, Fang Da grows to be a physically and emotionally broken man, and Fang Deng studies medicine, starts a family on her own and leaves China for Canada. It\'s not until 2008 that the story of the mother and the daughter she lost comes full circle in the wake of another earthquake in Sichuan. A massive commercial success in China, Tang Shan Da Di Zhen (aka Aftershock) made its North American debut at the 2010 Toronto International Film Festival. ~ Mark Deming, Rovi',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/24/11152465_mob.jpg'),(3633,'Trouble Every Day (Gargoyle)',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trouble_every_day/','770670250','0204700',1,NULL,'An erotic thriller dulled by a messy narrative.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/92/12/10921254_mob.jpg'),(3634,'Tennessee',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1206531-tennessee/','770729066','0770814',1,NULL,'Despite some beautiful scenery, Tennessee can\'t extend its simple premise beyond typical independent road trip movie tropes.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/87/50/10875092_mob.jpg'),(3635,'Touch of Pink',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/touch_of_pink/','13971','0374277',1,NULL,'Kyle MacLachlan does a very good imitation Cary Grant in this forced and contrived tale.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/36/10883617_mob.jpg'),(3636,'Time Out (L\' Emploi du temps)',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/time-out-l-emploi-du-temps/','351527815','0279065',1,NULL,'A haunting psychological drama, Time Out takes a penetrating look at the angst of the modern worker.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/29/81/39/2981398_mob.jpg'),(3637,'Grandma, a Thousand Times',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/grandma_a_thousand_times/','771240312','1811329',1,'Teta, Alf Marra is a poetic documentary that puts a feisty Beiruti grandmother at the center of brave film exercises concocted by her grandson to commemorate her many worlds before they are erased by the passage of time and her eventual death. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/23/11162360_mob.jpg'),(3638,'Mr. & Mrs. Smith',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mr_and_mrs_smith/','1121','0356910',1,NULL,'Although this action-romance suffers from weak writing and one too many explosions, the chemistry generated by onscreen couple Pitt and Jolie is palpable enough to make this a thoroughly enjoyable summer action flick.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/24/98/249802_mob.jpg'),(3639,'Saw II',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/saw_ii/','8918','0432348',1,NULL,'Saw II is likely to please the gore-happy fans of the original, though it may be too gruesome for those not familiar with first film\'s premise.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/04/250414_mob.jpg'),(3640,'School of Rock',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/school_of_rock/','10315','0332379',1,NULL,'Black\'s exuberant, gleeful performance turns School of Rock into a hilarious, rocking good time.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168965_mob.jpg'),(3641,'Shrek 2',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shrek_2/','10043','0298148',1,NULL,'It may not be as fresh as the original, but topical humor and colorful secondary characters make Shrek 2 a winner in its own right.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/37/253795_mob.jpg'),(3642,'Scary Movie',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/scary_movie/','12983','0175142',1,NULL,'Critics say Scary Movie overloads on crudity and grossness to get its laughs.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/99/10879941_mob.jpg'),(3643,'Spider-Man',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spiderman/','10122',NULL,1,NULL,'Not only does Spider-Man provide a good dose of web-swinging fun, it also has a heart, thanks to the combined charms of director Sam Raimi and star Tobey Maguire.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/52/11165293_mob.jpg'),(3644,'The Simpsons Movie',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/simpsons_movie/','406923403','0462538',1,NULL,'The Simpsons Movie contains the hearty laughs, biting satire, and honest portrayal of an American family that makes the show so popular. And it boasts slicker animation and polished writing that hearkens back to the show\'s glory days.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/84/37/10843725_mob.jpg'),(3645,'Spider-Man 3',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spiderman_3/','358167972','0413300',1,NULL,'Though there are more characters and plotlines, and the action sequences still dazzle, Spider-Man 3 nonetheless isn\'t quite as refined as the first two.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/52/11165292_mob.jpg'),(3646,'Shutter Island',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1198124-shutter_island/','770681152','1130884',1,'Martin Scorsese and Leonardo DiCaprio team up for a fourth time for this adaptation of Shutter Island, a novel by Dennis Lehane (Mystic River). The film opens in 1954 as World War II veteran and current federal marshal Teddy Daniels (Leonardo DiCaprio) and his new partner, Chuck (Mark Ruffalo), ferry to Shutter Island, a water-bound mental hospital housing the criminally insane. They have been asked to investigate the disappearance of Rachel Solando (Emily Mortimer), a patient admitted to the asylum after she murdered her three children. As Teddy quizzes Dr. Cawley (Ben Kingsley), the head of the institution, he begins to suspect that the authorities in charge might not be giving him the whole truth, and that a terrible fate may befall all the patients in the spooky Ward C -- a unit devoted to the most heinous of the hospital\'s inmates. Complicating matters further, Teddy has a secret of his own -- the arsonist who murdered his wife is incarcerated on Shutter Island. Driven to confront his wife\'s killer, and stranded on the island because of a hurricane, Teddy must unravel the secrets of the eerie place before succumbing to his own madness. Max von Sydow, Emily Mortimer, Michelle Williams, Patricia Clarkson, and Jackie Earle Haley round out the supporting cast. ~ Perry Seibert, Rovi','It may not rank with Scorsese\'s best work, but Shutter Island\'s gleefully unapologetic genre thrills represent the director at his most unrestrained.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/94/04/10940421_mob.jpg'),(3647,'Man of Steel',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/superman_man_of_steel/','770678819','0770828',1,'A young boy learns that he has extraordinary powers and is not of this Earth. As a young man, he journeys to discover where he came from and what he was sent here to do. But the hero in him must emerge if he is to save the world from annihilation and become the symbol of hope for all mankind. -- (C) Warner Bros',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/59/11165966_mob.jpg'),(3648,'The Amazing Spider-Man',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_amazing_spider_man/','770771659','0948470',1,'The Amazing Spider-Man is the story of Peter Parker (Garfield), an outcast high schooler who was abandoned by his parents as a boy, leaving him to be raised by his Uncle Ben (Sheen) and Aunt May (Field). Like most teenagers, Peter is trying to figure out who he is and how he got to be the person he is today. As Peter discovers a mysterious briefcase that belonged to his father, he begins a quest to understand his parents\' disappearance - leading him directly to Oscorp and the lab of Dr. Curt Connors (Ifans), his father\'s former partner. As Spider-Man is set on a collision course with Connors\' alter-ego, The Lizard, Peter will make life-altering choices to use his powers and shape his destiny to become a hero. -- (C) Sony','A well-chosen cast and sure-handed direction allow The Amazing Spider-Man to thrill, despite revisiting many of the same plot points from 2002\'s Spider-Man.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/74/11167406_mob.jpg'),(3649,'The Last Stand',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/last_stand_2013/','771249652','1549920',1,'After leaving his LAPD narcotics post following a bungled operation that left him wracked with remorse and regret, Sheriff Ray Owens (Schwarzenegger) moved out of Los Angeles and settled into a life fighting what little crime takes place in sleepy border town Sommerton Junction. But that peaceful existence is shattered when Gabriel Cortez (Eduardo Noriega), the most notorious, wanted drug kingpin in the western hemisphere, makes a deadly yet spectacular escape from an FBI prisoner convoy. (c) Lionsgate','There\'s nothing particularly distinguished about it, but for Schwarzenegger fans The Last Stand provides perfectly undemanding entertainment.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/70/11167087_mob.jpg'),(3650,'Seven Pounds',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/seven_pounds/','770767898','0814314',1,NULL,'Grim and morose, Seven Pounds is also undone by an illogical plot.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/87/76/10877624_mob.jpg'),(3651,'Snitch',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/snitch_2013/','771316320','0882977',1,'In the fast-paced action thriller SNITCH, Dwayne Johnson stars as a father whose teenage son is wrongly accused of a drug distribution crime and is looking at a mandatory minimum prison sentence of 10 years. Desperate and determined to rescue his son at all costs, he makes a deal with the U.S. attorney to work as an undercover informant and infiltrate a drug cartel on a dangerous mission -- risking everything, including his family and his own life. (c) Summit',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/83/11168350_mob.jpg'),(3652,'Stoker',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stoker_2013/','771312246','1682180',1,'After India\'s father dies in an auto accident, her Uncle Charlie, who she never knew existed, comes to live with her and her emotionally unstable mother. Soon after his arrival, she comes to suspect this mysterious, charming man has ulterior motives, but instead of feeling outrage or horror, this friendless girl becomes increasingly infatuated with him.',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/78/11167875_mob.jpg'),(3653,'The Amazing Spider-Man 2',2014,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_amazing_spider_man_2/','771249926',NULL,1,'The web-slingin\' wall-crawler hits the screens once again in this follow-up to Marc Webb\'s 2012 reboot of the series. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(3654,'Percy Jackson: Sea of Monsters',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/percy_jackson_sea_of_monsters/','771257656','1854564',1,'Percy Jackson, the son of Poseidon, continues his epic journey to fulfill his destiny, as he teams with his demigod friends to retrieve the Golden Fleece, which has the power to save their home and training ground, Camp Half-Blood.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(3655,'The Sorcerer and the White Snake',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_sorcerer_and_the_white_snake/','771252631','1857913',1,'Action director Ching Siu-Tung helms this fantasy film based on an old Chinese legend about an herbalist who falls in love with a thousand-year-old White Snake disguised as a woman. Jet Li stars as a sorcerer who discovers her true identity and battles to save the man\'s soul. (c) Magnolia',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/83/11168317_mob.jpg'),(3656,'The Sweeney',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_sweeney/','771303984','0857190',1,'Tearing up the streets of London, THE SWEENEY is a stylish, exhilarating action thriller proving sometimes you have to act like a criminal to catch a criminal. Armed and dangerous, the Sweeney Flying Squad are old school crime fighters enforcing the law. Led by legendary detective Jack Regan (Ray Winstone) and his loyal partner, they have their own unique way of operating and always get results. With a bank heist in progress and his old enemy making a reappearance on the London crime scene, Regan will do whatever it takes to get the job done, even defying orders from his no-nonsense boss (Damian Lewis). (c) eOne',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/68/11166895_mob.jpg'),(3657,'Sydney White',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sydney_white/','770674408','0815244',1,NULL,'Amanda Bynes is charming, but Sydney White is a poorly adapted take on Snow White, relying on tired ethnic stereotypes laughs.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/99/50/88/9950880_mob.jpg'),(3658,'The Angels\' Share',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_angels_share/','771303117',NULL,1,'The Angels\' Share introduces Robbie, an ex-offender and new father who embarks on an adventure with his new found friends to a whisky distillery and discovers that turning to drink might just change his life.',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/52/11165231_mob.jpg'),(3659,'The Sapphires',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_sapphires_2012/','771307345','1673697',1,'Inspired by a true story, THE SAPPHIRES follows four vivacious, young and talented Australian Aboriginal girls from a remote mission as they learn about love, friendship and war when their all girl group The Sapphires entertains the U.S. troops in Vietnam in 1968. Cynthia (Tapsell), Gail (Mailman), Julie (Mauboy) and Kay (Sebbens) are discovered by Dave (O\'Dowd), a good-humored talent scout with a kind heart, very little rhythm but a great knowledge of soul music. As their manager, Dave books the sisters their first true gig giving them their first taste of stardom, and travels them to Vietnam to sing for the American troops. (c) Weinstein','While it\'s plenty predictable and sentimental, The Sapphires also has an irresistible feel-good vibe, winning music and charming performances to spare.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/78/11167891_mob.jpg'),(3660,'Storage 24',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/storage_24/','771305466',NULL,1,'London is in chaos. A military cargo plane has crashed leaving its highly classified contents strewn across the city. Completely unaware London is in lockdown, Charlie and Shelley, accompanied by best friends Mark and Nikki, are at a Storage 24 dividing up their possessions after a recent break-up. Suddenly, the power goes off. Trapped in a dark maze of endless corridors, a mystery predator is hunting them one by one. In a place designed to keep things in, how do you get out?',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/85/11168577_mob.jpg'),(3661,'The Smurfs 2',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_smurfs_2/','771251238','2017020',1,'The Smurfs are back with this follow-up to the blockbuster smash hit from 2011. J. David Stem and David Weiss provide the script, from a story they wrote with Jay Scherick and David Ronn. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/74/11167458_mob.jpg'),(3662,'Starbuck',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/starbuck/','771243352','1756750',1,'Just when David Wosniak (Patrick Huard) decides to finally take control of his life, this eternal 42 year old teenager discovers that he\'s the biological father of 533 children. Suddenly, his life is much more complicated than he anticipated.',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/45/11164583_mob.jpg'),(3663,'The Seventh Son',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_seventh_son_2013/','771247934','1121096',1,'In a time long past, an evil is about to be unleashed that will reignite the war between the forces of the supernatural and humankind once more. Master Gregory (Jeff Bridges) is a knight who had imprisoned the malevolently powerful witch, Mother Malkin (Julianne Moore), centuries ago. But now she has escaped and is seeking vengeance. Summoning her followers of every incarnation, Mother Malkin is preparing to unleash her terrible wrath on an unsuspecting world. Only one thing stands in her way: Master Gregory. In a deadly reunion, Gregory comes face to face with the evil he always feared would someday return. He has only until the next full moon to do what usually takes years: train his new apprentice, Tom Ward (Ben Barnes) to fight a dark magic unlike any other. Man\'s only hope lies in the seventh son of a seventh son. (c) WB',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(3664,'The Lords of Salem',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_lords_of_salem/','771210038','1731697',1,'A Salem radio DJ receives a mysterious record that unleashes a diabolical force of evil on the town where a coven of witches were once burned alive in this slow-burn shocker written and directed by Rob Zombie, and produced by Paranormal Activity\'s Oren Peli. Back in 1692, Reverend Jonathan Hawthorne condemned a coven of witches led by Margaret Morgan (Meg Foster) to death, slaying them without remorse in the woods surrounding Salem. Just over 300 years later, the small town has become a beacon for anyone interested in the supernatural. Every night, Heidi (Sheri Moon-Zombie) and her two co-hosts (Ken Foree and Jeffrey Daniel Phillips) take to the airwaves for a popular radio show with a playful occult slant, and one day after interviewing noted author Francis Matthias (Bruce Davison) she receives a package containing a record from a band named The Lords. The following day, when Heidi impulsively plays the record on the airwaves, a strange spell falls over the locals. Later, as The Lords announce they will be performing a concert in town and the typically carefree Heidi grows increasingly withdrawn, Matthias senses that the sins of the past may be returning to haunt Salem. And he couldn\'t be more right. Something wicked has returned to this cursed town, and with each day that passes, Heidi slips ever deeper into its malevolent grasp. Patricia Quinn, Dee Wallace, Michael Berryman, and Sid Haig co-star. ~ Rovi',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(3665,'Mr. Peabody & Sherman',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mr_peabody_and_sherman/','771169232','0864835',1,'Rocky and Bullwinkle Show time-travelers Mr. Peabody and his adopted human sidekick, Sherman (voiced by Ty Burrell and Max Charles, respectively), strike out on their own for a big-screen CGI adventure in this feature directed by Rob Minkoff (The Haunted Mansion). Stephen Colbert and Allison Janney head up the rest of the voice cast. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(3666,'Stretch Armstrong',2014,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stretch_armstrong/','771189957','1379164',1,'Mr. Show\'s Bob Odenkirk takes a stab at the action comedy world with his script for the adaptation of the Hasbro action figure Stretch Armstrong. The Universal Pictures production is being produced by Brian Goldner and Bennett Schneir. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(3667,'The Stepfather',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10010668-stepfather/','770798701','0814335',1,NULL,'This tepid remake of the 1987 cult classic lacks the tension and satirical undercurrents of the original.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/93/10889320_mob.jpg'),(3668,'Like Someone in Love',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/like_someone_in_love/','771306001','1843287',1,'When Akiko (Rin Takanashi), a lovely Tokyo student who moonlights as a call girl, is dispatched to a new client in the suburbs, she is surprised to find the shy and elderly Takashi (81-year-old stage actor Tadashi Okuno), a committed academic constantly distracted by work-related phone calls. The lonely widower seems far more interested in playing house than having sex, however, and the young woman soon falls asleep. The next day, when the two encounter Akiko\'s volatile boyfriend Noriaki (Ryo Kase), Takashi plays into Noriaki\'s assumption that he is actually Akiko\'s grandfather. As the three settle into their new roles, Takashi finds himself becoming the protector that Akiko so desperately needs. (c) Sundance Selects',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/65/11166552_mob.jpg'),(3669,'Small Apartments',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/small_apartments_2012/','771271118','1272886',1,'Franklin Franklin plays the alphorn and dreams of Switzerland. His crazy brother sends him fingernail clippings in the mail. One of his neighbors is a forgetful pot-head, the other a gruff busybody who doesn\'t miss anything. Across the street live a mother and her fifteen-year-old daughter, whom he likes to watch from his window, but none of these are Franklin\'s real problem. His real problem is that his landlord is dead, laid out on the linoleum of his kitchen, and Switzerland seems farther away all the time. (c) Official site',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/87/11168796_mob.jpg'),(3670,'Saadi Love Story',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/saadi_love_story_2013/','771323597',NULL,1,'Preeti, who is a die hard romantic waits for her prince charming, who would come some day and sweep her off her feet. But when two boys show up at their door claiming to be the one that Preeti\'s sister Gurleen had chosen to spend her life with, Preeti and her family finds themselves in a delimma. They hear to the love stories of both Rajveer, one an aspiring photographer and the other an aspiring singer. Preeti who lives in the world of romance wishes that what the boys had narrated would both be true.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(3671,'Saving Lincoln',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/saving_lincoln/','771313112','2034098',1,'The story of Mr. Lincoln and his self-appointed bodyguard, U.S. Marshal Ward Hill Lamon - a banjo-playing Southerner who foiled repeated attempts on the President\'s life, and kept him functioning during the darkest hours of the Civil War. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/87/11168728_mob.jpg'),(3672,'Need For Speed',2014,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/need_for_speed/','771311994','2369135',1,'Walt Disney Pictures and DreamWorks Entertainment present this adaptation of the hit videogame series, Need for Speed. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(3673,'Our School',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/our-school/','770678673','1238762',1,'Three Roma children in a small Transylvanian town are among the pioneer participants in an initiative to integrate the ethnically segregated Romanian schools. When their school begins to desegregate, Alin, Benjamin, and Dana set out for the city school, optimistic for education and new friendships, even as funds earmarked for integration are questionably used to renovate the old Roma-only school in their village. (c) Official FB',NULL,'http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/38/11163868_mob.jpg'),(3674,'Something in the Air',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/771315926/','771315926','1846472',1,'On behalf of Sundance Selects, you and a guest are invited to a screening of SOMETHING IN THE AIR, the newest film by French filmmaker Olivier Assayas. Following his critical triumphs, SUMMER HOURS and CARLOS, Assayas\' semi-autobiographical new feature is a vibrant, incisively crafted story of a young man\'s artistic awakening in the politically turbulent French student movement of the early \'70s. In a nod to his earlier film COLD WATER, Assayas\' surrogate Gilles (newcomer Clement Metayer) is a graduating high school student in Paris deeply involved in the counterculture of the time. While Gilles begins to realize that his interests lie more in the revolutions in music and art, he finds himself pulled into ever more dangerous political protests by the people around him, especially his radicalized girlfriend (Lola Creton of GOODBYE FIRST LOVE). Illuminating and elegiac, Assayas\' story celebrates that thrilling, evanescent moment in history when young people could feel revolution just within their grasp.',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/66/11166638_mob.jpg'),(3675,'Singularity',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/singularity_2013/','771247275',NULL,1,'A father tries to keep the spirit of his injured son alive with the help of nanotechnology in this sci-fi tale from 2012 helmer, Roland Emmerich. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(3676,'Saw VI',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/saw_VI/','770797724','1233227',1,NULL,'It won\'t earn the franchise many new fans, but Saw VI is a surprising step up for what has become an intricately grisly annual tradition.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/91/54/10915413_mob.jpg'),(3677,'Sisterakas',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sisterakas_2013/','771324883','2590214',1,'The childhoods of Bernice and Detty were worlds apart, but they did have one thing in common: their father. Bernice\'s birth was the result of an infidelity on his behalf, however, and so while Detty grew up with a wealthy family, Bernice and his mother were left to fend for themselves. Years later, Bernice has become a wealthy and successful businessman. But his abrasive personality and rudeness have led to the resignation of his 75th assistant. Detty, meanwhile, is in dire need of a job and applies for the newly vacated position as executive assistant to a man that, unbeknownst to her, is actually her half-brother. For Detty, this job means she can take care of her daughters; for Bernice, it\'s a chance for payback.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(3678,'Spiders',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spiders_2013/','771325418',NULL,1,'SPIDERS centers on mutant spiders that fall to earth from a disabled Soviet space station. With New York City threatened to be overrun, it\'s up to transit supervisor Jason Cole and health inspector Rachel Cole to save their daughter and prevent the colossal Queen Spider from uniting with her eggs and creating an army of massive killer spiders.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(3679,'La Scala: Lohengrin',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/la_scala_lohengrin/','771322511',NULL,1,'Wagner\'s deeply romantic opera about a chivalrous but anonymous knight marked his first exploration of leitmotifs, a musical innovation that changed the history of opera.',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(3680,'One Night Stand: Overnight Musicals',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/one_night_stand_overnight_musicals/','771323411',NULL,1,'Experience what it\'s like for writers, composers, lyricists and talent to pull an all-nighter to write a script, compose music, add lyrics and learn lines-because in just 24 hours-the show will make its one night open and close at New York City\'s Gramercy Theatre. Audiences will also be treated to special behind the scenes footage and interviews with some of the actors in One Night Stand as they take us through their day-to-day lives. One Night Stand features some of New York and Hollywood\'s top theatre, film and television actors, writers and directors including: Richard Kind, Cheyenne Jackson, Jesse Tyler Ferguson, Rachel Dratch, Roger Bart, Mandy Gonzalez, Capathia Jenkins, Theresa McCarthy, Nellie McKay, Marnie Schulenburg, Scarlet Strallen, Tracie Thoms, Tamara Tunie, Alicia Witt and more!',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(3681,'The Other Side of the Ice',2013,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_other_side_of_the_ice/','771323796','2516320',1,'Hole in the Wall Productions has assembled a team of sailors, divers and filmmakers uniquely suited to not only take on the challenges of an Arctic expedition but to capture its geography and inhabitants on film in dramatic and compelling ways. The Arctic is always perilous. The film will be a journey for the ages, an unprecedented view into a stark and unforgiving world. (c) Official Site',NULL,'http://images.rottentomatoescdn.com/images/redesign/poster_default.gif'),(3682,'Quantum of Solace',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/quantum_of_solace/','770679948','0830515',1,NULL,'Brutal and breathless, Quantum Of Solace delivers tender emotions along with frenetic action. Not as good as franchise reboot Casino Royale, but still an impressive entry to the Bond canon.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/86/77/10867703_mob.jpg'),(3683,'Stop-Loss',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stop_loss/','770671517','0489281',1,NULL,'Stop-Loss is sincere and complex, and features strong performances, even if it tries to cover too much ground.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/84/63/10846366_mob.jpg'),(3684,'Saw IV',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/saw_4/','577164571','0890870',1,NULL,'Saw IV is more disturbing than compelling, with material already seen in the prior installments.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/98/90/53/9890532_mob.jpg'),(3685,'She\'s the Man',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shes_the_man/','112770423',NULL,1,NULL,'Shakespeare\'s wit gets lost in translation with She\'s the Man\'s broad slapstick, predictable jokes, and unconvincing plotline.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/31/32/313227_mob.jpg'),(3686,'Stardust',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stardust/','392799904','0486655',1,NULL,'A faithful interpretation that captures the spirit of whimsy, action, and off-kilter humor of Neil Gaiman, Stardust juggles multiple genres and tones to create a fantastical experience.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/87/30/70/8730702_mob.jpg'),(3687,'My Sister\'s Keeper',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10010662-my_sisters_keeper/','770785740','1078588',1,NULL,'My Sister\'s Keeper gets fine performances from its adult and child actors, but the director\'s heavy-handed approach turns a worthy emotional subject into an overly melodramatic tearjerker.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/81/10888148_mob.jpg'),(3688,'Speed Racer',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/speed_racer/','770669719','0811080',1,NULL,'The Wachowski Brothers have overloaded Speed Racer with headache-inducing special effects, and neglected to develop a coherent storyline.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/09/10880985_mob.jpg'),(3689,'Superman Returns',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/superman_returns/','155655236','0348150',1,NULL,'Singer\'s reverent and visually decadent adaptation gives the Man of Steel welcome emotional complexity. The result: a satisfying stick-to-your-ribs adaptation.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/45/20/452092_mob.jpg'),(3690,'Open Season',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/open_season/','287865419','0400717',1,NULL,'Open Season is a cliched palette of tired jokes and CG animal shenanigans that have been seen multiple times this cinematic year.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/91/66/10916662_mob.jpg'),(3691,'Sorority Row',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sorority_row/','770798314','1232783',1,NULL,'Though it\'s slick and stylish, Sorority Row offers nothing new to the slasher genre and misses the mark both in its attempts at humor and thrills.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/18/11151822_mob.jpg'),(3692,'The Strangers',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_strangers/','678555400','0482606',1,NULL,'The Strangers provides a few scares, but offers little else to distinguish itself from other slasher films.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/12/79/11127923_mob.jpg'),(3693,'All About Steve',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/all_about_steve/','770680913','0881891',1,NULL,'All About Steve is an oddly creepy, sour film, featuring a heroine so desperate and peculiar that audiences may be more likely to pity than root for her.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/89/33/10893339_mob.jpg'),(3694,'21 Jump Street',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/21-jump-street-2011/','770863876','1232829',1,'In the action-comedy 21 Jump Street, Schmidt (Jonah Hill) and Jenko (Channing Tatum) are more than ready to leave their adolescent problems behind. Joining the police force and the secret Jump Street unit, they use their youthful appearances to go undercover in a local high school. As they trade in their guns and badges for backpacks, Schmidt and Jenko risk their lives to investigate a violent and dangerous drug ring. But they find that high school is nothing like they left it just a few years earlier - and neither expects that they will have to confront the terror and anxiety of being a teenager again and all the issues they thought they had left behind. -- (C) Sony Pictures','A smart, affectionate satire of \'80s nostalgia and teen movie tropes, 21 Jump Street offers rowdy mainstream comedy with a surprisingly satisfying bite.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/56/11165666_mob.jpg'),(3695,'Shooter',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shooter/','462977108','0822854',1,NULL,'With an implausible story and numerous plot holes, Shooter fails to distinguish itself from other mindless action-thrillers.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168966_mob.jpg'),(3696,'Surrogates',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10009598-surrogates/','770801542','0986263',1,NULL,'Though it sports a slick look and feel, Surrogates fails to capitalize on a promising premise, relying instead on mindless action and a poor script.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/77/10887734_mob.jpg'),(3697,'Saw III',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/saw_3/','314387954','0489270',1,NULL,'Saw III does little beyond repeating its predecessor\'s tropes on a gorier level.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/27/09/94/2709946_mob.jpg'),(3698,'Perfect Stranger',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1171939-perfect_stranger/','462963908','0457433',1,NULL,'Despite the presence of Halle Berry and Bruce Willis, Perfect Stranger is too convoluted to work, and features a twist ending that\'s irritating and superfluous. It\'s a techno-thriller without thrills.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/92/11/10921173_mob.jpg'),(3699,'The Soloist',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/soloist/','770782191','0821642',1,NULL,'Though it features strong performances by its lead players, a lack of narrative focus prevents The Soloist from hitting its mark.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/85/89/10858997_mob.jpg'),(3700,'Scarface',1983,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1018324-scarface/','12881','0086250',1,NULL,'Director Brian De Palma and star Al Pacino take it to the limit in this stylized, ultra-violent and eminently quotable gangster epic that walks a thin white line between moral drama and celebratory excess.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/88/11168894_mob.jpg'),(3701,'Saving Private Ryan',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/saving_private_ryan/','13217','0120815',1,NULL,'Anchored by another winning performance from Hanks, Spielberg\'s unflinchingly realistic war film virtually redefines the genre.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/55/05/49/5505494_mob.jpg'),(3702,'Salt',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1213717-salt/','770805753','0944835',1,'As a CIA officer, Evelyn Salt (Jolie) swore an oath to duty, honor and country. Her loyalty will be tested when a defector accuses her of being a Russian spy. Salt goes on the run, using all her skills and years of experience as a covert operative to elude capture. Salt\'s efforts to prove her innocence only serve to cast doubt on her motives, as the hunt to uncover the truth behind her identity continues and the question remains: \"Who Is Salt?\"-- (C) Sony','Angelina Jolie gives it her all in the title role, and her seasoned performance is almost enough to save Salt from its predictable and ludicrous plot.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/92/75/10927520_mob.jpg'),(3703,'Scary Movie 4',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/scary_movie_4/','147302859','0362120',1,NULL,'Sure to inspire a few chuckles, but not enough to compensate for the recycled material from its predecessors.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/31/39/313998_mob.jpg'),(3704,'Semi-Pro',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/semi_pro/','770674955','0839980',1,NULL,'Semi-Pro is an intermittently funny, half-hearted attempt at sports satire, and one of Will Ferrell\'s weaker cinematic efforts.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/97/00/66/9700660_mob.jpg'),(3705,'Snakes on a Plane',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/snakes_on_a_plane/','264141101','0417148',1,NULL,'Snakes on a Plane lives up to its title, featuring snakes on a plane. It isn\'t perfect, but then again, it doesn\'t need to be.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/23/10882311_mob.jpg'),(3706,'Perfume: The Story of a Murderer',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/perfume_the_story_of_a_murderer/','343379439','0396171',1,NULL,'Perfume is what you\'d expect from a Tom Twyker-directed movie glamorizing a serial killer: a kinetic visual feast, with a dark antihero that\'s impossible to feel sympathy for.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/95/33/09/9533098_mob.jpg'),(3707,'Smokin\' Aces',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/smokin_aces/','387399996','0475394',1,NULL,'A violent mess of a movie, Smokin\' Aces has some Quentin Tarantino\'s style but not much of his wit or humor.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/33/10883345_mob.jpg'),(3708,'Scott Pilgrim vs. the World',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/scott_pilgrims_vs_the_world/','770782775','0446029',1,'Based on Bryan Lee O\'Malley\'s Oni Press comic book of the same name, Scott Pilgrim vs. the World follows the eponymous slacker rocker on his colorful quest to defeat his dream girl\'s seven evil ex-boyfriends. Twenty-two-year-old Scott Pilgrim (Michael Cera) may not have a job, but rocking the bass for his band, Sex Bob-omb, is a tough job unto itself. When Scott locks eyes with Ramona Flowers (Mary Elizabeth Winstead), he knows she\'s the girl he wants to grow old with. But Ramona has some serious baggage; her supercharged exes rue the thought of her being with another man, and they\'ll crush any guy who gives her a second glance. Now, in order to win Ramona\'s heart, Scott will do battle with everyone from vegan-powered rock gods to sinister skateboarders, never losing sight of his gorgeous goal as he pummels his way to victory. Shaun of the Dead\'s Edgar Wright directs the film from a script he penned with Michael Bacall. Superhero veterans Chris Evans and Brandon Routh co-star in the action comedy as two of the seven ex-boyfriends. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Its script may not be as dazzling as its eye-popping visuals, but Scott Pilgrim vs. the World is fast, funny, and inventive.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168901_mob.jpg'),(3709,'Secret Window',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/secret_window/','10587','0363988',1,NULL,'Depp is quirkily entertaining, but the movie runs out of steam by the end.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/16/10881658_mob.jpg'),(3710,'The Spirit',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_spirit/','770678782','0831887',1,NULL,'Though its visuals are unique, The Spirit\'s plot is almost incomprehensible, the dialogue is ludicrously mannered, and the characters are unmemorable.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/76/10877625_mob.jpg'),(3711,'Little Miss Sunshine',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/little_miss_sunshine/','190816246','0449059',1,NULL,'What happens when you stuff a failed motivation speaker, his wife, the nation\'s number one Proust scholar, an elderly potty-mouthed heroin addict, a teen who\'s mute by choice, and a bespectacled little pageant hopeful into a mini VW bus for a three day road trip? You get this hilarious but moving satire about a dysfunctional family obsessed with winning. Credit must go to the ensemble cast that includes Greg Kinnear, Steve Carell, Toni Collette, Alan Arkin, and Abigail Breslin and the delightfully funny script by Michael Arndt, which first-time directors Jonathan Dayton and Valerie Faris handled perfectly.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/18/56/91/1856911_mob.jpg'),(3712,'The Silence of the Lambs',1991,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/silence_of_the_lambs/','16286','0102926',1,NULL,'Director Jonathan Demme\'s smart, taut thriller teeters on the edge between psychological study and all-out horror, and benefits greatly from stellar performances by Anthony Hopkins and Jodie Foster.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/55/12/86/5512865_mob.jpg'),(3713,'Paranormal Activity',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/paranormal_activity/','770728015','1179904',1,NULL,'Using its low-budget effects and mockumentary method to great result, Paranormal Activity turns a simple haunted house story into 90 minutes of relentless suspense.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/91/11169199_mob.jpg'),(3714,'Silver Linings Playbook',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/silver_linings_playbook/','771253886','1045658',1,'Life doesn\'t always go according to plan. Pat Solatano (Bradley Cooper) has lost everything -- his house, his job, and his wife. He now finds himself living back with his mother (Jacki Weaver) and father (Robert DeNiro) after spending eight months is a state institution on a plea bargain. Pat is determined to rebuild his life, remain positive and reunite with his wife, despite the challenging circumstances of their separation. All Pat\'s parents want is for him to get back on his feet-and to share their family\'s obsession with the Philadelphia Eagles football team. When Pat meets Tiffany (Jennifer Lawrence), a mysterious girl with problems of her own, things get complicated. Tiffany offers to help Pat reconnect with his wife, but only if he\'ll do something very important for her in return. As their deal plays out, an unexpected bond begins to form between them, and silver linings appear in both of their lives. -- (C) Weinstein','Silver Linings Playbook walks a tricky thematic tightrope, but David O. Russell\'s sensitive direction and some sharp work from a talented cast gives it true balance.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/65/11166572_mob.jpg'),(3715,'Splice',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1208173-splice/','770682093','1017460',1,'Celebrated genetic engineers Clive (Adrien Brody) and Elsa (Sarah Polley) conduct a clandestine experiment to create an animal/human hybrid that could revolutionize modern medicine -- if it doesn\'t destroy humanity first. On the heels of engineering an entirely new species of animal, Clive and Elsa become the toast of the scientific community. Their experiment begins to spiral out of control, however, when the superstar scientists introduce human DNA into the equation. When Dren is born, Clive and Elsa welcome her into the world as the next leap in human evolution. Now, the faster Dren evolves, the more her creators start to realize they may have made a catastrophic mistake. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','It doesn\'t take its terrific premise quite as far as it should, but Splice is a smart, well-acted treat for horror fans.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/12/44/11124443_mob.jpg'),(3716,'Savages',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/savages_2012/','771241054','1615065',1,'Laguna Beach entrepreneurs Ben (Johnson), a peaceful and charitable Buddhist, and his closest friend Chon (Kitsch), a former Navy SEAL and ex-mercenary, run a lucrative, homegrown industry-raising some of the best marijuana ever developed. They also share a one-of-a-kind love with the extraordinary beauty Ophelia (Lively). Life is idyllic in their Southern California town...until the Mexican Baja Cartel decides to move in and demands that the trio partners with them. When the merciless head of the BC, Elena (Hayek), and her brutal enforcer, Lado (Del Toro), underestimate the unbreakable bond among these three friends, Ben and Chon-with the reluctant, slippery assistance of a dirty DEA agent (Travolta)-wage a seemingly unwinnable war against the cartel. -- (C) Universal','It\'s undeniably messy, but Savages finds Oliver Stone returning to dark, fearlessly lurid form.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/74/11167405_mob.jpg'),(3717,'Silent Hill',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/silent_hill/','150164942','0384537',1,NULL,'Silent Hill is visually impressive, but as with many video game adaptations, it\'s plagued by inane dialogue, a muddled plot, and an overlong runtime.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/31/40/314024_mob.jpg'),(3718,'Signs',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/signs/','10253','0286106',1,NULL,'With Signs, Shyamalan proves once again an expert at building suspense and giving audiences the chills.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/89/48/10894808_mob.jpg'),(3719,'Sleepy Hollow',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sleepy_hollow/','12871','0162661',1,NULL,'Sleepy Hollow entertains with its stunning visuals and creepy atmosphere.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168967_mob.jpg'),(3720,'Serenity',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/serenity/','8266','0379786',1,NULL,'Snappy dialogue and goofy characters make this Wild Wild West soap opera in space fun and adventurous.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/02/250218_mob.jpg'),(3721,'The Last King of Scotland',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/last_king_of_scotland/','287865404','0455590',1,NULL,'Forest Whitaker\'s performance as real-life megalomaniac dictator Idi Amin powers this fictionalized political thriller, a blunt and brutal tale about power and corruption.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/27/22/94/2722943_mob.jpg'),(3722,'The Sorcerer\'s Apprentice',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sorcerers_apprentice/','770796548','0963966',1,'Inspired by the beloved segment of the Walt Disney classic Fantasia, The Sorcerer\'s Apprentice moves the setting of the story to modern-day Manhattan, where decidedly average teen Dave Stutler (Jay Baruchel) hones his magical powers under the tutelage of master sorcerer Balthazar Blake (Nicolas Cage). Malevolent wizard Maxim Horvath (Alfred Molina) is determined to claim New York City as his own. And Horvath isn\'t alone in his diabolical endeavor, because by joining forces with the sinister sorcerer, pop illusionist Drake Stone (Toby Kebbell) aspires to gain powers beyond his wildest imagination. Realizing that he can\'t take on Horvath and Stone alone, Blake recruits Stutler as his reluctant assistant and begins training him the battle that will determine the fate of the Big Apple. Teresa Palmer and Monica Bellucci co-star. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','It has a likable cast and loads of CGI spectacle, but for all but the least demanding viewers, The Sorcerer\'s Apprentice will be less than spellbinding.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/11/99/11119967_mob.jpg'),(3723,'Schindler\'s List',1993,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/schindlers_list/','12903','0108052',1,NULL,'Schindler\'s List blends the abject horror of the Holocaust with Steven Spielberg\'s signature tender humanism to create the director\'s dramatic masterpiece.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/71/267112_mob.jpg'),(3724,'Stormbreaker (Alex Rider: Operation Stormbreaker)',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stormbreaker/','221154543','0457495',1,NULL,'Alex Rider: Operation Stormbreaker is strictly children\'s fare, as it lacks originality, excitement, and believabiltity.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/95/21/11/9521116_mob.jpg'),(3725,'Saw',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/saw/','16980','0387564',1,NULL,'A twisted and gory horror film that\'s not for the squeamish.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/28/57/285702_mob.jpg'),(3726,'Seven Psychopaths',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/seven_psychopaths/','771271681','1931533',1,'Marty (Farrell) is a struggling writer who dreams of finishing his screenplay, \"Seven Psychopaths\". Billy (Rockwell) is Marty\'s best friend, an unemployed actor and part time dog thief, who wants to help Marty by any means necessary. All he needs is a little focus and inspiration. Hans (Walken) is Billy\'s partner in crime. A religious man with a violent past. Charlie (Harrelson) is the psychopathetic gangster whose beloved dog, Billy and Hans have just stolen. Charlie\'s unpredictable, extremely violent and wouldn\'t think twice about killing anyone or anything associated with the theft. Marty is going to get all the focus and inspiration he needs, just as long as he lives to tell the tale. -- (C) Official Site','Seven Psychopaths delivers sly cinematic commentary while serving up a heaping helping of sharp dialogue and gleeful violence.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/85/11168525_mob.jpg'),(3727,'In Her Shoes',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/in_her_shoes/','8567','0388125',1,NULL,'Honesty and solid performances make In Her Shoes a solid fit for all audiences.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/02/250299_mob.jpg'),(3728,'Sicko',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sicko/','770670573','0386032',1,NULL,'Driven by Michael Moore\'s sincere humanism, Sicko is a devastating, convincing, and very entertaining documentary about the state of America\'s health care.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/75/30/61/7530614_mob.jpg'),(3729,'Skyfall',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/skyfall/','770680844','1074638',1,'In Skyfall, Bond\'s loyalty to M is tested as her past comes back to haunt her. As MI6 comes under attack, 007 must track down and destroy the threat, no matter how personal the cost. -- (C) Official Site','Sam Mendes brings Bond surging back with a smart, sexy, riveting action thriller that qualifies as one of the best 007 films to date.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/82/11168295_mob.jpg'),(3730,'Superman',1978,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/superman_the_movie/','2849381','0078346',1,NULL,'Superman deftly blends humor and gravitas, taking advantage of the perfectly cast Christopher Reeve to craft a loving, nostalgic tribute to an American pop culture icon.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/98/11159893_mob.jpg'),(3731,'Safe',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/safe_2011/','771242218','1656190',1,'A second-rate cage fighter on the mixed martial arts circuit, Luke Wright lives a numbing life of routine beatings and chump change...until the day he blows a rigged fight. Wanting to make an example of him, the Russian Mafia murders his family and banishes him from his life forever, leaving Luke to wander the streets of New York destitute, haunted by guilt, and tormented by the knowledge that he will always be watched, and anyone he develops a relationship with will also be killed. <br /><br /> But when he witnesses a frightened twelve-year-old Chinese girl, Mei, being pursued by the same gangsters who killed his wife, Luke impulsively jumps to action...and straight into the heart of a deadly high-stakes war. -- (C) Lionsgate','While hard-hitting and violently inventive, Safe ultimately proves too formulaic to set itself apart from the action thriller pack -- including some of its star\'s better films.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/31/11163138_mob.jpg'),(3732,'The Shining',1980,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shining/','14884','0081505',1,NULL,'Though it deviates from Stephen King\'s novel, Stanley Kubrick\'s The Shining is a chilling, often baroque journey into madness -- exemplified by an unforgettable turn from Jack Nicholson','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/80/11168032_mob.jpg'),(3733,'The Sixth Sense',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sixth_sense/','10054','0167404',1,NULL,'M Night Shayamalan\'s The Sixth Sense is a twisty ghost story with all the style of a classical Hollywood picture, but all the chills of a modern horror flick.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/38/253818_mob.jpg'),(3734,'Shutter',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10009254-shutter/','770670721','0482599',1,NULL,'Being a remake of a Thai horror film instead of Japanese doesn\'t prevent Shutter from being another lame Asian horror remake.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/87/04/10870439_mob.jpg'),(3735,'Meet the Spartans',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/meet_the_spartans/','770680135','1073498',1,NULL,'A tired, unfunny, offensive waste of time, Meet the Spartans scrapes the bottom of the cinematic barrel.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/79/98/10799893_mob.jpg'),(3736,'Wall Street: Money Never Sleeps',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wall_street_money_never_sleeps/','770814365','1027718',1,'Ambitious young investment banker Jacob Moore (Shia LaBeouf) discovers that greed is still the name of the game when he forges a fragile alliance with onetime Wall Street hotshot Gordon Gekko (Michael Douglas) shortly after Gekko is released from prison. Having served eight years for securities fraud, money laundering, and racketeering, Gekko emerges from prison to find that his daughter, Winnie (Carey Mulligan), prefers to remain estranged, and that his former Wall Street cohorts are still raking in the cash. Flash-forward to 2008, and Winnie is dating a proprietary trader named Jake Moore (LaBeouf), who expresses a passion for green energy while working for his mentor Louis Zabel (Frank Langella), of Keller Zabel Investments. Despite heading up one of the most prominent investment firms in the country, Louis Zabel is forced to personally fight for the future of Keller Zabel before the Federal Reserve after the company\'s stock takes a hit due to persistent rumors that it\'s being dragged down by debt. Denied a bailout from the government, Keller Zabel soon falls victim to a hostile takeover lead by powerful investment bank partner Bretton James (Josh Brolin), of Churchill Schwartz. His job on the line and his mentor out of the picture, Jake discovers that Gordon Gekko is out promoting his new book \"Is Greed Good?\" and decides to attend a lecture being given by the author at Fordham University. According to Gekko, greed is now sanctioned by the government, and the U.S. economy is on the verge of collapse as a direct result of leveraged debt and wild conjecture. When Jake goes behind Winnie\'s back to try and repair her relationship with her father, Gekko reveals his compelling theories on the likely reasons for Zabel\'s downfall. Later, as Jake begins plotting to avenge his mentor, Gekko starts to reveal his true colors. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','It\'s more entertaining than many sequels, but with Oliver Stone directing, a terrific cast, and a timely storyline that picks up where the original left off, Wall Street: Money Never Sleeps should be better.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/31/11153128_mob.jpg'),(3737,'Street Kings',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/street_kings/','770672506','0421073',1,NULL,'Street Kings contains formulaic violence but no shred of intelligence.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/20/10882007_mob.jpg'),(3738,'Lucky Number Slevin',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lucky_number_slevin/','140952467',NULL,1,NULL,'Trying too hard to be clever in a Pulp Fiction kind of way, this film succums to a convoluted plot, overly stylized characters and dizzying set design.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/91/98/10919808_mob.jpg'),(3739,'Real Steel',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/real_steel/','770858177','0433035',1,'A gritty, white-knuckle, action ride set in the near-future where the sport of boxing has gone high-tech, Real Steel stars Hugh Jackman as Charlie Kenton, a washed-up fighter who lost his chance at a title when 2000-pound, 8-foot-tall steel robots took over the ring. Now nothing but a small-time promoter, Charlie earns just enough money piecing together low-end bots from scrap metal to get from one underground boxing venue to the next. When Charlie hits rock bottom, he reluctantly teams up with his estranged son Max (Dakota Goyo) to build and train a championship contender. As the stakes in the brutal, no-holds-barred arena are raised, Charlie and Max, against all odds, get one last shot at a comeback. -- (C) Dreamworks','Silly premise notwithstanding, this is a well-made Hollywood movie: Thrilling and exciting action with just enough characterization.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/02/11160273_mob.jpg'),(3740,'Super 8',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/super_8/','771041011','1650062',1,'In the summer of 1979, a group of friends in a small Ohio town witness a catastrophic train crash while making a super 8 movie and soon suspect that it was not an accident. Shortly after, unusual disappearances and inexplicable events begin to take place in town, and the local Deputy tries to uncover the truth - something more terrifying than any of them could have imagined. -- (C) Official Site','It may evoke memories of classic summer blockbusters a little too eagerly for some, but Super 8 has thrills, visual dazzle, and emotional depth to spare.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/62/11156231_mob.jpg'),(3741,'I Am Sam',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/i_am_sam/','10389','0277027',1,NULL,'Not only does the manipulative I Am Sam oversimplify a complex issue, it drowns it in treacle.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/09/07/10090791_mob.jpg'),(3742,'Safe House',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/safe_house_2012/','771218288','1599348',1,'Denzel Washington and Ryan Reynolds star in the action-thriller Safe House. Washington plays the most dangerous renegade from the CIA, who comes back onto the grid after a decade on the run. When the South African safe house he\'s remanded to is attacked by mercenaries, a rookie operative (Reynolds) escapes with him. Now, the unlikely allies must stay alive long enough to uncover who wants them dead. -- (C) Official Site','Though Safe House is anchored by strong performances from Washington and Reynolds, they\'re let down by a thin script and choppily edited action sequences that betray the film\'s unfortunate lack of imagination.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/54/11165485_mob.jpg'),(3743,'Sucker Punch',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sucker-punch-2010/','770805422','0978764',1,'\"Sucker Punch\" is an epic action fantasy that takes us into the vivid imagination of a young girl whose dream world provides the ultimate escape from her darker reality. Unrestrained by the boundaries of time and place, she is free to go where her mind takes her, and her incredible adventures blur the lines between what\'s real and what is imaginary. She has been locked away against her will, but Babydoll (Emily Browning) has not lost her will to survive. Determined to fight for her freedom, she urges four other young girls-the reluctant Sweet Pea (Abbie Cornish), the outspoken Rocket (Jena Malone), the street-smart Blondie (Vanessa Hudgens) and the fiercely loyal Amber (Jamie Chung)-to band together and try to escape a terrible fate at the hands of their captors, Blue (Oscar Isaac) and Madam Gorski (Carla Gugino), before the mysterious High Roller (Jon Hamm) comes for Babydoll. Led by Babydoll, the girls engage in fantastical warfare against everything from samurais to serpents, with a virtual arsenal at their disposal. Together, they must decide what they are willing to sacrifice in order to stay alive. But with the help of a Wise Man (Scott Glenn), their unbelievable journey-if they succeed-will set them free.. -- (C) Warner Bros','It\'s technically impressive and loaded with eye-catching images, but without characters or a plot to support them, all of Sucker Punch\'s visual thrills are for naught.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/67/11166716_mob.jpg'),(3744,'Spider-Man 2',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spiderman_2/','11691','0316654',1,NULL,'Boasting an entertaining villain and deeper emotional focus, this is a nimble sequel that improves upon the original.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/52/11165291_mob.jpg'),(3745,'Spirited Away',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spirited_away/','10065','0245429',1,NULL,'Spirited Away is a dazzling, enchanting, and gorgeously drawn fairy tale that will leave viewers a little more curious and fascinated by the world around them.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/93/90/10939003_mob.jpg'),(3746,'Sweet Home Alabama',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sweet_home_alabama/','10199','0256415',1,NULL,'Reese Witherspoon is charming enough, but the road to Alabama is well-traveled.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/45/254526_mob.jpg'),(3747,'The Last Song',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10011984-last_song/','770808365','1294226',1,'Miley Cyrus stars as a teenager who reconnects with her father years after her parents go through a nasty divorce in this adaptation of the Nicholas Sparks novel. The novelist also provides the screenplay for the production, which is directed by Julie Ann Robinson. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi','As shamelessly manipulative as any Nicholas Sparks production, The Last Song is done no favors by its miscast and overmatched star, Miley Cyrus.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/95/54/10955405_mob.jpg'),(3748,'Superhero Movie',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1159618-superhero/','770684073','0426592',1,NULL,'Superhero Movie is not the worst of the spoof genre, but relies on tired gags and lame pop culture references all the same.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/83/93/10839344_mob.jpg'),(3749,'State of Play',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1193230-state_of_play/','770770175','0473705',1,NULL,'A taut, well-acted political thriller, State of Play overcomes some unsubtle plot twists with an intelligent script and swift direction.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/12/59/11125913_mob.jpg'),(3750,'Snatch',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/snatch/','16867','0208092',1,NULL,'Though perhaps a case of style over substance, Guy Ritchie\'s second crime caper is full of snappy dialogue, dark comedy, and interesting characters.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/93/72/10937277_mob.jpg'),(3751,'Shrek',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shrek/','10166','0126029',1,NULL,'While simultaneously embracing and subverting fairy tales, the irreverent Shrek also manages to tweak Disney\'s nose, provide a moral message to children, and offer viewers a funny, fast-paced ride.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/44/254400_mob.jpg'),(3752,'Scream 4',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/scream-4/','770807411','1262416',1,'In Scream 4, Sidney Prescott, now the author of a self-help book, returns home to Woodsboro on the last stop of her book tour. There she reconnects with Sheriff Dewey and Gale, who are now married, as well as her cousin Jill (played by Emma Roberts) and her Aunt Kate (Mary McDonnell). Unfortunately Sidney\'s appearance also brings about the return of Ghostface, putting Sidney, Gale, and Dewey, along with Jill, her friends, and the whole town of Woodsboro in danger. -- (C) Dimension','The franchise is showing its age, but Scream 4 is undeniably an improvement over its predecessor, with just enough meta humor and clever kills.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/58/11155803_mob.jpg'),(3753,'Stick It',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stick_it/','150164950','0430634',1,NULL,'Director Jessica Bendinger is unable to transfer her winning Bring It On formula to the world of gymnastics, despite Missy Peregrym\'s strong lead performance.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/31/40/314026_mob.jpg'),(3754,'Old School',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/old_school/','16825','0302886',1,NULL,'While not consistently funny, the movie does have its moments.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/31/25/312595_mob.jpg'),(3755,'Seven (Se7en)',1995,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/seven/','22538','0114369',1,NULL,'A brutal, relentlessly grimy shocker with taut performances, slick gore effects, and a haunting finale.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/67/11166782_mob.jpg'),(3756,'Syriana',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/syriana/','9369','0365737',1,NULL,'Ambitious, complicated, intellectual, and demanding of its audience, Syriana is both a gripping geopolitical thriller and wake-up call to the complacent.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/06/250615_mob.jpg'),(3757,'Sunshine',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sunshine/','512870265',NULL,1,NULL,'Danny Boyle continues his descent into mind-twisting sci-fi madness, taking us along for the ride. Sunshine fulfills the dual requisite necessary to become classic sci-fi: dazzling visuals with intelligent action.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/91/10/43/9110430_mob.jpg'),(3758,'2001: A Space Odyssey',1968,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1000085-2001_a_space_odyssey/','9917','0062622',1,NULL,'One of the most influential of all sci-fi films -- and one of the most controversial -- Stanley Kubrick\'s 2001 is a delicate, poetic meditation on the ingenuity -- and folly -- of mankind.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/80/11168008_mob.jpg'),(3759,'The Wedding Singer',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wedding_singer/','10214','0120888',1,NULL,'It\'s decidedly uneven -- and surprisingly sappy for an early Adam Sandler comedy -- but The Wedding Singer is also sweet, funny, and beguiling.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/87/41/10874148_mob.jpg'),(3760,'The King\'s Speech',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_kings_speech/','770816664','1504320',1,'After the death of his father King George V (Michael Gambon) and the scandalous abdication of King Edward VIII (Guy Pearce), Bertie (Colin Firth) who has suffered from a debilitating speech impediment all his life, is suddenly crowned King George VI of England. With his country on the brink of war and in desperate need of a leader, his wife, Elizabeth (Helena Bonham Carter), the future Queen Mother, arranges for her husband to see an eccentric speech therapist, Lionel Logue (Geoffrey Rush). After a rough start, the two delve into an unorthodox course of treatment and eventually form an unbreakable bond. With the support of Logue, his family, his government and Winston Churchill (Timothy Spall), the King will overcome his stammer and deliver a radio-address that inspires his people and unites them in battle. Based on the true story of King George VI, THE KING\'S SPEECH follows the Royal Monarch\'s quest to find his voice. -- (C) Weinstein','Colin Firth gives a masterful performance in The King\'s Speech, a predictable but stylishly produced and rousing period drama.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/44/11154473_mob.jpg'),(3761,'Season of the Witch',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10010694-season_of_the_witch/','770816170','0479997',1,'Oscar (R) winner Nicolas Cage (National Treasure, Ghost Rider) and Ron Perlman (Hellboy, Hellboy II) star in this supernatural action adventure about a heroic Crusader and his fellow soldier who must transport a woman accused of being a witch to a remote monastery. The arduous journey across perilous terrain tests their strength and courage as they discover the girl\'s secret and find themselves battling a terrifyingly powerful force that will determine the fate of the world. -- (C) Relativity Media','Slow, cheap-looking, and dull, Season of the Witch fails even as unintentional comedy.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/42/11154264_mob.jpg'),(3762,'Scary Movie 3',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/scary_movie_3/','11195','0306047',1,NULL,'Though an improvement over the second Scary Movie, the laughs are still inconsistent.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/95/259504_mob.jpg'),(3763,'The Sound of Music',1965,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sound_of_music/','9583','0059742',1,NULL,'Unapologetically sweet and maybe even a little corny, The Sound of Music will win over all but the most cynical filmgoers with its classic songs and irresistible warmth.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/44/11164469_mob.jpg'),(3764,'The Virgin Suicides',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/virgin_suicides/','13003','0159097',1,NULL,'Sofia\'s successful directorial debut lies in the movie\'s compelling story and the actors\' genuine emotions.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/86/10888641_mob.jpg'),(3765,'Scary Movie 2',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/scary_movie_2/','13021','0257106',1,NULL,'Instead of being funny, this gross-out sequel plays like a sloppy, rushed-out product.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/77/267706_mob.jpg'),(3766,'When Harry Met Sally',1989,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/when_harry_met_sally/','16317','0098635',1,NULL,'Rob Reiner\'s touching, funny film set a new standard for romantic comedies, and he was ably abetted by the sharp interplay between Billy Crystal and Meg Ryan.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/31/25/312596_mob.jpg'),(3767,'Running With Scissors',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/running_with_scissors/','314387196','0439289',1,NULL,'Despite a few great performances, the film lacks the sincerity and emotional edge of Burroughs\' well-loved memoir.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/97/36/08/9736088_mob.jpg'),(3768,'The Last Samurai',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/last_samurai/','133039558','0325710',1,NULL,'With high production values and thrilling battle scenes, The Last Samurai is a satisfying epic.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/68/11166861_mob.jpg'),(3769,'Shorts: The Adventures of the Wishing Rock',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shorts_the_adventures_of_the_wishing_rock/','770789860','1100119',1,NULL,'Shorts has imagination and energy, but most viewers beyond elementary school will likely tire of the kiddie humor and sensory overload.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/28/10892833_mob.jpg'),(3770,'The Science of Sleep',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_science_of_sleep/','263042951','0354899',1,NULL,'Lovely and diffuse, Sleep isn\'t as immediately absorbing as Gondry\'s previous work, but its messy beauty is its own reward.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/89/25/10892548_mob.jpg'),(3771,'The Spongebob Squarepants Movie',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spongebob_squarepants_movie/','10467','0345950',1,NULL,'Surreally goofy and entertaining for both children and their parents.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/12/84/11128492_mob.jpg'),(3772,'Scream',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1074316-scream/','17135','0117571',1,NULL,'A great mixed of bone chilling suspense and witty dialogues.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/84/96/10849637_mob.jpg'),(3773,'Hide and Seek',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1141193-hide_and_seek/','13261','0382077',1,NULL,'Robert De Niro and especially Dakota Fanning have earned some praise for their work in Hide and Seek, but critics have called the rest of the film derivative, illogical and somewhat silly.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/28/10882841_mob.jpg'),(3774,'Spawn',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spawn/','13886','0120177',1,NULL,'Spawn is an overbearing, over-violent film that adds little to the comic book adaptation genre.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/27/19/271926_mob.jpg'),(3775,'Smart People',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1192938-smart_people/','770675117','0858479',1,NULL,'Despite its sharp cast and a few laughs, Smart People is too thinly plotted to fully resonate.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/86/83/10868356_mob.jpg'),(3776,'West Side Story',1961,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/west_side_story/','21063','0055614',1,NULL,'Buoyed by Robert Wise\'s dazzling direction, Leonard Bernstein\'s score, and Stephen Sondheim\'s lyrics, West Side Story remains perhaps the most iconic of all the Shakespeare adaptations to visit the big screen.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/91/74/10917475_mob.jpg'),(3777,'Super Size Me',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/super_size_me/','10060',NULL,1,NULL,'Entertaining doc about the adverse effects of eating fast food.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/38/253828_mob.jpg'),(3778,'The Savages',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/savages/','528367213','0775529',1,NULL,'Thanks to a tender, funny script from director Tamara Jenkins, and fine performances from Philip Seymour Hoffman and Laura Linney, this film delivers a nuanced, beautifully three-dimensional look at the struggles and comforts of family bonds.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/71/10887193_mob.jpg'),(3779,'S.W.A.T.',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/swat/','11042','0257076',1,NULL,'A competent, but routine police thriller.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/79/85/10798543_mob.jpg'),(3780,'She\'s Out of My League',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shes_out_of_my_league/','770682073','0815236',1,'An airport security guard gets involved with a girl who\'s very obviously of a higher caliber than himself, and schemes to make the relationship last as his friends and family watch along in disbelief. Kirk (Jay Baruchel) was languishing in a dead-end job as an airport security agent when he somehow managed to earn the affections of the successful and drop-dead gorgeous Molly (Alice Eve). Even Kirk isn\'t exactly sure what Molly sees in him, though he\'s willing to do whatever it takes to make the relationship work. With his friends, family, and ex-girlfriend all watching stunned from the sidelines, Kirk discovers that he\'ll have to work overtime in order to convince Molly that he\'s worth hanging on to. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','She\'s Out of My League has moments of humor and insight, but it\'s bogged down by excessive vulgarity and cartoonishness.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/95/38/10953861_mob.jpg'),(3781,'Vanilla Sky',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/vanilla_sky/','13077','0259711',1,NULL,'An ambitious mix of genres, Vanilla Sky collapses into an incoherent jumble. Cruise\'s performance lacks depth, and it\'s hard to feel sympathy for his narcissistic character.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/26/79/267997_mob.jpg'),(3782,'Severance',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/severance/','299771637','0464196',1,NULL,'A twisted and bloody spoof on office life, Severance nicely balances comedy and nasty horror.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/64/27/07/6427075_mob.jpg'),(3783,'Austin Powers: The Spy Who Shagged Me',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/austin_powers_the_spy_who_shagged_me/','10667','0145660',1,NULL,'Provides lots of laughs with Myers at the healm; as funny or funnier than the original.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/86/89/10868999_mob.jpg'),(3784,'Starsky & Hutch',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/starsky_and_hutch/','11462','0335438',1,NULL,'It\'s uneven and occasionally somewhat aimless, but Starsky & Hutch benefits from Stiller and Wilson\'s chemistry and a surprisingly warm-hearted script.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/55/05/01/5505011_mob.jpg'),(3785,'The Smurfs',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_smurfs/','770672987','0472181',1,'The Smurfs make their first 3D trip to the big screen in Columbia Pictures\'/Sony Pictures Animation\'s hybrid live-action and animated family comedy, The Smurfs. When the evil wizard Gargamel chases the Smurfs out of their village, they\'re forced through a portal, out of their world and into ours, landing in the middle of New York\'s Central Park. Just three apples high and stuck in the Big Apple, the Smurfs must find a way to get back to their village before Gargamel tracks them down. -- (C) Sony Pictures','The Smurfs assembles an undeniably talented cast of voice actors and live-action stars -- then crushes them beneath a blue mound of lowest-common-denominator kiddie fare.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/36/11163657_mob.jpg'),(3786,'Swing Vote',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/swing_vote/','770682012','1027862',1,NULL,'Despite Kevin Costner providing his most charismatic performance in years, Swing Vote fails to find the right mix of political satire and heartfelt drama.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/92/09/10920934_mob.jpg'),(3787,'Lilo & Stitch',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lilo_and_stitch/','10291','0275847',1,NULL,'Edgier than traditional Disney fare, Lilo and Stitch explores issues of family while providing a fun and charming story.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/50/255008_mob.jpg'),(3788,'School for Scoundrels',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/school_for_scoundrels/','287865427','0462519',1,NULL,'School for Scoundrels squanders its talented cast with a formulaic, unfocused attempt at a romantic comedy that\'s neither romantic nor funny.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/27/22/94/2722945_mob.jpg'),(3789,'Sinister',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sinister_2012/','771259549','1922777',1,'Sinister is a frightening new thriller from the producer of the Paranormal Activity films and the writer-director of The Exorcism of Emily Rose. Ethan Hawke plays a true crime novelist who discovers a box of mysterious, disturbing home movies that plunge his family into a nightmarish experience of supernatural horror. -- (C) Summit','Its plot hinges on typically implausible horror-movie behavior and recycles countless genre cliches, but Sinister delivers a surprising number of fresh, diabolical twists.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/69/11166934_mob.jpg'),(3790,'No Strings Attached',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/no_strings_attached_2011/','771225438','1411238',1,'In this comedy, Emma (Natalie Portman) and Adam (Ashton Kutcher) are life-long friends who almost ruin everything by having sex one morning. In order to protect their friendship, they make a pact to keep their relationship strictly \"no strings attached.\" \"No strings\" means no jealousy, no expectations, no fighting, no flowers, no baby voices. It means they can do whatever they want, whenever they want, in whatever public place they want, as long as they don\'t fall in love. The questions become - Can you have sex without love getting in the way? And can their friendship survive? -- (C) Paramount','It benefits from the presence of Natalie Portman and director Ivan Reitman\'s steady hand, but No Strings Attached doesn\'t have the courage or conviction to follow through on its ribald premise.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/50/11155044_mob.jpg'),(3791,'The Switch',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_switch_2010/','770810632','0889573',1,'A woman approaching middle age yet still childless decides to get pregnant by artificial insemination, only to discover that the donor she chose may not be the father of her child in this comedy starring Jennifer Aniston and Jason Bateman. Wally Mars (Bateman) is a dyed-in-the-wool pessimist. Hopelessly neurotic and unrepentantly narcissistic, he gets no joy out of life except for the time he spends with his best friend Kassie (Jennifer Aniston). However, despite the fact that Wally pines to be more than just friends with Kassie, she isn\'t convinced they\'d make a good couple. When Kassie announces to Wally that she\'s found the perfect sperm donor, he\'s crestfallen; as far as he\'s concerned, the ideal candidate is standing right in front of her. Later, Kassie selects handsome stranger Roland (Patrick Wilson) to provide the seed. Things get complicated when Kassie\'s best friend Debbie (Juliette Lewis) throws an \"insemination party\" to commemorate the big event, and Wally intercepts Roland\'s special delivery, drunkenly replacing it with his own before blacking out. Pregnant and content, Kassie leaves the city for Minnesota, where she gives birth to a healthy baby boy. Flash-forward seven years, and Kassie returns to New York with her son, Sebastian (Thomas Robinson), who shares an uncanny number of physical and psychological traits with embittered bachelor Wally. Before long Wally and Sebastian have become good friends, and Wally becomes convinced that the boy is his biological son. His ideal family is finally within reach, and if he can just figure out a means of breaking the news to Kassie gently, perhaps she\'ll find it in her heart to forgive him, and recognize that he\'ll make the perfect father for Sebastian. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','The Switch has an interesting premise and a charming cast; unfortunately, it also has a trite script that hews too close to tired rom-com formulas.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/95/44/10954487_mob.jpg'),(3792,'Saw 3D',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/saw3d/','770852580','1477076',1,'The Saw series continues with this seventh entry, spearheaded by returning Saw VI director Kevin Greutert. Marcus Dunstan and Patrick Melton also are back to pen the script, which details the exploits of serial killer Jigsaw\'s surviving victims, who seek counseling from a self-help mentor (Sean Patrick Flanery) whose past as a previous victim figures directly into each one\'s fate. Cary Elwes returns to the franchise for the first time since his character survived Jigsaw\'s first cinematic outing in 2004. ~ Jeremy Wheeler, Rovi','Sloppily filmed, poorly acted, and illogically plotted, Saw 3D leaves viewers trapped in the most lackluster installment of the series.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/32/11153207_mob.jpg'),(3793,'Serendipity',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/serendipity/','10106','0240890',1,NULL,'Light and charming, Serendipity could benefit from less contrivances.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/41/254100_mob.jpg'),(3794,'Shallow Hal',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shallow_hal/','10941','0256380',1,NULL,'While surprisingly sweeter and warm-hearted than previous Farrelly outings, Shallow Hal is also less funny and more bland.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/47/11164723_mob.jpg'),(3795,'Superman II',1981,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/superman_ii/','10656','0081573',1,NULL,'The humor occasionally stumbles into slapstick territory, and the special effects are dated, but Superman II meets, if not exceeds, the standard set by its predecessor.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/98/11159894_mob.jpg'),(3796,'Sideways',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sideways/','12851','0375063',1,NULL,'An emotional and heartfelt comedy.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/68/266826_mob.jpg'),(3797,'Paranormal Activity 2',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/paranormal_activity_2/','770874913','1536044',1,'The sequel to the low-budget blockbuster Paranormal Activity takes place a few months before the events of the first film. Katie (Katie Featherston), the much put-upon leading lady in the original, has a sister living in an upscale Los Angeles suburb named Kristi (Sprague Grayden). Kristi has a new baby son, Hunter; a likable lug of a husband named Daniel (Brian Boland), who owns several fast-food joints; a teenage stepdaughter from her hubby\'s first marriage, Ali (Molly Ephraim); and a large, friendly dog. As the family gets used to the new arrival, strange noises are heard late at night and when they come home from an outing, they discover the house has been trashed, even though none of their valuables have been stolen. Daniel responds by installing a security system and a network of surveillance cameras, though that doesn\'t stop the noises or the Latino housekeeper\'s insistence that spirits lurk in the home. When Katie and her boyfriend, Micah (Micah Sloat), stop by for a visit, they discuss the strange goings-on with Kristi; the women of the house believe supernatural forces are at work, while the men find that notion ridiculous. That doesn\'t last long, as the spirits get noisier and angrier, especially when Ali begins doing some research on the subject, and before long the safety of the household is being threatened on several fronts, possibly due to some dirty dealings in the family\'s distant past. ~ Perry Seibert, Rovi','Paranormal Activity 2 doesn\'t cover any new ground, but its premise is still scary -- and in some respects, it\'s a better film than the original.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/29/11152957_mob.jpg'),(3798,'Kickin\' It Old Skool',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kickin_it_old_school/','630715373',NULL,1,NULL,'Kickin\' It Old Skool is one big unfunny pop culture reference that doesn\'t feature many laughs.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/64/89/74/6489743_mob.jpg'),(3799,'Vampires Suck',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/vampires_suck/','771201458','1666186',1,'The comedy masterminds behind Epic Movie, Disaster Movie, and Meet the Spartans drive a squeaky rubber stake through the heart of the Twilight series with this irreverent satire about a teenage girl who\'s torn between two supernatural suitors. As Becca struggles to contend with her overbearing father, two fierce rivals compete to win her heart. But Becca isn\'t the only high-school student having a hard time with boys; her friends are all desperate to find a date for the prom, and as the big night draws near, the rampant tension draws out the animals in everyone. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Witlessly broad and utterly devoid of laughs, Vampires Suck represents a slight step forward for the Friedberg-Seltzer team.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/07/11150745_mob.jpg'),(3800,'Superman III',1983,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/superman_iii/','12037','0086393',1,NULL,'When not overusing sight gags, slapstick, and Richard Pryor, Superman III resorts to plot points rehashed from the previous Superman flicks.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/36/263604_mob.jpg'),(3801,'Shakespeare in Love',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shakespeare_in_love/','14753','0138097',1,NULL,'Endlessly witty, visually rapturous, and sweetly romantic, Shakespeare in Love is a delightful romantic comedy that succeeds on nearly every level.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/27/61/276127_mob.jpg'),(3802,'Scream 2',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/scream_2/','16559','0120082',1,NULL,'It is scarier and funnier than the original.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/46/00/460098_mob.jpg'),(3803,'Scream 3',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/scream_3/','13688','0134084',1,NULL,'According to critics, Scream 3 has become what it originally spoofed. Despite some surprising twists, the movie seems to have lost its freshness and originality by falling back on the old horror formulas and cliches.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/55/05/97/5505978_mob.jpg'),(3804,'Strange Wilderness',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/strange_wilderness/','770671518','0489282',1,NULL,'Strange Wilderness is a laugh-free comedy that\'s both aimless and overly crass.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/58/58/10585876_mob.jpg'),(3805,'Skinwalkers',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/skinwalkers/','608999851','0461703',1,NULL,'Skinwalkers is an atrociously-acted project whose unoriginal and ineptly-staged action sequences remind viewers of far better werewolf and action movies.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/94/07/10940769_mob.jpg'),(3806,'A Single Man',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1218217-single_man/','770808473','1315981',1,NULL,'Though the costumes are beautiful and the art direction impeccable, what stands out most from this debut by fashion designer Tom Ford is the leading performance by Colin Firth.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/92/75/10927538_mob.jpg'),(3807,'We Were Soldiers',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/we_were_soldiers/','12912','0277434',1,NULL,'The war cliches are laid on a bit thick, but the movie succeeds at putting a human face on soldiers of both sides in the Vietnam War.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/92/29/10922992_mob.jpg'),(3808,'Mona Lisa Smile',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mona_lisa_smile/','10479','0304415',1,NULL,'Though Mona Lisa Smile espouses the value of breaking barriers, the movie itself is predictable and safe.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/59/255923_mob.jpg'),(3809,'Say Anything...',1989,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/say_anything/','10151','0098258',1,NULL,'One of the definitive Generation X movies, Say Anything is equally funny and heartfelt -- and it established John Cusack as an icon for left-of-center types everywhere.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/59/54/51/5954518_mob.jpg'),(3810,'Office Space',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/office_space/','13020','0151804',1,NULL,'Mike Judge lampoons the office grind with its inspired mix of sharp dialogue and witty one-liners.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/44/11164476_mob.jpg'),(3811,'Spanglish',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spanglish/','10163','0371246',1,NULL,'Paz Vega shines, and Adam Sandler gives a performance of thoughtfulness and depth, but Spanglish is ultimately undermined by sitcommy plotting and unearned uplift.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/55/36/27/5536274_mob.jpg'),(3812,'Running Scared',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10004288-running_scared/','49248746','0404390',1,NULL,'This film runs with frenetic energy punctuated by gratuitous violence but sorely lacks in plot, character development and stylistic flair.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/31/27/312798_mob.jpg'),(3813,'Swordfish',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/swordfish/','13173','0244244',1,NULL,'Swordfish is big on explosions, but critics dislike how it skimps on plot and logic. Also, the sight of a person typing at a computer just isn\'t that interesting.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/26/84/268491_mob.jpg'),(3814,'The Skeleton Key',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1149472-skeleton_key/','3618','0397101',1,NULL,'Thanks to its creaky and formulaic script, The Skeleton Key is more mumbo-jumbo than hoodoo and more dull than scary.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/24/99/249993_mob.jpg'),(3815,'Slither',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/slither/','133759650','0439815',1,NULL,'A slimy, rotten B-movie homage oozing with affection for low-budget horror films, Slither is a tale of creepy crawly little beasts that invade Smalltown, USA. Equally creepy and funny, critics say it\'s one of the most enjoyable of its type in years -- if you\'ve got the stomach for this sort of thing. Slither is a wicked good time: it\'ll make you squirm -- when you\'re not busting a gut laughing.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/31/35/313501_mob.jpg'),(3816,'Stay Alive',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10006370-stay_alive/','128388213','0441796',1,NULL,'A by-the-numbers teen horror flick, Stay Alive fails to exploit its premise for any real scares.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/87/03/10870338_mob.jpg'),(3817,'Skyline',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/skyline_2010/','771203481','1564585',1,'A series of blindingly bright lights appear all over Los Angeles, mesmerizing the citizens of the city while luring them to an uncertain fate in this sci-fi thriller from sibling filmmakers Greg and Colin Strause. As speculation regarding the origin of the mysterious lights runs rampant, a Los Angeles entrepreneur (Donald Faison), his best friend, Jarrod (Eric Balfour), and Jarrod\'s frightened girlfriend (Scottie Thompson) struggle to resist temptation as they seek out the source of the luminous threat. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','A middling sci-fi entry, Skyline offers proof that solid special effects alone cannot overcome a flat storyline filled with uninspired dialogue.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/19/11151968_mob.jpg'),(3818,'Sparkle',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sparkle_2012/','771264531','1876451',1,'Musical prodigy, Sparkle (Jordin Sparks) struggles to become a star while overcoming issues that are tearing her family apart. From an affluent Detroit area and daughter to a single mother (Whitney Houston), she tries to balance a new romance with music manager, Stix (Derek Luke) while dealing with the unexpected challenges her new life will bring as she and her two sisters (Carmen Ejogo and Tika Sumpter) strive to become a dynamic singing group during the Motown-era. -- (C) Sony','While undeniably melodramatic and old-fashioned, Sparkle transcends its formulaic trappings thanks to Salim Akil\'s empathetic direction and strong performances from a committed cast.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/79/11167979_mob.jpg'),(3819,'Sky High',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1142872-sky_high/','2127','0405325',1,NULL,'This highly derivative superhero coming-of-age flick is moderately entertaining, family-friendly fluff.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/24/98/249899_mob.jpg'),(3820,'The Perfect Storm',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/perfect_storm/','12647',NULL,1,NULL,'While the special effects are well done and quite impressive, this film suffers from any actual drama or characterization. The end result is a film that offers nifty eye-candy and nothing else.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/79/11167915_mob.jpg'),(3821,'Singin\' in the Rain',1952,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/singin_in_the_rain/','9924','0045152',1,NULL,'Clever, incisive, and funny, Singin\' in the Rain is a masterpiece of the classical Hollywood musical.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/99/11159981_mob.jpg'),(3822,'Sense and Sensibility',1995,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1068832-sense_and_sensibility/','10042','0114388',1,NULL,'Sense and Sensibility is an uncommonly deft, very funny Jane Austen adaptation, marked by Emma Thompson\'s finely tuned performance.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/12/50/11125040_mob.jpg'),(3823,'Shanghai Noon',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shanghai_noon/','10748','0184894',1,NULL,'Although the plot is really nothing to brag about, Jackie Chan and Owen Wilson work well together. The cinematography looks great, and Jackie delivers a hilarious performance. This is an old-fashioned crowd-pleaser.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/72/257299_mob.jpg'),(3824,'Silent House',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/silent_house_2012/','771228633','1767382',1,'From the directors of the hit film Open Water, Silent House is a uniquely unsettling horror thriller starring Elizabeth Olsen as Sarah, a young woman who finds herself sealed inside her family\'s secluded lake house. With no contact to the outside world, and no way out, panic turns to terror to terror as events become increasingly ominous in and around the house. Directed by filmmaking duo Chris Kentis and Laura Lau, Silent House uses meticulous camera choreography to take the audience on a tension-filled, real time journey, experienced in a single uninterrupted shot. -- (C) Open Road','Silent House is more technically proficient and ambitious than most fright-fests, but it also suffers from a disappointing payoff.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/35/11163514_mob.jpg'),(3825,'Seven Samurai (Shichinin no Samurai)',1954,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1018639-seven_samurai/','16992','0047478',1,NULL,'Arguably Akira Kurosawa\'s masterpiece, The Seven Samurai is an epic adventure classic with an engrossing story, memorable characters, and stunning action sequences that make it one of the most influential films ever made.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/39/91/08/3991085_mob.jpg'),(3826,'The Nativity Story',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nativity_story/','314097343','0762121',1,NULL,'The Nativity Story is a dull retelling of a well-worn tale with the look and feel of a high-school production.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/07/70/2507701_mob.jpg'),(3827,'Notes on a Scandal',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/notes_on_a_scandal/','398731787','0465551',1,NULL,'In this sharp psychological thriller, Judi Dench and Cate Blanchett give fierce, memorable performances as two schoolteachers locked in a battle of wits.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/27/11152769_mob.jpg'),(3828,'A Serious Man',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_serious_man/','770785948','1019452',1,NULL,'Blending dark humor with profoundly personal themes, the Coen brothers deliver what might be their most mature -- if not their best -- film to date.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/89/22/10892275_mob.jpg'),(3829,'Sahara',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1144274-sahara/','20','0318649',1,NULL,'A mindless adventure flick with a preposterous plot.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/24/97/249732_mob.jpg'),(3830,'Something New',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/something_new/','14662874','0437777',1,NULL,'Something New tackles serious questions about race and interracial relationships with genuine appeal and an alluring romance that develops as naturally as the plot.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/31/27/312703_mob.jpg'),(3831,'The Stepford Wives',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stepford_wives/','10977','0327162',1,NULL,'In exchanging the chilling satire of the original into mindless camp, this remake has itself become Stepford-ized.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/84/258412_mob.jpg'),(3832,'Shanghai Knights',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shanghai_knights/','10923','0300471',1,NULL,'A silly, anachronistic mess, but the pairing of Chan and Wilson makes the movie fun.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/89/55/10895588_mob.jpg'),(3833,'Stay',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stay/','8842','0371257',1,NULL,'A muddled brain-teaser, Stay has a solid cast and innovative visuals but little beneath the surface.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/89/83/10898338_mob.jpg'),(3834,'Spartacus',1960,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1019544-spartacus/','11189','0054331',1,NULL,'Featuring terrific performances and epic action, Kubrick\'s restored swords-and-sandals epic is a true classic.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/94/259493_mob.jpg'),(3835,'Silent Hill: Revelation',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/silent_hill_revelation/','771305539','0938330',1,'In Silent Hill: Revelation 3D, Heather Mason (Clemens) and her father (Bean) have been on the run, always one step ahead of dangerous forces that she doesn\'t fully understand. On the eve of her 18th birthday, plagued by horrific nightmares and the disappearance of her father, Heather discovers she\'s not who she thinks she is. The revelation leads her deeper into a demonic world that threatens to trap her forever. -- (C) Open Road','Featuring weak characters, an incomprehensible plot, and a decided shortage of scares, Silent Hill: Revelation 3D is a mediocre effort even by the standards of video game adaptations.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/83/11168300_mob.jpg'),(3836,'Weird Science',1985,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1023316-weird_science/','12065','0090305',1,NULL,'Hardly in the same league as John Hughes\' other teen movies, the resolutely goofy Weird Science nonetheless gets some laughs via its ridiculous premise and enjoyable performances.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/37/263714_mob.jpg'),(3837,'Hope Springs',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hope_springs_2012/','771253858','1535438',1,'Kay (Meryl Streep) and Arnold (Tommy Lee Jones) are a devoted couple, but decades of marriage have left Kay wanting to spice things up and reconnect with her husband. When she hears of a renowned couple\'s specialist (Steve Carell) in the small town of Great Hope Springs, she attempts to persuade her skeptical husband, a steadfast man of routine, to get on a plane for a week of marriage therapy. Just convincing the stubborn Arnold to go on the retreat is hard enough - the real challenge for both of them comes as they shed their bedroom hang-ups and try to re-ignite the spark that caused them to fall for each other in the first place. -- (C) Sony','Led by a pair of mesmerizing performances from Meryl Streep and Tommy Lee Jones, Hope Springs offers filmgoers some grown-up laughs -- and a thoughtful look at mature relationships.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/79/11167978_mob.jpg'),(3838,'Spun',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spun/','17102','0283003',1,NULL,'A chaotic drug movie that has little substance behind the stylistic flash.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/28/62/286297_mob.jpg'),(3839,'Somewhere',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/somewhere_2010/','770813470','1421051',1,'Roguish Hollywood star Johnny Marco (Stephen Dorff) finds his debauched life of excess unexpectedly interrupted when his 11-year-old daughter (Elle Fanning) shows up at the Chateau Marmont Hotel for an unscheduled visit. Later, as father and daughter reconnect, Johnny begins to reassess his sordid lifestyle. Writer/director Sofia Coppola teams with brother Roman to produce a film executive produced by Francis Ford Coppola, and released by Focus Features. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','It covers familiar territory for Sofia Coppola, but Somewhere remains a hypnotic, seductively pensive meditation on the nature of celebrity, anchored by charming performances from Stephen Dorff and Elle Fanning.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/44/11154456_mob.jpg'),(3840,'The Squid and the Whale',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/squid_and_the_whale/','8564','0367089',1,NULL,'This is a piercingly honest, acidly witty look at divorce and its impact on a family.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/02/250292_mob.jpg'),(3841,'Shopgirl',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shopgirl/','8849','0338427',1,NULL,'Shopgirl is precariously slight, but it has some intriguing moments, and Danes is luminous.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/04/250405_mob.jpg'),(3842,'Soul Surfer',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/soul_surfer/','771037147','1596346',1,'Bethany (AnnaSophia Robb) was born to surf. A natural talent who took to the waves at a young age, she was leading an idyllic life on Kauai, participating in national surf competitions with her best friend Alana (Lorraine Nicholson), when everything changed. On Halloween morning, a 14-foot tiger shark came out of nowhere and seemed to shatter all her dreams. Soul Surfer reveals Bethany\'s fight to recover from her ordeal and how she grappled with the question of her future. Strengthened by the love of her parents, Tom (Dennis Quaid) and Cheri (Helen Hunt), and supported by her youth group leader Sara (Carrie Underwood), Bethany refuses to give in or give up, and begins a bold return to the water. -- (C) Official Site','There\'s an amazing true story at the heart of Soul Surfer -- and unfortunately, it\'s drowned by waves of Hollywood cheese.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/57/11155754_mob.jpg'),(3843,'The Sentinel',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sentinel/','150164939','0443632',1,NULL,'The Sentinel starts off well enough but quickly wears thin with too many plot holes and conventional action sequences.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/31/40/314022_mob.jpg'),(3844,'Saved!',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/saved/','10371','0332375',1,NULL,'A satirical teen comedy that, unfortunately, pulls its punches.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/26/10892601_mob.jpg'),(3845,'Space Jam',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/space_jam/','12491','0117705',1,NULL,'A harmless mishmash of basketball and animation that\'ll entertain kids but leave adults less than thrilled.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/91/96/10919615_mob.jpg'),(3846,'The Sitter',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_sitter_2011/','771204355','1366344',1,'When the world\'s most irresponsible babysitter takes three of the world\'s worst kids on an unforgettable overnight adventure through the streets of New York City, it\'s anyone\'s guess who\'s going to make it home in one piece. The Sitter is a new level of twisted and debauched hilarity from the director of Pineapple Express, starring Jonah Hill. -- (C) Official Site','With its recycled plot, misguided gags, and formula performance from Jonah Hill, The Sitter adds up to another disappointing entry from director David Gordon Green.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/25/11162580_mob.jpg'),(3847,'Scent of a Woman',1992,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1042193-scent_of_a_woman/','12958','0105323',1,NULL,'It might soar on Al Pacino\'s performance more than the drama itself, but what a performance it is -- big, bold, occasionally over-the-top, and finally giving the Academy pause to award the star his first Oscar.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/55/05/23/5505231_mob.jpg'),(3848,'Ruby Sparks',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ruby_sparks/','771272475','1839492',1,'Calvin (Dano) is a young novelist who achieved phenomenal success early in his career but is now struggling with his writing - as well as his romantic life. Finally, he makes a breakthrough and creates a character named Ruby who inspires him. When Calvin finds Ruby (Kazan), in the flesh, sitting on his couch about a week later, he is completely flabbergasted that his words have turned into a living, breathing person. -- (C) Fox Searchlight',NULL,'http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/52/11165270_mob.jpg'),(3849,'Little Shop of Horrors',1986,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1012515-little_shop_of_horrors/','10070','0091419',1,NULL,'Remixing Roger Corman\'s B-movie by way of the Off-Broadway musical, Little Shop of Horrors offers camp, horror and catchy tunes in equal measure -- plus some inspired cameos by the likes of Steve Martin and Bill Murray.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/72/11167269_mob.jpg'),(3850,'Scoop',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/scoop/','248007453','0457513',1,NULL,'Rehashing old plot lines and characters, Scoop is a tiresome dipper and another disappointing addition to Woody Allen\'s repertoire.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/94/61/10946196_mob.jpg'),(3851,'Shame',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shame_2011/','771251632','1723811',1,'Brandon (Michael Fassbender) is a New Yorker who shuns intimacy with women but feeds his desires with a compulsive addiction to sex. When his wayward younger sister (Carey Mulligan) moves into his apartment stirring memories of their shared painful past, Brandon\'s insular life spirals out of control. -- (C) Official Site','Boasting stellar performances by Michael Fassbender and Carey Mulligan, Shame is a powerful plunge into the mania of addiction affliction.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/11/11161145_mob.jpg'),(3852,'About Schmidt',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/about_schmidt/','13852','0257360',1,NULL,'In this funny, touching character study, Nicholson gives one of the best performances of his career.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/89/01/10890128_mob.jpg'),(3853,'Secretary',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/secretary/','12936','0274812',1,NULL,'Maggie Gyllenhaal impresses in this romantic comedy with a kinky twist.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/72/267298_mob.jpg'),(3854,'Seabiscuit',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/seabiscuit/','120401399','0329575',1,NULL,'A life-affirming, if saccharine, epic treatment of a spirit-lifting figure in sports history.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/86/93/10869338_mob.jpg'),(3855,'Superman IV: The Quest for Peace',1987,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/superman_iv_the_quest_for_peace/','11847','0094074',1,NULL,'The Superman series bottoms out here: the action is boring, the special effects look cheaper, and none of the actors appear interested in where the plot\'s going.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/26/262698_mob.jpg'),(3856,'Secretariat',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/secretariat/','770819741','1028576',1,'Based on the Novel \"Secretariat: The Making of a Champion\" By William Nack, Secretariat chronicles the spectacular journey of the 1973 Triple Crown winner. Housewife and mother Penny Chenery (Diane Lane) agrees to take over her ailing father\'s Virginia-based Meadow Stables, despite her lack of horse-racing knowledge. Against all odds, Chenery-with the help of veteran trainer Lucien Laurin (John Malkovich)-manages to navigate the male-dominated business, ultimately fostering the first Triple Crown winner in 25 years and what may be the greatest racehorse of all time.-- (C) Disney','Rousing, heartwarming, and squarely traditional, Secretariat offers exactly what you\'d expect from an inspirational Disney drama -- no more, and no less.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/23/11152365_mob.jpg'),(3857,'Soul Men',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10009635-soul_men/','770681832','1111948',1,NULL,'Soul Men features lively performances from Bernie Mac and Samuel L. Jackson and some hilarious moments, but ultimately suffers from an unoriginal script.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/92/10/10921036_mob.jpg'),(3858,'Stepmom',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stepmom/','10393','0120686',1,NULL,'Great performances from the leads can\'t save this factory mill tearjerker.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/74/11157459_mob.jpg'),(3859,'Scooby-Doo',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1112357-scoobydoo/','11242','0267913',1,NULL,'Though Lillard is uncannily spot-on as Shaggy, Scooby Doo is a tired live-action update, filled with lame jokes.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/86/10/10861017_mob.jpg'),(3860,'Son of Rambow',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/son_of_rambow/','528392130','0845046',1,NULL,'Undeniable heart and charming young leads save the film\'s nostalgic storyline from suffering at the hands predictability.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/99/65/82/9965828_mob.jpg'),(3861,'The Scorpion King',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/scorpion_king/','11549','0277296',1,NULL,'Action adventure doesn\'t get much cheesier than The Scorpion King.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/36/11163680_mob.jpg'),(3862,'Sleepover',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sleepover/','11340','0368975',1,NULL,'\'Tween girls will enjoy this sugar coated fluff, but others will find Sleepover a snooze.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/94/27/10942700_mob.jpg'),(3863,'Mean Streets',1973,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mean_streets/','14993','0070379',1,NULL,'Mean Streets is a powerful tale of urban sin and guilt that marks Scorsese\'s arrival as an important cinematic voice and features electrifying performances from Harvey Keitel and Robert De Niro.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/03/11160320_mob.jpg'),(3864,'Sleepwalking',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sleepwalking/','770680970','0888693',1,NULL,'Despite some sharp performances, Sleepwalking suffers from a grimness of tone and sluggish pacing.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/84/04/10840437_mob.jpg'),(3865,'Sanctum',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sanctum/','771025840','0881320',1,'The 3-D action-thriller Sanctum, from executive producer James Cameron, follows a team of underwater cave divers on a treacherous expedition to the largest, most beautiful and least accessible cave system on Earth. When a tropical storm forces them deep into the caverns, they must fight raging water, deadly terrain and creeping panic as they search for an unknown escape route to the sea. Master diver Frank McGuire (Richard Roxburgh) has explored the South Pacific\'s Esa-ala Caves for months. But when his exit is cut off in a flash flood, Frank\'s team--including 17-year-old son Josh (Rhys Wakefield) and financier Carl Hurley (Ioan Gruffudd)--are forced to radically alter plans. With dwindling supplies, the crew must navigate an underwater labyrinth to make it out. Soon, they are confronted with the unavoidable question: Can they survive, or will they be trapped forever? Shot on location off the Gold Coast in Queensland, Australia, Sanctum employs 3-D photography techniques Cameron developed to lens Avatar. Designed to operate in extreme environments, the technology used to shoot the action-thriller will bring audiences on a breathless journey across plunging cliffs and into the furthest reaches of our subterranean world. -- (C) Universal','Sanctum is beautifully photographed, and it makes better use of 3-D technology than most, but that doesn\'t make up for its ham-handed script and lifeless cast.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/45/11154517_mob.jpg'),(3866,'Sabrina',1954,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1018047-sabrina/','18228','0047437',1,NULL,'With its humorous script and its stars\' immense charm, Sabrina remains a resonant romantic gem.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/93/36/10933669_mob.jpg'),(3867,'Stealth',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1146673-1146673-stealth/','2131','0382992',1,NULL,'Loud, preposterous, and predictable, Stealth borrows heavily and unsucessfully from Top Gun and 2001.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/93/21/10932137_mob.jpg'),(3868,'The Philadelphia Story',1940,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/philadelphia_story/','22180','0032904',1,NULL,'Offering a wonderfully witty script, spotless direction from George Cukor, and typically excellent lead performances, The Philadelphia Story is an unqualified classic.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/08/01/10080157_mob.jpg'),(3869,'Stuart Little',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stuart_little/','11550','0164912',1,NULL,'Critics say Stuart Little is charming with kids and adults for its humor and visual effects.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/12/261220_mob.jpg'),(3870,'Spy Kids',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spy_kids/','10344','0227538',1,NULL,'A kinetic and fun movie that\'s sure to thrill children of all ages.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/52/255297_mob.jpg'),(3871,'Shark Night 3D',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shark_night_3d/','771208380','1633356',1,'Arriving by boat at her family\'s Louisiana lake island cabin, Sara (Sara Paxton) and her friends quickly strip down to their swimsuits for a weekend of fun in the sun. But when star football player Malik (Sinqua Walls) stumbles from the salt-water lake with his arm torn off, the party mood quickly evaporates. Assuming the injury was caused by a freak wake-boarding accident, the group realizes they have to get Malik to a hospital on the other side of the lake, and fast. But as they set out in a tiny speedboat, the college friends discover the lake has been stocked with hundreds of massive, flesh-eating sharks! As they face one grisly death after another, Sara and the others struggle desperately to fend off the sharks, get help and stay alive long enough to reach the safety of dry land. -- (C) Relativity Media','A joyless excursion into the water that doesn\'t even produce good gore or nudity thanks to the neutered PG-13 rating.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/80/11158098_mob.jpg'),(3872,'Original Sin',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/original_sin/','17054','0218922',1,NULL,'Laughably melodramatic, Original Sin features bad acting, bad dialogue, and bad plotting.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/85/74/10857493_mob.jpg'),(3873,'Serpico',1973,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/serpico/','13410','0070666',1,NULL,'Serpico is an engrossing, immediate depiction of 1973 New York and includes a turn by a young Pacino that\'s both ferocious and career changing.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/26/96/269611_mob.jpg'),(3874,'Sweet November',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1104841-sweet_november/','10648','0230838',1,NULL,'Bad acting and direction plague this version of Sweet November. The story is unrealistic, as is the chemistry between Theron and Reeves.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/67/256799_mob.jpg'),(3875,'Solomon Kane',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/solomon_kane/','770682092','0970452',1,'Captain Solomon Kane is a brutally efficient 16th Century killing machine. Armed with his signature pistols, cutlass and rapier, he and his men unleash their bloodlust as they fight for England in war after war on all continents. As the story opens, Kane and his band of pillagers are carving a bloody path through hordes of defenders in an exotic city in northern Africa. But, when Kane decides to attack a mysterious nearby castle to plunder its rumored riches, his mission takes a fateful turn. One by one, Kane\'s men are picked off by demonic creatures until he alone is left to face the Devil\'s own Reaper -- dispatched from the depths of Hell to lay claim to his hopelessly corrupt soul. Though Kane at last manages to escape, he knows that he now must redeem himself by renouncing violence and devoting himself wholly to a life of peace and purity. -- (C) Official Site',NULL,'http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/68/11166823_mob.jpg'),(3876,'Shadowboxer',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shadowboxer/','190816146','0396857',1,NULL,'With random characters and a preposterous plot, this bizarre thriller might leave you with your mouth hanging open in disbelief.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/18/56/86/1856867_mob.jpg'),(3877,'Super',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/super-2010/','770875072','1512235',1,'In the outlandish dark comedy SUPER, James Gunn has created what is perhaps the definitive take on self-reflexive superheroes. When sad-sack loser Frank (Rainn Wilson) sees his ex-addict wife (Liv Tyler) willingly snatched by a seductive drug dealer (Kevin Bacon), he finds himself bereft and wholly unable to cope. But soon he decides to fight back under the guise of a DIY superhero called Crimson Bolt. With a hand-made suit, a wrench, and a crazed sidekick named Boltie (Ellen Page), the Crimson Bolt beats his way through the mean streets of crime in hopes of saving his wife. The rules were written a long time ago: You are not supposed to molest children, cut lines or key cars; if you do, prepare to face the wrath of the Crimson Bolt! No stranger to rebel filmmaking, James Gunn cut his teeth writing for Troma before making his directing debut with 2006\'s SLITHER. In a similar vein, his follow-up feature combines absurd humor with balls-out violence to create something that is both unashamed and inimitable. But this time Gunn adds a new ingredient, one that is dark, dramatic and subversive to the core. -- (c) IFC Films',NULL,'http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/59/11155913_mob.jpg'),(3878,'Shortbus',2006,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shortbus/','336025614','0367027',1,NULL,'The sex may be explicit, but Mitchell integrates it into the characters\' lives and serves the whole story up with a generous dose of sweetness and wit.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/56/76/43/5676430_mob.jpg'),(3879,'The Skin I Live In',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_skin_i_live_in/','771174272','1189073',1,'Ever since his wife was burned in a car crash, Dr. Robert Ledgard, an eminent plastic surgeon, has been interested in creating a new skin with which he could have saved her. After twelve years, he manages to cultivate a skin that is a real shield against every assault. In addition to years of study and experimentation, Robert needed a further three things: no scruples, an accomplice and a human guinea pig. Scruples were never a problem. Marilia, the woman who looked after him from the day he was born, is his most faithful accomplice. And as for the human guinea pig...-- (C) Sony','The Skin I Live In lacks Almodovar\'s famously charged romance, replaced with a wonderfully bizarre and unpredictable detour into arthouse ick.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/02/11160289_mob.jpg'),(3880,'The Sting',1973,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1020130-sting/','22491','0070735',1,NULL,'Paul Newman, Robert Redford, and director George Roy Hill prove that charm, humor, and a few slick twists can add up to a great film.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/11/96/11119697_mob.jpg'),(3881,'The Sessions',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_sessions/','771255623','1866249',1,'Based on the poignantly optimistic autobiographical writings of California-based journalist and poet Mark O\'Brien, The Sessions tells the story of a man confined to an iron lung who is determined - at age 38 - to lose his virginity. With the help of his therapists and the guidance of his priest, he sets out to make his dream a reality. -- (C) Fox Searchlight','Tender, funny, and touching, The Sessions provides an acting showcase for its talented stars and proves it\'s possible for Hollywood to produce a grown-up movie about sex.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/82/11168293_mob.jpg'),(3882,'The Score',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1108799-score/','13558','0227445',1,NULL,'Though the movie treads familar ground in the heist/caper genre, DeNiro, Norton, and Brando make the movie worth watching.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/89/11168972_mob.jpg'),(3883,'The Sword in the Stone',1963,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sword_in_the_stone/','9393','0057546',1,NULL,'A decent take on the legend of King Arthur, The Sword in the Stone suffers from relatively indifferent animation, but its characters are still memorable and appealing.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/07/250724_mob.jpg'),(3884,'America\'s Sweethearts',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/americas_sweethearts/','98831563','0265029',1,NULL,'Despite its famous cast, the movie lacks sympathetic characters and is only funny in spurts.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/50/54/39/5054399_mob.jpg'),(3885,'Surveillance',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/surveillance/','770685686','0409345',1,NULL,'This dark psycho-thriller from Jennifer Lynch, is violent, sharp and baffling, but not to everyone\'s taste.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/40/10884045_mob.jpg'),(3886,'Life or Something Like It',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/life_or_something_like_it/','10990','0282687',1,NULL,'Though Jolie is appealing, Life or Something Like It is too contrived and predictable to convincingly convey its message of stopping to smell the roses.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/48/11164892_mob.jpg'),(3887,'How She Move',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/how_she_move/','528347787','0770810',1,NULL,'Despite a formulaic plot, the energetic and gritty How She Move is elevated by a commanding debut performance by Rutina Wesley.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/86/53/10865389_mob.jpg'),(3888,'Sleepwalk With Me',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sleepwalk_with_me_2012/','771267283','2077851',1,'\"I\'m going to tell you a story, and it\'s true....I always have to tell people that.\" So asserts comedian-turned-playwright-turned-filmmaker Mike Birbiglia directly to the viewer at the outset of his autobiographically inspired, fictional feature debut. Birbiglia wears his incisive wit on his sleeve while portraying a cinematic surrogate. We are thrust into the tale of a burgeoning stand-up comedian struggling with the stress of a stalled career, a stale relationship threatening to race out of his control, and the wild spurts of severe sleepwalking he is desperate to ignore. Based on the successful one-man show, Sleepwalk With Me engages in the kind of passionate and personal storytelling that transfigures intimate anguish into comic art. -- (C) IFC','Laugh-out-loud funny and endearingly messy, Sleepwalk with Me overcomes its tonal inconsistencies to deliver a sweetly melancholic, amiably reassuring indie crowd-pleaser.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/58/11165803_mob.jpg'),(3889,'Stigmata',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stigmata/','16665','0145531',1,NULL,'The story is unconvincing and the acting is weak.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/12/87/29/1287292_mob.jpg'),(3890,'The Sandlot',1993,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sandlot/','10193','0108037',1,NULL,'It may be shamelessly derivative and overly nostalgic, but The Sandlot is nevertheless a genuinely sweet and funny coming-of-age adventure.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/84/98/10849850_mob.jpg'),(3891,'Sid & Nancy',1986,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sid_and_nancy/','16345','0091954',1,NULL,'Visceral, energetic, and often very sad, Sid & Nancy is also a surprisingly touching love story, and Gary Oldman is outstanding as the late punk rock icon Sid Vicious.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/28/34/283412_mob.jpg'),(3892,'The Perfect Score',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/perfect_score/','11692','0314498',1,NULL,'Neither funny nor suspenseful, this heist / teen flick also fails to explore its potentially socially relevant premise.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/19/261912_mob.jpg'),(3893,'Kicking & Screaming',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kicking_and_screaming/','11','0384642',1,NULL,'The script is mediocre and fails to give Ferrell a proper comedic showcase.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/24/97/249715_mob.jpg'),(3894,'Rock Star',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/rock_star/','13545',NULL,1,NULL,'Like its title, Rock Star is rather generic, being not so much about the heavy metal scene than about rock cliches and formula.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/27/02/270296_mob.jpg'),(3895,'After the Sunset',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/after_the_sunset/','12597','0367479',1,NULL,'A slick but bland thriller.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/15/26/66/1526667_mob.jpg'),(3896,'The Sea Inside (Mar Adentro) (The Sea Within)',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sea_inside/','10243','0369702',1,NULL,'Held aloft by a transfixing performance from Javier Bardem as a terminally ill man who chooses to die, The Sea Inside transcends its melodramatic story with tenderness and grace.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/62/05/50/6205505_mob.jpg'),(3897,'A Separation',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_separation_2011/','771237246','1832382',1,'Set in contemporary Iran, A Separation is a compelling drama about the dissolution of a marriage. Simin wants to leave Iran with her husband Nader and daughter Termeh. Simin sues for divorce when Nader refuses to leave behind his Alzheimer-suffering father. Her request having failed, Simin returns to her parents\' home, but Termeh decides to stay with Nader. When Nader hires a young woman to assist with his father in his wife\'s absence, he hopes that his life will return to a normal state. However, when he discovers that the new maid has been lying to him, he realizes that there is more on the line than just his marriage. -- (C) Sony Pictures Classics','Morally complex, suspenseful, and consistently involving, A Separation captures the messiness of a dissolving relationship with keen insight and searing intensity.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/09/11160942_mob.jpg'),(3898,'Shaolin Soccer',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shaolin_soccer/','16989','0286112',1,NULL,'The plot is utterly ridiculous, and the soccer in the movie is unlike any ever played anywhere on Earth, but watching Shaolin Soccer, you will probably find it impossible to care.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/28/57/285719_mob.jpg'),(3899,'Suspiria',1977,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1020662-suspiria/','18330','0076786',1,NULL,'The blood pours freely in Argento\'s classic Suspiria, a giallo horror as grandiose and glossy as it is gory.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/93/47/10934783_mob.jpg'),(3900,'Shine a Light',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/shine_a_light/','770671519','0893382',1,NULL,'It may offer little new for fans, but Martin Scorsese\'s document of the Rolling Stones\' electrifying live show should provide satisfaction to audiences.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/84/03/10840343_mob.jpg'),(3901,'13 Assassins',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/13_assassins_2011/','770820112','1436045',1,'Cult director Takeshi Miike (Ichi the Killer, Audition) delivers a bravado period action film set at the end of Japan\'s feudal era in which a group of unemployed samurai are enlisted to bring down a sadistic lord and prevent him from ascending to the throne and plunging the country into a wartorn future. --(c) Magnet Pictures','Takashi Miike\'s electric remake of Eiichi Kudo\'s 1963 period action film is a wild spectacle executed with killer, dizzying panache.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/15/67/11156764_mob.jpg'),(3902,'The Spy Who Loved Me',1977,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spy_who_loved_me/','10855','0076752',1,NULL,'Though it hints at the absurdity to come in later installments, The Spy Who Loved Me\'s sleek style, menacing villains, and sly wit make it the best of the Roger Moore era.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/65/10886552_mob.jpg'),(3903,'On Her Majesty\'s Secret Service',1969,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/on_her_majestys_secret_service/','10837','0064757',1,NULL,'George Lazenby\'s only appearance as 007 is a fine