om/movie/26/82/268215_mob.jpg'),(4926,'In the Mix',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/in_the_mix/','9362','0426615',1,NULL,'Fans may get a kick out of seeing Usher showcasing his charm on screen, but the movie itself is tone deaf and inconsequential, even by rom-com standards.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/25/06/250602_mob.jpg'),(4927,'Metropolis',1927,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1013775-metropolis/','18225','0017136',1,NULL,'A visually awe-inspiring science fiction classic from the silent era.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/93/38/10933866_mob.jpg'),(4928,'The Man',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the-man/','6931','0399327',1,NULL,'Despite the steely presence of Samuel L. Jackson and the comic timing of Eugene Levy, The Man\'s plot is pointless and its jokes rehashed, as it ends up playing out like the Odd Couple with gas.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/01/250105_mob.jpg'),(4929,'Man on a Ledge',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/man_on_a_ledge/','771241229','1568338',1,'An ex-cop and now wanted fugitive (Sam Worthington) stands on the ledge of a high-rise building while a hard-living New York Police Department negotiator (Elizabeth Banks)tries to talk him down. The longer they are on the ledge, the more she realizes that he might have an ulterior objective. -- (C) Summit Entertainment','Uninspired acting and preposterous plotlines defuse Man on a Ledge\'s mildly intriguing premise.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/05/11160586_mob.jpg'),(4930,'MirrorMask',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mirrormask/','8272','0366780',1,NULL,'While visually dazzling, there isn\'t enough story to hang all the fancy effects on.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/02/250291_mob.jpg'),(4931,'Mongol',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mongol/','770677229','0416044',1,NULL,'The sweeping Mongol mixes romance, family drama, and enough flesh-ripping battle scenes to make sense of Ghenghis Khan\'s legendary stature.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/86/89/10868965_mob.jpg'),(4932,'Mystery Men',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mystery_men/','10623','0132347',1,NULL,'Absurd characters and quirky gags are brought to life by a talented cast, providing this superhero spoof with lots of laughs.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/66/256628_mob.jpg'),(4933,'Monsters',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/monsters-2010/','771039394',NULL,1,'Six years ago NASA discovered the possibility of alien life within our solar system. A probe was launched to collect samples, but crashed upon re-entry over Central America. Soon after, new life forms began to appear and grow. In an effort to stem the destruction that resulted, half of Mexico was quarantined as an INFECTED ZONE. Today, the American and Mexican military still struggle to contain the massive creatures... Our story begins when a jaded US journalist (McNairy) begrudgingly agrees to find his boss\' daughter, a shaken American tourist (Able) and escort her through the infected zone to the safety of the US border. -- (C) Magnolia','It doesn\'t quite live up to its intriguing premise, but Monsters is a surprising blend of alien-invasion tropes, political themes, and relationship drama.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/15/11151578_mob.jpg'),(4934,'Marley',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/marley/','771269025','1183919',1,'Bob Marley\'s universal appeal, impact on music history and role as a social and political prophet is both unique and unparalleled. Marley is the definitive life story of the musician, revolutionary, and legend, from his early days to his rise to international superstardom. Made with the support of the Marley family, the film features rare footage, incredible performances and revelatory interviews with the people that knew him best. -- (C) Official Site','Kevin Macdonald\'s exhaustive, evenhanded portrait of Bob Marley offers electrifying concert footage and fascinating insights into reggae\'s greatest star.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/37/11163748_mob.jpg'),(4935,'Maverick',1994,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/maverick/','10520','0110478',1,NULL,'It isn\'t terribly deep, but it\'s witty and undeniably charming, and the cast is obviously having fun.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/61/256125_mob.jpg'),(4936,'The Matador',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10004925-matador/','24471','0365485',1,NULL,'This humorously amoral, oddball comic thriller features strong performances by Pierce Brosnan and Greg Kinnear as a flamboyant, aging hit-man and an out of work suburban businessman, respectively.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/90/01/10900185_mob.jpg'),(4937,'Heavy Metal',1981,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1068461-heavy_metal/','13299','0082509',1,NULL,'It\'s sexist, juvenile, and dated, but Heavy Metal makes up for its flaws with eye-popping animation and a classic, smartly used soundtrack.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/26/90/269098_mob.jpg'),(4938,'It\'s a Mad, Mad, Mad, Mad World',1963,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/its_a_mad_mad_mad_mad_world/','9830','0057193',1,NULL,'It\'s long, frantic, and stuffed to the gills with comic actors and set pieces -- and that\'s exactly its charm.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/83/10888317_mob.jpg'),(4939,'Martha Marcy May Marlene',2011,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/martha_marcy_may_marlene/','771224182','1441326',1,'Martha Marcy May Marlene is a powerful psychological thriller starring Elizabeth Olsen as Martha, a young woman rapidly unraveling amidst her attempt to reclaim a normal life after fleeing from a cult and its charismatic leader (John Hawkes). Seeking help from her estranged older sister Lucy (Sarah Paulson) and brother-in-law (Hugh Dancy), Martha is unable and unwilling to reveal the truth about her disappearance. When her memories trigger a chilling paranoia that her former cult could still be pursuing her, the line between Martha\'s reality and delusion begins to blur. -- (C) Fox Searchlight','Led by a mesmerizing debut performance from Elizabeth Olsen, Martha Marcy May Marlene is a distinctive, haunting psychological drama.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/16/02/11160215_mob.jpg'),(4940,'The Haunted Mansion',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/haunted_mansion/','11049','0338094',1,NULL,'Neither scary nor funny, The Haunted Mansion is as lifeless as the ghosts in the movie.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/87/258797_mob.jpg'),(4941,'Men of Honor',2000,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/men_of_honor/','13485','0203019',1,NULL,'De Niro and Goodings Jr. manage to turn in performances that make this by-the-numbers inspirational movie watchable.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/50/11165034_mob.jpg'),(4942,'Les Miserables',1998,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1083326-les_miserables/','10311','0119683',1,NULL,'This intelligent, handsomely crafted adaptation of Victor Hugo\'s classic novel condenses the story\'s developments without blunting its emotional impact.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/79/11167962_mob.jpg'),(4943,'Matilda',1996,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1072107-matilda/','12582','0117008',1,NULL,'Danny DeVito-directed version of Matilda is odd, charming, and while the movie diverges from Roald Dahl, it nonetheless captures the book\'s spirit.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/88/58/10885848_mob.jpg'),(4944,'M',1931,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1012928-m/','17470','0022100',1,NULL,'A landmark psychological thriller with arresting images, deep thoughts on modern society, and Peter Lorre in his finest performance.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/85/69/10856942_mob.jpg'),(4945,'The Wicker Man',1974,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1023637-wicker_man/','13290','0070917',1,NULL,'This intelligent horror film is subtle in its thrills and chills, with an ending that is both shocking and truly memorable.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/26/90/269021_mob.jpg'),(4946,'Middle Men',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/middle_men/','770809186','1251757',1,'Luke Wilson, Giovanni Ribisi, and Gabriel Macht headline director/co-screenwriter George Gallo\'s fact-based period comedy detailing the rise of the internet porn business in the mid-\'90s. Businessman Jack Harris (Wilson) made his living solving other people\'s problems. Wayne Beering (Ribisi) and Buck Dolby (Macht) were two technological innovators with a plan to make a mint by selling pornography online. When Jack met Wayne and Buck, it was a match made in money heaven. Before long the trio was making 200,000 dollars a day, but it wouldn\'t last. When a young porn star begins muscling Jack from one side and the FBI starts asking questions on the other, the foolproof plan to get wealthy beyond his wildest dreams becomes an inescapable trap that threatens to break up his family and destroy his livelihood. Kelsey Grammer, Kevin Pollack, Terry Crews, and Christopher McDonald co-star. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','Middle Men benefits from a solid cast, particularly Luke Wilson, but its muddled script lets them down.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/14/22/11142215_mob.jpg'),(4947,'The Majestic',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/majestic/','10998','0268995',1,NULL,'Ponderous and overlong, The Majestic drowns in forced sentimentality and resembles a mish-mash of other, better films.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/25/85/258513_mob.jpg'),(4948,'Harold and Maude',1971,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/harold_and_maude/','10059','0067185',1,NULL,'Hal Ashby\'s comedy is too dark and twisted for some, and occasionally oversteps its bounds, but there\'s no denying the film\'s warm humor and big heart.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/25/38/253827_mob.jpg'),(4949,'The Missing',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1127407-missing/','14330','0338188',1,NULL,'An expertly acted and directed Western. But like other Ron Howard features, the movie is hardly subtle.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/12/76/11127650_mob.jpg'),(4950,'The Messenger',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/10011016-messenger/','770780130','0790712',1,NULL,'A dark but timely subject is handled deftly by writer/directer Owen Moverman and superbly acted by Woody Harrleson and Ben Foster.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/96/11159683_mob.jpg'),(4951,'Manhattan',1979,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/manhattan/','13058','0079522',1,NULL,'One of Woody Allen\'s early classics, Manhattan combines modern, bittersweet humor and timeless romanticism with unerring grace.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/26/79/267901_mob.jpg'),(4952,'All About My Mother',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/all_about_my_mother/','13481','0185125',1,NULL,'Almodovar weaves together a magnificent tapestry of femininity with an affectionate wink to classics of theater and cinema in this poignant story of love, loss and compassion.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/95/09/10950921_mob.jpg'),(4953,'Mary and Max',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1209767-mary_and_max/','770799949','0978762',1,NULL,'Mary and Max is a lovingly crafted, startlingly inventive piece of animation whose technical craft is equaled by its emotional resonance.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/87/57/10875737_mob.jpg'),(4954,'Miracle',2004,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/miracle/','10022','0349825',1,NULL,'Kurt Russell\'s performance guides this cliche-ridden tale into the realm of inspirational, nostalgic goodness.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/25/36/253692_mob.jpg'),(4955,'Mortal Kombat: Annihilation',1997,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mortal_kombat_annihilation/','10903','0119707',1,NULL,'With its shallow characters, low budget special effects, and mindless fight scenes, Mortal Kombat - Annihilation offers minimal plot development and manages to underachieve the low bar set by its predecessor.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/16/86/11168614_mob.jpg'),(4956,'Malibu\'s Most Wanted',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/malibus_most_wanted/','11677','0328099',1,NULL,'There are some laughs, but not enough to sustain the running time.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/79/11167925_mob.jpg'),(4957,'The Muppet Movie',1979,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/muppet_movie/','9731','0079588',1,NULL,'The Muppet Movie, the big-screen debut of Jim Henson\'s plush creations, is smart, lighthearted, and fun for all ages.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/88/15/10881570_mob.jpg'),(4958,'Anatomy of a Murder',1959,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/anatomy-of-a-murder/','17143','0052561',1,NULL,'One of cinema\'s greatest courtroom dramas, Anatomy of a Murder is tense, thought-provoking, and brilliantly acted, with great performances from James Stewart and George C. Scott.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/14/87/11148722_mob.jpg'),(4959,'Man on Wire',2008,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/man_on_wire/','770682536','1155592',1,NULL,'James Marsh\'s doc about artist Phililppe Petit\'s artful caper brings you every ounce of suspense that can be wrung from a man on a (suspended) wire.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/12/53/11125304_mob.jpg'),(4960,'Man of the House',2005,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/man_of_the_house/','136262883','0331933',1,NULL,'A high-concept movie that plays out like a mediocre TV sitcom.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/91/27/10912719_mob.jpg'),(4961,'May',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/may/','13543','0303361',1,NULL,'Above average slasher flick.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/87/03/10870399_mob.jpg'),(4962,'The Man in the Moon',1991,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1037780-man_in_the_moon/','11058','0102388',1,NULL,'It\'s sentimental, and some viewers may feel manipulated by the melodramatic final act, but The Man in the Moon offers a finely drawn coming-of-age story with an excellent cast -- including Reese Witherspoon in her film debut.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/63/65/90/6365909_mob.jpg'),(4963,'Moonstruck',1987,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/moonstruck/','10256','0093565',1,NULL,'Led by energetic performances from Nicolas Cage and Cher, Moonstruck is an exuberantly funny tribute to love and one of the decade\'s most appealing comedies.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/85/77/10857754_mob.jpg'),(4964,'15 Minutes',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/15_minutes/','14582','0179626',1,NULL,'As critical as it is about sensationalism in the media, 15 Minutes itself indulges in lurid violence, and its satire is too heavy-handed to be effective.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/55/34/84/5534846_mob.jpg'),(4965,'Mrs. Miniver',1942,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mrs_miniver/','18387','0035093',1,NULL,'An excessively sentimental piece of propaganda, Mrs. Miniver nonetheless succeeds, due largely to Greer Garson\'s powerful performance.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/81/11168109_mob.jpg'),(4966,'Lost in La Mancha',2002,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lost_in_la_mancha/','13829','0308514',1,NULL,'A remarkable behind-the-scenes look at a movie that wasn\'t, Lost in La Mancha is an incisive, entertaining document of the difficulties inherent in the moviemaking process.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/93/78/10937849_mob.jpg'),(4967,'Moonraker',1979,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1014217-moonraker/','11476','0079574',1,NULL,'Featuring one of the series\' more ludicrous plots but outfitted with primo gadgets and spectacular sets, Moonraker is both silly and entertaining.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/26/08/260897_mob.jpg'),(4968,'The Killer Inside Me',2010,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_killer_inside_me/','770871812','0954947',1,'The second feature-length adaptation of author Jim Thompson\'s acclaimed 1952 crime novel, Michael Winterbottom\'s unflinching, psychosexual post-noir stars Casey Affleck as Deputy Sheriff Lou Ford, a stoic small-town lawman leading a secret life as a serial killer. His West Texas jurisdiction plagued by a series of unsolved murders, Deputy Sheriff Ford does his best to maintain a cool facade while working to deflect the suspicions of the locals. When those suspicions grow too strong to ignore, the psychotic sheriff begins to buckle under the pressure. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi','The Killer Inside Me is stylish and beautifully shot, but Michael Winterbottom\'s distance from his characters robs this often brutally violent film of crucial emotional context.','http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/13/11151359_mob.jpg'),(4969,'A Mighty Wind',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mighty_wind/','10423','0310281',1,NULL,'Though not as uproariously funny as Guest\'s previous movies, A Mighty Wind is also more heartfelt.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/79/11167913_mob.jpg'),(4970,'Monsieur Lazhar',2012,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/monsieur_lazhar_2011/','771253439','2011971',1,'In Montreal, an elementary school teacher dies abruptly. Having learned of the incident in the newspaper, Bachir Lazhar (Mohamed Fellag), a 55-year-old Algerian immigrant, goes to the school to offer his services as a substitute teacher. Quickly hired to replace the deceased, he finds himself in an establishment in crisis, while going through his own personal tragedy. The cultural gap between Bachir and his class is made immediately apparent when he gives them a dictation exercise that is beyond their reach. Little by little, Bachir learns to better know this group of shaken but endearing kids, among whom are Alice and Simon, two charismatic pupils particularly affected by their teacher\'s death. While the class goes through the healing process, nobody in the school is aware of Bachir\'s painful past; nor do they suspect that he is at risk of being deported at any moment. -- (C) Music Box','Monsieur Lahzar is a tender and thoughtful portrait of a man with hidden grief and also a compelling exploration of the teacher-student dynamic.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/35/11163580_mob.jpg'),(4971,'Mother (Madeo)',2009,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/madeo/','770809233','1216496',1,NULL,'As fleshy as it is funny, Bong Joon-Ho\'s Mother straddles family drama, horror and comedy with a deft grasp of tone and plenty of eerie visuals.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/12/76/11127689_mob.jpg'),(4972,'Mystery, Alaska',1999,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mystery_alaska/','12982','0134618',1,NULL,'The lack of hockey action and authenticity left critics cold.','http://content6.flixster.com/movie/26/75/267504_mob.jpg'),(4973,'Major League',1989,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/major_league/','13022','0097815',1,NULL,'Major League may be predictable and formulaic, but buoyed by the script\'s light, silly humor -- not to mention the well-built sports action sequences and funny performances.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/26/77/267709_mob.jpg'),(4974,'My Life Without Me',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/my_life_without_me/','14012',NULL,1,NULL,'Sarah Polley keeps this production afloat with her moving performance.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/89/49/10894989_mob.jpg'),(4975,'Margot at the Wedding',2007,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/margot_at_the_wedding/','770673924','0757361',1,NULL,'Despite a great cast, the characters in Margot at the Wedding are too unlikable to enthrall viewers.','http://content8.flixster.com/movie/93/38/83/9338834_mob.jpg'),(4976,'Metropolis (Metoroporisu)',2001,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1111058-metropolis/','11593','0293416',1,NULL,'Even though the storyline is nothing new, Metropolis is an eye-popping visual treat.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/93/38/10933865_mob.jpg'),(4977,'The Medallion',2003,'http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/medallion/','11888','0288045',1,NULL,'The use of special effects diminishes some of Chan\'s appeal in this disposable picture.','http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/78/11157837_mob.jpg'),(4978,'Mean Machine',2001,'http://www.rottentom